NK021(zha)001:1: // badz+ra s+ya so p+aa nam n+aa mo ma h+aa sa
NK021(zha)001:2: m+aa dza s+au tra s+y+aa b+hi shi ny+tsa bi d+hi
NK021(zha)001:5: / 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dbang gi cho ga rdo rje'i them skas zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK021(zha)001:7: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dbang gi chu bo bzhi
NK021(zha)001:8: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gcig tu dril nas
NK021(zha)001:9: bskur ba'i cho ga bde ba chen po'i khang bzang
NK021(zha)001:10: du 'jug pa'i rdo rje'i them skas zhes bya ba
NK021(zha)001:11: / bla ma dang bcom ldan 'das dpal sgrol byed
NK021(zha)001:12: thugs rje'i rgyal po shin tu rnam par grol ba
NK021(zha)001:14: gang zhig rnam 'gyur kun rtog sder bcas dbyings su grol bas zag med kyi //
NK021(zha)001:15: dpal ldan bde chen nyin mor byed sku ye shes rdo rje 'od po che //
NK021(zha)001:16: phan bde'i snang bas phyogs kyi cha 'gengs mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i dpyid //
NK021(zha)001:17: mchog gsum ngo bo dkyil 'khor kun bdag gter chen bla ma spyi bos mchod //
NK021(zha)001:18: ro gcig dbyings su bden gnyis rtsal las dkyil 'khor rnam gsum rol pa can //
NK021(zha)001:19: sku bzhi'i bdag nyid ye shes lnga dngos kun 'dus drug pa 'khor lo'i mgon //
NK021(zha)001:20: yan lag bdun ldan dbang phyug brgyad dang gar dgu'i nyams 'gyur bye bas 'khyud //
NK021(zha)001:21: stobs bcu'i rtsal mnga' he ru ka dpal 'khor lor bcas la gus phyag 'tshal /
NK021(zha)001:22: 'dus pa mdo yi dbang don nyi zla'i 'od //
NK021(zha)001:23: legs par 'grel ba'i snang ba mtshungs pa med //
NK021(zha)001:24: bsnyengs bral mkha' la brtson pa'i shing rta yis //
NK021(zha)001:25: 'dren bzod slob dpon chen po bde ba gsal //
NK021(zha)001:26: gang gi bka' srol bdud rtsis cher myos pas //
NK021(zha)001:27: legs bshad rgyang glu len mkhas gnubs chen dang //
NK021(zha)001:28: zur chen mes dbon glan sogs gsang ba'i bdag /
NK021(zha)001:29: mi yi zol bzung rnams la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK021(zha)001:30: kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' la ye shes rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:31: rnam rol bde ba chen po'i khang bzang du //
NK021(zha)001:32: skal ldan 'jug pa'i thabs mchog 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK021(zha)001:33: dbang chu rdo rje'i them skas bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:34: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub las bzhir bcas //
NK021(zha)001:35: rim gnyis sngon du song ba'i lag rjes te //
NK021(zha)001:36: de la'ang dbang bskur sngon du 'gro ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:37: rdo rje theg pa'i lam gyi rtsa bar grub //
NK021(zha)001:38: 'on te rgyud dang man ngag so so'i lugs //
NK021(zha)001:39: ma phyed bzhin du gya tshom bkral mthong nas //
NK021(zha)001:40: 'dus gsal rdzogs pa'i ngag gis chu bo bzhi'i //
NK021(zha)001:41: dbang chog chos don gnyer ba'i dpal du sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:42: de la 'dir lus can rnams kyi sems nyid dkyil
NK021(zha)001:43: 'khor rnam gsum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gnas pa
NK021(zha)001:45: de nyid gdod ma nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa yin kyang /
NK021(zha)001:46: sbyang bya'i dri ma glo bur ba ma rig pa'i rkyen las /
NK021(zha)001:47: med snang 'khor ba'i rnam par shar nas /
NK021(zha)001:48: sdug bsngal bzod par dka' bas khor mor mnar ba rnams la brtse ba'i gzhan dbang gis /
NK021(zha)001:49: sbyang 'bras rang gnas rang byung gi ye shes nyid
NK021(zha)001:50: ji lta ba bzhin mngon du gyur pa'i go 'phang
NK021(zha)001:52: sbyong byed rnam par grol ba'i lam gsungs pa thams
NK021(zha)001:53: cad kyi nang nas mchog gam rtse mo ni rdo
NK021(zha)001:55: de nyid kyi lam gyi gzhi dang rtsa bar gyur
NK021(zha)001:56: pa 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dkyil 'khor du smin
NK021(zha)001:57: byed kyi dbang bskur ba'i thabs khyad par can la
NK021(zha)001:58: 'bad pa chen pos bsgrub par bya ba yin no
NK021(zha)001:60: sngon 'gro sgo 'byed kyi dbang bskur ba /
NK021(zha)001:61: dngos gzhi bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang 'brel ba'am /
NK021(zha)001:63: chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur ba //
NK021(zha)001:64: rjes gtad rgya bya zhing mtha' brten du tshe'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:65: de las sngon rjes gnyis la dbye ba gzhan med cing /
NK021(zha)001:66: dngos gzhi la lugs gnyis te /
NK021(zha)001:67: thun mong ba'am thun min gang rung gi rtsa ba'i
NK021(zha)001:68: dkyil 'khor du rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa'i
NK021(zha)001:69: skal ldan khyad par can la /
NK021(zha)001:70: chu bo bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang sum cu rtsa drug bskur ba rgyud kyi lugs dang /
NK021(zha)001:71: yang yo ga man chad yan lag gi dkyil 'khor drug tu phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo /
NK021(zha)001:72: 'dren pa'i las byang che ler bshad pa'i tshogs chen
NK021(zha)001:73: 'dus pa rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor thun mong par nang
NK021(zha)001:75: rtsa rgyud kyi tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub lugs las
NK021(zha)001:76: gsungs pa dur khrod gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor zhes rtsa
NK021(zha)001:77: ba'i dkyil 'khor thun mong ma yin par sgrub dbang
NK021(zha)001:79: byang sems rnam pa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du gsang
NK021(zha)001:80: dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo rnams sbyangs pas snod du
NK021(zha)001:81: gyur pa'i slob ma la theg pa thams cad 'dus
NK021(zha)001:82: pa'i mdo dbang rtsa ba so drug las yan lag
NK021(zha)001:83: rags pa brgyad brgya so gcig tu phye nas bskur
NK021(zha)001:84: ba / bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las tho'i dgongs pa ltar man ngag gi lugs te /
NK021(zha)001:85: de ltar rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gnyis po
NK021(zha)001:86: da lta'i dus su gcig tu dril nas bskur ba
NK021(zha)001:87: bla ma rnams kyi phyag len du snang bas 'dir
NK021(zha)001:88: yang de bzhin du 'bri bar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:89: de la thog mar gleng gzhi dang 'brel ba'i mchog dbang bcu drug gis sgo phye la /
NK021(zha)001:90: de rjes lha mi nas yo ga'i bar yan lag
NK021(zha)001:91: gi dkyil 'khor drug tu man ngag gi lugs kyi
NK021(zha)001:92: phyi dbang / de nas rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor thun
NK021(zha)001:93: mong ba tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor du rgyud
NK021(zha)001:94: lugs kyi chu bo bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa /
NK021(zha)001:95: de rjes yan lag gi dkyil 'khor so sor man
NK021(zha)001:96: ngag gi lugs kyi gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo
NK021(zha)001:97: gnyis dang / skabs su babs na gtad rgya byas rjes /
NK021(zha)001:98: mtha' brten du tshe dbang dang bcas pa bskur bar mdzad do //
NK021(zha)001:99: de ltar na phyi gsang gi dbang gnyis lugs gnyis ka bskur bas zlos shing /
NK021(zha)001:100: nang sgrub gnyis kyi dbang rgyud lugs las ma byung bas chad par ma zad /
NK021(zha)001:101: sgrub dbang gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor kyang chad pas /
NK021(zha)001:102: phyag len 'di la chad pa dang lhag pa gnyis ka'i skyon gnas so snyam na /
NK021(zha)001:104: rgyu mtshan phyi dbang lugs gnyis grangs dang bskur thabs mi 'dra bas so sor bskur dgos shing /
NK021(zha)001:105: nang dbang la lugs gnyis lha dbang gi skabs cung
NK021(zha)001:106: zad tsam las gzhan khyad par med pas gcig gis
NK021(zha)001:107: go chod / tshogs sgrub dus dbang gis mos slob
NK021(zha)001:108: tsam la brten pa shas che bas yan lag gi
NK021(zha)001:109: dkyil 'khor dor nas rgyud lugs nyid gtso bor ston
NK021(zha)001:110: go chod / cing / de'ang rtsa dkyil thun mong bar bskur ba'i lugs mdzad /
NK021(zha)001:111: gsang dbang ni rgyud lugs la zab khyad ma sbyar
NK021(zha)001:112: bas slob ma thun mong ba rnams rjes su 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:113: pa'i phyir mdor bsdus pa tsam gyis sa khongs bzung
NK021(zha)001:114: / de rjes rdzogs rim don du gnyer ba'i slob
NK021(zha)001:115: ma khyad par can yang srid pas de dag rjes
NK021(zha)001:116: su 'dzin pa'i phyir man ngag gi lugs de nyid
NK021(zha)001:117: zur du phye nas bskur ba'i phyag len mdzad la
NK021(zha)001:118: / / rgyu mtshan de dag gis na /
NK021(zha)001:119: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gnyis 'dor len gyi
NK021(zha)001:120: gnad kyis gcig tu dril nas bskur bas gnas skabs
NK021(zha)001:122: brgyud nas lugs gnyis po gcig gis gcig mi nub
NK021(zha)001:123: par chabs gcig tu 'phel ba'i dgongs pa khyad par
NK021(zha)001:125: de ltar na rgyud dang man ngag gis lugs gnyis so so'i khyad par dang /
NK021(zha)001:126: de gnyis gcig tu dril nas bskur ba'i gnad 'di /
NK021(zha)001:127: kho bo'i yongs 'dzin bla ma dam pa sogs skyes mchog khyad par can 'ga' zhig las /
NK021(zha)001:128: phyi rabs kyi sngags pa phal gyis rtogs par ma gyur pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:129: thob yig dang las tho zin byang sogs so so'i lag rjes kyis gsal por bstan pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:130: da phyin chad yi ge 'di'i mthu las kun gyis rtogs par gyur cig ces smon pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:131: yang lugs gnyis gcig tu dril nas bskur ba gzhir bzhag la'ang /
NK021(zha)001:132: lag len rgyas bsdus kyi sgo zur tsam zhig bstan na /
NK021(zha)001:133: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang ma 'brel ba'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:134: rkyang tsam gyi lugs rab gnas sngon song gi ras
NK021(zha)001:135: bris steng nas bskur ba la /
NK021(zha)001:136: dbang chog gi ras bris steng nas bskur ba la /
NK021(zha)001:137: dbang chog gi yi ge 'di nyid kyi steng du /
NK021(zha)001:138: yan lag gi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi sgrub dkyil dngos grub 'dod 'jo /
NK021(zha)001:139: yan lag can rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs dang /
NK021(zha)001:141: dri med 'od phreng ste yig sna bzhi po 'dis chog cing /
NK021(zha)001:142: rgyas pa bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang 'brel ba'i lugs la /
NK021(zha)001:143: yig sna bzhi po 'di'i steng du spyi'i khog dbub sgrub khog gi chings dang /
NK021(zha)001:144: de'ang ras bris gsar pa'am rdul tshon gyi phyogs la rab gnas bsnan pa la sogs te /
NK021(zha)001:145: rab gnas sbyin sreg sogs 'bri 'gyur gyi zur 'debs gzhan rnams kyang tshang bar dgos pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:146: yang yig sna bzhi po la brten pa shin tu bsdus pa'i phyogs la'ang /
NK021(zha)001:147: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi bum pa dang slob ma sta gon ni nges par bya dgos shing /
NK021(zha)001:148: lha sta gon yang rdul tshon gyi phyogs la nges par mdzad cing /
NK021(zha)001:149: ras bris la rgya gzhung rnams su byed dgos pa'i gsal kha ma byung bas /
NK021(zha)001:150: ma 'grub na'ang chad pa'i skyon med mod /
NK021(zha)001:151: 'grub na phun sum tshogs pa'i yan lag yin pas ci 'grub bya ste /
NK021(zha)001:152: snyan gsan dbab pa ni dkyil 'khor bri ba kho nar ma zad /
NK021(zha)001:153: bsgrub pa'i phyir yang yin pas so //
NK021(zha)001:154: de ltar yang gang gi ched du snyan gsan 'bebs pa'i sbyor ba'i tshig /
NK021(zha)001:155: khyed rnams mos shing mchod pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:156: zhes sogs kyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mchod pa
NK021(zha)001:157: la sogs pa'i ched du dkyil 'khor gyi las rnams
NK021(zha)001:158: rdzogs par bya ba'i zhu ba yin gyi /
NK021(zha)001:159: bri ba kho na'i ched du ma yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK021(zha)001:160: bka' drin rang gi ngo bo zhu ba'i tshig /
NK021(zha)001:161: thugs rjes nye bar dgongs mdzad de //
NK021(zha)001:162: zhes sogs kyis kyang dkyil 'khor byin gyis brlab pa'i
NK021(zha)001:163: sgo nas sa gzhi bzung bar mdzod ces gsol ba
NK021(zha)001:165: yang kho bos dngos grub 'dod 'jor glan chen po
NK021(zha)001:166: rdo rje 'od dang 'gos kyi phyag bzhes ltar yan
NK021(zha)001:167: lag gi dkyil 'khor kri yog gnyis la'ang slob ma
NK021(zha)001:168: sta gon bris pa yin la /
NK021(zha)001:169: de lta na'ang zur ham gyi phyag srol ltar ding
NK021(zha)001:170: sang rdul tshon dang ras bris gang la'ang mi mdzad
NK021(zha)001:172: lag len bsdus pa'i tshe ma 'grub kyang skyon med dam snyam zhing /
NK021(zha)001:173: sa chog ni dkyil 'khor khang pa rnying par rdul
NK021(zha)001:174: tshon la brten pa'i phyogs la'ang ma byas pas chog
NK021(zha)001:175: / gnas khang gsar pa yin na ras bris la'ang byas na legs te /
NK021(zha)001:176: sa chog ni sa gzhi la dkyil 'khor bri ba kho na'i ched ma yin gyi /
NK021(zha)001:177: phyi nang gi bdud dang bar chad gzhom pa'i ched yin pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:178: des na phyis kyi sngags pa phal cher /
NK021(zha)001:179: ras bris kyi phyogs la sa chog mtha' gcig tu
NK021(zha)001:180: mi dgos par 'dod pa la snying po med cing
NK021(zha)001:181: / yang ras bris kyi tshe lha sta gon la /
NK021(zha)001:183: rin po che'i man+dala lta bur lha grangs kyi tshom
NK021(zha)001:184: bu bkod pa dkyil 'khor gang du dgram pa'i gzhir
NK021(zha)001:186: kha cig de mi rigs zhes nan gyis dgag pa'ang /
NK021(zha)001:187: gzhi de nyid la bri ba'i ched kho nar sta gon byas par bsam pa las /
NK021(zha)001:188: don gyi gnad 'di ma rtogs pas nongs pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:189: dkyil chog khungs ma 'ga' zhig tu gzhi'i steng gi
NK021(zha)001:190: nam mkhar lha spyan drangs pa la mchod bstod dang
NK021(zha)001:191: snyan gsan 'bebs par bshad pa'ang yod pa'i phyir na
NK021(zha)001:192: dgram pa'i gzhi'i steng du man+dala la tshom bu byas
NK021(zha)001:195: rgyud dang man ngag gcig dril gyi //
NK021(zha)001:196: dbang chog go don rgyas bsdus gnas /
NK021(zha)001:197: bde blag rtogs byed chos kyi chings //
NK021(zha)001:198: thos chung gsar bu'i dapala du sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:199: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang chog rdo rje them skas las /
NK021(zha)001:200: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gcig tu dril ba'i
NK021(zha)001:201: go don dang lag len gyi gnad bshad pa'i skabs
NK021(zha)001:205: dmigs med thugs rjes 'dren mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:206: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa la //
NK021(zha)001:207: phyag byas sgo 'byed dbang chog bshad //
NK021(zha)001:208: 'dir phyag na rdo rje ngan song gnas 'dren gyi
NK021(zha)001:209: dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa sgrub
NK021(zha)001:211: slob dpon rang nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dbang len pa'am /
NK021(zha)001:212: bsdus pa la dga' na rig pa'i me tog dor
NK021(zha)001:213: ba tsam gyis dkyil 'khor du zhugs te lha dang
NK021(zha)001:214: skal pa mnyam par byas la /
NK021(zha)001:215: de dang slob bu rnams gzhug cing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:216: thog mar khrus bya zhing bgegs skrod pa dkyil 'khor khang par 'jug pa'i snga rol tu bya ba'am /
NK021(zha)001:217: zor yang ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK021(zha)001:218: phyag byas te gral du 'khod nas kyang rung ste /
NK021(zha)001:220: de nas bgegs gtor la dri chab dang las bum
NK021(zha)001:221: gyi chu 'thor zhing big+h+n+aam dang a mri tas bsang
NK021(zha)001:223: stong pa'i ngang la b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i snod
NK021(zha)001:224: du yig zhu ba las byung ba'i gtor ma 'dod
NK021(zha)001:225: pa'i yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sprin 'phro
NK021(zha)001:226: bar bsam la / +aahmh'u lan gsum gyis brlab /
NK021(zha)001:227: sarba big+h+n+aam na mahsarba nas kham grih+ne dam ba ling+ta
NK021(zha)001:228: s+w+aa h+aa gsum gyis gtor ma bskor zhing bsngosa la
NK021(zha)001:229: / h+aum mdzad kyi phyag rgya bcings te /
NK021(zha)001:231: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:232: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:233: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:234: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bden pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:235: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:236: sprul pa yang sprul phyag brnyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:237: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:238: deng 'dir rdo rje'i slob ma 'di rnams dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:239: du 'jug cing dbang bskur ba nod pa la bar
NK021(zha)001:240: du gcod pa'i gdon bgegs thams cad gtor ma byin
NK021(zha)001:242: dpag tshad dang rgyang grags su ma gnas par song zhig /
NK021(zha)001:243: ces gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK021(zha)001:245: rol mo'i sgra drag tu bya zhing /
NK021(zha)001:246: sum+b+ha la sogs pa'i drags sngags bzlas pas bgegs rnams bskrad /
NK021(zha)001:247: badz+ra pany+tsa ra dz+wa la ram /
NK021(zha)001:248: zhes brjod pas rdo rje srung ba'i gur khang ye
NK021(zha)001:249: shes kyi me 'bar bar phyogs kun gtams te cis
NK021(zha)001:250: kyang mi shigs par bsam mo //
NK021(zha)001:251: de nas blo bcos shing spro ba bskyed pa'i ched
NK021(zha)001:252: du zab mo'i chos dang gleng gzhi bshad par bya
NK021(zha)001:253: ste / nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can
NK021(zha)001:254: thams cad kyi don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi
NK021(zha)001:256: de'i ched du 'dus pa chen po mdo yongs su
NK021(zha)001:257: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor du rim gyis zhugs te smin
NK021(zha)001:258: grol gyi lam zab cing rgya che ba mnyan nas
NK021(zha)001:259: nyams su blang bar bagyi'o snyam pa rnyog pa dang
NK021(zha)001:260: bral ba'i byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang
NK021(zha)001:261: / chos gsan pa'i kun tu spyod pa yang skyes rabs las /
NK021(zha)001:262: rab tu dma' ba'i stan la 'dug /
NK021(zha)001:263: dul ba'i dpal ni rnam par bskyed //
NK021(zha)001:264: dga' dang 'dun pa'i mig gis blta //
NK021(zha)001:265: tshig gi bdud rtsi 'thung ba bzhin //
NK021(zha)001:268: rtog pa thams cad legs par bsdus nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:269: shin tu bsam pa bzang po ldan pas nyon //
NK021(zha)001:270: brjed ngas blo la rdo rje sems dpa' sogs //
NK021(zha)001:271: bde bar gshegs pa rnams kyis byin mi rlob //
NK021(zha)001:272: ces pas snod kyi skyon rnams spangs la sgo gsum legs par bsdams te gsan 'tshal /
NK021(zha)001:273: de yang slob dpon chen po pad+ma'i zhal nas /
NK021(zha)001:274: yang yang rnyed dka' u dum wa ra 'dra //
NK021(zha)001:275: rnyed pa don can yid bzhin nor bu 'du //
NK021(zha)001:277: 'o skol rnams kyis da res stes dbang gis rnyed
NK021(zha)001:278: pa'i mi lus rin po che 'di ni yang yang
NK021(zha)001:279: rnyed dka' ba u dum wa ra'i me tog dang
NK021(zha)001:280: 'dra / skyon mtha' dag spong ba dang yon tan
NK021(zha)001:281: mtha' dag sgrub tu rung ba'i rten yin pas rnyed
NK021(zha)001:282: na don che ba yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin
NK021(zha)001:284: skyon yon gyi cha rnams 'dor len nus pa'i rten
NK021(zha)001:285: 'di las gzhan lha klu gnod sbyin sogs gang la'ang
NK021(zha)001:286: med pas rnyed pa'i mchog rab tu rnyed pa yin
NK021(zha)001:287: pa'i phyir / de ltar yang tsan+d+ra go mis /
NK021(zha)001:288: gang zhig thob na skye ba'i rgya mtsho mthar byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:289: byang chub mchog gi sa bon dge ba'ang 'debs byed la //
NK021(zha)001:290: yid bzhin nor bu bas kyang yon tan ches lhag pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:291: mi nyid de ni su zhig 'bras bu med par byed //
NK021(zha)001:292: kun mkhyen lam brten 'gro ba 'dren par chas gyur cing //
NK021(zha)001:293: sems kyi stobs chen mi yis rnyed pa gang yin pa //
NK021(zha)001:294: lam de lha dang klu yis mi rnyed lha min dang //
NK021(zha)001:295: mkha' lding rig 'dzin mi 'am ci dang lto 'phyes min //
NK021(zha)001:296: zhes gsungs pas gru yod dus chu bo las brgal
NK021(zha)001:297: dgos pa bzhin du thar lam sgrub pa'i mthun rkyen
NK021(zha)001:298: thams cad tshang ba'i rten phun sum tshogs pa thob
NK021(zha)001:299: pa'i dus 'dir 'khor ba las nges par thar pa'i
NK021(zha)001:300: bya ba don yod pa la 'bad dgos te /
NK021(zha)001:302: da res phun tshogs rkyen kun 'byor skabs 'dir //
NK021(zha)001:303: brtson 'grus drag pos srid las 'da' bar mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:305: de ltar rten bzang po 'di thob tu zin na'ang mi rtag ste /
NK021(zha)001:307: de ring kho na mi 'chi zhes //
NK021(zha)001:308: bde bar 'dug pa rigs ma yin //
NK021(zha)001:309: bdag ni med par 'gyur pa'i dus //
NK021(zha)001:310: de ni gdon mi za bar 'byung //
NK021(zha)001:312: rang cag rnams kyi lus 'di chu bur dang 'dra ste /
NK021(zha)001:313: mi brtan pas myur du 'jig tshe srog 'di bar
NK021(zha)001:314: snang gi glog 'gyu ba dang 'dra ste nam 'chi
NK021(zha)001:315: cha med / gza' gdong thug lta bus glo bur du shi pa mang po zhig mthong bas /
NK021(zha)001:316: de ring tsam yang mi 'chi snyam pa'i blo gdengs mi thub /
NK021(zha)001:317: des na don chen sgrub pa'i bya ba phyi bshol
NK021(zha)001:318: du mi 'jog par da lta nyid rang nas dam
NK021(zha)001:319: pa'i chos la brtson 'grus dang brtul ba brtan pos
NK021(zha)001:322: 'di ni sang bya 'di ni thang gcig 'og tu bya //
NK021(zha)001:323: 'di ni de ring bya zhes skye bos sems byed na //
NK021(zha)001:324: gshin rje be con lag thogs zur gyis blta ba yis //
NK021(zha)001:325: mig rtsa dmar khros ma rangs gad mo re snyam 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:327: de ltar rnyed dka' 'jig sla'i rten thob dus gtan bde'i 'dun ma dam pa'i chos ma bsgrub na /
NK021(zha)001:328: tshe 'di ltos kyi bya ba dpal 'byor longs spyod
NK021(zha)001:329: snyan grags sogs 'bad pas bsgrub kyang snying po med
NK021(zha)001:330: de / 'phral bde bde ltar snang ba 'di kun
NK021(zha)001:331: kyang gnyid thums re'i rmi lam bzang ba dang 'dra
NK021(zha)001:333: tshe 'di'i bde skyid ji ltar che yang 'chi ba'i
NK021(zha)001:334: tshe rang gi rjes su mi 'brang bas phan pa
NK021(zha)001:337: longs spyod skad cig kho nas 'bral ba'i gnyen //
NK021(zha)001:338: 'byor pa rmi lam bag ma len dang mtshungs //
NK021(zha)001:339: bde ba'i dpal ni rlung bsnun mar me'i rtse //
NK021(zha)001:340: srid pa'i spyod tshul 'di dag smyon pa'i gar //
NK021(zha)001:342: 'on kyang tshe 'di'i bde skyid kyi ched du bsags
NK021(zha)001:343: pa'i las dge sdig ni nam yang chud mi za
NK021(zha)001:344: bar lus dang grib ma ltar shi nas kyang rjes
NK021(zha)001:346: gal te rang gis sdig pa byas zin pa ni mi 'dod kyang bskyur dbang med /
NK021(zha)001:347: dge ba rang gis ma byas par khyer rgyu ni med /
NK021(zha)001:348: las kyi dbang gis 'khor ba 'di mtho dman gang du skyes kyang /
NK021(zha)001:350: mi gtsang 'dam na dri zhim med bzhin 'gro lnga dag na bde ba med //
NK021(zha)001:351: ces gsungs pa ltar sdug bsngal gyi yo lang las ma 'das pas /
NK021(zha)001:352: zug gzer rgyun mi chad pa'i nad pa dang 'dra ste /
NK021(zha)001:354: de'i nang nas kyang ngan song gsum du skyes na ci tsug byed /
NK021(zha)001:355: mi skye ba'i gdengs ni med /
NK021(zha)001:356: des na las ci la thug kyang dge sdig la blang dor ma nor bar bya dgos te /
NK021(zha)001:358: tshe rabs mang por sdug bsngal rgyur 'gyur ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:359: sdig pas tshe 'dir bde bas ci zhig bya //
NK021(zha)001:360: tshe 'di yun thung lo zla 'ga' zhig yin //
NK021(zha)001:361: 'jig rten phyi mar tshad bzung med pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:362: skye ba gzhan du sdug bsngal mi 'byung zhing //
NK021(zha)001:363: bde ba'i thabs su dge sdig blang dor bya //
NK021(zha)001:365: de ltar na las rgyu 'bras bslu med du yid ches bskyed /
NK021(zha)001:366: des kun nas bslangs te srog la babs kyang dge
NK021(zha)001:367: sdig la blang dor ma nor bar byed pa'i zhe
NK021(zha)001:369: snying po med pas mngon mtho'i go 'phang la mi
NK021(zha)001:370: dam 'cha' / smon zhing / 'khor ba mtha' dag
NK021(zha)001:371: sdug bsngal gyi phung po chen por nges pa gting
NK021(zha)001:372: dam 'cha' / smon zhing / tshugs pas / nag
NK021(zha)001:373: can btson dong nas 'bros pa lta bu'i 'du shes
NK021(zha)001:374: dam 'cha' / smon zhing / tshugs pas / kyis
NK021(zha)001:375: / da res 'khor ba las nges pas thar pa
NK021(zha)001:376: zhig bya snyam du nges 'byung gi bsam pa brtan
NK021(zha)001:377: dam 'cha' / smon zhing / tshugs pas / kyis
NK021(zha)001:378: / po bskyed 'tshal / de yang rang gcig pu
NK021(zha)001:379: 'khor ba las thar 'dod kyi blo tsam gyis ni
NK021(zha)001:382: nye du 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho'i khong du chud gyur pa //
NK021(zha)001:383: klong gi nang du lhung ba lta bu mthong bzhin du //
NK021(zha)001:384: skye shi 'phos pas ngo ma shes pa de bor nas //
NK021(zha)001:385: gal te bdag thar byed na de las khrel bor med //
NK021(zha)001:387: tshe 'phos pas ngo ma shes pa ma gtogs /
NK021(zha)001:388: rang cag sems can thams cad phan tshun ma bu
NK021(zha)001:389: khyo shugs sogs lan grangs dpag tu med pa byas
NK021(zha)001:390: nas / phan btags pa la tshad med pas drin can sha stag yin pa la /
NK021(zha)001:391: 'di thams cad sdug bsngal gyi khur chen pos ni non /
NK021(zha)001:392: bde ba'i thabs ni mi shes /
NK021(zha)001:393: bde ba 'dod kyang sdug bsngal gyi rgyu kho na bsgrub pas /
NK021(zha)001:394: zhe 'dod dang lag len phyin ci log tu gyur
NK021(zha)001:395: pa'i smyon pa lta bu 'di rnams yal bar bor
NK021(zha)001:396: nas / rang nyid gcig pu zhi bder gzhol 'dod
NK021(zha)001:397: kyi blo ni shin tu tha chad pa yin pas
NK021(zha)001:399: don dam par sems can thams cad ye nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas /
NK021(zha)001:400: 'khor ba med snang sgyu ma lta bu'i chos yin kyang /
NK021(zha)001:401: de ltar ma rtogs pas rmi lam gyi rgyu 'bras ltar /
NK021(zha)001:402: gting mtha' med pa'i 'khor ba'i rgya mtshor ni lhungs /
NK021(zha)001:403: 'jigs su rung ba'i sdug bsngal gyi rba klong drag pos ni g.yengs te /
NK021(zha)001:404: shin tu nyams thag par gyur pa'i mkha' khyab kyi sems can la /
NK021(zha)001:405: bcos min gyi snying rjes kun nas bslangs te /
NK021(zha)001:406: nyan rang gi byang chub don gnyer gyi blo spangs nas /
NK021(zha)001:407: theg pa chen po'i blo mchog rang gzhan gyi don
NK021(zha)001:408: gnyis phun sum tshogs pa sgrub pa la rtse gcig
NK021(zha)001:411: 'jig rten don sgrub tshul la mthu med pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:412: theg pa gnyis po gtan du spang bya zhing //
NK021(zha)001:413: thub rgyal rgya che snying po'i theg pa la //
NK021(zha)001:414: gzhan phan ro gcig rang bzhin de la 'jug /
NK021(zha)001:416: theg pa chen po de la'ang /
NK021(zha)001:417: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis su yod pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:418: 'dir rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa las /
NK021(zha)001:421: thabs la mkhas pa'i khyad par gyis mchog tu gyur
NK021(zha)001:422: pa gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa bla na med
NK021(zha)001:424: zhugs nas lam gyi gzhi mngon par dbang bskur ba
NK021(zha)001:425: zab mo mnyan du yod pa 'di ni rnyed pa'i
NK021(zha)001:426: mchog rab tu brnyed pa yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:427: dga' zhing spro ba'i blo gzengs bstod par mdzad 'tshal /
NK021(zha)001:428: de yang khyad par can gyi dbang zab mo 'di ni 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan pa yin te /
NK021(zha)001:432: phyag bzhes byin rlabs dang 'brel ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:433: de la rgyud dbang dang 'brel te /
NK021(zha)001:434: rtsa ba'i rgyud kun 'dus rig pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:435: bshad rgyud dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo /
NK021(zha)001:436: ye shes rngam pa glog gi 'khor lo //
NK021(zha)001:437: he ru ka 'dus pa la sogs pa /
NK021(zha)001:438: rgyab brten gyi rgyud rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan+t+ra /
NK021(zha)001:439: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud rnams dang 'brel lo //
NK021(zha)001:441: gnubs chen gyis gtad rgya'i rtsa bar /
NK021(zha)001:442: dang po gab pa'i dbang le drug /
NK021(zha)001:443: spyi dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi dang //
NK021(zha)001:444: 'dren pa'i las byang che le dang //
NK021(zha)001:445: 'dren pa'i las byang chung le dang /
NK021(zha)001:446: yongs su grub pa'i dbang le dang //
NK021(zha)001:447: lta ba ye 'byams dbang le dang //
NK021(zha)001:448: kun bzang thugs kyi gdams le ste //
NK021(zha)001:449: rnam pa drug tu lung nyer bsdus //
NK021(zha)001:450: bar du dgos pa'i sgrub thabs drug /
NK021(zha)001:451: dbang don bsdus dang dbang don 'byed //
NK021(zha)001:452: dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:453: las tho rab gnas bshad pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:454: na rag dong sprugs bshad pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:455: drug gis sgrub pa'i don rnams bshad //
NK021(zha)001:456: tha mar dgos pa'i cha rkyen drug /
NK021(zha)001:457: sbyin sreg lhag chog dkyil 'khor thig /
NK021(zha)001:458: phyi nang gnyis kyi tsa ka li //
NK021(zha)001:459: rgyud khungs gtad rgya'i gleng gzhi drug /
NK021(zha)001:460: drug gsum bco brgyad yi ge 'di //
NK021(zha)001:461: sangs rgyas ye shes bdag gis rnyed //
NK021(zha)001:462: snod ldan rnams dang 'phrad par shog /
NK021(zha)001:463: ces gsungs pa ltar drug gsum bco brgyad man ngag dang 'brel lo //
NK021(zha)001:464: gdams ngag phyag bzhes dang 'brel te //
NK021(zha)001:465: bla ma gong ma tshad ma'i skyes bu dbang du
NK021(zha)001:466: gyur pa rnams kyi las tho khyad par can rnams
NK021(zha)001:467: las gzhan du ma bcos ma bslad pa'i rnam dag
NK021(zha)001:468: legs pa'i phyag len gyi srol bzang po dang 'brel
NK021(zha)001:469: lo // phyag bzhes byin rlabs dang 'brel te //
NK021(zha)001:470: brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad grub brnyes rig pa
NK021(zha)001:471: 'dzin pa'i skyes chen sha stag bzang za ra tshags
NK021(zha)001:472: su byin pas byin rlabs kyi bka' babs 'gran zla
NK021(zha)001:473: med pa dang 'brel ba yin no //
NK021(zha)001:474: de ltar 'brel ba bzhi dang ldan pa'i dbang 'di
NK021(zha)001:475: nyid yul phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan dgos
NK021(zha)001:476: te / de la gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:477: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i gnas khang //
NK021(zha)001:478: ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK021(zha)001:479: thar pa chen po'i grong mchog /
NK021(zha)001:481: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gnas chen po lags pas tha mal gyi khang pa'i 'du shes spangs te /
NK021(zha)001:482: ye shes rang snang gi pho brang du blta ba gal che /
NK021(zha)001:483: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:484: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i rdo rje slob dpon te /
NK021(zha)001:485: de la dge ba'i bshes gnyen phal par blta ba'i 'du shes spangs nas /
NK021(zha)001:486: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun 'dus kyi ngo bor shes pa /
NK021(zha)001:487: rang rgyud la sangs rgyas kyi phrin las sbyin pa'i bka' drin dran pa /
NK021(zha)001:488: gdung shugs drag pos tha mal gyi snang ba 'gog nus pa /
NK021(zha)001:489: yang yang ma brjed par dran pas rig pa bsgyur thub pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:490: khyad par bzhi dang ldan pa'i mos gus yod na /
NK021(zha)001:492: ye shes skad cig la phebs /
NK021(zha)001:493: mchog dang thun mong gi 'dod don dka' ba med par 'grub par 'gyur ba yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:496: snod kyi skyon gsum dang bral ba //
NK021(zha)001:498: dad brtson shes rab dang ldan pa'i slob ma zhig dgos na /
NK021(zha)001:499: mtshan nyid dang ldan par lags pas /
NK021(zha)001:500: 'dir tshogs kyi mched lcam thams cad phan tshun mig
NK021(zha)001:501: gi 'bras bu ltar gces pa'i brtse gdungs rgyun mi
NK021(zha)001:502: chad cing / thams cad dag pa'i snang ba lha dang lha mo'i rol par blta 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:503: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:504: sgrub mchod dang dbang gi rdzas sogs gang dgos thams
NK021(zha)001:505: cad mngon du tshogs pa'i yo byad kyi rnam pa
NK021(zha)001:506: khyad par can 'di dag bde ba chen po'i ye
NK021(zha)001:507: shes kyi spyod yul du thag chod par mdzod cig
NK021(zha)001:508: / dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:511: yo byad rnams legs par 'dzom pa'i dus 'di nyid yin zhing /
NK021(zha)001:513: dang po sems bskyed 'jug dus su //
NK021(zha)001:514: rdzas kyi dbang bcu rdzogs par sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:515: zhes pa bsnyen pa rdzogs nas lhag pa'i sems skyes
NK021(zha)001:516: pa ni dbang bskur ba'i dus su gsungs pa ltar
NK021(zha)001:517: / skabs su babs pa 'dus pa mdo'i dbang bskur ba'i bka' srol bzang po 'dir 'jug pa'i sgor /
NK021(zha)001:519: spyi dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi dang //
NK021(zha)001:520: zhes gsungs pa'i don rnam par snang mdzad thig le
NK021(zha)001:521: dbang gi tan+t+ra las bkol ba'i gleng gzhi rgyud tshig
NK021(zha)001:523: dbang so so'i phan yon rnams skabs de dang der 'byung bas na /
NK021(zha)001:524: 'dir tshig sbyor cung zad bsdus te 'chad par byed pas legs par gsan 'tshal /
NK021(zha)001:526: 'dod khams 'di na bram ze dung gi phreng ba gyon pa rdzu 'phrul dang ldan pa zhig la /
NK021(zha)001:527: slob ma rgyal po'i phru gu zhig yod pas //
NK021(zha)001:528: bram zes slob sbyangs la sogs pa yon tan mang po bslabs pa las /
NK021(zha)001:529: rgyal bu nga rgyal skyes te bsam pas /
NK021(zha)001:530: 'di na nga'i gong na su yang shes rab snyems can med de gong du mi 'chor na /
NK021(zha)001:531: bram ze 'di gong du mi btang snyam nas //
NK021(zha)001:533: rgun chang mang du blud nas bzi ru bcug ste myos pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:535: lce lcags kyus drangs te spu gris bcad /
NK021(zha)001:536: lus la rus sbal gyi khrag gis byugs /
NK021(zha)001:537: bud med mang po'i zhabs mas gril cing mnan /
NK021(zha)001:538: sgyid pa spu gris bregs te bzhag pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:539: bram ze de myos pa sangs nas /
NK021(zha)001:540: drung na su 'dug 'bod par brtsams pa na lce med pas smra ma shes /
NK021(zha)001:541: bud med mang po'i zhabs mas bstums shing bril bas dran pa'ang cher nyams /
NK021(zha)001:542: ldang bar bsam pas sgyid pas ldang ma nus /
NK021(zha)001:543: su 'dug blta bar mig gi ma mthong /
NK021(zha)001:544: lus rus sbal gyi khrag gis byugs pas chu bur dang rkong pos gang bar gyur te /
NK021(zha)001:545: sdug bsngal zhing nyam thag nas /
NK021(zha)001:547: nga kho na 'di 'dra bar gyur pa /
NK021(zha)001:548: tshe rabs sngon gyi las kyi rnam par smin pa zhig yin nam /
NK021(zha)001:549: 'on te gong du shor dogs pa'i phrag dog gis
NK021(zha)001:550: 'di ltar byas sam snyam nas yid la bsams pa
NK021(zha)001:551: dang / rgyal bu slob mas gong du shor gyis
NK021(zha)001:552: dogs nas sdug bsngal gyi rnam pa de dag byas
NK021(zha)001:553: par bram zes mngon shes kyis rig nas /
NK021(zha)001:555: 'o rgyal po'i phru gu khyod la /
NK021(zha)001:556: ngas lo zla de snyed cig tu slob sbyongs byas pas /
NK021(zha)001:557: nga la 'di 'dra ba'i las byed pa /
NK021(zha)001:558: khyod kyang tshe lus 'di nyid la /
NK021(zha)001:559: lus la nad rnams pa drug gi thebs shing /
NK021(zha)001:560: sha za mo stong gi tshang bca' bar gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:563: rkang pas 'gro mi nus par shog cig /
NK021(zha)001:564: tshe 'phos nas kyang dmyal ba'i gnas su yun ring du skyes nas /
NK021(zha)001:565: ngan song gsum gyi gnas brgyud par shog cig /
NK021(zha)001:567: 'phags pa'i zhal nyi zer tsam yang mi mthong zhing /
NK021(zha)001:568: byang chub kyi myu gu gtan nas skams par gyur cig ces dmod pa bor te /
NK021(zha)001:570: de nas rgyal bu de rang gi nyes byas kyi rnam smin dang /
NK021(zha)001:571: bram ze'i dmod pa bor ba 'dom nas /
NK021(zha)001:572: tshe de nyid la lus la nad rnam pa drug gis phyi nang du thebs te /
NK021(zha)001:573: sha za mo stong gis tshang bcas nas 'jib /
NK021(zha)001:579: sems byang chub kyi myu gu'ang sngo skams su 'gyur ba la thug /
NK021(zha)001:580: de nas tshe las 'das shing 'phos nas kyang dmyal
NK021(zha)001:581: khams bcu drug kha brgyud pa sogs ngan song gsum
NK021(zha)001:582: brgyud de / bskal pa grangs med pa'i bar du
NK021(zha)001:583: 'phags pa'i zhal nyi zer tsam yang mthong ba'i skabs
NK021(zha)001:584: brgyud de / med do // de rnams 'phos nas
NK021(zha)001:585: sems can kyi nang na lus srul po gcer bu
NK021(zha)001:587: yang lus la nad rnam pa drug gis thebs te sdug bsngal ba la /
NK021(zha)001:588: bcom ldan 'das rnam pa snang mdzad kyi thugs rjes gzigs nas /
NK021(zha)001:589: dpal phyag na rdo rje thugs ka nas phyungs so //
NK021(zha)001:590: de nas dpal phyag na rdo rje mdun drang por 'dug ste /
NK021(zha)001:592: bcom ldan 'das sems can gyi nang na lus srul
NK021(zha)001:593: po gcer bu ba duhkha sna tshogs kyis nyen pa
NK021(zha)001:595: rgyu dang rkyen ji lta bu /
NK021(zha)001:597: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK021(zha)001:598: sems can lus srul po gcer bu 'di ni sngon
NK021(zha)001:599: bskal pa grangs med pa'i gong du rgyal bu zhig
NK021(zha)001:601: slob dpon bram ze zhig gi lus la ngan sna tshogs byas pa'i rnam smin dang /
NK021(zha)001:602: bram ze'i dmod pa 'dom pa'i dbang gis /
NK021(zha)001:603: da ltar yang byang chub kyi myu gu sngo skams la thug /
NK021(zha)001:604: lus kyi rgyud ni shin tu nyon mongs shing sdug bsngal /
NK021(zha)001:605: de las 'das nas dmyal khams kyi kha brgyud de thar pa'i dus med par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:606: de nas lag na rdo rjes /
NK021(zha)001:607: bcom ldan 'das nyon mongs pa'i sems can 'di thugs rjes bzung du gsol /
NK021(zha)001:609: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK021(zha)001:610: lag na rdo rje khyod song la /
NK021(zha)001:611: khyod kyis sems can nyam thag pa de la /
NK021(zha)001:612: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis brlabs
NK021(zha)001:613: kyi dbang dam pa thob par byed pa 'di rnams
NK021(zha)001:614: kyis srungs la sdug bsngal gyi nad rnams bsal ba
NK021(zha)001:615: dang / ngan song dmyal khams su skye ba la slar bzlog par bya ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:616: mtho ris kyi gnas su skye bar 'gyur ba'i thabs dbang 'di dag bskur ba'i las byos shig /
NK021(zha)001:618: lag na rdo rje rjes su yi rang nas /
NK021(zha)001:619: slar bcom ldan 'das la gsol pa /
NK021(zha)001:621: dbang thams cad kyi rang bzhin bshad du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:623: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK021(zha)001:624: rgyal rigs btsun par skyes pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:625: rgyal srid 'bangs kyis phul ba na //
NK021(zha)001:626: tshig btsan yul la dbang bsgyur ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:627: sa bdag rgyal por gnas pa bzhin //
NK021(zha)001:628: bcom ldan byang chub spyod pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:629: bde gshegs lha klu 'khor bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:630: dbang bskur rdzas kyis mnga' gsol bas //
NK021(zha)001:631: de nas byang chub mngon sangs rgyas //
NK021(zha)001:632: de bzhin phyag rgyas gnas bsrung ste //
NK021(zha)001:633: gsang dbang bum pas sdig pa bkru //
NK021(zha)001:634: 'phreng ba tshul khrims cod pan dang //
NK021(zha)001:635: rnam lnga'i thur mas bag chags bsal //
NK021(zha)001:636: me long 'khor lo'i stegs btsugs te //
NK021(zha)001:637: chos dung rdo rje rgya gram dang //
NK021(zha)001:638: rin chen sna bdun dgos pa skong //
NK021(zha)001:639: ral gris shes rab seng+ge sgra //
NK021(zha)001:640: nyi zla thabs dang shes rab dang //
NK021(zha)001:641: mda' gzhu zhi gnas lhag mthong dang //
NK021(zha)001:642: 'bras bu bkra shis rdzas brgyad sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:643: bden pa'i bka' brjod bden brdar nas //
NK021(zha)001:644: ting 'dzin tshangs pa'i glu dbyangs dang //
NK021(zha)001:645: rten 'brel rdzas rnams tshogs byas nas //
NK021(zha)001:646: dbang chog des ni dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:657: rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbang dang /
NK021(zha)001:658: rin chen sna bdun gyi dbang dang /
NK021(zha)001:663: bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang dang bcu drug go //
NK021(zha)001:664: de nas lag na rdo rjes rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK021(zha)001:665: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK021(zha)001:666: rdo rje rnam par dag pa'i phyag rgya bcings te
NK021(zha)001:667: / sems can lus srul po de'i gnas lngar gtugs
NK021(zha)001:668: shing bskrad pas sha za mo stong yod pa byer
NK021(zha)001:669: / to // de nas 'du 'bral med pa byang
NK021(zha)001:670: chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas byang chub sems kyi
NK021(zha)001:671: myu gu sos te de bzhin gshegs pa'i snying po
NK021(zha)001:672: can du byin gyi brlabs so //
NK021(zha)001:673: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rjes byin gyis
NK021(zha)001:674: brlabs pa'i bdud rtsi'i bum pa'i dbang bskur bas lus
NK021(zha)001:675: mi bde ba'i nad rnams dag cing byang bar gyur
NK021(zha)001:676: to // me tog gi phreng bas dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:677: tshul khrims kyi phreng ba zhig ral yongs su rdzogs
NK021(zha)001:678: nas ngan song gsum du ltung ba las ldog pa'i
NK021(zha)001:680: cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas khams gsum na gnas
NK021(zha)001:681: kyang sbyor ba ngan pa'i bag chags dang bral bar
NK021(zha)001:682: gyur to // thur ma'i dbang bskur bas ma rig
NK021(zha)001:683: pa'i ling thog 'thibs po byang nas gsal bar gyur
NK021(zha)001:684: gyur to // to // me long gi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:685: bas chos thams cad gzugs brnyan rten 'brel sgyu ma
NK021(zha)001:687: 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa
NK021(zha)001:688: dang ldan te khams gsum gyi gnas thams cad du
NK021(zha)001:690: dung gi tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun sum tshogs par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:691: rgya gram gyis phyogs bcu nas sngags 'chang rnams kyis bsrung bar gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:692: de nas rin po che sna bdun nam mkha' las
NK021(zha)001:693: brgyud mar byung ste dbang bskur bas phyir mi ldog
NK021(zha)001:694: pa'i 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i mchog sprin phung
NK021(zha)001:696: de nas ye shes kyi ral gris dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:697: dug gsum gzung 'dzin gyi 'khrul pa rgyun chad de
NK021(zha)001:698: bag chags thams cad byang zhing dag pa'i shes rab
NK021(zha)001:700: de nas brjid pa'i seng ge myur ba'i gzugs zhig
NK021(zha)001:701: lag tu byin te dbang bskur bas gsung rab rgya
NK021(zha)001:702: mtsho'i sgras log pa'i phyogs zil gyis mnan nas skad
NK021(zha)001:703: cig ma gcig gis stong spyi phud kyi steng du
NK021(zha)001:705: lus srul po'i de'i mtshan bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po zhes bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:706: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis legs so legs so zhes bya bas bstod do //
NK021(zha)001:707: de nas nyi zla phyag tu gtad de dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:708: de ma thag tu nyi mas skye 'gro ma lus
NK021(zha)001:709: pa'i sems can gyi rgyud la ye shes kyi 'od
NK021(zha)001:710: zer chen po mtha' med par shar bas dro zhing
NK021(zha)001:712: zla bas stong gsum gyi mun pa thams cad dus
NK021(zha)001:713: gcig tu bsal nas dus dang rnam par thams cad
NK021(zha)001:714: du bsil zhing snang bar gyur te /
NK021(zha)001:715: des thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang chen po rdzogs par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:716: de nas mda' gzhu phyag tu phul bas thabs dang
NK021(zha)001:717: shes rab dbyings dang ye shes zung du 'brel ba'i
NK021(zha)001:718: ye shes dag pa'i rtse mo la gnas par gyur
NK021(zha)001:719: to // de nas thams cad du bkra shis shing grub pa'i rdzas su gsungs pa /
NK021(zha)001:720: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang /
NK021(zha)001:721: byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang /
NK021(zha)001:726: gang zag dad pas bsam zhing rig pa'i glang po dang /
NK021(zha)001:727: mkhyen pa'i dpal la sogs te legs pa'i sbyin gnas
NK021(zha)001:728: su bskyed pa'i phyir bkra shis kyis mnga' gsol nas
NK021(zha)001:729: / 'gro ba gzhan la phan pa'i don du tshigs su bcad pas bstod pa /
NK021(zha)001:730: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa dgyes pa kye //
NK021(zha)001:731: rdo rje bdag yongs gtan du ma btang zhig /
NK021(zha)001:732: yungs kar dngos grub bgegs kyi sbyor ba rnam 'joms dang //
NK021(zha)001:733: zho yis rgyas byed ting 'dzin bcud kyis 'tsho ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:734: durbasa dge ba'i rtsa ba dpag med tshogs ldan dang //
NK021(zha)001:735: li khris lha mo mang po dbang du sdud pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:736: me long gis ni chos kun gzugs brnyan ltar rtogs dang //
NK021(zha)001:737: dung gis 'jig rten gsum du grags pa thob pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:738: gi'u wam dug gsum zhi byed chos srog 'tsho ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:739: bilbasa bla med byang chub snying po thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:741: de skad brjod nas bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyis mnga'
NK021(zha)001:742: gsol bas so so'i yon tan ji skad gsungs pa
NK021(zha)001:743: bzhin bkra shis par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:744: de lta bas na rang gzhan gyi rgyud kyi sdig pa mtshams med pa lnga dang /
NK021(zha)001:746: log pa brgyad la sogs pa rnams 'dag pa lta ci smos /
NK021(zha)001:747: bla ma la brnyas pa la sogs te 'da' dka'
NK021(zha)001:748: rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig nyams pa'i rnam smin
NK021(zha)001:749: rnams kyang dbang bskur ba'i phrin las khyad par can
NK021(zha)001:750: 'dis 'byang zhing 'dag par 'gyur ba ni rmad du
NK021(zha)001:752: don chen po dang ldan par gda' bas dga' ba dang spro ba yang dag par mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:753: des gleng gzhi bshad pa'i rim pa song nas //
NK021(zha)001:754: da ni dbang de dag bskur yang mi chags pa'i gegs brgyad bshad par bya ste /
NK021(zha)001:755: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos grub mchog /
NK021(zha)001:756: dbang dang byin rlabs 'byung ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:757: dper na rgya mtsho dwangs pa la //
NK021(zha)001:760: byin rlabs dbang mchog 'byung ba'i gegs //
NK021(zha)001:761: rnam pa brgyad du 'byung bar bshad //
NK021(zha)001:762: sngon 'byung ston pa slob dpon la //
NK021(zha)001:763: bka' cog brnyas pa byed pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:764: dbang dang dngos grub dang po'i gegs //
NK021(zha)001:765: bla med 'gro ba'i rdo rje spun //
NK021(zha)001:766: 'khu ldog gdung ba'i sems med na //
NK021(zha)001:767: dbang dang dngos grub gnyis pa'i gegs //
NK021(zha)001:768: byang chub sems la 'dud med cing //
NK021(zha)001:769: thar lam 'dren pa'i lha spong ba //
NK021(zha)001:770: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gegs gsum pa //
NK021(zha)001:771: snying rje'i yul gyur sems can la //
NK021(zha)001:772: thag pa gcod pa gegs bzhi pa //
NK021(zha)001:773: gsang sngags gsang ba'i lta spyod rnams //
NK021(zha)001:774: yongs la sbyin pa lnga pa'i gegs //
NK021(zha)001:775: thar lam ston la 'dud med cing //
NK021(zha)001:776: ser snas bcings pa drug pa'i gegs //
NK021(zha)001:777: gzu lum dbang med las la spyod //
NK021(zha)001:778: dngos grub 'byung ba'i gegs bdun pa //
NK021(zha)001:779: 'dod pa khe grags lhur len cing //
NK021(zha)001:780: gsang ba'i dam tshig spong ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:781: 'di ni brgyad pa'i gegs su bstan //
NK021(zha)001:782: nyams pa 'di dag sus spong ba //
NK021(zha)001:783: dngos grub dbang gi snod du bshad //
NK021(zha)001:785: 'dir rmi lam brtag pa'i rkang pa gsum sbrel ba
NK021(zha)001:786: ni slob ma sta gon gyi shan shor bar snang
NK021(zha)001:788: de ltar dbang mi chags pa'i rgyu gegs brgyad las ldog par gdams nas /
NK021(zha)001:789: sngar bshad pa bzhin phan yon khyad par can gyi
NK021(zha)001:790: gleng gzhi dang 'brel bar mtshams med lnga sbyongs kyi
NK021(zha)001:791: phrin las rmad du byung ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:792: de'ang 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dkyil 'khor du rim
NK021(zha)001:793: gyis 'jug pa'i thog mar rgyud sbyong ba'i spyi khrus
NK021(zha)001:794: sgo 'byed du grags pa phyag na rdo rje ngan
NK021(zha)001:795: song gnas 'dren gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba
NK021(zha)001:796: la / slob ma'i bya ba bla ma dang gsang
NK021(zha)001:797: bdag tha mi dad pa la dkyil 'khor du 'jug
NK021(zha)001:798: du 'jug cing dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul
NK021(zha)001:799: la / nas / gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:800: gsang bdag gtso bo khyod la 'dud //
NK021(zha)001:801: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK021(zha)001:802: de nyid dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK021(zha)001:803: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song zhing //
NK021(zha)001:804: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:805: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK021(zha)001:807: de nas bla ma dang dpal phyag na rdo rje
NK021(zha)001:808: tha mi dad pa sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK021(zha)001:809: dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba mdun gyi nam mkhar sad
NK021(zha)001:810: par mos la rgyun bshags yan lag brgyad pa ni
NK021(zha)001:812: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK021(zha)001:813: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:814: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK021(zha)001:815: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK021(zha)001:816: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:817: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:818: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK021(zha)001:819: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:820: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK021(zha)001:821: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK021(zha)001:822: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK021(zha)001:823: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK021(zha)001:824: bde gshegs byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK021(zha)001:825: dag pa gsum gyis lus dbul lo //
NK021(zha)001:826: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK021(zha)001:827: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK021(zha)001:828: zhes lan gsum gyis rgyud dag par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:829: 'dir phyag dang skyabs sems len chog spyi bye brag
NK021(zha)001:830: mang po mdzad pa'i srol snang yang yig rnying rnams
NK021(zha)001:832: 'di la ma tshang ba'ang med pas de tsam mo /
NK021(zha)001:833: de nas sbyor ba ngan song gi las sgrib sbyang ba'i sgo nas dkyil 'khor du drang ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:835: kye ma kyi hud rdo rje 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:836: 'gro mgon thugs rjes bdag skyobs shig /
NK021(zha)001:837: dbang mchog rgyal po bsgrag tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:838: slad nas mi 'chab mi sbed do //
NK021(zha)001:840: gnang ba byin pa ni rus /
NK021(zha)001:841: bu 'dir shog cig rigs kyi bu //
NK021(zha)001:842: rang gi nyams dang zlas nyams kyis //
NK021(zha)001:843: ngan song gsum du ltung ba las //
NK021(zha)001:844: skyob phyir dbang chog sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:845: zhes las kyi rdo rjes nang du drangs te dbang stegs la bkod /
NK021(zha)001:846: de nas nyes byas la bshags sdoms kyi bsam pa drag pos /
NK021(zha)001:847: kye ma kye hud bdag 'dra bas //
NK021(zha)001:848: las ngan rnam smin myong 'gyur na //
NK021(zha)001:849: nyes byas 'gyod pas mthol lo bshags //
NK021(zha)001:850: mgon po'i thugs rjes bdag sgrol cig /
NK021(zha)001:851: de nas slob bus tshe rabs thog ma med pa
NK021(zha)001:852: nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad gsang gnas su
NK021(zha)001:854: snying gar pre rnams kyi rnam par gnas pa so
NK021(zha)001:855: so'i steng du rig pa'i ye shes ram yam kham
NK021(zha)001:857: slob dpon gsang bdag tu gsal ba'i lag pa g.yas
NK021(zha)001:858: g.yon gyi sor mo lnga la sa bon 'bru lnga
NK021(zha)001:859: las rigs lnga yab yum bcur gyur pa rjes chags
NK021(zha)001:861: su ra ta s+t+wam zhes thal mo sbyar /
NK021(zha)001:862: badz+ra any+dza lis sor mo bsnol /
NK021(zha)001:863: badz+ra ban+d+ha bam gyis bsdams nas /
NK021(zha)001:864: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:865: rigs kyi bu 'dis nyon mongs pa zhe sdang gi
NK021(zha)001:866: sgo nas bsags pa'i las kyis dmyal bar skye 'gyur
NK021(zha)001:867: gyii sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa thams cad
NK021(zha)001:868: byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:869: na ra ka shud+d+ha tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK021(zha)001:870: ces phyag rgya bkrol nas sprug cing /
NK021(zha)001:871: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka ga ti he tum h'u phata /
NK021(zha)001:872: ces sngar basngagasa pa'i bye ma'am yungs thun gyis brabs pas du yig nyams smad par bsam /
NK021(zha)001:873: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od kyis 'byung ba'i yi ge gsum bskul /
NK021(zha)001:874: ye shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas gsang gnas kyi du yig /
NK021(zha)001:876: a zhes brjod pas du yig mi dmigs pa stong
NK021(zha)001:877: pa nyid du thim pas zhe sdang gi sgo nas
NK021(zha)001:878: bsags pa'i sdig sgrib dag par byas pa yin no
NK021(zha)001:879: // de nas sor mo'i rigs lnga gsal btab la /
NK021(zha)001:883: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:884: rigs kyi bu 'dis nyon mongs pa 'dod chags kyi
NK021(zha)001:885: sgo nas bsags pa'i las kyis yi dwags su skye
NK021(zha)001:886: 'gyur gyi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa thams
NK021(zha)001:887: cad byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:888: pre ta ka tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK021(zha)001:890: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ka ga ti he tum h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:892: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od kyis 'byung ba'i yi ge gsum bskul /
NK021(zha)001:893: ye shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas snying ga'i pre yig /
NK021(zha)001:895: a zhes pre yig mi dmigs pas 'dod chags kyi
NK021(zha)001:896: sgo nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib dag par byas pa
NK021(zha)001:897: yin no // de nas sngar ltar /
NK021(zha)001:901: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK021(zha)001:902: rigs kyi bu 'dis nyon mongs pa gti mug gi
NK021(zha)001:903: sgo nas bsags pa'i las kyis dud 'gror skye 'gyur
NK021(zha)001:904: gyi sa bon bag chags dang bcas pa thams cad
NK021(zha)001:905: byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:906: tir+ya ka ga ti tsak+shu pra be sha ya phata /
NK021(zha)001:908: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ka ga ti he tam h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:910: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od kyis 'byung ba'i yi ge gsum bskul /
NK021(zha)001:911: ye shes kyi me rlung chur gyur pas lte ba'i tri yig /
NK021(zha)001:913: a zhes tri mi dmigs par thim pas gti mug
NK021(zha)001:914: gi sgo nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib dag par byas
NK021(zha)001:915: pa yin no // zhar byung nga rgyal dang phrag dog sogs kyi las sgrib sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:918: na mo b+ha ga wa te sarba durga ti pa
NK021(zha)001:919: ri sho d+ha na r+aa dz+wa ya ta th+aa ga
NK021(zha)001:920: ta ya ar+ha te sam myak+sam bud+d+h+aa ya /
NK021(zha)001:922: sho d+ha ne sho d+ha ne sarba p+aa pam bi
NK021(zha)001:923: sho d+ha na shud+d+he bi shud+d+he sarba karma a wa
NK021(zha)001:924: ra na bi shud+d+he s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:925: nang sems mi 'khrug cing zhing rnam par dag par skye ba'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:926: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /

NK021(zha)001:933: rigs kyi bu 'dis tshe 'khor ba thog ma med
NK021(zha)001:934: pa nas bsags pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad sh+aan+tim ku

NK021(zha)001:954: rigs lnga'i phyag rgya gnas lngar bcings nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:955: skal ldan skyes bu khyod la dbang bskur bas //

NK021(zha)001:959: gshibs te sgreng ba mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag ste
NK021(zha)001:960: / badz+ra mu dra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK021(zha)001:964: rin po che'i dbu rgyan spyi bor bskon te /
NK021(zha)001:965: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:966: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun 'dus pa //

NK021(zha)001:971: cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje rnam par dag

NK021(zha)001:975: // de bzhin du bden pa des rigs kyi bu

NK021(zha)001:977: gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i dbang dam pa thob
NK021(zha)001:978: // par gyur cig / gnyis pa gsang dbang ni /

NK021(zha)001:1036: gyur cig / drug pa thur ma thogs te /

NK021(zha)001:1222: rdzas gsum byin gyis brlabs shing //
NK021(zha)001:1223: shis pa'i yungs kar phyag tu phul bas /
NK021(zha)001:1224: bgegs kyi rigs stong phrag brgyad cu'i rtog pa rnams
NK021(zha)001:1225: kyi bsam sbyor ngan pa kun gcod par mdzad do
NK021(zha)001:1226: // de bzhin du bden pa des skal ldan rig
NK021(zha)001:1227: pa 'dzin pa khyod yungs kar gyi rdzas kyis bkra
NK021(zha)001:1229: gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:1230: yun ring gnas par gyur pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:1231: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog kyang //
NK021(zha)001:1232: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:1233: yungs kar rdo rjes bgegs tshogs 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:1234: bgegs rnams 'joms pa'i mthu stobs ldan //
NK021(zha)001:1235: dgra bgegs kun las rgyal ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:1236: byin rlabs mchog gi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:1238: sngon bcom ldan 'das la khyim bdag bzang skyong gis
NK021(zha)001:1239: zho phul bas kun gyi dbang po'i bcud yongs su
NK021(zha)001:1240: tshim par byed pa 'dod 'jo'i ba khyad par can
NK021(zha)001:1242: de bzhin du bden pa des skal ldan rig pa
NK021(zha)001:1243: 'dzin pa khyod zho'i rdzas kyis bkra shis par gyur
NK021(zha)001:1244: cig / zho ni kun gyi snying por gyur pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:1245: snying po rnam dag byang chub sems rtogs shing //
NK021(zha)001:1246: yon tan kun gyi snying por gyur pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:1247: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK021(zha)001:1249: sngon bcom ldan 'das la bram ze kun+da lis rtsa durba phul bas /
NK021(zha)001:1250: durba lo 'dab rgyas shing 'phel ba bzhin du sems
NK021(zha)001:1251: can thams cad kyi bsod nams 'phel bar byin gyis
NK021(zha)001:1252: brlabs so // de bzhin du bden pa des skal
NK021(zha)001:1253: ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod durba'i rdzas kyis bkra
NK021(zha)001:1255: durbasa tshe 'di 'phel bar byed pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:1256: 'chi med rdo rje'i tshe ni rab grub pas //
NK021(zha)001:1257: sdug bsngal skye shi'i rtsa ba rgyun bcad de //
NK021(zha)001:1258: bkra shis des kyang tshe ni brtan gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:1260: sngon bcom ldan 'das la sa'i lha mo brtan mas li khri phul bas /
NK021(zha)001:1261: li khri chags shing zhen pa bzhin du thugs rje
NK021(zha)001:1262: chen po'i dbang gis nyon mongs pa'i sems can mi
NK021(zha)001:1263: gtong bar thugs dam du bzhes so //
NK021(zha)001:1264: de bzhin du bden pa des skal ldan rig pa
NK021(zha)001:1265: 'dzin pa khyod li khri'i rdzas kyis bkra shis par
NK021(zha)001:1266: gyur cig / li khri dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin can //
NK021(zha)001:1267: chos rnams ma lus dbang du gyur pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:1268: chos kyi rgyal srid rab tu brtan gyur pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:1269: bkra shis des kyang chos srid brtan gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:1271: sngon bcom ldan 'das la glang po che sa srungs
NK021(zha)001:1272: kyi bus gi'u wam phyag tu phul ba bdud rtsi
NK021(zha)001:1273: sman gyi mchog tu gyur te nad bzhi brgya rtsa
NK021(zha)001:1274: bzhi'i gnyen pos byin gyis brlabs so //
NK021(zha)001:1275: de bzhin du bden pa des skal ldan rig pa
NK021(zha)001:1276: 'dzin pa khyod gi'u wam gi rdzas kyis bkra shis
NK021(zha)001:1277: par gyur cig / gi'u wam dug gsum 'joms pa nad kyi sman //
NK021(zha)001:1278: sman mchog chos nyid rab tu rtogs gyur te //
NK021(zha)001:1279: nyon mongs zug rngu med par gyur pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:1280: bkra shis des kyang sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK021(zha)001:1282: sngon bcom ldan 'das la lha'i dbang po brgya byin
NK021(zha)001:1283: gyis dung g.yas su 'khyil ba bcu drug pa zhig
NK021(zha)001:1285: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas man chad nas 'jig
NK021(zha)001:1286: rten so so'i ris su tshangs pa'i sgra skad phun
NK021(zha)001:1287: sum tshogs pas chos kyi sgra chen po yongs su
NK021(zha)001:1289: de bzhin du bden pa des skal ldan rig pa
NK021(zha)001:1290: 'dzin pa khyod dung dkar gyi rdzas kyis bkra shis
NK021(zha)001:1291: par gyur cig / dung ni chos kyi sgra rnams sgrog pa'i tshul //
NK021(zha)001:1292: yon tan rgya mtsho mchog tu dag gyur nas //
NK021(zha)001:1293: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:1294: bkra shis des kyang tshig gi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:1296: sngon bcom ldan 'das la sa'i lha mo gzugs brnyan
NK021(zha)001:1297: ston gyis me long phul bas me long g.ya' dag
NK021(zha)001:1298: pa la gzugs kyi dngos po snang la stong pa
NK021(zha)001:1299: bzhin du / thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi
NK021(zha)001:1300: go 'phang rdzogs par stong zhing snang bar mdzad do
NK021(zha)001:1301: bzhin du / // de bzhin du bden pa des
NK021(zha)001:1302: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod me long gi
NK021(zha)001:1303: rdzas kyis bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:1304: me long ye shes chen po'i gzugs brnyan te //
NK021(zha)001:1305: ye shes rgya mtsho nyid du dag gyur nas //
NK021(zha)001:1306: rnam dag chos la thogs med longs spyod pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:1307: bkra shis des kyas don gyi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:1309: sngon bcom ldan 'das la shing gi lha mo 'od
NK021(zha)001:1310: 'chang gis shing tog bil ba phyag tu phul bas
NK021(zha)001:1311: / bilba ji ltar smin zhing 'bras bu rgyas pas gang bar gyur te /
NK021(zha)001:1312: mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa bde ba chen po'i dbyings su rdzogs par sangs rgyas so //
NK021(zha)001:1313: de bzhin du bden pa des skal ldan rig pa
NK021(zha)001:1314: 'dzin pa khyod bil ba'i rdzas kyi bkra shis par
NK021(zha)001:1315: gyur cig / bil ba rgyu rkyen 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK021(zha)001:1316: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i spyod pa kun //
NK021(zha)001:1317: byang chub snying po mchog tu gyur pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:1318: bkra shis de ni 'gro bas thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:1320: rnam bum gyi chus bkru zhing 'thung du'ang gzhug go //
NK021(zha)001:1321: de ltar mchog dbang bcu drug legs par bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:1322: sngon byung gi dbang dang rigs 'gre'i rang skal gyi
NK021(zha)001:1323: dri ma sbyangs shing dge ba'i sa bon gsos thebs
NK021(zha)001:1324: pa ni rgyud 'gyur ba'i khyad par te /
NK021(zha)001:1325: dbang thob pa'am rgyud smin par byas pa yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:1326: de ltar nges shes bskyed 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:1327: rjes kyi bya ba dbang thob pa'i lam khyer la bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:1328: dang po skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya lam du khyer ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:1331: sdug bsngal gsum rang bzhin gyis ma dmigs na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:1332: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams 'khor ba 'dir sdug bsngal gyis mnar zhing /
NK021(zha)001:1334: de rnams kyi sdug bsngal bla ma dkon mchog gis
NK021(zha)001:1335: skyobs nus par nges shes khyad par can bskyed nas
NK021(zha)001:1336: / de'i phan yon dran pas rtag tu rang nyid skyabs 'gror 'bad cing /
NK021(zha)001:1337: snying rje chen pos skye bo gzhan rnams skyabs su 'gror gzhug /
NK021(zha)001:1338: bla ma dang dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan dran pas dad pa bsgom zhing gsol ba 'debs /
NK021(zha)001:1339: bka' drin dran pas phyag mchod dang bstod pa bya /
NK021(zha)001:1340: nyes dmigs dran pas srog la babs kyang skyabs yul ma spong /
NK021(zha)001:1341: yid ches dran pas bde sdug ci byung yang bla
NK021(zha)001:1342: ma dang dkon mchog la mi 'khang zhing gzhan la
NK021(zha)001:1343: blo mi gtod / dkon mchog gsum gyi rten la'ang
NK021(zha)001:1344: dkon mchog dngos su 'du shes pas phyag mchod 'bul
NK021(zha)001:1345: blo mi gtod / zhing / 'o brgyal sar mi 'jog /
NK021(zha)001:1346: gta' mar 'jog pa dang btsongs te glud za ba
NK021(zha)001:1347: sogs ma gus pa'i las thams cad spang bar bya
NK021(zha)001:1348: ste / dgag sgrub kyi bslab bya rgyas par gzhan las shes dgos shing /
NK021(zha)001:1349: 'dir ni las dang po ba la nye bar mkho ba rags pa tsam zhig bsdus pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:1350: gnyis pa dbang gi dam tshig lam du khyer ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:1351: sngar gdams pa'i dbang gi gegs brgyad po de shes par byas nas 'bad pas bsrung ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:1352: gsum pa lha lam du khyer ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:1353: rang nyid gsang bdag gi sku'i rnam pa me long nang gi gzugs brnyan ltar /
NK021(zha)001:1354: snang la 'dzin pa med pa'i lha sku gsal stong du lam du khyer ro //
NK021(zha)001:1355: bzhi pa snying po lam du khyer ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:1356: ngag tu n+ai lam wa ra d+ha ra sogs ci nus bzla zhing /
NK021(zha)001:1357: de yang sngags kyi sgra gdangs grags stong du lam du khyer ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:1358: de ltar tshul bzhin du bsgrub par bagyi'o snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:1359: gtso bos ji ltar bka' stsal pa //
NK021(zha)001:1360: de dag thams cad bdag gis bgyid //
NK021(zha)001:1362: dbang rdzogs par thob par gtang rag gi yon du man+dala phul /
NK021(zha)001:1363: lus longs spyod dus gsum dge tshogs rgya mtsho dang
NK021(zha)001:1364: bcas pa 'bul na cha shas nas longs spyad du
NK021(zha)001:1365: gsol snyam pas / deng nas brtsams te bdag bran du //
NK021(zha)001:1366: khyod la bdag ni 'bul lags na //
NK021(zha)001:1367: khyod kyi slob mar bzung ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:1368: cha shas kyis kyang spyad du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:1370: des rang gzhan gyi don rgya chen po grub pa
NK021(zha)001:1371: yin pas dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK021(zha)001:1373: bsod nams 'di yis sogs kyis bsngosa te /
NK021(zha)001:1374: slob ma rnams rang gnas su btang nas /
NK021(zha)001:1375: rjes chog rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:1376: gleng gzhi'i man ngag dang 'brel bar //
NK021(zha)001:1377: sgo 'byed gsang bdag dbang bskur khrigs //
NK021(zha)001:1378: chos 'dir mos pa'i blo gsal la //
NK021(zha)001:1379: phan phyir go bde'i dpal 'di bskrun //
NK021(zha)001:1380: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang chog rdo rje'i them skas las /
NK021(zha)001:1381: sngon 'gro sgo 'byed kyi dbang chog bshad pa'i skabs te gnyis pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:1384: srid pa'i 'gyur ba sgrib med du //
NK021(zha)001:1385: gzigs nas mngon mtho'i lam stegs las //
NK021(zha)001:1386: bde chen rdo rjera 'dren mdzad der //
NK021(zha)001:1387: btud nas lha mi'i dbang chog bshad //
NK021(zha)001:1388: da ni dngos gzhi chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur ba las /
NK021(zha)001:1389: thog mar mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas pa
NK021(zha)001:1390: yan lag gi dkyil 'khor du phyi dbang bskur ba
NK021(zha)001:1391: la drug gi / dang po lha mi'i theg pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:1392: dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa sgrub thabs ltar grub rjes /
NK021(zha)001:1394: slob dpon bdag nyid sh+aakya thub par gsal ba la /
NK021(zha)001:1395: snang rig gi bcud thams cad 'od zer gyi rnam par bsdus pa spyi bo nas thim pas /
NK021(zha)001:1396: spyi bor rin po che 'bar bas mtshan par gyur /
NK021(zha)001:1398: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas mchod /
NK021(zha)001:1399: de dag gi byin rlabs 'od zer gyi rnam par rang la thim pas rjes su gnang ba thob /
NK021(zha)001:1400: yang spyi bo'i rin po che las 'phroos pa'i 'od
NK021(zha)001:1401: kyis sems can thams cad kyi dgos 'dod re ba
NK021(zha)001:1402: yid bzhin du skong ba'i yi ge dbyangs gsal gyi
NK021(zha)001:1403: rnam par bsdus nas rang la thim pas /
NK021(zha)001:1404: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis byin gyis brlabs par bsam mo //
NK021(zha)001:1405: de nas slob ma gzhug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:1407: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad /
NK021(zha)001:1408: sems bskyed dang chos nyan pa'i kun spyod sngar ltar gsal btab cing nyan par bskul nas /
NK021(zha)001:1409: 'dir gang gsan par bya ba'i chos ni rgyal ba
NK021(zha)001:1410: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thabs mkhas la
NK021(zha)001:1411: thugs rje chen po mnga' ba de nyid kyis sems
NK021(zha)001:1412: can rnams kyi bsam pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1414: skal pa'i khyad par dang rjes su mthun pa'i chos
NK021(zha)001:1415: kyi phung po bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig gsungs
NK021(zha)001:1416: pa thams cad kyang bsdu na gnyis su 'du ste
NK021(zha)001:1418: kye ho gsang ba'i rdo rje 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:1419: nga yi theg pa bsam yas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:1420: bshad lugs rnam pa gnyis su 'dus //
NK021(zha)001:1422: zhes pas 'jig rten pa dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa gnyis /
NK021(zha)001:1423: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK021(zha)001:1424: thabs gang gis mthar phyin par bsgrubs pas 'bras bu
NK021(zha)001:1425: 'jig rten las 'phags nus mi nus kyis phye ba'o
NK021(zha)001:1426: // de la thog mar 'jig rten lha mi'i theg pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:1427: ngan song la 'jigs nas mtho ris kyi bde 'bras
NK021(zha)001:1428: don du gnyer bas mngon mtho'i rten sgrub byed de
NK021(zha)001:1429: / pha rol tu phyin pa'i man ngag skyes bu gsum gyi lam rim dang sbyar na /
NK021(zha)001:1430: 'jigs skyob dang legs smon tsam la bsten pa skyes bu chung du'i lam ste /
NK021(zha)001:1432: 'jig rten pa'i yang dag pa'i lta ba dang ldan
NK021(zha)001:1433: pas dge bcu'i las lam la spyad pa'i 'bras bu
NK021(zha)001:1435: de'i steng du bsam gtan bzhi dang gzugs med pa'i
NK021(zha)001:1436: snyoms 'jug sogs la brten nas khams gong ma'i lha'i
NK021(zha)001:1438: lang gshegs su snga ma lha'i theg pa zhes gtso bo'i sgras smos pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1439: phyi ma la 'dod nyon gyis gtsang bas tshangs pa'i theg pa zhes gsungs shing /
NK021(zha)001:1440: de'ang rin chen phreng ba las /
NK021(zha)001:1441: mi yi chos lugs legs spyad na //
NK021(zha)001:1442: lha yul bgrod pa thag mi ring //
NK021(zha)001:1443: lha dang mi yi them skas la //
NK021(zha)001:1445: ces pas 'di ni theg pa thams cad kyi gazhi'am lam stegs su gyur pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:1446: gnyis pa 'jig rten las 'das pa'i theg pa la /
NK021(zha)001:1448: lang+ka'i bdag po gzhan yang gang //
NK021(zha)001:1449: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:1450: gsum du nges par bstan pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:1452: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:1453: zhes gsum du snang ba la /
NK021(zha)001:1454: dang po kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:1455: 'khor ba las rang gcig pu thar 'dod kyi blos
NK021(zha)001:1456: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i thabs su gyur
NK021(zha)001:1457: pa nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1458: de'i steng du rten 'brel gyi lam zab mo bsgom
NK021(zha)001:1459: pas bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs kyi thabs su
NK021(zha)001:1460: gyur pa rang rgyal gyi theg pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1461: chos thams cad bdag med par rtogs shing snying rje
NK021(zha)001:1462: chen pos gzhan don rlabs po che la spyod pa'i
NK021(zha)001:1463: thabs su gyur pa byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa
NK021(zha)001:1464: ste / dang po gnyis skyes bu 'bring po dang /
NK021(zha)001:1465: tha ma skyes bu chen po'i lam stegs mtshan nyid sde gsum mo //
NK021(zha)001:1466: gnyis pa dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:1467: don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag par
NK021(zha)001:1468: rtogs pas kun rdzob tu dngos grub gzhan la re
NK021(zha)001:1469: zhing rtsol ba'i thabs su gyur pa kri ya'i theg
NK021(zha)001:1470: pa dang / lta sgom yo ga dang spyod pa
NK021(zha)001:1471: bya ba dang cha 'dra bar spyod pas dngos grub
NK021(zha)001:1472: pa'i thabs su gyur pa u pa ya'i theg pa
NK021(zha)001:1473: pa dang / dang / don dam mtshan ma med
NK021(zha)001:1474: pa'i chos nyid kyi byin rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje
NK021(zha)001:1475: dbyings kyi lhar brtags te rtog pa bzang ngan blang
NK021(zha)001:1476: dor gyi rtsol bas 'bras bu sgrub pa'i thabs su
NK021(zha)001:1477: gyur pa yo ga'i theg pa ste phyi rgyud sde
NK021(zha)001:1478: pa dang / dang / gsum mo // gsum pa dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa la'ang gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:1479: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa la gtso bor brten pa'i
NK021(zha)001:1480: sgo nas lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi don
NK021(zha)001:1481: la rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas grol ba ster ba'i
NK021(zha)001:1482: thabs su gyur pa bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i
NK021(zha)001:1483: theg pa dang / shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa
NK021(zha)001:1484: la gtso bor brten pa'i sgo nas dbyings dang ye
NK021(zha)001:1485: shes gnyis su med pa'i don la rtogs goms kyi
NK021(zha)001:1486: sbyor bas grol ba thob pa'i thabs su gyur pa
NK021(zha)001:1487: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga'i theg pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1488: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don rang thog tu grol
NK021(zha)001:1489: bar byed pa'i thabs mchog spang blang re dogs dang
NK021(zha)001:1490: bral ba'i rang bzhin can rdzogs pa chen po a
NK021(zha)001:1491: ti yo ga ste nang rgyud sde gsum mo //
NK021(zha)001:1492: de ltar nges legs sam rnam par grol ba'i lam la theg pa dgur phye ba las /
NK021(zha)001:1494: lung a nu yo ga 'dus pa chen po mdo'i
NK021(zha)001:1495: dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bar byed pa yin la
NK021(zha)001:1496: / de la'ang 'grel pa lung bstan ma las /
NK021(zha)001:1497: ji ltar rgyal sras bcas pa la //
NK021(zha)001:1498: mdzes pa'i yon tan rdzogs pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:1499: dbang bskur khungs su yid ches nas //
NK021(zha)001:1500: dam pa brgyud pa'i man ngag gis //
NK021(zha)001:1501: rjes 'jug tu yang shes par bya //
NK021(zha)001:1503: dbang don bsdus pa las kyang //
NK021(zha)001:1504: sems can rnams kyi don ched du //
NK021(zha)001:1505: dbang gi don rnams bsdu bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:1506: chu bo chen po bzhi rnams la //
NK021(zha)001:1507: sngon byung dang ni rjes su 'jug /
NK021(zha)001:1508: ces pas sngon byung rgyal ba'i mdzad spyod kyi sgo nas gdul bya spro ba bskyed pa'i dbang dang /
NK021(zha)001:1509: rjes 'jug gang zag nyams len gyi sgo nas gdul
NK021(zha)001:1510: bya chud mi za bar byed pa'i dbang gnyis las
NK021(zha)001:1511: / dang po sngon byung gi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:1513: sngon byung chu bo rnam bzhi la //
NK021(zha)001:1514: yul dang dbang po dgos ched dang //
NK021(zha)001:1515: thabs dang rtags dang gnas dang drug /
NK021(zha)001:1516: ces don drug tu bsdu bar mdzad pa'i sngon byung gi dbang gi go don ni /
NK021(zha)001:1517: spyir slob dpon rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis /
NK021(zha)001:1518: slob bu rgyu'i theg pa'i mi slob lam brnyes pa'i rgyal ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:1519: sngags rang lugs kyi mthar lam rgyun tha la bzhugs pa'i rgyal tshab skyes bu dam pa rnams la /
NK021(zha)001:1520: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du 'bras dus kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:1521: mthar thug gi 'bras bu'i go 'phang la sbyor bar byed pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:1523: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'dzin pa la //
NK021(zha)001:1524: sa mtha'i sems dpa' chen po yis //
NK021(zha)001:1525: ji ltar mchod cing zhus pa ltar //
NK021(zha)001:1528: rdo rje can gyis sangs rgyas la //
NK021(zha)001:1529: 'gro ba skyob pa'i ched du dbang //
NK021(zha)001:1530: yon tan 'byung gnas ji ltar stsal //
NK021(zha)001:1532: khyad par spyi mdo'i skyes bu dam pa dang dbang thob pa'i le'ura /
NK021(zha)001:1533: la las ni rgyud kyi chu bo'i dbang gis dbang byin no //
NK021(zha)001:1534: la las ni 'byung ba'i chu bo'i dbang gis dbang byin no //
NK021(zha)001:1535: la las ni grags pa'i chu bo'i dbang gis dbang byin no //
NK021(zha)001:1536: la las ni rdzogs pa'i chu bo'i dbang gis dbang byin no //
NK021(zha)001:1537: zhes sngon byung gi chu bo bzhi rgyal tshab skyes
NK021(zha)001:1538: bu lnga la thun mong du bskur ba'ang mi 'gal
NK021(zha)001:1539: zhing / bye brag tshul bstan gyi dbang du byas
NK021(zha)001:1540: na dam pa tog dkar po sogs bzhi la skal
NK021(zha)001:1541: pa che chung gis thun min du so sor bskur
NK021(zha)001:1542: zhing / ba'ang bshad do // gnyis pa rjes 'jug gi dbang la'ang /
NK021(zha)001:1544: las dang po pa'i dbang gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:1545: dang po lam pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:1546: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK021(zha)001:1547: rjes 'jug lam pa'i gnas skabs na //
NK021(zha)001:1548: rgyun ni rnal 'byor rnam pa lnga //
NK021(zha)001:1549: zhes gsungs pa ltar mos spyod kyi lam dang /
NK021(zha)001:1551: slob pa'i lam bzhir gnas pa'i slob ma la /
NK021(zha)001:1552: rim par chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:1553: lam gong ma gong ma la sbyor bar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:1554: slob dpon gyis rjes 'jug lam pa'i dbang zhes gsungs te /
NK021(zha)001:1555: don la snga ma gsum lam dus kyi dbang dngos dang /
NK021(zha)001:1556: phyi ma gcig po 'bras dus kyi dbang du 'du ba yin no //
NK021(zha)001:1557: 'dir ni de dag las gzhan du gyur pa /
NK021(zha)001:1558: gtso bor smin byed rgyu dus kyi dbang ste /
NK021(zha)001:1559: rjes 'jug las dang po pa'i dbang zhes grags pa gang yin pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:1560: de yang dbang don bsdus pa las /
NK021(zha)001:1561: rjes 'jug las kyi dang po la //
NK021(zha)001:1562: chu bo bzhi yi dbang bskur ba //
NK021(zha)001:1563: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK021(zha)001:1564: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bor bya //
NK021(zha)001:1565: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la //
NK021(zha)001:1566: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK021(zha)001:1567: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK021(zha)001:1568: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK021(zha)001:1569: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga la //
NK021(zha)001:1570: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK021(zha)001:1572: de la'ang rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs kyis bskur tshul gnyis te //
NK021(zha)001:1573: rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pas zab mo'i don
NK021(zha)001:1574: la mos pa'i skal ldan khyad par can la mdo
NK021(zha)001:1575: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du chu bo bzhi rdzogs kyi
NK021(zha)001:1576: dbang sum cu rtsa drug bskur ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:1577: sbyangs pas snod du gyur pa rgya che ba la
NK021(zha)001:1578: mos pa'i skal ldan la mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs
NK021(zha)001:1579: yan lag gi dkyil 'khor so sor phye bar theg
NK021(zha)001:1580: pa thams cad 'dus pa'i mdo dbang rtsa ba so
NK021(zha)001:1581: drug las yan lag rags pa brgyad brgya so gcig
NK021(zha)001:1582: tu phye nas bskur bar gsungs shing lugs de gnyis
NK021(zha)001:1583: ka sa yo ga bzhi rdzogs dang /
NK021(zha)001:1584: theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa la 'dra ba yin te /
NK021(zha)001:1585: rtsa ba so drug gi dbang du mdzad nas dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK021(zha)001:1586: bcu yis byang chub rigs can 'gyur //
NK021(zha)001:1587: bcu gcig gsang ba nang par 'gyur //
NK021(zha)001:1588: bcu gsum bla ma chen por grags //
NK021(zha)001:1589: gnyis kyis theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:1591: des na yan lag gi dkyil 'khor so sor phye ba mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs de yang /
NK021(zha)001:1592: theg brgyad sgos kyi cho ga de dang de ston
NK021(zha)001:1593: pa'i mdo rgyud so so nas bsdus te spyi'i cho
NK021(zha)001:1594: gar byas pa lta bu ni ma yin gyi /
NK021(zha)001:1595: sa dang po 'gyur ba ma nges pa nas /
NK021(zha)001:1596: sa bcu pa rdzogs pa cir chib kyi bar non par bya ba'i don du /
NK021(zha)001:1597: lha mi'i dbang nas brtsams te /
NK021(zha)001:1598: a nu rang lugs kyi rdzogs rim mthar thug pa a ti'i bar la /
NK021(zha)001:1599: bya spyod so sor bgrangs pas dbang gi rim pa bcu byung ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:1600: bya spyod gcig tu byas pa'i theg pa dgu dang tshul 'dra bas theg dgu'i dbang zhes grags shing /
NK021(zha)001:1601: de yang chu bo bzhis sa bcu dang rnal 'byor bzhi rdzogs tshul gyis mtshams ni /
NK021(zha)001:1602: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo rdzogs pas /
NK021(zha)001:1603: sa dang po 'gyur ba ma nges pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1604: bdun pa dmigs pa 'bras bu skye bas bar gyi
NK021(zha)001:1605: sa bdun non nas yo ga ste rnal 'byor du
NK021(zha)001:1606: 'gyur / nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo nod pas
NK021(zha)001:1607: sa brgyad pa gnas pa mi g.yo ba'i sa non
NK021(zha)001:1609: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo nod pas sa dgu
NK021(zha)001:1610: pa brdal ba chos nyid kyi sa non nas rjes
NK021(zha)001:1612: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo nod pas sa bcu
NK021(zha)001:1613: pa rdzogs pa cir chib kyi sa non nas shin
NK021(zha)001:1614: tu rnal 'byor du 'gyur pa yin zhing /
NK021(zha)001:1615: de lta bu'i lam stegs kyi theg pa rnams so so'i lam dang tshul 'dra rung du byung yang /
NK021(zha)001:1616: don la 'bras bu'i theg pa'i thabs mkhas kyis zin pas /
NK021(zha)001:1617: theg pa rang rang gi spangs thob dang rigs 'dra'i
NK021(zha)001:1618: yon tan de dang de skye ba'i myur lam du
NK021(zha)001:1620: des na 'dir rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs kyi dbang mdo khyad par ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:1621: mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs gnyis gcig tu dril nas bskur ba las /
NK021(zha)001:1622: thog mar mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas pa'i
NK021(zha)001:1623: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil
NK021(zha)001:1624: 'khor dang po lha mi'i theg pa'i dkyil 'khor du
NK021(zha)001:1625: dbang bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK021(zha)001:1627: slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams sngon du song nas /
NK021(zha)001:1628: gnyis pa khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur
NK021(zha)001:1629: pa la dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod
NK021(zha)001:1631: de ltar man+dala phul nas snyim pa me tog dang
NK021(zha)001:1632: bcas pas thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa
NK021(zha)001:1634: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK021(zha)001:1635: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnams sbyong ba //
NK021(zha)001:1636: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen mchog /
NK021(zha)001:1637: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin gsol //
NK021(zha)001:1639: de nas gtan khrims 'bogs pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:1640: phyag btsal nas pus gtsugs thal sbyar gyis 'dug tu bcug la /
NK021(zha)001:1641: khyed cag mngon mtho'i theg pa la bslab pa de la'ang /
NK021(zha)001:1643: lha yi theg dang tshangs pa'i theg /
NK021(zha)001:1644: ces gsungs pa'i lha'i theg pa ni bsam gtan gyis
NK021(zha)001:1645: yongs su ma bzung ba'i dge bcu'i las lam ste
NK021(zha)001:1647: dge bcu spyod cing mi dge spong byed pa //
NK021(zha)001:1648: 'dod khams lha dang mi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NK021(zha)001:1650: de'ang lha dang tshangs pa'i theg pa gnyis kyis bgrod par bya ba'i rten gyi gang zag la ni /
NK021(zha)001:1651: phyi rol pa dang nang pa gnyis ga yod na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:1652: 'dir ni rnam grol gyi theg pa'i lam stegs yin pas nang pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK021(zha)001:1655: mos pa rnams kyi dbang mdzad nas //
NK021(zha)001:1656: skyabs gsum rnam par bzhag pa yin //
NK021(zha)001:1658: 'dir thar pa don gnyer gyi blo med par //
NK021(zha)001:1659: skyes bu chung ngu'i blos ngan song gi sdug bsngal
NK021(zha)001:1660: la 'jigs nas dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro
NK021(zha)001:1661: ba yin na'ang / da res bsam pa yar ldan du byas te /
NK021(zha)001:1662: bdag gzhan 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las thar 'dod kyi
NK021(zha)001:1663: blos skyabs gsum sngon du 'gro ba can gyis mi
NK021(zha)001:1664: dge bcu spong gi tshul khrims yang dag par blang
NK021(zha)001:1666: sngar chos 'brel med na btsun pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1667: yod na slob dpon dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:1668: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK021(zha)001:1669: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:1670: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK021(zha)001:1671: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:1675: bdag ji srid 'tsho'i bar du lha mi'i theg pa la gnas par slob dpon gyis bzung du gsol /
NK021(zha)001:1679: de ltar dge bcu'i las lam gyi khrims yang dag
NK021(zha)001:1680: par thob pa de'i mi mthun phyogs mi dge bcu
NK021(zha)001:1681: spangs te / de las ldog par bagyi'o snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:1683: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyis lha mi'i theg pa la zhugs te /
NK021(zha)001:1684: ji srid 'tsho'i bar du srog gcod pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:1685: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1686: 'dod pas log par g.yem pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:1693: log par lta ba'i las mi dge ba bcu spangs te /
NK021(zha)001:1694: mi dge ba bcu las slar log pa de bzhin du /
NK021(zha)001:1695: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas
NK021(zha)001:1696: bzung ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du mi dge ba
NK021(zha)001:1697: bcu spangs te / mi dge ba bcu las slar ldog par bagyi'o //
NK021(zha)001:1698: yan lag bcu po 'dis bdag 'phags pa dgra bcom
