NK021(zha)001:1699: pa rnams kyis bslabs pa'i lha mi'i theg pa bzang
NK021(zha)001:1700: po la rjes su slob bo //
NK021(zha)001:1706: de nas tshangs pa'i theg pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:1707: tshad med bzhi spyod mi g.yo sgom byed pa //
NK021(zha)001:1708: tshangs gnas la sogs skye ba'i rgyu yin no //
NK021(zha)001:1709: zhes pa ltar tshangs theg gi lam dngos bsam gtan bzhi dang /
NK021(zha)001:1711: tshangs theg gi yon tan khyad par can tshad med bzhi dang /
NK021(zha)001:1712: mngon par shes pa lnga rnams la tshul bzhin du bslab par bya snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:1714: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa drang srong chen po
NK021(zha)001:1715: de dag gis bsam gtan dang snyoms 'jug gi sems
NK021(zha)001:1716: bsgrubs te / bsam gtan dang mngon par shes pa brnyes pa de bzhin du /
NK021(zha)001:1717: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang byams pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1720: btang snyoms tshad med pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:1721: bsam gtan gyi sems rtog dpyod dang bral ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:1723: gnas te 'phags pa'i bsam gtan dang mngon par shes pa thob par bagyi'o //
NK021(zha)001:1724: ji ltar sngon gyi 'phags pa drang srong chen po rnams kyi rjes su slob bo //
NK021(zha)001:1730: 'dod lha'i go 'phang sgrub pa tsam la gso sbyong ma blangs kyang chog ste /
NK021(zha)001:1731: yang dag pa'i lta bas zin pa'i dge bcu'i las lam gyis 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:1732: de lta na'ang 'dod lha ris drug gi rten khyad
NK021(zha)001:1733: par can sgrub pa la gso sbyong blangs na bzang
NK021(zha)001:1735: gso sbyong 'dod spyod lha lus yid 'ong ba //
NK021(zha)001:1736: skyes pa bud med dag la stsol bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:1738: ji ltar len pa'i cho ga ni /
NK021(zha)001:1739: gnas 'jog gi mdo las gsungs pa ltar blangs na legs mod kyi /
NK021(zha)001:1740: 'on kyang dbang bskur yul khyim pa dang rab byung la nges pa med cing /
NK021(zha)001:1741: rab tu byung ba yin na'ang theg pa chen po'i gso sbyong blang ba mi 'gal bas /
NK021(zha)001:1742: 'dir de ltar blang bar bya snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:1743: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad dang /
NK021(zha)001:1744: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:1745: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK021(zha)001:1746: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rta cang shes
NK021(zha)001:1747: lta bu / glang po chen po /
NK021(zha)001:1751: rang gi don rjes su thob pa //
NK021(zha)001:1752: srid pa kun tu sbyor ba yongs su zad pa /
NK021(zha)001:1754: legs par rnam par grol ba'i thugs //
NK021(zha)001:1755: legs par rnam par grol ba'i shes rab can de dag gis /
NK021(zha)001:1756: sems can thams cad kyi don gyi phyir dang /
NK021(zha)001:1757: phan par bya ba'i phyir dang //
NK021(zha)001:1758: grol bar bya ba'i phyir dang //
NK021(zha)001:1759: nad med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK021(zha)001:1760: mu ge med par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK021(zha)001:1761: byang chub phyogs kyi chos rnams yongs su rdzogs par
NK021(zha)001:1762: bya ba'i phyir du gso sbyong nges par mdzad pa
NK021(zha)001:1763: de bzhin du / bdag ming 'di zhes bya bas
NK021(zha)001:1764: kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste sang nyi ma ma
NK021(zha)001:1765: shar gyi bar du gso sbyong nges par yang dag
NK021(zha)001:1767: zhes lan gsum gyis blangs te thabs legs bya /
NK021(zha)001:1768: de nas bslab pa brjod pa'i don du 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:1769: deng nas srog gcod mi bya zhing //
NK021(zha)001:1770: gzhan gyi nor yang blang mi bya //
NK021(zha)001:1771: 'khrig pa'i chos kyang mi bya ste //
NK021(zha)001:1772: rdzun gyi tshig kyang mi smra'o //
NK021(zha)001:1773: skyon ni mang po nyer brten pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:1774: chang ni yongs su spang bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:1775: khri stan mthon po mi bya zhing //
NK021(zha)001:1776: de bzhin dus ma yin pa'i zas //
NK021(zha)001:1777: dri dang 'phreng ba dang ni rgyan //
NK021(zha)001:1778: gar dang glu sogs spang bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:1779: ji ltar dgra bcom rtag tu ni //
NK021(zha)001:1780: srog gcod la sogs mi byed ltar //
NK021(zha)001:1781: de bzhin srog gcod la sogs spang /
NK021(zha)001:1782: bla med byang chub myur thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:1783: sdug bsngal mang 'khrugs sems can rnams //
NK021(zha)001:1784: srid pa'i mtsho las sgrol bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:1785: ces lan gcig dang thabs legs bya /
NK021(zha)001:1786: 'di ni nam langs kyi dus su len dgos pas dbang bskur dang dus ma 'grig na /
NK021(zha)001:1787: de'i zhogs zur du blangs kyang mi 'gal zhing /
NK021(zha)001:1788: gzhan du lha mi tsam pa'i dbang du byas na
NK021(zha)001:1789: sngar bshad pa ltar ma blangs kyang chad pa'i skyon
NK021(zha)001:1790: med do // de nas chos bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:1791: theg pa 'di ni theg pa kun gyi phyi mo'am gzhir gyur pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:1792: gang dge ba bcu'i las kyi lam la mi spyod
NK021(zha)001:1793: pa'i theg pa ni gang na'ang yod pa ma yin
NK021(zha)001:1794: pa'i phyir dang / 'di ni theg pa thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba'ang yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK021(zha)001:1795: de ltar yang kye rdor las /
NK021(zha)001:1796: dge ba bcu las brtsams nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:1797: de yi chos ni rab tu dbye //
NK021(zha)001:1799: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas kyang /
NK021(zha)001:1800: gzhi yi theg pa'i dang por zhog /
NK021(zha)001:1802: dge bcu'i las lam dang bsam gzugs kyi lam mi g.yo ba'i las la spyod pa 'di dag kyang /
NK021(zha)001:1803: yang dag pa'i lta ba zhes bya ba /
NK021(zha)001:1805: las 'bras la yid ches pa'i lta bas nges par zin dgos te /
NK021(zha)001:1806: de las ldog nas dge ba spyad kyang 'bras bu sdug bsngal du smin par 'gyur te /
NK021(zha)001:1808: gang zag log par lta bas legs spyad kyang //
NK021(zha)001:1809: thams cad rnam par smin pa mi bzad ldan //
NK021(zha)001:1811: de bas na ngan song gi rgyu mi dge ba spong ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK021(zha)001:1812: 'dod pa'i mtho ris kyi rgyu yang dag pa'i lta bas zin pa'i dge bcu'i las lam dang /
NK021(zha)001:1813: khams gong ma'i rgyu bsam gzugs kyi ting nge 'dzin dang tshad med bzhi sogs sgom pa /
NK021(zha)001:1814: khyad par du'ang nges legs kyi theg pa'i gzhir 'gro
NK021(zha)001:1815: bas chos kyi rgyal po thob pa'i rgyur dkon mchog
NK021(zha)001:1816: gsum la dad pa yang dag pa bskyed 'tshal lo
NK021(zha)001:1817: // de ltar 'jug sgo grub nas dbang bskur ba dngos la dmigs pa 'di bzhin du mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:1818: lha dang slob dpon la gus 'dud byas pas /
NK021(zha)001:1819: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i byin rlabs thams cad
NK021(zha)001:1820: ngo bo rgya yig kun bzang dang bod yig thub
NK021(zha)001:1821: dbang la / rnam pa rgya yig lnga bcu dang bod yig sum cu'i rnam par byon te /
NK021(zha)001:1822: slob dpon dang dbang rdzas rnams la thim /
NK021(zha)001:1823: de nas dbang bskur ba'i tshe bla ma dang //
NK021(zha)001:1824: dbang rten dkyil 'khor dang tsaka li rnams las /
NK021(zha)001:1825: gang bskur ba'i rdzas de dang de mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi rnam par byung ste /
NK021(zha)001:1826: so so rang rang la thim pas dgos 'dod thams
NK021(zha)001:1827: cad yid bzhin du 'grub par gyur snyam pa'i mos
NK021(zha)001:1828: pa mdzod / ces brda sbyar la /
NK021(zha)001:1829: thog mar lha mi'i chas 'jug gi dbang bcu gcig las /
NK021(zha)001:1830: dang po dbu rgyan bskon te /
NK021(zha)001:1832: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bshin gshegs pa thams cad kyi byin gyis rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:1833: rigs kyi bu la rin po che cod pan gyi
NK021(zha)001:1834: dbang bskur bas rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad las rnam
NK021(zha)001:1835: par rgyal ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:1836: / gnyis pa yum gyi tsakli spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK021(zha)001:1838: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK021(zha)001:1839: cad kyi byin rigs kyi bu la yum gyi phyag
NK021(zha)001:1840: gis reg cing dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i sdug
NK021(zha)001:1841: bsngal thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:1842: gsum pa seng phrug zung gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:1844: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rigs
NK021(zha)001:1845: kyi bu la seng phrug zung gcig gi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:1846: bas rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i
NK021(zha)001:1847: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:1848: bzhi pa glang chen phru gu zung gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:1850: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa //
NK021(zha)001:1851: rigs kyi bu la glang po che'i phru gu zung
NK021(zha)001:1852: gcig gi dbang bskur bas 'jig rten 'degs pa'i stobs
NK021(zha)001:1853: dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:1854: / lnga pa ka shi ka'i ras zung gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:1856: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la na
NK021(zha)001:1857: bza' ka shi ka'i ras kyi dbang bskur bas mkhyen
NK021(zha)001:1858: pa'i ye shes gsal zhing ma 'dres pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:1860: drug pa bum chu spyi bor gtigs shing blud de /
NK021(zha)001:1862: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la bum
NK021(zha)001:1863: rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i bag chags
NK021(zha)001:1864: kyi dri ma byang zhing dag pa'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:1867: don thams cad grub pa zhes pa mi dang lha'i
NK021(zha)001:1868: rgyal po lta bu'i ming mtho ris las grags pa
NK021(zha)001:1871: rigs kyi bu la don thams cad grub pa zhes
NK021(zha)001:1872: bya ba'i ming gi dbang bskur bas shes bya la
NK021(zha)001:1873: ma rmongs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:1874: / brgyad pa rgyan chas gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:1876: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la rgyan
NK021(zha)001:1877: gyi bye brag gi dbang bskur bas 'gro ba thams
NK021(zha)001:1878: cad kyi sems shes pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK021(zha)001:1879: gyur cig / dgu pa yig shing gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:1881: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la yig
NK021(zha)001:1882: shing gi dbang bskur bas chos kyi sgra sgrog pa'i
NK021(zha)001:1883: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:1884: bcu pa mda' gzhu gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:1886: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la gnam
NK021(zha)001:1887: ru zung gcig gi dbang bskur bas snyan pa'i sgra
NK021(zha)001:1888: sgrog cing bdud dpung 'dul ba'i 'phongs rtsal dang ldan
NK021(zha)001:1889: par gyur cig / bcu gcig pa btsun mo gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:1891: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la btsun
NK021(zha)001:1892: mo'i dbang bskur bas bstan pa'i rigs mi nub cing
NK021(zha)001:1893: ji ltar 'dul ba de bzhin du 'gro ba'i don
NK021(zha)001:1894: byed pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:1895: de ltar dga' ldan du byams pa rgyal tshab tu dbang bskur ba nas /
NK021(zha)001:1896: btsun mo'i 'khor gyis dgyes par rol pa'i bar te /
NK021(zha)001:1897: gzhon nu don thams cad grub pa khyim na spyod
NK021(zha)001:1898: pa'i rnam thar dang rjes su mthun pa'i dbang bcu
NK021(zha)001:1899: gcig bskur bas / mtho ris kyi rten phun sum
NK021(zha)001:1900: tshogs pa la bdag gir spyod pa'i skal ba can
NK021(zha)001:1902: de nas mngon mtho'i rten sgrub byed blang dor gyi
NK021(zha)001:1903: gnas shes pa ni thos bsam la rag las shing
NK021(zha)001:1904: / de yang yi ge'i tha snyad la brten dgos
NK021(zha)001:1905: pas na lha mi'i dbang gi gtso bo +aa li
NK021(zha)001:1906: k+aa li'i yi ge'i dbang bskur ba las /
NK021(zha)001:1907: rgya yig lnga bcu'i gzugs rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:1909: rang bzhin thams cad stong par ston //
NK021(zha)001:1910: ka ni bya ba'i ye shes te //
NK021(zha)001:1911: las kyis thams cad grol bar ston /
NK021(zha)001:1912: kha ni khyab par byed pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1913: mi dmigs thams cad grol bar ston //
NK021(zha)001:1914: ga ni don du 'gyur ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1915: yul med thams cad grol bar ston //
NK021(zha)001:1916: g+ha ni gnas pa'i sgo yin te //
NK021(zha)001:1917: gcig tu ma nges grol bar ston //
NK021(zha)001:1918: nga ni 'dzin pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1919: 'dzin bral thams cad grol bar ston //
NK021(zha)001:1920: tsa ni 'gag pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1921: cir yang snang ba thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1922: tsha ni 'da' ba med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1923: 'bral ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1924: dza ni ma byung ba yi sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1925: mi gnas pas ni thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1926: dz+ha ni rnyog pa bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1927: dri ma dag pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1928: nya ni spyod dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1929: bya ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1930: ta ni nga rgyal med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1931: ri bo med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1932: tha ni sgyu rtsal med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1933: byed pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1934: da ni 'dres pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1935: rtsod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1936: d+ha ni bslu ba med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1937: sgyu ma thams cad grol bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:1938: na ni kun tu 'gyur ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1939: g.yo ba bskyod pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1940: ta ni tha snyad med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1941: brjod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1942: tha ni rten dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1943: gnas pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1944: da ni gtong dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1945: len pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1946: d+ha ni rang bzhin med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1947: mtshan nyid med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1948: na ni yul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1949: 'dzin pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1950: pa ni nges par 'byung ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1951: 'gag pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1952: pha ni dngos po med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1953: ci yang med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1954: ba ni brjod pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1955: brjod pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1956: b+ha ni rdul dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1957: rtog pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1958: ma ni chags pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1959: rtag pa med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1960: ya ni chags pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1961: gos pa med pa'i thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1962: wa ni rgyu rkyen med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1963: 'bras bu med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1964: ra ni skyon dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1965: dor ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1966: la ni blang ba med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1967: yon tan med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1968: sha ni spros pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1969: zhi bas thams cad grol bar byed /
NK021(zha)001:1970: sha ni khur dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1971: lci ba med pas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1972: sa ni yang dag gsang ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1973: nges pas thams cad grol bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:1974: ha ni rgyu dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1975: rkyen dang bral bas grol bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:1976: k+sha ni khams dang bral ba'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1977: mtshan nyid med pas grol bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:1978: i +ai mthong ba med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1979: gzugs dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1980: u +au thos pa med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1981: sgra dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1982: e ee tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1983: dri dang bral bas grol bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:1984: o oo tshor ba med pa'i sgo //
NK021(zha)001:1985: reg dang bral bas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1987: cir yang snang bas thams cad grol //
NK021(zha)001:1988: ri r+ai dngos dang dngos med dang //
NK021(zha)001:1989: srid dang srid min stong par grol //
NK021(zha)001:1990: li l+ai shes dang shes bya dang //
NK021(zha)001:1991: stong dang snying rje'i bdag po grol //
NK021(zha)001:1992: gsung gi 'dul ba'i dus byung na //
NK021(zha)001:1993: dbyangs kyi yan lag drug cu la //
NK021(zha)001:1994: sogs pa'i sgra skad sna tshogs dang //
NK021(zha)001:1995: yi ge'i gzugs su bstan nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:1996: 'khor ba'i khams su snang bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:1997: ci'i phyir zhe na yi ge ni //
NK021(zha)001:1998: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rang bzhin te //
NK021(zha)001:1999: thugs rje'i rang bzhin yin pas na //
NK021(zha)001:2000: thabs kyi bye brag sna tshogs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:2001: thams cad grol bar mdzad pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:2002: dbang bskur snang ba chen po sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:2003: zhes brjod cing dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:2004: de nas yul tha dad kyi skad dang yi ge
NK021(zha)001:2005: thams cad kyang sangs rgyas kyi mthu'i byin rlabs gang
NK021(zha)001:2007: yul gang dang gang du de dang de'i skad dang
NK021(zha)001:2008: yi ges tha snyad mtshon dgos pa yin pas na
NK021(zha)001:2009: 'dir bod yig gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:2010: k+aa li sum cu'i gzugs rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:2011: ka ni dbang byed sgrol ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:2012: zhes pas khams gsum gyi sems can la dbang byed cing nyon mongs pa sgrol bar byed pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2013: de'i byin rlabs kyis chos sku don gyi gsung gzugs
NK021(zha)001:2014: brnyan du byung ba'i gsung yi ge 'dis thams cad
NK021(zha)001:2015: la dbang byed cing nyon mongs pa sgrol ba'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2017: kha ni khams gsum yongs kyi rgyan //
NK021(zha)001:2019: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyi rgyan du gyur pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2020: de'i byin rlabs kyis chos sku'i gsung gi gzugs brnyan
NK021(zha)001:2021: yi ge 'dis sems can gyi rgyan du gyur te
NK021(zha)001:2022: 'khor ba las sgrol ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK021(zha)001:2023: cig / ga ni ma chags dag par mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:2024: ces pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK021(zha)001:2025: po ci la'ang ma chags shing rnam par dag pa
NK021(zha)001:2026: ste / de'i byin rlabs kyis chos sku'i gsung yi
NK021(zha)001:2027: ge 'dis 'gro ba rnams ci la'ang ma chags shing
NK021(zha)001:2028: rnam par dag pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:2029: ste / / nga ni nga med nga las rgyal //
NK021(zha)001:2030: zhes pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK021(zha)001:2031: po mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing
NK021(zha)001:2032: mtshan ma las rgyal ba yin te /
NK021(zha)001:2033: de'i byin rlabs kyis sems can thams cad chos dbyings
NK021(zha)001:2034: mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las ma g.yos shing mtshan
NK021(zha)001:2035: ma las rgyal ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:2036: / ca ni gnyis med don rtogs te //
NK021(zha)001:2037: zhes pas dus gsum du chos sku bde ba chen
NK021(zha)001:2038: po de mtshan ma dang mtshan med gnyis su med
NK021(zha)001:2039: pa ste / de'i byin rlabs kyis sems can thams
NK021(zha)001:2040: cad mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis su
NK021(zha)001:2041: med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2042: cha ni thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK021(zha)001:2043: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po las thabs
NK021(zha)001:2044: shes gnyis med kyi sprul pa ji snyed cig byung
NK021(zha)001:2046: de'i byin rlabs kyis thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2047: ja ni chos sku dag par mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:2048: ces pas chos sku bag chags kyis ma gos shing
NK021(zha)001:2049: rnam par dag pa yin te de'i byin rlabs kyis
NK021(zha)001:2050: chos sku bag chags kyis ma gos shing dag pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2051: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2052: nya ni chos nyid brdar sha gcod //
NK021(zha)001:2053: ces pas chos nyid rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang 'dra
NK021(zha)001:2054: ba la rig pa'i ye shes rlabs dang 'dra bas
NK021(zha)001:2056: de'i byin rlabs kyis chos nyid kyi rgya mtsho las
NK021(zha)001:2057: rig pa ye shes kyi byin rlabs la dbang ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2058: dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2059: ta ni mkhas pa'i 'od zer can //
NK021(zha)001:2060: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba yin te /
NK021(zha)001:2061: de'i byin rlabs kyis bu rnams kyi sems la snying
NK021(zha)001:2062: rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK021(zha)001:2063: cig / tha ni dkon mchog 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK021(zha)001:2064: zhes pas dus gsum gyi chos sku bde ba chen po la dgongs pa zab mo 'byung ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:2065: de'i byin rlabs kyis chos sku'i dgongs pa zab mo'i
NK021(zha)001:2066: ye shes rtogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:2067: / da ni rgyu 'bras gnyis med la //
NK021(zha)001:2068: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po la rgyu 'bras kyi chos gnyis su med pa yin te /
NK021(zha)001:2069: de'i byin rlabs kyis 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol
NK021(zha)001:2070: te mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang du bde ba'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2072: na ni sdug bsngal med pas bde //
NK021(zha)001:2073: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po la sdug bsngal med cing ngang gis bde ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:2074: de'i byin rlabs kyis 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal gtan spangs
NK021(zha)001:2075: te ngang gis bde ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK021(zha)001:2076: cig / pa ni thams cad bskyed par byed //
NK021(zha)001:2077: ces pas chos sku bde ba chen po las rig pa'i ye shes bskyed pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2078: de'i byin rlabs kyi gsung 'di mthong ba tsam gyis
NK021(zha)001:2079: gzhan rig bskyed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:2080: / pha ni pha rol phyin la gnas //
NK021(zha)001:2081: zhes pas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad kyi pha
NK021(zha)001:2082: rol tu phyin cing mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las
NK021(zha)001:2083: 'das pa ste / de'i byin rlabs kyi 'khor ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2084: sdug bsngal las pha rol tu son nas mya ngan
NK021(zha)001:2085: las 'da' ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2086: ba ni bde ba chen po ste //
NK021(zha)001:2087: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po de mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du bde ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:2088: de'i byin rlabs kyis dngos po dang mtshan ma thams
NK021(zha)001:2089: cad mnyam pa chen po'i ngang du bde ba'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2091: ma ni srid gsum yongs kyi ma //
NK021(zha)001:2092: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po yongs kyi gzhi mar gyur pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2093: de'i byin rlabs kyis srid pa gsum las rgyal zhing
NK021(zha)001:2094: kun gyi gzhi rten du gyur pa'i dbang dang ldan
NK021(zha)001:2095: par gyur cig / tsa ni 'du 'bral med pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:2096: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po ni sku
NK021(zha)001:2097: dang yeshesa dang stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs
NK021(zha)001:2098: pa 'du 'bral med pa'i gnas yin te /
NK021(zha)001:2099: de'i byin rlabs kyis sku dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2100: tsha ni don dam lus la rdzogs //
NK021(zha)001:2101: zhes pas don dam chos kyi sku ni rgyu dang
NK021(zha)001:2102: 'bras bu'i chos thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa yin
NK021(zha)001:2103: te / de'i byin rlabs kyis chos sku'i rgyu 'bras
NK021(zha)001:2104: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dang ldan par
NK021(zha)001:2105: te / gyur cig / dza ni 'bar ba'i yul la gnas //
NK021(zha)001:2106: zhes pas chos sku las thugs rje'i 'od zer 'bar ba'i gnas te /
NK021(zha)001:2107: de'i byin rlabs kyis thugs rje'i 'od zer 'byung ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2108: wa ni mya ngan thams cad 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:2109: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po'i ngang las 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul te /
NK021(zha)001:2110: de'i byin rlabs kyis 'khor ba'i mya ngan thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2111: zha ni gzhal yas bde ba che //
NK021(zha)001:2112: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po thams cad kyi gnas yin te /
NK021(zha)001:2113: de'i byin rlabs kyis gzhal yas khang bde ba chen po'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2114: za ni skye med chos las 'phags //
NK021(zha)001:2115: zhes pas chos thams cad rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2116: de'i byin rlabs kyis chos nyid gsal ba'i ye shes
NK021(zha)001:2117: kyis ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i dbang dang
NK021(zha)001:2119: 'a ni goms pa'i tshogs la brtson //
NK021(zha)001:2120: zhes pas chos sku bde ba chen po'i ngang du
NK021(zha)001:2121: gsung gi tshogs rang bzhin med par sgrog pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2123: ya ni mthar byed pho nya'i bdag /
NK021(zha)001:2124: ces pas chos kyi sku las gzugs sku rnam pa
NK021(zha)001:2125: gnyis byung nas 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang
NK021(zha)001:2127: ra ni gcod byed yul la dbang //
NK021(zha)001:2128: zhes pas ye shes kyis gcod par bya ba'i yul
NK021(zha)001:2129: nyon mongs pa gcod pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK021(zha)001:2130: cig / la ni mnyam nyid sprul pa'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:2131: zhes pas chos nyid mnyam pa nyid las ye shes sprul pa'i sku byung ste /
NK021(zha)001:2132: sems can gyi don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2133: sha ni snang byed mkha' la shar //
NK021(zha)001:2134: zhes pas chos kyi sku las ye shes kyi rol
NK021(zha)001:2135: par shar nas 'gro ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang
NK021(zha)001:2137: sa ni 'khor ba'i rang bzhin te //
NK021(zha)001:2138: zhes pas thugs phyag mtshan sna tshogs byung nas 'gro
NK021(zha)001:2139: ba'i don byed pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:2140: / ha ni thabs mkhas dbyings nas byon //
NK021(zha)001:2141: zhes pas bde ba chen po'i dbyings nas thabs la
NK021(zha)001:2142: mkhas pa'i mdzad spyod bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'gro
NK021(zha)001:2143: don mthar phyin pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:2144: / a ni skye med chos kyi dbyings //
NK021(zha)001:2145: zhes pas rgyu rkyen dang bral ba'i dbyings nas 'gro
NK021(zha)001:2146: ba'i don ma 'gags par shar bas 'gro don mthar
NK021(zha)001:2147: phyin pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2149: de nas lha dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:2150: dkyil 'khor gyi lha las mar me gcig las gnyis
NK021(zha)001:2151: chad kyi rnam par lha so so rim par byon
NK021(zha)001:2152: pa spyi bo nas thim pas rgyud byin gyis brlabs
NK021(zha)001:2153: shing / lha de dang de'i skur lam lam gyur pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:2154: lha tsaka rnams rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:2156: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK021(zha)001:2157: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku
NK021(zha)001:2158: bcom ldan 'das kun rig rnam par snang mdzad ngan
NK021(zha)001:2159: song thams cad sbyong zhing mngon shes dang rdzu 'phrul
NK021(zha)001:2160: ster ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2161: sarba bid a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK021(zha)001:2163: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK021(zha)001:2164: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku mngon par dga' ba'i zhing
NK021(zha)001:2165: khams na bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa sku mdog
NK021(zha)001:2167: g.yon mnyam bzhag mdzad pa'i sku mthong ba'am /
NK021(zha)001:2169: de dran pa tsam gyis sdig sgrib dang ngan 'gro
NK021(zha)001:2170: thams cad sel zhing mtho ris dang thar pa thob
NK021(zha)001:2171: par mdzad de de'i dbang mchog thob par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:2173: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK021(zha)001:2174: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku stong gi lha rgyal ba
NK021(zha)001:2175: sh+aakya thub pa sku mdog gser btso ma lta bu
NK021(zha)001:2176: g.yas sa gnon / g.yon mnyam bzhag lhung bzed can
NK021(zha)001:2177: gang gis sngon sbyin pa'i bsod nams thob pa las
NK021(zha)001:2178: g.yas sa gnon / bsngosa te / bdag mngon par
NK021(zha)001:2179: rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa ni bdag gi 'khor rnam
NK021(zha)001:2180: bzhi 'tsho bas mi brel ba'i smon lam grub pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2181: byin rlabs kyis stong la bsnyen gnas bsrungs pas phyogs
NK021(zha)001:2182: dus gnas skabs thams cad du mu ge'i bskal pa
NK021(zha)001:2183: las thar ba'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:2184: g.yas sa gnon / bsngosa te / cig / na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2185: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK021(zha)001:2186: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku nya'i lha snang ba mtha'
NK021(zha)001:2187: yas sku mdog dmar po mnyam bzhag tshe bum can
NK021(zha)001:2188: de nyid kyis thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab kyi
NK021(zha)001:2189: bsod nams thob pa las bsngosa te /
NK021(zha)001:2190: bdag mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa na bdag
NK021(zha)001:2191: gi 'khor rnams kyis bde ba can gyi zhing khams
NK021(zha)001:2192: su phyir mi ldog pa'i 'phags pa thob par smon
NK021(zha)001:2193: lam grub pa'i byin rlabs kyis nya la bsnyen gnas
NK021(zha)001:2194: bsrungs pas phyogs dus thams cad du mtshon gyi bskal
NK021(zha)001:2195: pa las thar pa'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par
NK021(zha)001:2197: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lha mi'i
NK021(zha)001:2198: gtso bo sprul pa'i sku tshes brgyad kyi lha sman
NK021(zha)001:2199: gyi bla bee d+aur+ya 'od kyi rgyal po sku mdog
NK021(zha)001:2200: mthing ga g.yas mchog sbyin a ru ra /
NK021(zha)001:2201: g.yon mnyam bzhag lhung bzed can /
NK021(zha)001:2202: smon lam gyi mthu las gang gis bdag gis mtshan lan bdun brjod cing phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2204: tshes brgyad la bsnyen gnas bsrungs pas phyogs dus thams cad du rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2209: nad kyi bskal pa las thar pa'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2211: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa /
NK021(zha)001:2212: nyi ma shar ba shar gyi phyogs //
NK021(zha)001:2213: shar phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang //
NK021(zha)001:2214: gang zag chos ldan rnams skyong bar 'dzam bu gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK021(zha)001:2215: dri za'i rgyal po yul 'khor srung gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2217: mchod 'os rnams kyi nyi ma 'phel ba lho yi phyogs /
NK021(zha)001:2218: lho phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang /
NK021(zha)001:2219: gang zag chos ldan rnams skyong bar dzam bu gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK021(zha)001:2220: grul bum gyi rgyal po 'phags skyes po'i dbang dam pa thob pa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2221: mchod 'os rnams nyi ma bgrod pa nub kyi phyogs //
NK021(zha)001:2222: nub phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang /
NK021(zha)001:2223: gang zag chos ldan rnams skyong bar dzam+bu gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK021(zha)001:2224: klu'i rgyal po mig mi bzang gi dbang dam pa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2225: mchod 'os rnams kyi nyi ma dbus nas lhun po byang /
NK021(zha)001:2226: byang phyogs mtha' yas kyi thub pa'i chos dang /
NK021(zha)001:2227: gang zag chos ldan rnams skyong bar dzam+bu gling du mnga' gsol ba /
NK021(zha)001:2228: gnod sbyin gyi rgyal po rnam thos sras kyi dbang dam pa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2229: mchod 'os rnams kyi shar na lha'i dbang po brgya
NK021(zha)001:2230: byin dang btsun mo 'gro ba sems can thams cad
NK021(zha)001:2231: la bde ba ster ba de'i dbang dam pa thob
NK021(zha)001:2233: mchod 'os rnams shar gling g.yas na mngags gzhug 'gro
NK021(zha)001:2234: ba kun gyi yid du 'ong ba skye 'gro'i nyon
NK021(zha)001:2235: mongs pa gcod pa de'i dbang dam pa na mo
NK021(zha)001:2236: / mchod 'os rnams kyi shar gling g.yon na pho
NK021(zha)001:2237: nya rab tu myur ba'i shugs can ngan song gsum
NK021(zha)001:2238: gyi sdug bsngal las sgrol ba de'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:2239: / na mo / mchod 'os rnams kyi lho dzam+bu
NK021(zha)001:2240: gling na lha tshangs pa dang btsun mo tshangs ma
NK021(zha)001:2241: 'dod khams kyi sdug bsngal dang bral zhing 'khor ba
NK021(zha)001:2242: gyod khrims dang 'dra ba'i skyon gyis ma gos pa
NK021(zha)001:2243: de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2244: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa lho gling
NK021(zha)001:2245: g.yas na mngags gzhug 'gro ba'i yid du 'ong ba
NK021(zha)001:2246: nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa de'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:2247: pa na mo / mchod 'os rnams kyi lho gling
NK021(zha)001:2248: g.yon na pho nya myur ba'i shugs can ngan song
NK021(zha)001:2249: gsum gyi sdug bsngal las sgrol ba de'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:2250: pa na mo / pa na mo / mchod 'os
NK021(zha)001:2251: rnams kyi nub na lha khyab 'jug dang btsun mo
NK021(zha)001:2252: dpal lha mo 'phrin las kyis kun tu khyab pa
NK021(zha)001:2253: de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2254: mchod 'os rnams nub gling g.yas na mngags gzhug rdo
NK021(zha)001:2255: rje bde bas nyon mongs pa gcod pa de'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2257: mchod 'os rnams kyi nub gling g.yon na pho nya
NK021(zha)001:2258: rdo rje sde dpon 'gro ba la chos kyi 'khor
NK021(zha)001:2259: lo bskor ba de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2260: mchod 'os rnams kyi byang na lha dbang phyug chen
NK021(zha)001:2261: po dang btsun mo dka' thub pa zlog ma dug
NK021(zha)001:2262: gsum 'joms par byed pa de'i dbang dam pa na
NK021(zha)001:2263: mo / mchod 'os rnams byang gling g.yas na mngags
NK021(zha)001:2264: gzhug rdo rje rnon po 'gro ba'i nyon mongs gcod
NK021(zha)001:2265: par mdzad pa de'i dbang dam pa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2266: mchod 'os rnams kyi mchod gnas dam pa /
NK021(zha)001:2267: byang gling g.yon na pho nya drang srong khros pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2268: cha byad can 'gro ba kun la rnam par snang
NK021(zha)001:2269: ba de'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2271: de ltar lha mi'i theg pa'i dbang bskur bas mdo
NK021(zha)001:2272: rang lugs kyi tshogs lam dang po 'dun pa sems
NK021(zha)001:2273: pa'i rnal 'byor 'gyur ba ma nges pa'i sa non
NK021(zha)001:2274: pa dang rigs 'dra'i yon tan gsos thebs pas /
NK021(zha)001:2275: rkyen 'gyur las kyi bag chags rags pa dag /
NK021(zha)001:2276: ngan song du skye 'gyur las thar bar byas //
NK021(zha)001:2277: rnam grol gyi theg pa'i sgor 'jug pa'i byang chub kyi sems g.yo ba'i stegs su gyur /
NK021(zha)001:2278: mngon mtho'i rten khyad par can thob nges pa'i skal pa can du byas pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:2279: rjes kyi bya ba la spyi don gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:2282: gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid gdab pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:2283: spyi don dang po lam khyer la bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:2284: dang po theg pa lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:2288: 'jug sgo lta ba tshul khrims dang //
NK021(zha)001:2289: sgom pa phrin las 'bras bu rnams //
NK021(zha)001:2290: rim pa bzhin du shes bya ste //
NK021(zha)001:2293: ngan song gi sdug bsngal la 'jigs nas mtho ris
NK021(zha)001:2294: kyi bde 'bras 'dod pas mi dge bcu spong ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2296: de la mi dge bcu ni /
NK021(zha)001:2297: lus kyi las srog gcod pa /
NK021(zha)001:2309: lus kyi dbye ba rnam gsum ste //
NK021(zha)001:2310: ngag gi dbye ba rnam pa bzhi //
NK021(zha)001:2311: yid kyi rab tu dbye ba gsum //
NK021(zha)001:2312: mi dge bcu ru de dag 'dod //
NK021(zha)001:2316: las rgyu 'bras la yid ches pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2317: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK021(zha)001:2318: 'jig rten pa yi yang dag lta //
NK021(zha)001:2319: chen po gang la yod gyur pa //
NK021(zha)001:2320: de ni tshe rabs stong du yang //
NK021(zha)001:2324: mi dge bcu spong gi gtan khrims sam /
NK021(zha)001:2325: dus khrims yan lag brgyad pa'i gso sbyong ngo //
NK021(zha)001:2327: spyir rang gi 'bras bu 'byin nus kyi bar du goms par byed pa yin la /
NK021(zha)001:2328: bye brag khams gong mar skye ba la /
NK021(zha)001:2329: rang rang gi 'og ma la rags par lta zhing /
NK021(zha)001:2330: rang sa la zhi bar lta bas /
NK021(zha)001:2331: sa 'og ma'i chags pa bral byed kyi lam tshad med bzhi dang /
NK021(zha)001:2333: gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug brgyad sgom pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:2335: zag pa dang bcas pa'i dge bcu'i las lam 'khor bcas la spyod pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2337: sems can gyi srog skyob pa /
NK021(zha)001:2339: tshul khrims bsrung ba dang gsum /
NK021(zha)001:2340: ngag gi bden par smra ba /
NK021(zha)001:2342: zhi zhing des par smra ba /
NK021(zha)001:2343: gzhan gyi yon tan brjod pa dang bzhi /
NK021(zha)001:2346: las 'bras la yid ches bskyed pa dang gsum mo //
NK021(zha)001:2348: dge ba'i las stobs che chung gis gling bzhi'i mi dang 'dod lha ris drug ste /
NK021(zha)001:2349: mthar thug mi'i 'khor los sgyur rgyal dang /
NK021(zha)001:2350: 'dod lha'i gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi bdag po'i bar bgrod cing /
NK021(zha)001:2351: gzugs la chags bral ma thob cing bsam gtan bzhi'i ro la chags pas gzugs khams kyi lha dang /
NK021(zha)001:2352: gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug ming bzhi la ldan pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2353: ting nge 'dzin la bdag tu bzung bas gzugs med
NK021(zha)001:2354: skye mched mu bzhi'i lhar skye ba yin no //
NK021(zha)001:2355: gnyis pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:2356: ngan song sbyong ba'i lha rnam snang /
NK021(zha)001:2357: zhing sbyong ba'i lha mi 'khrugs pa /
NK021(zha)001:2358: dus bzang gsum las stong gi lha sh+aaka thub /
NK021(zha)001:2360: tshes brgyad kyi lha sman bla ste /
NK021(zha)001:2361: lha de dag dran zhing mos pas rgyal ba'i bka' las mi 'da' bar bslab par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:2362: gsum pa snying po lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:2367: sman bla'i b+hee sha dz+ye'i gzungs rnams bzla zhing /
NK021(zha)001:2368: gzungs mi shes na lha so so'i mtshan nas brjod pa'i skyabs 'gro la 'bad do //
NK021(zha)001:2369: de yang dus bzang gi lha gsum ni dus de
NK021(zha)001:2370: dang de'i tshe snga dro gso sbyong blangs nas so
NK021(zha)001:2371: so'i lam khyer gnyis la bslab pa yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:2372: rgyun du rnam snang dang mi 'khrugs pa'i lam khyer la gtso bor dril bas chog go //
NK021(zha)001:2373: bzhi pa bslab bya lam du khyer ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:2374: spyir ngo tsha khrel yod kyis kun nas bslangs te
NK021(zha)001:2375: lus ngag gi bya ba ya rabs kyi tshul dang
NK021(zha)001:2376: mthun pa'i spyod pa gsum la bslab dgos te /
NK021(zha)001:2378: bkur bar 'os pa legs khur zhing //
NK021(zha)001:2379: mgon med rnams la lhag par byams //
NK021(zha)001:2380: byas la drin lan mi brjed pa //
NK021(zha)001:2381: dam pa rnams kyi mdzad spyod yin //
NK021(zha)001:2383: khyad par mi chos bcu drug bslab ste /
NK021(zha)001:2385: dkon mchog gsum la dad pa skyo ngal med par byed pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2386: don dam par dam pa'i chos btsal ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2387: gtsug lag bzang po la mkhas par slob pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:2388: ci la'ang dran cing tshod zin pa bya ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2389: ma bcol ba'i las la gtogs 'dod mi byed pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2390: mig mtho sar blta zhing gong ma rnams kyi rjes snyeg pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2391: dus gsum gyi pha ma la drin lan bslan pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2392: phu nu dang pha tshan nang du shongs yangs che ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2393: rim pa rgan pa la bkur bsti bya ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2394: khyim mtshes la byams par bya ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2395: gnyen grogs kyi dge bshes la dka' las kyi phan 'dogs pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2396: srid kyis 'brel ba'i nye ring la chab gang mthar dbyung ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2397: rig byed bzo la mkhas pas gzhan la phan pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2398: ltos pa'i mi drin gyis skyabs 'og tu gzhug pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2399: ngan byed kyi gros bkag nas rgyal khams bde yangs kyi gros gzhi 'ding ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2400: las mtha' chos la gtad de phyi mar bu smad kyis byang chub kyi gzhi thob par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:2401: zhes pa ltar mi'i chos lugs gtsang ma la bslab par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:2402: spyi don gnyis pa 'gag drug bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2404: gang du gang gi gang la ci phyir dgos //
NK021(zha)001:2405: 'di ni lha mi'i theg pa'i 'gag drug yin //
NK021(zha)001:2407: gang du bshad pa'i gnas ni /
NK021(zha)001:2408: chu bo nee r+aany+dza na'i 'gram du'o //
NK021(zha)001:2409: gang gis bshad pa'i ston pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2410: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thub pa chen po'o //
NK021(zha)001:2412: byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad grub pa la'o //
NK021(zha)001:2413: gang bshad pa'i theg pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2414: mngon par mtho ba lha mi'i theg pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:2416: +aa li k+ai li'i yi ge'i dbang bskur bas ngan
NK021(zha)001:2417: 'gro las thar nas mtho ris kyi rten thob pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2418: ched du'o // de ltar bstan pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2419: rnam grol gyi theg pa'i lam stegs su 'gro ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK021(zha)001:2420: spyi don gsum pa gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid ni /
NK021(zha)001:2421: rang gi spyi bor zla ba'i dkyil 'khor nya gang
NK021(zha)001:2422: ba'i steng na bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa rtag
NK021(zha)001:2424: de nyid yang dang yang du gsal gdab cing rjes
NK021(zha)001:2425: su dran pa'i sgo nas rang gi bya byed kyi
NK021(zha)001:2426: blang dor thams cad des bstan pa'i bka' las mi
NK021(zha)001:2427: 'da' bar bslab par bya'o zhes dran pa dang shes
NK021(zha)001:2429: de nas sems can thams cad bde ba tshad med
NK021(zha)001:2430: pa dang ldan par gyur cig snyam du dran pa
NK021(zha)001:2431: rtse gcig la mnyam par 'jog pa sogs tshad med
NK021(zha)001:2433: de nas ngang sgom chung ngu nas 'byung ba ltar bsam gzugs kyi ting nge 'dzin sgom ste /
NK021(zha)001:2435: 'dod yon gyi nyes dmigs dang bsam gtan gyi phan yon shes par byas nas /
NK021(zha)001:2436: stan bde ba la lus gnad g.yo med du bcings /
NK021(zha)001:2437: dmigs pa'i gnad sems phyir mi g.yeng bar nang du
NK021(zha)001:2438: glan te dmigs pa la dang por rtse gcig tu
NK021(zha)001:2439: 'jog / de nas rnam rtog skyer mi 'jug par de nyid kyi steng du ma bcos par 'jog /
NK021(zha)001:2440: de ltar sems gnas pa'i thabs dgu sogs shes par byas nas mnyam par bzhag pas /
NK021(zha)001:2441: 'dod yon la chags sdang dang bral ba'i ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2442: lus sems la shin sbyangs thob pa'i dga' bde skye zhing /
NK021(zha)001:2443: 'dod yon phra mos gos ma gos kyi rtog dpyod dang bcas pa ste bsam gtan dang po'o //
NK021(zha)001:2444: de nyid brtan nas nang du shes pa rang lugs su bzhag ste bskyangs pas /
NK021(zha)001:2445: sngar gyi rtog dpyod kyi zhen pa nub cing lus
NK021(zha)001:2446: sems la dga' bde sngar las lhag pa skyes pa
NK021(zha)001:2448: de nas dga' ba la zhen med kyi rnal 'byor
NK021(zha)001:2449: sgoms pas lus kyi dga' bde'i zhen pa nub nas
NK021(zha)001:2450: sems bde g.yo med kyis khyab pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:2452: de nas sems kyi bde ba la chags zhen med
NK021(zha)001:2453: pa'i rnal 'byor btang snyoms yongs su dag pa dang
NK021(zha)001:2454: / dran pa yongs su dag pa can bsgoms pas
NK021(zha)001:2455: rlung gi g.yo ba 'gags shing bde ba'i zhen pa
NK021(zha)001:2456: nub nas sems gsal dwangs la rtse gcig tu gnas
NK021(zha)001:2457: / pa ni / bsam gtan bzhi pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:2458: de ltar slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas /
NK021(zha)001:2459: tshad med bzhi dang bsam gtan bzhi //
NK021(zha)001:2460: rim pas so sor bdag 'dzin cing //
NK021(zha)001:2461: gzugs rnams kun la bdag tu rtog /
NK021(zha)001:2462: 'di ni tshangs gnas rim par skye //
NK021(zha)001:2464: de nas bsam gtan bzhi'i 'du shes la yid byung nas /
NK021(zha)001:2465: gzugs med pa'i snyoms 'jug bzhi sgom ste /
NK021(zha)001:2466: de la gzugs snang sna tshogs pa 'di dag nam
NK021(zha)001:2467: mkha' dang 'dra ba'o zhes snang med kyi ting nge
NK021(zha)001:2468: 'dzin la rtse gcig tu bzhag pas snang ba thams
NK021(zha)001:2469: cad rim gyis nub nas nam mkha' lta bu'i stong
NK021(zha)001:2470: nyid kyi ngang la gnas pa ni nam mkha' mtha'
NK021(zha)001:2471: yas so // de las 'das nas sems rang gi
NK021(zha)001:2472: ngo bo la g.yo med du bzhag pas sngar gyi
NK021(zha)001:2473: stong 'dzin gyi 'du shes de yang nub nas rnam
NK021(zha)001:2474: shes rig tsam mtha' dbus med pa la gnas pa
NK021(zha)001:2475: ni rnam shes mtha' yas so //
NK021(zha)001:2476: de nas rnam shes kyi ngo bo yang stong nyid
NK021(zha)001:2477: dngos med ci yang med pa'o zhes rtse gcig tu
NK021(zha)001:2478: bsgoms pas rnam shes kyi 'dzin pa'ang rim gyis nub
NK021(zha)001:2479: nas gzugs sems kyi mtshan ma cung zad kyang med
NK021(zha)001:2480: pa'i ngang la gnas pa ni ci yang med pa'o
NK021(zha)001:2481: // de nas 'das dang chos gang la'ang yod pa
NK021(zha)001:2482: dang med pa'i 'dzin pa dor te ci yang yid
NK021(zha)001:2483: la mi byed pa rtsol med du bzhag pas /
NK021(zha)001:2484: ci yang med pa'i 'dzin pa'ang grol nas 'jig rten
NK021(zha)001:2485: pa'i mi rtog rab kyi rtse mor phyin pa ni
NK021(zha)001:2487: de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK021(zha)001:2488: mnyam dang gzugs med ma rtogs nas //
NK021(zha)001:2489: ming gzhi med par ma shes te //
NK021(zha)001:2490: skye mched bzhi la gnas gyur na //
NK021(zha)001:2491: srid pa'i rtse mo'i sa ru skye //
NK021(zha)001:2494: 'jig rten dang po bsam gtan bzhi //
NK021(zha)001:2495: snyoms 'jug bzhi gol sa dgu ste //
NK021(zha)001:2496: zhes pas bsam gzugs brgyad kyi steng du 'dod khams
NK021(zha)001:2497: kyi sa gcig ste gol sa dgur lam rim du
NK021(zha)001:2498: gsungs mod / de lta na'ang 'jig rten las 'das
NK021(zha)001:2499: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi rten du 'gyur ba mi
NK021(zha)001:2500: gsungs mod / 'gal zhing / khyad par du'ang lam
NK021(zha)001:2501: gong ma'i yon tan gyi rten du 'gro ba la
NK021(zha)001:2502: bsam gtan bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin bzang bas de nyid
NK021(zha)001:2504: de la spyir mdo dbang thos pa'i shes rab can la dbang bskur du byed pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2505: bsam pa'i shes rab can la bshad par byed pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2506: sgom pa'i shes rab can la khrid du 'debs pa'i phyag bzhes ltar las /
NK021(zha)001:2507: da res 'dir dbang gtso bor byas pas zhar byung du gzhan gnyis sbrel ba'i lugs te /
NK021(zha)001:2508: tshul des lha mi'i theg pa'i dbang bskur man ngag dang bcas pa legs par grub pas /
NK021(zha)001:2509: de ltar gdams pa'i don rnams las nam yang mi 'da' bar bsgrub par bagyi'o snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:2510: gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blangs /
NK021(zha)001:2512: deng nas brtsams te sogs dang /
NK021(zha)001:2513: dge ba bsngo ba sngar ltar byas rjes slob ma rnams ci bder btang /
NK021(zha)001:2514: de nas rjes chog rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:2515: man ngag rtsa ba ma 'chugs shing //
NK021(zha)001:2516: brjod bdes legs brgyan dbang chog khrigs //
NK021(zha)001:2517: bklag pa tsam gyis phyag bzhes chos //
NK021(zha)001:2518: rtogs byed legs bshad ngo mtshar dpal //
NK021(zha)001:2519: lha mi'i theg pa'i dbang chog gi le tshan no //
NK021(zha)001:2523: nyer zhi rdo rje rin po che'i //
NK021(zha)001:2524: gling du sgrol mdzad ded dpon la //
NK021(zha)001:2525: gus btud nyan thos dbang chog bshad //
NK021(zha)001:2526: da ni gnyis pa nyan thos kyi theg pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:2527: dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa sgrub thabs ltar grub rjes /
NK021(zha)001:2529: slob dpon bdag nyid sh+aaka thub tu mos pa'i spyi bor rin po che 'bar ba /
NK021(zha)001:2530: de'i 'od kyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang phyogs bcu'i
NK021(zha)001:2531: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i byin rlabs 'od zer
NK021(zha)001:2532: gyi rnam par bsdus te rang la thim pas rjes
NK021(zha)001:2534: yang spyi bo'i 'od kyis bskul bas dkyil 'khor la
NK021(zha)001:2535: bkod pa'i ston pa sangs rgyas 'khor 'phags pa nyan
NK021(zha)001:2536: thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mar me gcig
NK021(zha)001:2537: las gnyis chad kyi rnam par byon pa spyi bo
NK021(zha)001:2538: nas thim pa'i byin rlabs kyis sdug bsngal dang kun
NK021(zha)001:2539: 'byung 'gags na / 'gog lam gyi yon tan khyad par can rgyud la skyes par bsam pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:2540: de nas slob ma gzhug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2542: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad /
NK021(zha)001:2543: sems bskyed dang chos nyan pa'i kun spyod gsal 'debs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK021(zha)001:2544: 'dir gang gsan par bya ba'i chos ni /
NK021(zha)001:2546: thog mar mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2547: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil
NK021(zha)001:2548: 'khor / zhes pa'i bar lha mi'i dbang ltar las /
NK021(zha)001:2549: rgyas bsdus skabs thob kyi spro bsdu byas rjes /
NK021(zha)001:2550: gnyis pa nyan thos kyi theg pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK021(zha)001:2552: slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams sngar song nas /
NK021(zha)001:2553: khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:2555: de ltar man+dala phul nas gsol ba gdab pa'i slad du /
NK021(zha)001:2556: 'gog bden dang lam bden gyis bsdus pa'i don dam
NK021(zha)001:2557: pa'i dkon mchog gsum la yid ches kyi dad pa
NK021(zha)001:2558: bskyed nas / de mtshon byed dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i ston pa sangs rgyas dang /
NK021(zha)001:2560: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun dang bcas pa rnams la yan
NK021(zha)001:2561: lag lnga sa la phab pa'i phyag lan gsum mdzad
NK021(zha)001:2563: de nas slob dpon ston pa thub pa'i dbang por
NK021(zha)001:2564: gsal ba'i gtsug tor gyi rtse mor nor bu rin
NK021(zha)001:2565: po che 'od zer mtha' yas par 'phro ba las
NK021(zha)001:2566: rang gi 'dod dgu ma lus pa 'byung bar mos
NK021(zha)001:2567: la snyims pa me tog dang bcas pas thal mo
NK021(zha)001:2569: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK021(zha)001:2570: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnam sbyong ba //
NK021(zha)001:2571: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen gter //
NK021(zha)001:2572: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin gsol //
NK021(zha)001:2574: de nas sdom pa 'bogs pa'i cho ga ni /
NK021(zha)001:2575: slob dpon la phyag gsum btsal nas pus btsugs thal sbyar gyis 'dug tu bcug ste /
NK021(zha)001:2576: khyed cag nyan thos kyi theg pa'i sgor 'jug pa la /
NK021(zha)001:2578: tshul gnas thos dang bsam ldan pa //
NK021(zha)001:2579: bsgom pa la ni rab tu sbyar //
NK021(zha)001:2580: zhes gsungs pa ltar yon tan gyi gzhi rten du
NK021(zha)001:2581: so so thar pa'i sdom pa blang ba gal che
NK021(zha)001:2582: / des bla ma 'ga' zhig gi phyag bzhes su
NK021(zha)001:2583: 'dul ba rang gzhung ltar gyi tshigs gsum 'bogs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2584: las chog rgyas par mdzad pa byung na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:2585: bsgrub bya nyid rab tu byung ba 'dod cing nus pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2586: las grwa sogs mthun rkyen 'dzom na skabs 'dir nyan
NK021(zha)001:2587: thos rang lugs kyi cho ga'i sgos chos sbyar na
NK021(zha)001:2588: 'gal ba med pa la dgongs pa yin mod kyi
NK021(zha)001:2589: / de lta na'ang 'dir slob dpon dang slob ma
NK021(zha)001:2590: gnyis ka rten rab tu byung ba dang khyim pa
NK021(zha)001:2591: la mtha' gcig tu ma nges pas na /
NK021(zha)001:2592: phyag bzhes zhib tu re ba de nyid legs pa ma yin zhing /
NK021(zha)001:2593: de bas na yig rnying rnams kyi dgongs pa ltar /
NK021(zha)001:2594: cho ga'i rnam bzhag nyan thos dang tshul 'dra rung
NK021(zha)001:2595: tsam gyi tshigs gsum gyi dod yod pa tsam las
NK021(zha)001:2596: / cho ga rang gi ngo bo theg chen so
NK021(zha)001:2597: thar thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs su mdzad pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2599: de ltar sgrub par byed pa la /
NK021(zha)001:2600: spyir nyan rang gi theg pa'i bsam pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2601: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las thar 'dod kyi zhi bde don gnyer te /
NK021(zha)001:2602: skyes bu 'bring po'i blo yin na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:2603: da res bsam pa yar ldan du byas te /
NK021(zha)001:2604: sems can thams cad kyi don du mtha' gnyis la
NK021(zha)001:2605: mi gnas pa'i myang 'das thob par bya ba'i ched
NK021(zha)001:2606: du thog mar dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa blang snyam
NK021(zha)001:2607: pas / phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang
NK021(zha)001:2608: byang chub sems dpa' 'phags pa nyan thos thams cad
NK021(zha)001:2609: pas / dang / slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:2610: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas dus 'di nas bzung
NK021(zha)001:2611: ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du rkang gnyis rnams kyi
NK021(zha)001:2612: mchog / sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK021(zha)001:2613: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:2617: bdag ji srid 'tsho'i bar du dge bsnyen du bzung du gsol /
NK021(zha)001:2620: de nas rab tu byung ba'i thog mar bar chad dri ba'i dod /
NK021(zha)001:2621: khyed cag bstan pa'i sgor rab tu dbyung ba la /
NK021(zha)001:2622: sdom pa skye ba'i 'gal rkyen du gyur pa'i bar chad gang yang ma mchis sam /
NK021(zha)001:2624: gzhan gyis len du bcug pa ma yin nam /
NK021(zha)001:2625: rang gzhan gyi don gnyis bsgrub pa'i phyir rab tu byung bar 'dod dam /
NK021(zha)001:2626: zhes pa'i lan du rim par /
NK021(zha)001:2629: 'dod lags zhes brjod du gzhug go //
NK021(zha)001:2630: khyed rnams rab tu dbyung ba la /
NK021(zha)001:2631: spyir dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK021(zha)001:2632: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2633: byang chub sems dpa' spyod pa rnam par dag pa la 'di skad ces bka' stsal to //
NK021(zha)001:2634: skyes bu dam pa khyod gnyis kyis khyim bdag 'di
NK021(zha)001:2635: rnams rab tu phyungs la bsnyen par rdzogs par gyis
NK021(zha)001:2636: shig / ces bcom ldan 'das kyis gnang nas /
NK021(zha)001:2637: byang chub sems dpa' byams pas khyim bdag dgu stong rab tu phyung ngo //
NK021(zha)001:2638: byang chub sems dpa' spyod pa rnam par dag pas khyim bdag bdun stong rab tu phyung ngo //
NK021(zha)001:2639: zhes gsungs pa ltar byams pa dang 'jam dbyangs khyim
NK021(zha)001:2640: pa'i cha lugs su bzhugs pas bsgrub bya khyim pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2641: gzugs ma bsgyur bar rab byung bsnyen rdzogs phog pa
NK021(zha)001:2642: ltar 'dir yang de dag dang rjes su mthun par
NK021(zha)001:2643: 'bogs byed slob dpon dang bsgrub bya slob ma gnyis
NK021(zha)001:2644: ka rab byung dang khyim pa gos dkar can la
NK021(zha)001:2645: mtha' ma bkag pas na theg chen thun mong ma
NK021(zha)001:2646: yin pa'i lugs su snang zhing /
NK021(zha)001:2647: rgyu mtshan des rtags bsgyur ba la ched du ma ltos mod /
NK021(zha)001:2648: 'on kyang sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byon nas de'i
NK021(zha)001:2649: rnam thar gyi rjes su 'jug par mos pa'i rten
NK021(zha)001:2650: tsam du khyim pa yin na'ang rtags ster ba'i dod
NK021(zha)001:2651: tsam zhig mdzad pa'i phyag len ltar /
NK021(zha)001:2653: gos dang snod spyad kyi rtags rnams blangs nas ston
NK021(zha)001:2654: pa sangs rgyas kyi rjes su 'jug par bagyi'o snyam
NK021(zha)001:2657: bstan pa la dga' ba'i lha rnams dgyes pa bskyed du gsol /
NK021(zha)001:2659: dkon mchog gsum las gras pa'i ming btags /
NK021(zha)001:2660: de nas bla gos dang thang gos 'ding ba rnams gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:2661: ji ltar bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa /
NK021(zha)001:2663: sh+aakya'i rgyal po gtso bo de rab tu byung ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2664: na bza' dur smrig gi chos gos 'di khyod la
NK021(zha)001:2665: bskon gyi / khyod kyis 'phangs shing gces pa'i tshad mig gi 'bras bu ltar gyis la /
NK021(zha)001:2666: mi 'bral ba'i tshad sha dang rus pa ltar gyis la gyon zhig /
NK021(zha)001:2667: khyod kyi gos kyi bya ba gyis la bag yod par spyod cig /
NK021(zha)001:2669: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:2670: skal ldan khyod la na bza' dur smrig gi rgyal
NK021(zha)001:2671: mtshan 'di gtad pas tshe rabs kun tu ngo tsha
NK021(zha)001:2672: khrel yod kyi gos gyon te /
NK021(zha)001:2673: tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i rgyan dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2674: lhung bzed dang chu tshags gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:2675: ji ltar bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa mngon par
NK021(zha)001:2676: rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa de'i zas kyi bya ba
NK021(zha)001:2677: byed pa'i lhung bzed chu tshags dang bcas pa 'di
NK021(zha)001:2678: khyod la gtad pas srog chags la mi gnod pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2679: sgo nas zas kyi bya ba legs par gyis shig
NK021(zha)001:2681: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden skal ldan khyod la lhung
NK021(zha)001:2682: bzed dang chu tshags gtad pas mu ge'i bskal pa
NK021(zha)001:2685: gzhan yang me tog 'thor bzhin du /
NK021(zha)001:2687: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i tshe dang ldan pa 'di rnams kyi tshul khrims kyi phung po dang /
NK021(zha)001:2688: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang /
NK021(zha)001:2689: shes rab kyi phung po dang /
NK021(zha)001:2690: rnam par grol ba'i phung po dang //
NK021(zha)001:2691: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes gzigs pa'i phung po yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2693: de ltar ming dang rtags spos pa'i dgos pa'ang bsam pa barje ba yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:2694: 'khor ba 'di thams cad sdug bsngal gyi gnas me'i
NK021(zha)001:2695: 'obs lta bur gyur pa las rang gzhan sems can
NK021(zha)001:2696: thams cad bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi gnas
NK021(zha)001:2698: de'i ched du khyim gyi 'du 'dzi las rab tu dbyung bar bya'o snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:2699: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' /
NK021(zha)001:2700: 'phags pa nyan thos thams cad dang slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:2701: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du /
NK021(zha)001:2703: sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK021(zha)001:2704: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:2705: chos la skyabs tshogs rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:2706: dge 'dun la sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa /
NK021(zha)001:2708: sh+aakya'i rgyal po gtso bo de rang tu byung ba'i rjes su slob par 'tshal gyis /
NK021(zha)001:2709: bdag rab tu dbyung du gsol /
NK021(zha)001:2712: de nas rang gzhan thams cad 'khor ba las rnam
NK021(zha)001:2713: par grol bar bya ba'i ched du dge tshul gyi
NK021(zha)001:2715: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa rnams kyi gdung gsob par bya'o snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:2716: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang sems dpa' /
NK021(zha)001:2717: 'phags pa nyan thos thams cad dang /
NK021(zha)001:2719: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK021(zha)001:2720: ste ji srid 'tsho ba'i bar du rkang gnyis rnams
NK021(zha)001:2721: kyi mchog / sangs rgyas la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK021(zha)001:2722: 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:2723: chos la skyabs su tshogs rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:2724: dge 'dun bdag ji srid 'tsho'i bar du dge tshul du bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:2727: de nas so sor thar pa'i sdom pa rnams kyi mchog dge slong gi sdom pa yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:2728: bdag gis mkha' khyab kyi sems can thams cad 'khor
NK021(zha)001:2729: ba las bsgral ba'i ched du dus 'di nas bzung
NK021(zha)001:2730: ste ji srid 'tsho'i bar du nyes spyod spang ba
NK021(zha)001:2731: yongs su rdzogs pa dge slong gi bslab pa yang
NK021(zha)001:2732: dag par blangs te rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi gdung
NK021(zha)001:2734: ston pa sangs rgyas dang chos smra ba'i 'phags pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2735: dge slong gi dge 'dun thams cad tshe dang ldan
NK021(zha)001:2736: pa bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba la dgongs su
NK021(zha)001:2737: gsol // tshe dang ldan pa bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dge slong du bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:2740: des dkon mchog gsum gyi byin rlabs kyis khyod rnams
NK021(zha)001:2741: kyi rgyud la nyes spyod spong ba yongs su rdzogs
NK021(zha)001:2742: pa dge slong gi sdom pa thob pa yin pas
NK021(zha)001:2743: bslab bya mdo tsam bstan na /
NK021(zha)001:2744: da phyin chad khyed rnams kyis dge sbyong gi chos bzhi la bslab par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:2746: gshe yang slar mi gshe ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:2747: khros kyang slar mi khro ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:2748: brdegs kyang slar mi brdeg pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:2749: mtshang brus kyang slar mtshang mi 'bru bar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:2751: 'di ltar lus kyi rtags dang cha lugs la ma
NK021(zha)001:2752: ltos par sems kyi tshangs spyod la slob pas dge
NK021(zha)001:2753: tshul slong du bzhag pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2754: sngar drangs pa ltar dkon brtsegs su gsungs pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:2755: gzhan yang drag shul can gyis zhus pa /
NK021(zha)001:2756: sgyu ma mkhan bzang po lung bstan pa /
NK021(zha)001:2757: 'jam dpal rnam par rol pa'i bu mo gser mchog
NK021(zha)001:2758: 'od dpal lung bstan pa'i skabs rnams nas kyang gsal
NK021(zha)001:2760: 'dul ba lung nyid las kyang grags pa khyim pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2761: rtags la gnas bzhin du dge slong du gsungs pa
NK021(zha)001:2762: ste / rgyan gyis brgyan par byas kyang chos spyod cing //
NK021(zha)001:2763: dul zhing yang dag sdom la tshangs par spyod //
NK021(zha)001:2764: 'byung po kun la chad pa spangs pa de //
NK021(zha)001:2765: dge slong dge sbyong de yin /
NK021(zha)001:2766: zhes gsungs pa lta bu dang /
NK021(zha)001:2767: sa'i snying po'i 'khor lo bcu pa dang 'dul lung mthun par /
NK021(zha)001:2768: khyim pa 'phags pa'i chos dang ldan pa don dam
NK021(zha)001:2769: pa'i dge slong gi khongs su bsdus pa sogs rgyas
NK021(zha)001:2771: de nas chos bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:2772: theg pa 'di'i lugs kyis dkyil 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK021(zha)001:2773: gyis yid skyo nas zhi bde don du gnyer ba
NK021(zha)001:2774: skyes bu 'bring po'i lam yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:2775: bden bzhi la dmigs pa'i blang dor gyi sgo nas bslab dgos /
NK021(zha)001:2776: de la 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal ni nad kyi zug rngu lta bu dang /
NK021(zha)001:2777: kun 'byung ni nad de bskyed byed kyi rgyu lta bu dang /
NK021(zha)001:2778: lam bden ni nad 'joms pa'i gnyen po sman dpyad lta bu dang /
NK021(zha)001:2779: 'gog ba den ni nad las grol ba'i bde ba lta bu yin pas na /
NK021(zha)001:2780: sdug bsngal shes par byas nas /
NK021(zha)001:2782: 'gog bden thob bya'i dmigs yul du byas la /
NK021(zha)001:2783: lam bden bsten byar byed pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2784: bden bzhi la dmigs pa'i las rgyu 'bras kyi blang dor ma nor bar mdzad 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:2787: thog mar lha dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:2788: dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i lha rnams las mar me
NK021(zha)001:2789: gcig las gnyis chad kyi rnam par lha so so
NK021(zha)001:2791: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bo nas thim pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:2793: kun 'byung 'gags te 'gog lam gyi yon tan khyad par can rgyud la skyes pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:2795: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK021(zha)001:2796: dus gsum sangs rgyas ji snyed pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:2797: bcom ldan gtso bo'i dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:2798: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:2799: sdug bsngal bden pa nyer len phung po dang //
NK021(zha)001:2800: kun 'byung bden pa las dang nyon mongs dang //
NK021(zha)001:2801: 'gog pa'i bden pa sdug bsngal zhi ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:2802: lam gyi bden pa gang zag bden med de //
NK021(zha)001:2803: sdug kun spangs nas 'gog lam lhag bcas dang //
NK021(zha)001:2804: lhag med dgra bcom sa la phyin par shog /
NK021(zha)001:2805: sarba sa ni sa ta a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:2807: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:2808: rigs kyi bu la 'gro ba'i gtso bo skye dgu'i bla ma thub pa chen po'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:2809: tshe rabs kun tu sangs rgyas mthong ba dang mi 'bral ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2810: dam pa'i chos thos pa dang mi 'bral ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:2811: 'phags pa'i dge 'dun dang rtag tu mi 'bral ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2812: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:2813: nyan thos bcu drug gi tsakli rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:2815: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:2816: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa kun dga' bo'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2817: bskur bas sangs rgyas kyi zhabs 'bring rtag tu byed
NK021(zha)001:2818: pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2819: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2820: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa sh+aa ri'i bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:2821: shes rab can gyi mchog tu gyur ba'i dbang dam pa mu ne na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2822: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa
NK021(zha)001:2823: moong+gala gyi bu'i dbang bskur bas rdzu 'phrul can gyi
NK021(zha)001:2824: mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne na
NK021(zha)001:2825: mo / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa
NK021(zha)001:2826: rab 'byor gyi dbang bskur bas 'dri zhing lan ldon
NK021(zha)001:2827: pa'i mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne
NK021(zha)001:2828: mo / na mo / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu
NK021(zha)001:2829: la 'phags pa ma 'gags pa'i dbang bskur bas lha'i
NK021(zha)001:2830: mig mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne
NK021(zha)001:2831: mo / na mo / na mo / dkon mchog
NK021(zha)001:2832: rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa 'char ka'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:2833: bas khyim bdag dad pa bskyed pa'i mchog tu gyur
NK021(zha)001:2834: pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2835: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la kun shes koo di
NK021(zha)001:2836: n+ya'i dbang bskur bas thos grol snga ba'i mchog tu
NK021(zha)001:2837: gyur pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2838: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa rta thul
NK021(zha)001:2839: gyi dbang bskur bas spyod lam mdzes pa'i mchog tu
NK021(zha)001:2840: gyur pa'i dbang mu ne na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2841: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa nye ba
NK021(zha)001:2842: 'khor gyi dbang bskur bas 'dul ba 'dzin pa'i mchog
NK021(zha)001:2843: tu gyur pa'i dbang mu ne /
NK021(zha)001:2844: na mo dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la
NK021(zha)001:2845: 'phags pa ba lang bdag gi dbang bskur bas 'gog
NK021(zha)001:2846: pa'i ting nge 'dzin mchog du gyur pa'i dbang mu
NK021(zha)001:2847: ne na mo / dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:2848: bu la 'phags pa 'od srung chen po'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:2849: bas sbyangs pa'i yon tan che ba mchog tu gyur
NK021(zha)001:2850: pa'i dbang mu ne na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2851: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa
NK021(zha)001:2852: sgra gcan zin gyi dbang bskur bas bslab pa la
NK021(zha)001:2853: gus pa mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang mu ne na
NK021(zha)001:2854: mo / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa
NK021(zha)001:2855: gcung dga' bo'i dbang bskur bas mtshan dang dpe byad
NK021(zha)001:2856: mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang mu ne na mo /
NK021(zha)001:2857: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rigs kyi bu
NK021(zha)001:2858: la 'phags pa ming can gyi dbang bskur bas rgyal
NK021(zha)001:2859: ba'i bka' las gus pa mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2861: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa nor sbyin
NK021(zha)001:2862: 'dzin gyi dbang bskur bas dbul ba sel ba'i mchog
NK021(zha)001:2863: tu gyur pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne na mo
NK021(zha)001:2864: / dkon mchog gsum rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa
NK021(zha)001:2865: gang po'i dbang bskur bas yon sbyong ba mchog tu
NK021(zha)001:2866: gyur pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne gnas brtan bcu
NK021(zha)001:2869: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK021(zha)001:2870: gnas kyi bar du skyong bar mdzad pa po 'phags
NK021(zha)001:2871: pa gnas brtan chen po yan lag 'byung gi dbang
NK021(zha)001:2872: bskur bas dam pa chos kyi chab srid 'dzin pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2873: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2874: mu ne mu ne de bzhin du re re'i 'gor /
NK021(zha)001:2876: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rgyal ba'i bstan pa
NK021(zha)001:2877: gnas kyi bar du skyong bar mdzad pa po 'phags
NK021(zha)001:2880: ma pham pa'i nags na gnas kyi dus ldan gyi
NK021(zha)001:2881: rdo rje mo'i bu'i bzang po'i gser be'u'i b+ha ra
NK021(zha)001:2882: d+h+wa dza gser can gyi ba ku la'i sgra gcan
NK021(zha)001:2883: zin gyi lam phran brtan gyi b+ha ra d+h+wa dza
NK021(zha)001:2884: bsod snyoms len gyi lam brtan gyi klu'i sde'i sbed
NK021(zha)001:2885: byed kyi mi phyed pa'i de re re'i mtshan mthar
NK021(zha)001:2886: / dbang bskur bas dam pa chos kyi chab srid 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2888: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la dge tshul tsun+da'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2889: bskur bas rgyal ba rnams mya ngan las mi 'da'
NK021(zha)001:2890: bar gsol ba 'debs pa'i mchog tu gyur pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2891: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2893: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'phags pa'i dge bsnyen
NK021(zha)001:2894: chen po d+harma t+aa'i dbang bskur bas 'phags pa dgra
NK021(zha)001:2895: bcom pa rnams kyi zhabs 'bring rtag tu byed pa'i
NK021(zha)001:2896: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2898: de nas rdzas dbang bcu bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:2899: dang po bum chus bkru zhing blud de /
NK021(zha)001:2901: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la bum rdzas chu'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2902: bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma
NK021(zha)001:2903: byang zhing dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:2904: cig / mu ne gnyis pa sngar btags pa'i ming bcug ste /
NK021(zha)001:2906: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'di zhes bya ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2907: ming gi dbang bskur bas shes bya la ma rmongs
NK021(zha)001:2908: pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne gsum pa shing rta
NK021(zha)001:2910: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la shing rta'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:2911: bas skye rga na 'chi'i sdug bsngal las rab tu
NK021(zha)001:2912: byung nas chos kyi rgyal srid la dbang bskur ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2913: dbang dam pa mu ni bzhi pa chibs pa /
NK021(zha)001:2915: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la chibs kyi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:2916: bas rtag tu rab tu phyungs nas nyon mongs pa
NK021(zha)001:2917: las thar pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne lnga pa
NK021(zha)001:2919: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la shan ral gri'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2920: bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:2921: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2922: mu ne drug pa gseg par /
NK021(zha)001:2924: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la gseg par gyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:2925: bskur bas bdag dang 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin par
NK021(zha)001:2926: rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne bdun pa chos
NK021(zha)001:2928: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la na bza' dur smrig
NK021(zha)001:2929: gi dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i gdung ba las skyob
NK021(zha)001:2930: pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne brgyad pa sbrang rtsi
NK021(zha)001:2932: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la bkra shis kyi rdzas
NK021(zha)001:2933: sbrang rtsi'i dbang bskur bas 'bras bu phun sum tshogs
NK021(zha)001:2934: pa'i dbang dam pa mu ne dgu pa 'bras chan
NK021(zha)001:2936: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la 'o thug 'bras chan
NK021(zha)001:2937: gyi dbang bskur bas mtshan dang dpe byad 'bar ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2938: dbang dam pa mu ne bcu pa r+ts+wa zor ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2940: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la r+ts+wa dar+b+ha'i rdzas kyi
NK021(zha)001:2941: dbang bskur bas bkra shis shing bar chad thams cad
NK021(zha)001:2942: kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:2943: cig / mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:2944: de ltar bum chab kyi dbang sngon du 'gro ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2945: sgo nas nges par 'byung bas khyim spangs te sangs
NK021(zha)001:2946: rgyas pa'i bar gyi ston pa bcom ldan 'das rab
NK021(zha)001:2947: tu byung nas zhi ba brnyes pa'i rnam thar dang
NK021(zha)001:2948: rjes su mthun pa'i dbang bcu bskur bas 'khor ba
NK021(zha)001:2949: las rnam par grol ba'i skal ba can du byas
NK021(zha)001:2950: pa yin no // de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi sku las thugs rje'i 'od zer 'phros /
NK021(zha)001:2951: khyed rang rnams la reg pas lus sems kyi skyon
NK021(zha)001:2952: thams cad sbyangs nas dam pa'i chos kyi snod rung
NK021(zha)001:2953: du byas / yang lha rnams kyi sku'i 'od zer gyis 'phags pa rnams kyi thugs dam bskul /
NK021(zha)001:2954: sems can thams cad kyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:2955: tshur 'dus khyed rang rnams la thim pas mthu thob ste /
NK021(zha)001:2956: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi sku gsung thugs dang mtshungs par byin gyis brlabs pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:2957: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu ne sh+aakya mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:2959: mu ne'i sngags byang gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:2961: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis rigs
NK021(zha)001:2962: kyi bu la chos sgo brgyad khri stong tshang ba'i
NK021(zha)001:2963: snying po'i dbang bskur bas dam pa'i chos kyi mdzod
NK021(zha)001:2964: 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:2966: de ltar nyan thos kyi theg pa'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:2967: mdo rang lugs kyi tshogs lam gnyis pa las dang
NK021(zha)001:2968: po pa'i rnal 'byor rten pa gzhi'i sa non pa
NK021(zha)001:2969: dang rigs 'dra'i yon tan gsos theb pas /
NK021(zha)001:2970: las kyi bag chags phra ba dag /
NK021(zha)001:2971: 'khor ba las rnam par grol ba'i rgyu dang /
NK021(zha)001:2972: lam gong ma la smon pa byang chub kyi sems skye ba'i stegs su gyur /
NK021(zha)001:2974: mthar thug nyan thos dgra bcom gyi rtogs rigs dang
NK021(zha)001:2975: 'dra ba'i yon tan khyad par can thob pa'i skal
NK021(zha)001:2976: pa can du byas pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:2977: rjes kyi bya ba la spyi don gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:2980: gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid gdab pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:2981: spyi don dang po lam khyer la bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:2982: dang po theg pa lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:2983: nyan thos kyi theg pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2986: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs mthong nas rang nyid zhi bde 'dod pas /
NK021(zha)001:2987: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhis bsdus pa'i rnam pa bcu
NK021(zha)001:2988: drug la dmigs pa'i rgyu 'bras spang blang gi sgo
NK021(zha)001:2990: gzung yul dngos po rags snang dang 'dzin pa sems
NK021(zha)001:2991: kyi rgyun 'di rang bzhin med par 'dod pas gang
NK021(zha)001:2992: zag gi bdag med rtogs na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:2993: rags snang rtsom gzhi rdul phran bye smras cha ldan sil bu dang /
NK021(zha)001:2994: mdo sde bas reg la ma 'byar ba'i cha med /
NK021(zha)001:2995: 'dzin sems skad cig ma bye mdo gnyis mthun par dus kyi cha dang bral bar 'dod pas na /
NK021(zha)001:2996: gzung 'dzin phra ba don dam bden par lta bas chos kyi bdag ma rtogs pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:2998: chos tsam lta ba'i nyan thos pa //
NK021(zha)001:2999: mdo sde pa dang bye brag gnyis //
NK021(zha)001:3000: phyi rol rdul la rtsod byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:3001: shes pa skad cig snang byed mthun //
NK021(zha)001:3004: so thar rigs brgyad gang rung ste /
NK021(zha)001:3006: so so thar zhes bya rnam brgyad //
NK021(zha)001:3007: rdzas su rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK021(zha)001:3008: mtshan las ming ni 'pho ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:3009: tha dad de dag 'gal ba med //
NK021(zha)001:3010: spang bya lnga brgyad bcu dang ni /
NK021(zha)001:3011: thams cad spong ba nos pa las //
NK021(zha)001:3012: dge bsnyen dang ni bsnyen gnas dang //
NK021(zha)001:3013: dge tshul che dang dge slong nyid //
NK021(zha)001:3016: nyan thos kyi sde snod thos /
NK021(zha)001:3018: bsam pa'i don sgom pa la 'jug pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:3020: nyon mongs pa gang dang gang shas che ba de dang de'i gnyen por rim bzhin /
NK021(zha)001:3022: zhe sdang la byams snying rje /
NK021(zha)001:3023: gti mug la rten 'brel gyi rab dbye /
NK021(zha)001:3024: rnam rtog la dbugs 'byung rngub bgrang ba /
NK021(zha)001:3025: nga rgyal la khams kyi rnam pa'i rab dbye rnams sgom pas sems las su rung bar byas rjes /
NK021(zha)001:3027: bden bzhi'i rnam pa bcu drug bsgoms pas /
NK021(zha)001:3028: khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa mthong bas spong ba sogs ye shes bcu drug gis spong ste /
NK021(zha)001:3033: rjes bzod de bcu drug go //
NK021(zha)001:3035: sbyangs yon bcu gnyis la gnas pas rang don gtso bor spyod pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3037: lam lnga byang phyogs so bdun gyi rim pas bgrod
NK021(zha)001:3038: pa'i 'phags lam ni dge sbyong gi 'bras bu bzhi
NK021(zha)001:3042: dgra bcom pa ste skyes bu zung bzhi dang /
NK021(zha)001:3043: re re la'ang zhugs gnas gnyis gnyis su phye bas ya brgyad du 'dod do //
NK021(zha)001:3044: de yang nyan thos kyi rtogs bya thams cad 'dir yang rtogs dgos mod /
NK021(zha)001:3045: thob bya rnams ni theg chen gyi gol sa yin pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:3046: lam stegs su mngon du byed dgos pa ma yin no //
NK021(zha)001:3047: gnyis pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:3048: bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i dbang po 'phags pa nyan
NK021(zha)001:3049: thos kyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa mdun du spyan
NK021(zha)001:3050: drangs te / bzhugs pa la dmigs nas phyag mchod 'bul ba sogs kyis tshogs bsag go //
NK021(zha)001:3051: gsum pa snying po lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:3052: lha rnams kyi sku las 'phros pa'i 'od kyis lus
NK021(zha)001:3053: sems kyi skyon sbyangs shing rgyud byin gyis brlabs par
NK021(zha)001:3054: bsams la / mu ne'i gzungs bzla ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:3055: bzhi pa bslab bya lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:3056: mi dge bcu dgra ltar spong zhing /
NK021(zha)001:3057: dge bcu 'chi gsos kyi sman mchog ltar brten par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:3058: de'ang thun mong du 'du shes bcu ste /
NK021(zha)001:3059: srog gcod pa la btsan dug lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3060: nyon mongs pa la dug sbrul lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3061: kha zas la rgan rgon bu sha za ba lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3062: gos la smad dkris lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3063: rnyed bkur la rgya dang rnyi lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3064: bla ma dang dkon mchog la nor bu rin po che lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3065: chos la lam bzang po lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3066: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gser lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3067: tshul khrims la rgyan lta bu'i 'du shes dang /
NK021(zha)001:3068: chos nyid mngon du gyur pa la mun khung du
NK021(zha)001:3069: sgron me bteg pa lta bu'i 'du shes rnams la
NK021(zha)001:3070: bslab par bya'o // spyi don gnyis pa 'gag drug bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3072: gang du gang gis gang la gang bstan pa //
NK021(zha)001:3073: ci'i phyir bshad pa'i dgos pa bcas pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:3074: 'di ni nyan thos theg pa'i 'gag drug yin //
NK021(zha)001:3076: gang du bshad pa'i gnas ni /
NK021(zha)001:3077: w+aa ra n+aa s+ai'i bsil khang du'o //
NK021(zha)001:3078: gang gis bshad pa'i ston pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3079: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3081: nyan thos chen po mchog brgyad dam bcu drug sogs la'o //
NK021(zha)001:3082: gang bstan pa'i theg pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3083: bden bzhis bsdus pa nyan thos kyi theg pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3084: ci'i phyir na bden bzhi'i dbang bskur bas nyan thos
NK021(zha)001:3085: dgra bcom gyi rtogs rigs dang 'dra ba'i yon tan
NK021(zha)001:3087: de ltar bstan pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3088: bdag rtag chad du 'dzin pa zhig pas 'khor ba las nges par 'byin pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3089: spyi don gsum pa gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid la /
NK021(zha)001:3091: tshe 'di dang 'khor ba la yid byung ba'i skyo
NK021(zha)001:3092: shas kyis 'du 'dzin dang mi dge ba'i sems spangs
NK021(zha)001:3093: te / bsgom bya'i ngo bo ni /
NK021(zha)001:3094: rang gi dpral bar rus pa'i thig le yungs 'bru tsam zhig bsgom /
NK021(zha)001:3095: de las shes pa gtad de bzhag pas /
NK021(zha)001:3096: thig le de je che je cher 'phel bas snang
NK021(zha)001:3097: ba thams cad keng rus su skya khrol gyis song
NK021(zha)001:3098: ba la rtse gcig tu mnyam par bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3099: de las yang sdud pa'i sbyor bas rang lus tsam keng rus su dmigs nas bsgom ste /
NK021(zha)001:3101: keng rus chags bcas thams cad la //
NK021(zha)001:3102: rus pa rgya mtsho'i bar du ni //
NK021(zha)001:3103: spro zhing bsdud pa las dang po //
NK021(zha)001:3104: zhes pas 'di ni las dang po pa'i mi sdug pa sgom tshul te /
NK021(zha)001:3105: de la brten nas spro ba sngar bzhin las bsdu
NK021(zha)001:3106: ba na rkang rus bor ba nas thod phyed kyi
NK021(zha)001:3107: bar dang / shin tu brtan nas thod phyed kyang
NK021(zha)001:3108: bsdus la smin ma gnyis kyi bar du sems 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:3109: bar dang / pa ste / de las /
NK021(zha)001:3110: rkang rus nas ni thod phyed bar //
NK021(zha)001:3111: btang bas sbyang ba byas par bshad //
NK021(zha)001:3112: smin ma'i bar du sems 'dzin pas //
NK021(zha)001:3113: yid la byed pa rdzogs pa yin //
NK021(zha)001:3115: de ltar mi sdug pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis chags sdang 'gags nas sems las su rung ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:3116: de nas lhag mthong sgom ste /
NK021(zha)001:3117: lam lngar byang phyogs so bdun nam /
NK021(zha)001:3118: bden bzhi rnam pa bcu drug tu phye nas bsgom pa yin na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:3119: 'dir lam gong ma'i stegs su gang zag gi bdag
NK021(zha)001:3120: med bsgom pa'i lta khrid tsam zhig bstan pa bya'o
NK021(zha)001:3121: // de yang rang lus nyer len gyi phung po
NK021(zha)001:3122: 'di la bdag tu sgro btags nas ngar 'dzin 'jug
NK021(zha)001:3123: // pas / de sun dbyung ba'i don du 'di ltar bsgom ste /
NK021(zha)001:3124: nga'o zhes rnam par btags pa'i yul la dmigs na nga zhes bya ba grub pa med de /
NK021(zha)001:3125: lus rnams rdul phran gyi bar du gshig cing /
NK021(zha)001:3126: sems kyang skad cig gi bar du rnam par bshig pa na /
NK021(zha)001:3127: lus sems gnyis kyang nga ma yin la /
NK021(zha)001:3128: de gnyis kyi tshogs pa'ang ma grub pas nga ma yin /
NK021(zha)001:3129: de gnyis las logs pa'ang med pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:3130: gang zag med par rtogs pa na /
NK021(zha)001:3131: de'i ngang la mnyam par gzhag par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:3132: de ltar gtan la phab ste bsgoms pas /
NK021(zha)001:3133: nga'am bdag tu 'dzin pa log pas ni /
NK021(zha)001:3134: nga yir 'dzin pa'am bdag gir 'dzin pa mi 'byung zhing /
NK021(zha)001:3135: de ltar nyes pa thams cad kyi rtsa ba bdag
NK021(zha)001:3136: dang bdag gir 'dzin pa log pas ni nyon mongs
NK021(zha)001:3137: pa ldog / de log pas las zad par 'gyur la /
NK021(zha)001:3138: las dang nyon mongs pa zad pas ni skye ba zad par 'gyur bas na /
NK021(zha)001:3139: rnam par grol ba thob par 'gyur te /
NK021(zha)001:3141: las dang nyon mongs zad las thar //
NK021(zha)001:3142: zhes gsungs pa ltar yin pas brtson pas bslab par byos shig /
