NK021(zha)001:3143: tshul des nyan thos theg pa'i dbang bskur man ngag dang bcas pa legs par grub pas /
NK021(zha)001:3144: de ltar gdams pa las mi 'da' bar bsgrub par bya'o snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:3145: gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blangs /
NK021(zha)001:3147: deng nas brtsams te sogs dang /
NK021(zha)001:3148: dge ba bsngo ba rnams sngar ltar dang /
NK021(zha)001:3149: rjes chog rnams sgrub thabs bzhin bya ba yin no //
NK021(zha)001:3150: nyung gsal brjod bde'i ngag tshig gis //
NK021(zha)001:3151: don kun yongs tshang dbang chog khrigs //
NK021(zha)001:3152: legs bshad rmad byung chos skyes 'di //
NK021(zha)001:3153: skal bzang dga' byed dpal du sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:3154: nyan thos theg pa'i dbang chog gi le tshan no //
NK021(zha)001:3157: 'gyur chos srid rtsa gang zag dang //
NK021(zha)001:3158: chos phyed gzung rtog bdag med kyi //
NK021(zha)001:3159: rdo rjesa gzhom mdzad la btud nas //
NK021(zha)001:3160: rang rgyal theg pa'i dbang chog bshad //
NK021(zha)001:3161: da ni gsum pa rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:3162: dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa sgrub thabs ltar grub rjes /
NK021(zha)001:3164: slob dpon bdag nyid ston pa thub pa'i dbang por
NK021(zha)001:3165: bsams pa'i gtsug tor gyi 'od kyis dkyil 'khor gyi
NK021(zha)001:3166: lha dang phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba sras bcas kyi byin
NK021(zha)001:3167: rlabs bsdus nas spyi bor zhugs pas rjes su gnang
NK021(zha)001:3168: ba thob / slar yang spyi bo'i 'od kyis bskul
NK021(zha)001:3169: bas dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i ston pa sangs rgyas
NK021(zha)001:3170: ba thob / / 'khor 'phags pa rang rgyal gyi
NK021(zha)001:3171: dge 'dun dang bcas pa las rang 'dra'i sku gnyis
NK021(zha)001:3173: rang gi spyi bor thim pas rten 'brel lugs 'byung gi rgyu 'bras sdug kun 'gags nas /
NK021(zha)001:3174: lugs ldog 'gog lam gyi yon tan rgyud la skyes par bsam pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3175: de nas slob ma gzhug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3177: bgegs ga tor btang la mtshams bcad /
NK021(zha)001:3178: sems bskyed dang chos nyan pa'i kun spyod gsal 'debs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK021(zha)001:3179: 'dir gang gsan par bya ba'i chos ni /
NK021(zha)001:3181: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor /
NK021(zha)001:3182: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar las skabs babs kyi spro bsdu byas rjes /
NK021(zha)001:3183: gsum pa rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK021(zha)001:3185: slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams grub nas /
NK021(zha)001:3186: khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:3188: de nas gsol ba gdab pa'i slad du don dam
NK021(zha)001:3189: pa'i dkon mchog gsum la yid ches kyi dad pa
NK021(zha)001:3190: bskyed nas / de mtshon byed brdar btags dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK021(zha)001:3192: 'phags pa rang rgyal gyi dge 'dun dang bcas pa
NK021(zha)001:3193: rnams la yan lag lnga sa la phab pa'i phyag
NK021(zha)001:3195: slob dpon thub pa'i dbang por gsal ba'i gtsug tor
NK021(zha)001:3196: gyi nor bu 'od zer 'phro ba las dgos dgu
NK021(zha)001:3197: ma lus pa 'byung bar mos la snyim pa me
NK021(zha)001:3199: kun mkhyen ye shes phung po can //
NK021(zha)001:3200: srid pa'i 'khor lo rnams sbyong ba //
NK021(zha)001:3201: de ring bshad pa'i rin chen gter //
NK021(zha)001:3202: gtso bos bdag la bka' drin gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3204: de nas sdom pa 'bogs pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3205: bsrung bya'i tshul khrims nyan thos dang 'dra bas 'dir zur du blang mi dgos shing /
NK021(zha)001:3207: theg pa 'di'i lugs kyis 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba skyes bu 'bring po'i lam yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:3208: bden bzhi la blang dor gyi sgo nas bslab dgos /
NK021(zha)001:3209: de yang dmigs yul bden pa bzhis bsdus pa'i chos la /
NK021(zha)001:3210: rten 'brel 'byung ldog gis sgom pas khams gsum gyi phra rgyas rnams spong bar 'dod pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:3212: rgyu yod na 'bras bu 'byung ba'i rten 'brel lugs 'byung dang /
NK021(zha)001:3213: log na ldog pa'i lugs ldog dpe byas nas /
NK021(zha)001:3214: nang gi rten 'brel dur khrod kyi rus pa la brtags te /
NK021(zha)001:3216: 'di rga shi las byung zhes rim par brtags pa
NK021(zha)001:3217: na 'khor ba'i rtsa ba ma rig par thug pas
NK021(zha)001:3218: / de 'gags na 'du byed 'gag pa sogs rga shi'i bar 'gags te /
NK021(zha)001:3219: rgyu kun 'byung las nyon zad pas 'bras bu 'khor ba'i nyes pa las grol te /
NK021(zha)001:3220: 'gog lam gyi yon tan thob par 'gyur ba yin
NK021(zha)001:3221: pas na ma rig pa'i gnyen po bdag med rtogs
NK021(zha)001:3222: pa'i shes rab la bsten par mdzad 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:3225: thog mar rang rgyal gyi chas su 'jug pa'i rdzas dbang drug bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:3226: dang po bum chus bkru zhing 'thung du bcug ste /
NK021(zha)001:3228: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:3229: rigs kyi bu la bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:3230: nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma byang zhing
NK021(zha)001:3231: dag pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:3232: ye d+har+m+aa he tu pra b+ha wa he tun+te sh+aan+ta th+aa ga to h+ya ba data /
NK021(zha)001:3233: te sh+aany+tsa yo ni ro d+ha e wam b+aa d+ai ma h+aa sh+ra ma na ye s+w+aah+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3234: gnyis pa sngar rab byung gi ming bcug ste /
NK021(zha)001:3236: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la 'di zhes
NK021(zha)001:3237: bya ba'i ming gi dbang bskur bas shes bya la
NK021(zha)001:3238: ma rmongs pa rang sangs rgyas kyi dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:3239: ye d+har+m+aa gsum pa spu gri /
NK021(zha)001:3241: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyii bu la shan ral
NK021(zha)001:3242: gri'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod
NK021(zha)001:3243: pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa bzhi pa chos gos
NK021(zha)001:3245: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi bu la na bza'
NK021(zha)001:3246: dur smrig gi dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i gdung
NK021(zha)001:3247: ba las skyob pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa lnga
NK021(zha)001:3249: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la bkra shis pa'i rdzas
NK021(zha)001:3250: sbrang rtsi'i dbang bskur bas 'bras bu phun sum tshogs
NK021(zha)001:3251: pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa drug pa r+ts+wa zor
NK021(zha)001:3253: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la r+ts+wa dar+b+ha'i rdzas kyi
NK021(zha)001:3254: dbang bskur bas bkra shis shing bar chad thams cad
NK021(zha)001:3255: kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa de
NK021(zha)001:3256: ltar bum chab kyi khrus sngon du 'gro bas ston
NK021(zha)001:3257: pa sangs rgyas ji ltar rab tu byung ba'i nyer
NK021(zha)001:3258: spyod rnams kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:3259: rang sangs rgyas kyi tshul khrims rang byung gi dge
NK021(zha)001:3260: slong du gyur nas 'khor ba las 'byin pa'i skal
NK021(zha)001:3261: ba can du byas pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:3262: de nas rang sangs rgyas kyi byang chub mngon du
NK021(zha)001:3263: byed pa'i lam zab mo rten 'brel 'byung ldog gi
NK021(zha)001:3265: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi tsakli thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:3266: nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni //
NK021(zha)001:3267: ma rig rgan mo long ba 'dra //
NK021(zha)001:3268: 'du byed rdza mkhan lta bu ste //
NK021(zha)001:3269: rnam shes spre'u ming gzugs gru //
NK021(zha)001:3270: skye mched khang pa stong pa 'dra //
NK021(zha)001:3271: reg pa pho mo 'o byed bzhin //
NK021(zha)001:3272: tshor ba pus mor mda' zug 'dra //
NK021(zha)001:3273: sred pa chang 'thung lta bu ste //
NK021(zha)001:3275: srid pa 'khrig pa'am sbrum ma ste //
NK021(zha)001:3276: skye ba ma las bu skye 'dra //
NK021(zha)001:3277: rga shi gud dang shi ba 'dra //
NK021(zha)001:3278: phyi yi rten 'brel bcu gnyis ni //
NK021(zha)001:3279: sa bon myu gu sdong po dang //
NK021(zha)001:3280: lo ma me tog 'bras bu ste //
NK021(zha)001:3281: rgyu dang 'brel ba drug ces bya //
NK021(zha)001:3282: mkha' rlung me chu sa khams lnga //
NK021(zha)001:3283: dus kyi 'gyur ba dang bcas pa //
NK021(zha)001:3284: rkyen dang 'brel ba drug yin te //
NK021(zha)001:3286: lugs 'byung lugs ldog mngon gyur nas //
NK021(zha)001:3287: yid bzhin bde ba mchog thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:3289: bse ru dang ni ne tso lta bu yi //
NK021(zha)001:3290: 'bras bu la sogs phyi yi rten 'brel dang //
NK021(zha)001:3291: ma rig pa sogs nang gi rten 'brel dang //
NK021(zha)001:3292: lugs 'byung 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras spang bya zhing //
NK021(zha)001:3293: lugs ldog 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras rab bsgrubs nas //
NK021(zha)001:3294: 'jig rten pa dang nyan thos rang sa drug /
NK021(zha)001:3295: 'das nas rang sangs rgyas kyi sar phyin shog /
NK021(zha)001:3297: dkon mchog gsum gyi rigs kyi bu khyod la rten
NK021(zha)001:3298: 'brel gyi dbang bskur bas yid bzhin bde ba mchog
NK021(zha)001:3299: gi sa thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:3300: / ye d+har+m+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3301: de nas lha dbang bskur ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:3302: dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i lha rnams las mar me
NK021(zha)001:3303: gcig las gnyis chad kyi rnam par lha so so
NK021(zha)001:3305: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bo nas thim pa'i byin rlabs kyis rten 'brel 'jug ldog dang /
NK021(zha)001:3306: bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs pa'i yon tan khyad par can rgyud la skyes pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:3307: gtso bo thub dbang gi sku thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:3308: 'das dang ma byon da ltar gyi //
NK021(zha)001:3309: dus gsum sangs rgyas ji snyed pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:3310: bcom ldan gtso bo'i dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:3311: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:3312: ye d+har+m+aa rang rgyal bse ru dang ne tso lta bu'i tsakli thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:3314: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas bse
NK021(zha)001:3315: ru lta bu dang ne tso lta bu'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:3316: bas gcig pur bsam gtan la gnas pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:3317: tshogs spyod kyi grogs la brten te bsam gtan mthar
NK021(zha)001:3318: phyin nas yid bzhin bde ba mchog gis rang rgyal
NK021(zha)001:3319: dgra bcom gyi rtogs rigs mngon du gyur pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:3320: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:3321: ye d+har+m+aa rang rgyal bcu gnyis kyi tsakli rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:3323: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas rdo
NK021(zha)001:3324: rje 'jigs med kyi dbang bskur bas 'khor bskrag par
NK021(zha)001:3325: byed pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:3326: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas snang
NK021(zha)001:3327: ba brtsegs pa'i dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin rab
NK021(zha)001:3328: tu snang ba'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo
NK021(zha)001:3329: / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas
NK021(zha)001:3330: dpa' bo 'dul ba'i dbang bskur bas srid pa bsnyil
NK021(zha)001:3331: ba'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:3332: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas gdung
NK021(zha)001:3333: ba sel ba'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i gdung
NK021(zha)001:3334: ba sel ba'i dbang ye d+har+m+aa na mo /
NK021(zha)001:3335: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas shes
NK021(zha)001:3336: rab mgyogs chen gyi dbang bskur bas shes rab kyi
NK021(zha)001:3337: rtsal dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na
NK021(zha)001:3338: mo / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs
NK021(zha)001:3339: rgyas rdzu 'phrul cher ston gyi dbang bskur bas sprul
NK021(zha)001:3340: pa'i cho 'phrul dang ldan pa'i dbang ye d+har+m+aa na
NK021(zha)001:3341: mo / mo / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la
NK021(zha)001:3342: rang sangs rgyas gdung ba sel byed kyi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:3343: bas dug lnga 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa
NK021(zha)001:3344: mo / mo / na mo / dkon mchog rigs
NK021(zha)001:3345: kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas sgra chen po'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:3346: bskur bas gsung gi dbang phyug tu gyur pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:3347: dam pa ye d+harma na mo /
NK021(zha)001:3348: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas bse
NK021(zha)001:3349: ru lta bu'i dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin rtse
NK021(zha)001:3350: gcig tu gyur pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na
NK021(zha)001:3351: mo / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs
NK021(zha)001:3352: rgyas ri'i rgyal po'i dbang bskur bas 'khor ba'i rlung
NK021(zha)001:3353: gi mi bskyod pa'i dbang dam pa ye d+har+m+aa na
NK021(zha)001:3354: mo / mo / dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la
NK021(zha)001:3355: rang sangs rgyas seng ge lta bu'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:3356: 'jigs pa thams cad dang bral ba'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:3358: dkon mchog rigs kyi bu la rang sangs rgyas yid
NK021(zha)001:3359: myur ba'i dbang bskur bas ting nge 'dzin rdzu 'phrul
NK021(zha)001:3360: myur ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:3362: de ltar rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:3363: mdo rang lugs kyi sbyor lam dang po rigs chen
NK021(zha)001:3364: 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor gal chen sbyong ba'i sa non
NK021(zha)001:3365: pa dang rigs 'dra ba'i yon tan gsos thebs pas
NK021(zha)001:3366: / mngon du rgyu'i bag chags rags pa dag /
NK021(zha)001:3367: lam gong ma la sbyor ba'i ldang ba byang chub kyi sems skyes shing /
NK021(zha)001:3368: 'khor ba las rnam par grol ba'i rgyur gyur /
NK021(zha)001:3369: rang rgyal dgra bcom gyi rtogs rigs dang 'dra ba'i
NK021(zha)001:3370: yon tan khyad par can thob pa'i skal pa can
NK021(zha)001:3372: rjes kyi bya ba la spyi don gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:3375: gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid gdab pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3376: spyi don dang po lam khyer la bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:3377: dang po theg pa lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:3378: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa ste de la'ang drug las /
NK021(zha)001:3380: rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK021(zha)001:3381: rgyu dang 'brel ba sa bon nas 'bras bu'i bar drug /
NK021(zha)001:3382: rkyen dang 'brel ba 'byung lnga dus kyi 'gyur ba dang drug gis phyi'i rten 'brel bcu gnyis /
NK021(zha)001:3383: rgyu yod na 'bras bu 'byung ba'i lugs 'byung dang /
NK021(zha)001:3384: log na ldog pa'i lugs ldog dper byas te /
NK021(zha)001:3385: nang gi rten 'brel dur khrod kyi rus pa la brten nas /
NK021(zha)001:3386: de rga shi las byung ba sogs rim gyis brtags pas /
NK021(zha)001:3387: 'di ltar 'khor ba'i rtsa ba ma rig par rtogs te /
NK021(zha)001:3388: de log na 'du byed nas rga shi'i bar ldog par shes nas 'jug ste /
NK021(zha)001:3389: de yang bskal chen brgya'i bar tshogs bsags la /
NK021(zha)001:3390: srid pa tha ma'i tshe mkhan slob med par rang
NK021(zha)001:3391: byung gi dge slong du gyur nas dur khrod du
NK021(zha)001:3392: phyin pa na / rus pa mthong ma thag rten
NK021(zha)001:3393: 'brel 'byung ldog gi 'gros rtogs pa'i sgo nas so
NK021(zha)001:3394: phyin pa na / // lta ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:3395: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i steng du gzung
NK021(zha)001:3396: ba chos kyi bdag med rtogs pa bsnan pas bdag
NK021(zha)001:3397: med phyed dang gnyis rtogs te /
NK021(zha)001:3399: gzung don rtog pa spong phyir dang //
NK021(zha)001:3400: 'dzin pa mi spong phyir dang ni //
NK021(zha)001:3401: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK021(zha)001:3402: yang dag bsdus par shes par bya //
NK021(zha)001:3407: nyan thos kyi bden bzhi rnam pa bcu drug gi
NK021(zha)001:3408: steng du rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba zab mo
NK021(zha)001:3409: bsnan nas sgom / spyod pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3410: rang don gtso bor spyod cing /
NK021(zha)001:3411: gzhan la chos ston pa na ngag gi rnam rig
NK021(zha)001:3412: la mi brten par rdzu 'phrul gyi bkod pas lus
NK021(zha)001:3413: kyi rnam rig gis ston no //
NK021(zha)001:3414: 'bras bu la mtshams sbyor byed rang rgyal du smon lam btab pa ltar /
NK021(zha)001:3416: tshogs na spyod pa chen po dang chung ngu rnams rim par lam lnga dang /
NK021(zha)001:3418: gsum stan thog gcig tu mngon du rdzogs nas rang
NK021(zha)001:3419: rgyal dgra bcom gyi go 'phang la sbyor ba ste
NK021(zha)001:3420: / thob bya de nyid 'di'i lam stegs su mngon du byed mi dgos kyang /
NK021(zha)001:3421: rtogs bya thams cad 'dir yang rtogs dgos pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:3422: gnyis pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:3423: bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i dbang po la /
NK021(zha)001:3424: 'khor 'phags pa rang sangs rgyas kyi dge 'dun dang
NK021(zha)001:3425: bcas pa spyan drangs te bzhugs pa'i spyan sngar tshogs
NK021(zha)001:3426: bsags pa'o // gsum pa snying po lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:3427: lha de rnams kyi sku las 'phros pa'i 'od zer dkar pos lus sems kyi skyon sbyangs shing /
NK021(zha)001:3428: rgyud byin gyis brlabs par bsams la /
NK021(zha)001:3430: rten 'brel snying po'i gzugs bzla ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:3431: bzhi pa bslab bya lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:3432: spyir nyan thos ltar dge mi dge'i las kyi blang dor ma nor bar bya zhing /
NK021(zha)001:3433: khyad par mkhas par bya ba'i chos drug la mkhas par slob pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:3439: gnas dang gnas ma yin pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:3441: spyi don gnyis pa 'gag drug bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3443: gang du gang gis gang la gang bstan pa //
NK021(zha)001:3444: ci'i phyir bshad pa'i dgos pa dang bcas pa //
NK021(zha)001:3445: 'di ni rang rgyal theg pa'i 'gag drug yin //
NK021(zha)001:3447: gang du bshad pa'i gnas ni /
NK021(zha)001:3448: ri bo bya rkang can du'o //
NK021(zha)001:3449: gang gis bshad pa'i ston pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3450: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK021(zha)001:3452: nyan thos dbang rnon rnams la'o //
NK021(zha)001:3453: gang bstan pa'i theg pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3454: rang rgyal gyi theg pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:3455: de ston pa'i sde snod kyang ma skyes dgra'i 'gyod
NK021(zha)001:3456: pa bsal ba'i mdo sogs su nyan thos kyi sde
NK021(zha)001:3457: snod las logs pa yod par bshad do //
NK021(zha)001:3458: ci'i phyir na rten 'brel gyi dbang bskur bas rten
NK021(zha)001:3459: 'brel 'byung ldog gi don rtogs te rang rgyal dgra
NK021(zha)001:3460: bcom gyi rtogs rigs dang 'dra ba'i yon tan thob
NK021(zha)001:3461: pa'i ched du'o // de ltar bstan pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3462: 'khor ba las thar pa'i byang chub 'bring thob pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK021(zha)001:3463: spyi don gsum pa gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid ni //
NK021(zha)001:3464: rang gi spyi bor theg le dmar po dang //
NK021(zha)001:3465: de la khru gang tsam gyis mtho bar thig le dkar po ste /
NK021(zha)001:3466: gnyis ka che chung sran ma tsam du bsgom /
NK021(zha)001:3467: de ltar gsal thebs pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:3468: thig le dmar po de la shes pa gtad pas /
NK021(zha)001:3469: de je che je cher 'phel nas /
NK021(zha)001:3470: snang ba thams cad dmar lam gyis song ba la rtse gcig tu mnyam par bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3471: yang thig le dkar po la shes pa gtad pas /
NK021(zha)001:3472: de je che je cher 'phel nas snang ba thams
NK021(zha)001:3473: cad dkar lam gyis song ba la rtse gcigs tu
NK021(zha)001:3474: 'jog ste / dmar dkar gnyis po de rten 'brel lugs 'byung ldog gi chos su shes par bya /
NK021(zha)001:3475: de nas dkar dmar gnyis 'dres pa spyi bo nas
NK021(zha)001:3476: babs te snying gar thim pa'i ngang la ma bcos
NK021(zha)001:3478: de brtan nas lta khrid ni /
NK021(zha)001:3479: lus sems rdul phran dang skad cig ma'i bar du gshig pa nyan thos ltar las /
NK021(zha)001:3480: don du snang ba rdul phran du bsil ba de
NK021(zha)001:3481: yang rnam par gshig pas mtha' med du gyur nas
NK021(zha)001:3482: cir yang ma grub pa'i ngang la mnyam par bzhag
NK021(zha)001:3483: / de ltar bsgoms pas gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa'i steng du /
NK021(zha)001:3484: gzung ba chos kyi bdag med kyang rtogs par 'gyur ba yin no //
NK021(zha)001:3485: des rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i dbang bskur ba man ngag dang bcas pa grub pas /
NK021(zha)001:3486: ji ltar gdams pa ltar tshul bzhin du bsgrub par bya snyam du /
NK021(zha)001:3487: gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blang /
NK021(zha)001:3489: deng nas brtsams te sogs kyi yon dbul zhing /
NK021(zha)001:3490: dge ba bsngo ba rnams sngar ltar dang /
NK021(zha)001:3491: rjes chog rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:3492: mkhas pa'i man ngag ji lta bar //
NK021(zha)001:3493: rang rgyal theg pa'i dbang chog khrigs //
NK021(zha)001:3495: legs bshad snang ba'i dpal 'di spros //
NK021(zha)001:3496: rang rgyal theg pa'i dbang mchog gi le tshan no //
NK021(zha)001:3499: 'gyur med dbyings su thams mkhas kyi //
NK021(zha)001:3500: rdo rje sgrib gnyis dpung bcom nas //
NK021(zha)001:3501: 'gro kun sgrol mdzad bla ma la //
NK021(zha)001:3502: btud nas byang sems dbang chog bshad //
NK021(zha)001:3503: da ni bzhi pa byang sems kyi theg pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:3504: dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa sgrub thabs ltar grub rjes /
NK021(zha)001:3506: slob dpon bdag nyid ston pa thub pa'i dbang por
NK021(zha)001:3507: bsams pa'i dbu gtsug tu nor bu rin po che
NK021(zha)001:3508: dbang gi rgyal po 'od zer mtha' yas pa 'phro
NK021(zha)001:3509: ba des / dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang phyogs bcu'i
NK021(zha)001:3510: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i byin rlabs thams cad
NK021(zha)001:3511: ba des / bsdus te / spyi bo nas thim pas rjes su gnang ba thob /
NK021(zha)001:3512: slar yang spyi bo'i 'od kyis dkyil 'khor la bkod
NK021(zha)001:3513: pa'i yum shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma
NK021(zha)001:3514: dang / sras ston pa thub pa'i dbang po la
NK021(zha)001:3515: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs
NK021(zha)001:3516: kyi bskor ba rnams las rang 'dra ba'i sku re
NK021(zha)001:3517: dang / re chad de / rang gi spyi bo nas thim pas sgrib gnyis byang zhing /
NK021(zha)001:3518: de rnams kyi thugs gnyis su med pa'i ye shes rang rgyud la thob par bsam pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3519: de nas slob ma gzhug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3521: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad /
NK021(zha)001:3522: sems bskyed dang chos nyan pa'i kun spyod gsal 'debs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK021(zha)001:3523: 'dir gang gsan par bya ba'i chos ni /
NK021(zha)001:3525: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor /
NK021(zha)001:3526: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar las spro bsdu byas rjes /
NK021(zha)001:3527: bzhi pa byang sems kyi theg pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba skabs su babs pa yin /
NK021(zha)001:3528: de la'ang gnyis las slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams grub nas /
NK021(zha)001:3529: da khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK021(zha)001:3530: 'jug cing dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala phul mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:3532: de nas slob dpon la phyag gsum tshol la pus btsugs thal sbyar gyi 'dug cig /
NK021(zha)001:3534: khyed cag byang sems kyi theg pa'i sgor 'jug pa la /
NK021(zha)001:3535: theg chen gyi thun mong ma yin pa'i lam gyi
NK021(zha)001:3536: thog ma ni sems bskyed nas 'go 'dzin dgos pas
NK021(zha)001:3537: / skabs 'dir 'jug sgo sems bskyed kyi sdom pa blang ba gal che ste /
NK021(zha)001:3538: sems ma bskyed pa'i sems can yod do cog gi
NK021(zha)001:3539: dge ba rgya chen po lan grangs dpag tu med
NK021(zha)001:3541: sems bskyed pa'i gang zag gcig gis dge ba phra
NK021(zha)001:3542: mo lan gcig byas pa'ang bsod nams ches lhag pa'i
NK021(zha)001:3543: phyir te / rin po che'i phung po'i mdo las /
NK021(zha)001:3544: sems can gang dag srid pa gsum du gtogs pa
NK021(zha)001:3545: de dag thams cad kyis so so nas de bzhin
NK021(zha)001:3546: gshegs pa'i mchod rten 'phang du ri'i rgyal po ri
NK021(zha)001:3548: de dag la bskal pa gang+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma
NK021(zha)001:3549: snyed du so so nas sti stang du bya ba
NK021(zha)001:3550: thams cad kyis sti stang du byas pa las /
NK021(zha)001:3551: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi
NK021(zha)001:3552: sems dang ma bral ba gcig gis me tog gcig
NK021(zha)001:3553: phul na / de ni bsod nams kyi phung po
NK021(zha)001:3554: snga ma las bsod nams ches mang du bskyed do
NK021(zha)001:3556: yang de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang ba'i mdo las /
NK021(zha)001:3557: byang chub sems kyi bsod nams gang //
NK021(zha)001:3558: de la gal te gzugs mchis na //
NK021(zha)001:3559: nam mkha'i khams ni kun gang ste //
NK021(zha)001:3560: de ni de bas lhag par 'gyur //
NK021(zha)001:3561: zhes sogs 'phags pa klu sgrub kyis mdo kun las
NK021(zha)001:3562: btus su drangs nas bshad pa ltar phan yon bsam
NK021(zha)001:3563: gyis mi khyab pa yod pa yin /
NK021(zha)001:3564: de lta bu'i phan yon can gyi byang chub tu
NK021(zha)001:3565: sems bskyed pa'i ched du yul khyad par can la
NK021(zha)001:3567: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la ston pa'i 'du shes bskyed de 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:3569: bdag la dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK021(zha)001:3570: cad kyi bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam skyabs gsum sngon
NK021(zha)001:3571: du 'gro ba can byang chub kyi mchog tu sems
NK021(zha)001:3573: zhes lan gsum gsol ba btab pa'i lan du gnang ba byin pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3575: nus pa ji lta ba bzhin du sbyin par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:3577: de nas smon 'jug gi sems bskyed pa'i rgyu'i gtso
NK021(zha)001:3578: bor thabs khyad par can gyi sgo nas tshogs bsags
NK021(zha)001:3579: dgos pas / 'di ltar dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i dkon mchog gsum gyis mtshon nas /
NK021(zha)001:3580: mdun gyi nam mkha'i gnas su phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas
NK021(zha)001:3581: dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad sprin 'thibs pa
NK021(zha)001:3583: rang gi lus zhing gi rdul snyed du sprul nas
NK021(zha)001:3584: phyag 'tshal ba sogs yan lag bdun phul bar mos
NK021(zha)001:3585: pa la don dran bzhin pas 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:3586: phyogs bcu dus gsum bzhugs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:3587: rgyal ba sras dang bcas rnams la /
NK021(zha)001:3588: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:3589: mchod sprin rgya mtshos kun tu mchod //
NK021(zha)001:3590: sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags //
NK021(zha)001:3591: dge ba kun la rjes yi rang //
NK021(zha)001:3592: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul //
NK021(zha)001:3594: dge ba byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK021(zha)001:3596: de nas theg pa chen po'i blo khyad par can du byed cing /
NK021(zha)001:3598: rten khyad par can la skyabs su 'gro ba gal che ste /
NK021(zha)001:3599: de yang don dam par gang gis skyob pa'i rten dkon mchog gsum dang /
NK021(zha)001:3600: gang skyob pa'i yul 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad
NK021(zha)001:3601: gdod nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i stong
NK021(zha)001:3603: de ltar ma rtogs pas kun rdzob tu 'khor ba'i
NK021(zha)001:3604: gnas su sdug bsngal gyis nyam thag cing skyabs med
NK021(zha)001:3605: mgon med du gyur pa'i tshe rabs kyi pha ma
NK021(zha)001:3606: drin can 'di rnams sdug bsngal rgyu dang bcas pa
NK021(zha)001:3607: las skyob nus pa ni dkon mchog rin po che
NK021(zha)001:3608: gsum ma gtogs gzhan med pas /
NK021(zha)001:3609: de la re ltos zhe thag pa nas bcas te /
NK021(zha)001:3610: bdag la 'gro kun sgrol nus kyi nus pa yod
NK021(zha)001:3611: pa dkon mchog gsum mkhyen snyam pas thal mo sbyar
NK021(zha)001:3613: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:3614: slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:3615: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba dus 'di nas bzung
NK021(zha)001:3616: nas ji srid byang chub snying po la mchis kyi
NK021(zha)001:3617: bar du / rkang gnyis rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:3618: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams la skyabs su mchi'o //
NK021(zha)001:3619: zhi ba 'dod chags dang bral ba rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:3620: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i dam pa'i chos rnams la tshogs rnams kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:3621: phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i dge
NK021(zha)001:3622: 'dun phyir mi ldog pa rnams la skyabs su mchi'o
NK021(zha)001:3624: de nas sems bskyed pa dngos gzhi ni /
NK021(zha)001:3626: sems can dang sdug bsngal gsum rang bzhin gyis ma dmigs kyang /
NK021(zha)001:3627: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sems can rnams bsgral bar bya ba'o snyam pa smon sems dang /
NK021(zha)001:3628: bdag dang lam rang bzhin gyis ma dmigs kyang 'gro
NK021(zha)001:3629: ba rnams bsgral ba'i ched du sbyin sogs la 'bad
NK021(zha)001:3630: par bya'o snyam pa 'jug pa sems bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:3631: 'dir smon 'jug gnyis stabs gcig tu len pa yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:3632: ji ltar dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dang byang chub
NK021(zha)001:3633: sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi smon pa dang 'jug
NK021(zha)001:3634: pa'i bdag nyid can gyi byang chub mchog tu thugs
NK021(zha)001:3635: bskyed pa de bzhin du bdag gis kyang byang chub
NK021(zha)001:3636: mchog tu sems bskyed par bagyi'o snyam pas 'di'i rjes
NK021(zha)001:3637: zlos / phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas dang
NK021(zha)001:3638: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad bdag la dgongs su
NK021(zha)001:3639: zlos / gsol / slob dpon bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:3640: ji ltar sngon gyi de bzhin gshegs pa dgra bcom
NK021(zha)001:3641: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan
NK021(zha)001:3642: 'das rnams dang / byang chub sems dpa' chen po rnams kyi byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:3643: sems can thams cad kyi don du bla na med
NK021(zha)001:3644: pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu mngon
NK021(zha)001:3645: par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas nas /
NK021(zha)001:3646: sems can ma bsgral ba rnams bsgral ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:3647: ma grol ba rnams dgrol ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:3648: dbugs ma phyin pa rnams dbugs phyung pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:3649: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs
NK021(zha)001:3650: su myang ngan las 'das pa'i sa la bkod pa
NK021(zha)001:3651: de bzhin du / bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas kyang dus 'di nas bzung ste /
NK021(zha)001:3652: snying po byang chub la mchis kyi bar du byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:3653: sems can ma bsgral ba rnams sgrol ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:3654: ma grol ba rnams dgrol ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:3655: dbugs ma phyin pa rnams dbugs dbyung ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:3656: yongs su mya ngan las ma 'das pa rnams yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar bagyi'o //
NK021(zha)001:3658: brjod pa tha ma la sdom pa skyes par bsam du gzhug /
NK021(zha)001:3660: rjes kyi cho ga gsum las /
NK021(zha)001:3661: rang dga' ba sgom pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3662: khyed rnams deng phyin chad byang chub sems dpar gyur
NK021(zha)001:3663: pas mi lus thob pa don yod par byas snyam
NK021(zha)001:3664: du gzengs gtod pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:3665: deng dus bdag tshe 'bras bu yod //
NK021(zha)001:3666: mi yi srid pa legs par thob //
NK021(zha)001:3667: de ring sangs rgyas rigs su skyes //
NK021(zha)001:3668: sangs rgyas sras su da gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:3670: gzhan dga' ba sgom du gzhug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3671: khyed rnams kyis sems bskyed pa de dkar phyogs pa
NK021(zha)001:3672: rnams kyis thos na dga' ba skye ba yin pas
NK021(zha)001:3673: / de dag la smon pa'i bsam pas rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:3674: bdag gis de ring skyob pa thams cad kyi //
NK021(zha)001:3675: spyan sngar 'gro ba bde gshegs nyid dang ni /
NK021(zha)001:3676: bar du bde la mgron du bos zin gyis //
NK021(zha)001:3677: lha dang lha min la sogs dga' bar gyis //
NK021(zha)001:3679: de ltar rang gzhan spro ba bskyed nas sdom pa brtan par bya ba'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:3680: ji ltar bcas pa las mi 'da' bar dam bca' ba 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:3681: da ni bdag gis ci nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:3682: rigs dang mthun pa'i las brtsams te //
NK021(zha)001:3683: skyon med btsun pa'i rigs 'di la //
NK021(zha)001:3684: rnyog par mi 'gyur de ltar bya //
NK021(zha)001:3686: de nas chos bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3687: theg pa 'di'i lugs kyis srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis las
NK021(zha)001:3688: nges par 'byung ba skyes bu chen po'i lam yin
NK021(zha)001:3689: pas / thabs shes zung 'jug gi sgo nas bslab dgos //
NK021(zha)001:3690: de la don dam par gshis rang bzhin gyis rnam
NK021(zha)001:3691: par dag pa'i dbyings su 'khor 'das ro mnyam yang
NK021(zha)001:3692: / kun rdzob rten 'brel ma 'gags pa'i 'char sgor 'khor 'das so sor snang bas /
NK021(zha)001:3693: sdug bsngal can gyi 'khor ba pa la snying rje
NK021(zha)001:3694: chen pos drangs pa'i gzhan phan byang chub kyi sems
NK021(zha)001:3695: khyad par can gyis zin pa'i thabs shes zung 'brel
NK021(zha)001:3696: gyis srid zhi'i mtha' gnyis la mi gnas par spyod
NK021(zha)001:3698: chos thams cad la bden zhen gyis ma gos pas chu zla ltar snang ba'i ngang nas /
NK021(zha)001:3699: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub la dmigs te /
NK021(zha)001:3700: gzhi'i steng gi dri ma sbyong ba'i gnyen po lam
NK021(zha)001:3701: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin sgom zhing
NK021(zha)001:3702: / smon 'jug gi sdom pa mi nyams shing yang
NK021(zha)001:3703: yang bskyar bas gong 'phel gyi sgo nas pha rol
NK021(zha)001:3705: bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi sogs la spyod par byed pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:3706: sgom spyod zung du 'brel ba de yang /
NK021(zha)001:3707: bdag med gnyis rtogs kyi lta ba rnam par dag
NK021(zha)001:3708: pas 'go bsdus nas nyams su len pa la brtson
NK021(zha)001:3711: bla ma la ston pa sangs rgyas kyi 'du shes bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:3712: dbang dngos gzhi zhu ba'i don du man+dala 'bul du bcug /
NK021(zha)001:3713: de nas slob dpon thub pa'i dbang por gsal ba'i
NK021(zha)001:3714: gtsug tor nor bu dbang gi rgyal po 'od zer
NK021(zha)001:3716: dgos 'dod ma lus pa 'byung bar mos la /
NK021(zha)001:3717: snyim pa me tog dang bcas pas thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:3718: slob dpon sangs rgyas dgongs su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3719: bden gnyis don rtogs theg chen gyi //
NK021(zha)001:3720: rgyal ba'i mdzad pa mthar phyin pa //
NK021(zha)001:3721: zab cing rgya che'i dbang rnams stsol //
NK021(zha)001:3722: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab nas /
NK021(zha)001:3724: thog mar lha dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:3725: dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i lha rnams las mar me
NK021(zha)001:3726: gcig las gnyis chad kyi rnam par lha so so
NK021(zha)001:3728: khyed rang rnams kyi spyi bo nas thim pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:3730: bdag med gnyis rtogs kyi yon tan rnam par mi
NK021(zha)001:3731: rtog pa'i ye shes khyad par can rgyud la skyes
NK021(zha)001:3733: lha tsaka rnams rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:3735: gser gyi mdog can rkang gnyis gtso //
NK021(zha)001:3736: spyan yangs mthing ga mdzod spur ldan //
NK021(zha)001:3739: sh+aakya'i rgyal pos byin gyis rlobs //
NK021(zha)001:3740: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3741: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3743: shar phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK021(zha)001:3744: yum chen rgyan ldan rdo rje skyil //
NK021(zha)001:3745: gser mdog sku ni shin tu rgyas //
NK021(zha)001:3746: phyag bzhi'i dang po mnyam bzhag can //
NK021(zha)001:3748: 'gro ba sems can don mdzad pa /
NK021(zha)001:3749: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3750: d+h+ai pra dz+ny+aa ma h+aa pra dz+ny+aa d+harma d+h+aa tu s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3752: lho phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK021(zha)001:3753: phyag na rdo rje zhi ba'i zhal //
NK021(zha)001:3755: rin chen rgyan ldan sems skyil bzhugs //
NK021(zha)001:3756: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3757: badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:3759: nub phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK021(zha)001:3760: sh+aa ri'i bu ni ser skya'i mdog /
NK021(zha)001:3761: rab byung 'khar gsil lhung bzed bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3762: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3763: na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam pra b+ha ta th+aa ga
NK021(zha)001:3764: ta a ba lo ki te k+aa ru na sa
NK021(zha)001:3767: byang phyogs pad+ma zla rgyas steng //
NK021(zha)001:3768: spyan ras gzigs dbang chu shel mdog /
NK021(zha)001:3770: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3771: +aar+ya a ba lo ki te shwa ra ma h+aa k+aa ru ni ka na ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3773: gzhal yas shar phyogs pad zla'i steng //
NK021(zha)001:3774: bde gshegs dkon mchog 'byung gnas ni //
NK021(zha)001:3775: sku mdog shel ltar dkar ba la //
NK021(zha)001:3776: mchog sbyin rin chen g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3777: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3778: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a yur ga ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3780: gzhal yas lho phyogs pad zla'i steng //
NK021(zha)001:3781: bde gshegs mya ngan med pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3782: sngon po 'khor lo g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3783: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3784: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na a tsi ya ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3785: a b+hi nub phyogs pad steng pad zla'i steng //
NK021(zha)001:3787: g.yas pa mche ba g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3788: de yi dbang mchog sarba ta th+aa ga ta tri
NK021(zha)001:3789: ti sha ga pa ri b+hi sh+aa ri s+w+aa h+aa
NK021(zha)001:3790: / a b+hi byang phyogs pad steng pad zla'i steng //
NK021(zha)001:3791: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i dbang po ljang //
NK021(zha)001:3792: g.yas pa pad dkar g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3793: de yis dbang mchog sarba ta th+aa ga ta pi sha rat+na san ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3794: a b+hi shar lho bde gshegs pad+ma dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3795: dung mdog pad+ma g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3797: de yi dbang mchog sarba ta th+aa ga ta du ma le ka do ba ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3798: a b+hi lho nub pad steng bde gshegs ni //
NK021(zha)001:3799: nyi ma snang ba dam pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3800: dmar smug nyi ma g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3801: de yi dbang mchog sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi muk+ti mrgad ru sha ma ti s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3802: a b+hi nub byang pad zlar bde gshegs ni //
NK021(zha)001:3803: gdugs chen dam pa in+d+ra'i mdog /
NK021(zha)001:3804: sna tshogs rdo rje g.yon mnyam bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3805: de yi dbang sarba ta th+aa ga ta s+aur+ya bi ta la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3806: a b+hi byang shar pad zlar bde gshegs ni //
NK021(zha)001:3807: glang po dam pa gser ltar 'tsher //
NK021(zha)001:3809: de yi dbang sarba ta th+aa ga ta bid+h+ya bi sha ya b+ha ba s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3810: a b+hi steng gi bde gshegs dga' ba dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3811: sngon po rin chen bum pa g.yas //
NK021(zha)001:3812: g.yon pa dkur brten skyil krung bzhugs //
NK021(zha)001:3813: de yi dbang sarba ta th+aa ga ta ra ti ra ma ti badz+ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3814: a b+hi 'og gi sangs rgyas pad+mo dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3815: gser mdog g.yas pa pad+ma bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3816: g.yon pa lte bar mthil phyin bstan //
NK021(zha)001:3817: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:3818: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma b+ha la s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3820: de rnams kyis rtsa ba'i lha'i dbang song nas /
NK021(zha)001:3821: da mgron thabs kyi lha rnams kyi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:3822: dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i yum chen mo /
NK021(zha)001:3823: sras thub dbang phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas dang bcas pa
NK021(zha)001:3824: rnams gang 'dul gyi rnam par snang ba tshom bu'i
NK021(zha)001:3825: 'khor dang bcas pa sogs spros nas rang rang gi
NK021(zha)001:3826: spyi bor thim pa'i mos pa mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:3829: rnam dag dbus kyi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK021(zha)001:3830: yang dag rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub //
NK021(zha)001:3831: sa gnon mnyam bzhag gseg gshang par bu can //
NK021(zha)001:3832: yum chen gser mdog ral gri mchog sbyin g.yas //
NK021(zha)001:3833: g.yon pa ut+pala pusti phreng ba can //
NK021(zha)001:3834: rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas phyogs mdog rim pa bzhin //
NK021(zha)001:3835: glang po rin 'byung pad+mo ting 'dzin rgyal //
NK021(zha)001:3836: g.yas rnams rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3837: thugs kar bsnams shing g.yon pa mnyam gzhag mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:3838: yum bzhi phyoogs mdog rdo rje rin chen chos //
NK021(zha)001:3839: las ma bzhi ste phyag mtshan yab dang mthun //
NK021(zha)001:3840: rigs lnga yab yum thugs rjes 'di zung zhig /
NK021(zha)001:3841: byin rlabs dbang bskur dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3842: mu ne mu ne ma h+aa mu na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3844: ga te ga te p+aa ra ga te p+aa ra sam ga te bo d+hi s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:3847: shar phyogs sangs rgyas dkon mchog 'byung gnas dkar //
NK021(zha)001:3848: g.yas pa mchog sbyin 'khor lo g.yon skyabs sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:3849: shar lho nub byang dkar sngo dmar ljang mdog /
NK021(zha)001:3850: chos kyi rgyal mtshan chu srin rgyal mtshan can //
NK021(zha)001:3851: dbang phyug rgyal po lcags kyu 'bar ba 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3852: bkod pa'i rgyal mtshan mdzes pa'i me tog bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3853: rin chen 'od 'phro nor bu rin chen 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3854: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3855: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3856: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3857: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3858: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3859: lho phyogs sangs rgyas mya ngan med dpal sngo //
NK021(zha)001:3860: thugs kar skyabs sbyin rin chen g.yon mnyam gzhag /
NK021(zha)001:3861: shar lho nub byang dkar ser dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3862: snang ba'i mchog ni phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3863: phyag rgya'i rgyal po rdo rje rgya gram 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3864: spos kyi glang po 'bud dung dkar po ste //
NK021(zha)001:3865: spobs pa brtsegs pa gser g.yu'i za ma tog /
NK021(zha)001:3866: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3867: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3868: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3869: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3870: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3872: skyabs sbyin thugs kar pad+ma bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3873: g.yon pa mchog sbyin pus mo'i steng //
NK021(zha)001:3874: phyogs bzhir dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3875: pad+ma'i rgyal po sgrom bu ste //
NK021(zha)001:3877: rdo rje mi g.yo lcags kyu'o //
NK021(zha)001:3878: thogs med rgyal po ral gri 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3879: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3880: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3881: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3882: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3883: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3884: byang phyogs rgyal pa'i dbang po ljang //
NK021(zha)001:3885: g.yas pa skyabs sbyin nyi ma ste //
NK021(zha)001:3886: g.yon pa mchog sbyin rdo rje can //
NK021(zha)001:3887: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3889: grub pa sna tshogs rdo rje ste //
NK021(zha)001:3890: dga' ba ston pa me long can //
NK021(zha)001:3891: mi g.yo ba ni mnyam bzhag rgya //
NK021(zha)001:3892: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3893: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3894: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3895: dbang bskur byin gyi brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3896: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3897: byang shar glang po dam pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3898: ljang gu thugs kar pusti bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3899: g.yon pa mchog sbyin chos gos 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3900: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3901: phyag na rdo rje rtse dgu ste //
NK021(zha)001:3902: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad dkar 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3903: nam mkha'i snying po za ma tog /
NK021(zha)001:3904: sa snying rin chen myu gu'o //
NK021(zha)001:3905: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3906: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3907: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3908: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3909: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3910: shar lho pad+mo dam pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3911: dkar ser g.yas pa nyi ma ste //
NK021(zha)001:3912: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3913: kun bzang rin chen sdong bu ste //
NK021(zha)001:3916: byams pa klu shing gun+d+he bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3917: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3918: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3919: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3920: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3921: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3922: lho nub snang ba dam pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3923: dmar ser nyi ma thugs kar bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3924: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3925: mthu chen thob ni rdo rje ste //
NK021(zha)001:3926: sman gyi rgyal po bum pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:3927: yon tan snying po rin chen snye //
NK021(zha)001:3928: mthong na dga' ba klu shing ngo //
NK021(zha)001:3929: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3930: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3931: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3932: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3933: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3934: nub byang gdugs mdzes dam pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3935: dmar ljang g.yas na gdugs kyis brjid //
NK021(zha)001:3936: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3937: gzhon nu rgyal mtshan ut+pa la //
NK021(zha)001:3938: skyes bu dam pa dung rnga yab //
NK021(zha)001:3939: seng ge sgra ni ku mu d+aa //
NK021(zha)001:3941: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3942: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3943: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3944: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3945: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3946: steng phyogs sangs rgyas dga' ba'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:3947: dkar po g.yas na rgyal mtshan bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3948: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3949: bzang skyong gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3950: dkon mchog 'byung gnas rin chen sgrom //
NK021(zha)001:3951: dpa' bar 'gro ba ral gri ste //
NK021(zha)001:3952: zla 'od gzhon nu zla tshes so //
NK021(zha)001:3953: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3954: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3955: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3956: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3957: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3960: phyogs bzhi dkar sngo dmar ljang sems //
NK021(zha)001:3961: ye shes tog ni tog dkar po //
NK021(zha)001:3962: mya ngan med mchog ral gri ste //
NK021(zha)001:3964: ye shes 'od de rdo rje bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3965: shar nub sems dpa' lho byang nyan thos tshul //
NK021(zha)001:3966: sems ma rdo rje rin chen pad rgya gram //
NK021(zha)001:3967: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3968: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3969: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3970: shar du glang po'i gdan khri la //
NK021(zha)001:3971: brgya byin ser po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3972: shar lhor ra skyes gdan steng du //
NK021(zha)001:3974: lho ru ma he'i gdan la ni //
NK021(zha)001:3975: gshin rje sngon po be con 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3976: lho nub ro langs gdan steng du //
NK021(zha)001:3977: srin po smug nag ral gri 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3978: nub tu chu srin gdan la ni //
NK021(zha)001:3979: chu lha dmar po sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3980: nub byang sha ba'i gdan steng du //
NK021(zha)001:3981: rlung lha ljang gu ba dan 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3982: byang du rta yi gdan la ni //
NK021(zha)001:3983: gnod sbyin ljang sngon dbyug pa 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3984: byang shar khyu mchog gdan la ni //
NK021(zha)001:3985: dbang ldan nag po rtse gsum 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:3986: steng du ngang pa'i gdan steng du //
NK021(zha)001:3988: 'og tu phag gi gdan la ni //
NK021(zha)001:3989: brtan ma ser po gter bum bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:3990: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3991: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3992: mu ne ga te a b+hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:3993: sgeg phreng glu gar me tog spos //
NK021(zha)001:3994: mar me dri chab sgo skyong bzhi //
NK021(zha)001:3995: rgyal ba mchod cing bstan pa bsrung //
NK021(zha)001:3996: tshad med phrin las gdul bya skyong //
NK021(zha)001:3997: 'gro la thugs rjes bzung du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:3998: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:4000: ga te a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:4002: de nas rgyal po bka' rtags sam 'gro 'dul mtshan
NK021(zha)001:4003: nyid kyi dbang du grags pa byang chub sems dpa'i
NK021(zha)001:4004: mdzad pa nyi shu'i rdzas dbang rnams bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:4005: sngon byung ston pa'i rnam thar dang rjes su mthun
NK021(zha)001:4006: pa'i yon tan khyad par can de dag rgyud la
NK021(zha)001:4007: thob par gyur snyam pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:4008: de la rdzas dbang nyi shu las /
NK021(zha)001:4009: dang po dbu rgyan bskon te /
NK021(zha)001:4010: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK021(zha)001:4011: dga' ldan gyi gnas nas yum sgyu ma lha mdzes
NK021(zha)001:4012: kyi lhums su gshegs pa'i tshe dbu las rin po
NK021(zha)001:4013: che'i phrog zhu phud nas mi pham mgon la chos
NK021(zha)001:4014: kyi rgyal tshab tu lha rnams kyi ston par dbang
NK021(zha)001:4015: bskur ro // de bzhin du rin po che'i con
NK021(zha)001:4016: pan gyi dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal tshab byed
NK021(zha)001:4017: pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4019: tog dkar dbu las rin chen cod pan phud //
NK021(zha)001:4020: de nyid phyag gis bu yi dbu la bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:4021: mi pham mgon po chos kyi rgyal tshab rje //
NK021(zha)001:4022: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po byed par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4023: chos kyi dbyings nas byung nas ga na bar //
NK021(zha)001:4024: sprul sku kun khyab yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK021(zha)001:4025: dang po tshogs rdzogs smon lam mthar phyin pa //
NK021(zha)001:4026: 'di ni bsod nams rdzogs pa'i dbang gi bkra shis dang po'o //
NK021(zha)001:4027: gnyis pa yum gyi tsakli spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK021(zha)001:4028: sngon byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po
NK021(zha)001:4029: de yum gyi lhums na bzhugs pa'i tshe yum gyi
NK021(zha)001:4030: phyag gis sems cad rnams la reg cing dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:4031: bas sems cad rnams kyi nad dang sdug bsngal thams
NK021(zha)001:4033: de bzhin du yum gyi phyag gis reg cing dbang
NK021(zha)001:4034: bskur bas nyon mongs pa dang nad dang sdug bsngal
NK021(zha)001:4035: thams cad zhi bar gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4036: sgyu ma lha mdzes lha yi lcam //
NK021(zha)001:4037: lha yi lus la rin chen mdzes //
NK021(zha)001:4038: nyon mongs sdug bsngal kun zhi nas //
NK021(zha)001:4039: na tsha'i sdug bsngal las thar shog /
NK021(zha)001:4040: byin rlabs yum chen shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK021(zha)001:4041: kun la byams snyoms thugs rje che ba'i ma //
NK021(zha)001:4042: gzhan la phan mdzad don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK021(zha)001:4043: 'di ni lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang gi bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4044: gsum pa seng phrug zung gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:4045: sngon byang chub sems dpa' lum+bi ni'i tshal du yum
NK021(zha)001:4046: gyi lhums nas bltams pa'i tshe seng ge'i phru gu
NK021(zha)001:4047: zung zhig gis bskor ba byas shing dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4048: rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis gnan pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:4049: thob bo // de bzhin du seng phrug gi phyir
NK021(zha)001:4050: rgol ba'i phyogs thams cad zil gyis gnon pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:4052: seng ge'i nga ro skad chem thogs med pas //
NK021(zha)001:4053: 'jigs pa med pa'i sgra chen bsgrags nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:4054: bar du gcod pa'i bdud kyi sde btul te //
NK021(zha)001:4055: rgol ba'i tshogs rnams zil gyis gnon par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4056: thams cad zil gnon cho 'phrul che ba'i lha //
NK021(zha)001:4057: yon tan kun tshang gdug pa zil gyis gnon //
NK021(zha)001:4058: che ba'i mthu stobs khyad pa kun la 'phags //
NK021(zha)001:4059: 'di ni che btsan mthu stobs dbang gi bkra shis gsum pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4060: bzhi pa glang chen phru gu zung gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:4061: sngon byang chub sems dpa' grong khyer ser skya na
NK021(zha)001:4062: bzhugs pa'i tshe glang po che'i phru gu gnyis kyi
NK021(zha)001:4063: snas byugs shing dbang bskur bas 'jig rten 'degs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4065: de bzhin du glang po che'i phru gu zung gi
NK021(zha)001:4066: dbang bskur bas 'jig rten 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan
NK021(zha)001:4067: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4069: theg pa bzhi yi don rtogs nas //
NK021(zha)001:4070: bye brag 'byed pa'i stobs rdzogs te //
NK021(zha)001:4071: stobs kyi pha rol phyin rdzogs shing //
NK021(zha)001:4072: mthu stobs phun tshogs ldan pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:4073: rin chen gser rgyan kun gyis spras //
NK021(zha)001:4074: dpe byad mtshan rdzogs glang po'i stobs //
NK021(zha)001:4075: 'di ni stobs bcu ldan pa'i dbang gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4076: lnga pa ka shi ka'i ras bzung /
NK021(zha)001:4077: sngon byang chub sems dpa' lum+bi ni'i tshal du sku
NK021(zha)001:4078: bltams pa'i tshe tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis blangs
NK021(zha)001:4079: nas na bza' ka shi ka'i ras gsol te dbang
NK021(zha)001:4080: bskur bas mkhyen pa'i bye brag gsal zhing ma 'dres
NK021(zha)001:4082: de bzhin du na bza' ka shi ka'i ras kyi
NK021(zha)001:4083: dbang bskur bas mkhyen pa'i ye shes gsal zhing ma
NK021(zha)001:4084: 'dres pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4085: nyon mongs skyon spangs ka shi'i ras //
NK021(zha)001:4086: legs pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs te //
NK021(zha)001:4087: nyes pa'i skyon las skyob pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:4088: mkhyen pa'i bye brag gsal bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:4089: brgya byin bsod nams dag pa'i lha //
NK021(zha)001:4090: tshangs pa mngon shes lnga dang ldan //
NK021(zha)001:4091: bdud rtsi chos 'khor zhu ba'i bdag /
NK021(zha)001:4092: 'di ni yon tan rin chen dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4093: drug pa tsakli dang bum pa sbrags nas bum chu spyi bor gtigs shing blud de /
NK021(zha)001:4094: sngon byang chub sems dpa' yum gyi lhums nas bltams
NK021(zha)001:4095: pa'i tshe klu'i rgyal po dga' bo dang nyer dga'
NK021(zha)001:4096: gnyis kyis lho phyogs kyi chu mig rta rnga 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:4097: nas bdud rtsi'i chu blangs te khrus gsol bas nyon
NK021(zha)001:4098: mongs pa'i dri ma dag pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK021(zha)001:4099: de bzhin du bum rdzas chu'i dbang bskur bas nyon
NK021(zha)001:4100: mongs pa'i bag chags kyi dri ma byang zhing dag
NK021(zha)001:4101: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4102: klu rgyal bdud rtsi'i chu blangs te //
NK021(zha)001:4103: bcom ldan drin lan bsrab pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4104: sku yi dri ma yongs su bkru //
NK021(zha)001:4105: skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4106: yon tan kun ldan byang chub sems dpa'i rigs //
NK021(zha)001:4107: bcom ldan rjes dran smon lam grub pa'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4108: dri ma kun 'khrud legs pa mthar phyin pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4109: 'di ni sku tshe ring ba'i dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4110: bdun pa ming gi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:4111: rgyal ba'i sras zhes pa lta bu byang sems dang phar phyin bcu las gras pa'i ming btags te /
NK021(zha)001:4112: sngon byang chub sems dpa' bltams nas dgung lo bdun
NK021(zha)001:4113: lon pa'i tshe sh+aakya'i rigs rnams 'tshogs nas gzhon nu
NK021(zha)001:4114: don grub pa zhes mtshan btags te dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4115: shes bya la ma rmongs pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK021(zha)001:4116: de bzhin du rigs kyi bu la rgyal ba'i sras
NK021(zha)001:4117: po zhes bya ba'i ming gi dbang bskur bas shes
NK021(zha)001:4118: bya la ma rmongs pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:4119: / rigs kyi bu khyod deng phan chad //
NK021(zha)001:4120: ming mchog grags pas dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:4121: gzhon nu don grub yin pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4122: rgyal bu don grub thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4123: rgyal rigs khrims gtsang mang po 'dus pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:4124: lha mi kun la dbang bsgyur rgyal por bskos //
NK021(zha)001:4125: kun las 'phags pa'i rgyal dbang dam pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:4126: 'di ni kun gyi rgyal po'i dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4127: brgyad pa rgyan cha gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:4128: sngon byang chub sems dpa' la sru skye dgu'i bdag
NK021(zha)001:4129: mos rgyan gyi bye brag gis brgyan cing dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:4130: bas sa rdo la byas pa'i bsam mno med pa
NK021(zha)001:4131: phyag gis tshur stsal ba'i dbang thob bo //
NK021(zha)001:4132: de bzhin du rgyan gyi bye brag gi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:4133: bas 'gro ba thams cad shes pa dang ldan par
NK021(zha)001:4134: byed pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4135: mdzes pa'i rgyan rnams myur du 'phags nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:4136: legs pa'i yon tan kun tshang ye shes sku //
NK021(zha)001:4137: ma rig thar lam ma lus 'dren pa'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4138: rtogs pa'i yon tan mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4139: yon tan kun rdzogs sru mos mdzes pa'i rgyan //
NK021(zha)001:4140: legs pa kun rdzogs yon tan mthar phyin pa //
NK021(zha)001:4141: che ba'i yon tan gzhal gyis mi lang ste //
NK021(zha)001:4142: 'di ni legs pa kun rdzogs dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4144: sngon byang chub sems dpas yig dpon kun gyi bshes gnyen las yi ge slob pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:4145: tsan+dana sbrul gyi snying po'i byang shing gser gyi wam
NK021(zha)001:4146: mig btags pa rin po che sna tshogs kyis brgyan
NK021(zha)001:4147: te yi ge slob pa'i dbang bskur bas yig dpon
NK021(zha)001:4148: yang dngangs te lha mi'i yi ge thams cad la
NK021(zha)001:4150: de bzhin du yig shing gi dbang bskur bas chos
NK021(zha)001:4151: kyi sgra sgrog pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:4152: cig / tsan+dana sbrul gyi yig shing la //
NK021(zha)001:4153: rin chen gser gyi wam mig btags //
NK021(zha)001:4154: 'gro ba'i don byed yi ge'i mthu //
NK021(zha)001:4155: chos kyi sgra rnams sgrogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4156: chos nyid kun ston rdzu 'phrul yi ge'i mthu //
NK021(zha)001:4157: pha rol zil gnon chos rnams kun las rgyal //
NK021(zha)001:4158: 'di 'dra'i yon tan gzhan na med pa'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4159: 'di ni yi ge tshogs rdzogs dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4161: sngon byang chub sems dpa' sgyu rtsal gyi stobs 'gran
NK021(zha)001:4162: pa'i tshe mes seng ge 'gram gyi gnam ru brdungs
NK021(zha)001:4163: pas sgra'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa byung
NK021(zha)001:4164: ste sgyu rtsal gyis 'dul ba'i dbang thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:4165: to // de bzhin du gnam ru'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4166: snyan pa'i sgra sgrog cing bdud dpung 'dul ba'i 'phongs
NK021(zha)001:4167: rtsal dang ldan pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4168: snyan pa sgra sgrog gnam ru mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4169: 'gro ba kun gyi yid tshim zhing //
NK021(zha)001:4170: gnod pa'i bdud rnams bcom nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:4171: ma rung 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:4172: thams cad kun 'dul mthu stobs phun sum tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:4173: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyis pha rol zil gyis gnon //
NK021(zha)001:4174: don dang mi 'gal gdug pa zhi mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:4175: 'di ni gnam ru dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4177: sngon byang chub sems dpa' rgyal srid khab tu bzhes
NK021(zha)001:4178: pa'i tshe sh+aakya sa 'tsho ma khab tu phul te
NK021(zha)001:4179: dbang bskur bas rigs mi nub cing 'gro ba khyim
NK021(zha)001:4181: de bzhin du btsun mo'i dbang bskur bas rigs mi
NK021(zha)001:4182: nub cing ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin du 'gro don
NK021(zha)001:4183: byed pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4184: nor bu rin chen byi dor byas shing gsal //
NK021(zha)001:4185: sh+aakya sa 'tsho ma bkab phyar na yang //
NK021(zha)001:4186: blo mos yid gcugs dang bas sems bskyed de //
NK021(zha)001:4187: dgos pa'i don rnams yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4188: khyim dang 'du 'dzis 'dul bar gzigs pa yi /
NK021(zha)001:4189: khab dang rgyal srid 'khor los sgyur ba'i tshul /
NK021(zha)001:4190: khams gsum khyim pa rnams kyi don mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:4191: 'di ni btsun mo dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4193: sngon byang chub sems dpa' grong khyer gyi phyogs bzhir
NK021(zha)001:4194: shing rta'i kha lo bsgyur bas 'khor ba'i chos thams
NK021(zha)001:4195: cad mi rtag par mkhyen pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK021(zha)001:4196: de bzhin du shing rta'i dbang bskur bas skye rga
NK021(zha)001:4197: na 'chi'i sdug bsngal sun dbyung ba'i dbang thob par
NK021(zha)001:4198: gyur cig / rgyal srid longs spyod dpal dang ldan pa'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4199: 'gro ba'i don mdzad 'khor los sgyur ba'i lha //
NK021(zha)001:4200: lha mi yongs kyi spyod pa bsam mi khyab //
NK021(zha)001:4201: skye shi mi rtag pa las bzlog par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4202: rgyal srid dpal 'byor longs spyod phun sum tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:4203: gling bzhi mtha' skor skye rga na 'chi spong //
NK021(zha)001:4204: 'khor ba'i skyon shas sdug bsngal sel mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:4205: 'di ni shing rta dbang ba'i bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4207: sngon byang chub sems dpa' khab nas byung ba'i tshe
NK021(zha)001:4208: 'bangs mos pas chibs basngagasa ldan rin po che brgyan
NK021(zha)001:4209: te phul bas mtshan phyed la dpags tshad brgya 'das
NK021(zha)001:4210: te rab tu byung nas nyon mongs las thar pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4211: dbang thob bo // de bzhin du chibs kyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:4212: bskur bas rab tu 'byung zhing nyon mongs pa las
NK021(zha)001:4213: grol ba'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4214: gar yang thogs med brtson 'grus myur ba'i shugs //
NK021(zha)001:4215: tshangs pa brgya byin mthu byin che ba'i lha //
NK021(zha)001:4216: rgyal chen rigs bzhis 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan //
NK021(zha)001:4217: thogs med tshangs par spyod pa'i mthu ldan shog /
NK021(zha)001:4218: 'khor ba'i chos rnams mchil ma bzhin du dor //
NK021(zha)001:4219: nyes tshogs dgra rnams ma lus gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4220: 'dod pa'i rgyu spong rnam rtogs 'joms mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:4221: 'di ni chibs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4223: sngon byang chub sems dpa' mchod rten rnam dag gi
NK021(zha)001:4224: drung du rab tu byung ba'i tshe sum cu rtsa
NK021(zha)001:4225: gsum gyi lha mdzes pa'i tog gis shan ral gri
NK021(zha)001:4226: phul te dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba
NK021(zha)001:4228: de bzhin du shan ral gri'i dbang bskur bas nyon
NK021(zha)001:4229: mongs pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i dbang thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:4230: cig / nyon mongs d+r+wa ba gcod pa'i ral gri ste //
NK021(zha)001:4231: mi shes nyon mongs rgyu rnams bcad nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:4232: bla med byang chub gnas su 'god pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4233: nyon mongs sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba gcod par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4234: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus bcom nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:4235: bde ba'i don rtogs nags khrod dben par gnas //
NK021(zha)001:4236: bdag don lhun grub gzhan don mthar phyin pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4237: 'di ni tshul khrims dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4239: sngon byang chub sems dpa' chu bo nee rany+dza na'i
NK021(zha)001:4240: 'gram du dka' thub rdzogs pa'i tshe sum cu rtsa
NK021(zha)001:4241: gsum pa'i lha'i bu yid bzhin 'byung bar gseg gshang
NK021(zha)001:4242: dang par bu phal bas 'gro don mthar phyin pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4243: dbang thob bo // de bzhin du gseg gshang dang
NK021(zha)001:4244: par bu'i dbang bskur bas 'gro don mthar phyin pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4246: ser sna'i mdud pa 'grol phyir gseg gshang bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4247: chog shes dgang ba sla phyir par bu bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4248: bsod nams tshogs rdzogs byang chub nyid kyi sku //
NK021(zha)001:4249: bdag dang gzhan don mthar phyin rdzogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4250: ma rig gnyid slong sil byed sgra //
NK021(zha)001:4251: lhung bzed zag med yon tan snod //
NK021(zha)001:4252: zhi zhing dbang po rab dul ba //
NK021(zha)001:4253: 'di ni don grub dbang gi bkra shis bco lnga pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4254: bcu drug pa na bza' dur smrig /
NK021(zha)001:4255: sngon byang chub sems dpa' rab tu byung ba'i tshe
NK021(zha)001:4256: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bus na bza' dur
NK021(zha)001:4257: smrig phul bas srid pa'i gdung ba las skyob pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4258: dbang thob bo // de bzhin du na bza' dur
NK021(zha)001:4259: smrig gi dbang bskur bas srid pa'i gdung ba las
NK021(zha)001:4260: skyob pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4261: ngan 'gro skyob phyir na bza' chos gos gsol //
NK021(zha)001:4262: mi shes rmongs pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:4263: bag chag skyon gyi dri mas ma gos pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4264: 'bras bu byang chub gnas su 'grub par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4265: bslab gsum tshul khrims sgo gsum rnam par dag /
NK021(zha)001:4266: bde ba mchog brnyes 'jigs pa'i dgra las rgyal //
NK021(zha)001:4267: rab byung dge sbyong rkang gnyis lha mi'i gtso //
NK021(zha)001:4268: na bza' dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4270: sngon byang chub sems dpa' chu bo nee rany+dza na'i
NK021(zha)001:4271: 'gram du bka' thub lo gnyis la 'bras nyag ma
NK021(zha)001:4272: re / lo gnyis la chu thig pa re /
NK021(zha)001:4273: lo gnyis la ci yang ma gsol ba la tshor
NK021(zha)001:4274: ba mi mnga' yang sku rid cing skams pa'i tshe
NK021(zha)001:4275: grong pa'i bu mo legs skyes mas 'o thug 'bras
NK021(zha)001:4276: chan 'khar gzhong gang phul bas sku gser gyi gtan
NK021(zha)001:4277: pa phyis pa ltar gyur te mtshan dang dpe byad
NK021(zha)001:4278: dang ldan pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK021(zha)001:4279: de bzhin du 'o thug 'bras chan gyi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:4280: bas sku mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:4282: nyon mongs med pa'i 'bras bu'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4283: zhi ba'i ngang la rab tu gnas //
NK021(zha)001:4284: bsod nams thob phyir bsngosa pa 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:4285: mtshan dang dpe byad rdzogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4286: zag med bdud rtsi chos kyi ro //
NK021(zha)001:4287: bsod nams lus rdzogs ye shes kyi //
NK021(zha)001:4288: mtshan dpes rab brjid rgyal ba'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:4289: dbang mchog bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4290: bco brgyad pa r+ts+wa dar+b+ha'i stan //
NK021(zha)001:4291: sngon byang chub sems dpa' byang chub kyi shing drung
NK021(zha)001:4292: du gshegs pa'i tshe r+ts+wa 'tshong bkra shis kyis r+ts+wa
NK021(zha)001:4293: rma bya'i mgrin pa ltar sngo ba phyag tu phul
NK021(zha)001:4294: ba stan du bting ste bzhugs pas bdud kyi bar
NK021(zha)001:4295: chad kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang thob bo //
NK021(zha)001:4296: de bzhin du r+ts+wa dar+b+ha'i rdzas kyi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4297: bar chad thams cad kyis mi tshugs pa'i dbang thob
NK021(zha)001:4298: par gyur cig / sngon gyi drang srong rnams kyi grub pa'i rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:4299: ngo mtshar r+ts+wa mchog rma bya'i mgrin pa 'dra //
NK021(zha)001:4300: nyes med legs pa mtha' dag rdzogs byed pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4301: 'gro ba'i don du bkra shis rdzogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4302: mnyam nyid mi g.yo rdo rje lta bu'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:4303: ting 'dzin 'jig tshogs lta ba nyi shu 'joms //
NK021(zha)001:4304: bdud rigs tshogs btul mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4305: r+ts+wa mchog dbang gi bkra shis bco brgyad pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4307: sngon bcom ldan 'das ma ga d+har bsod snyoms la
NK021(zha)001:4308: gshegs pa'i tshe spre'usa sbrang rtsi lhung bzed gang phul
NK021(zha)001:4309: bas bkra shis pa'i rdzas su mnga' brnyes par gyur
NK021(zha)001:4310: to // de bzhin du bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyi
NK021(zha)001:4311: dbang bskur bas 'bras bu phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:4313: rgyal rigs spre'u'i gtso bo yis //
NK021(zha)001:4314: sbrang rtsi phul ba'i bsod nams mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4315: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:4316: bkra shis stobs mchog ldan par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4317: stong nyid rang byung zag med snying po'i bcud //
NK021(zha)001:4318: dus gsum rgyal bas zhen med rol par mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:4319: gang gis 'di 'thung mnyam nyid sku gsum rdzogs //
NK021(zha)001:4320: rtsi mchog dbang gi bkra shis bcu dgu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4322: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyes bu gyad kyi nye 'khor
NK021(zha)001:4323: na bzhugs pa'i tshe byang phyogs kyi tshong pa ga
NK021(zha)001:4324: gon dang bzang pos bu ram dang sbrang rtsi phul
NK021(zha)001:4325: ba bzhes pa shin tu bkra shis pa'i rdzas la
NK021(zha)001:4327: de bzhin du bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:4328: bas skye 'chi med pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:4329: / kun gyi snying po yon mchog dang bas phul //
NK021(zha)001:4330: mchod gnas mchog gis rab bzhes 'bras bu ni //
NK021(zha)001:4331: rgyal bar lung bstan smon lam myur thob phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4332: 'di dag bkra shis thogs med rdzogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4333: yon tan rab rdzogs sangs rgyas sa la gnas //
NK021(zha)001:4334: go 'phang bla med rgyal thabs spyod pa gcig /
NK021(zha)001:4335: 'gro don mthar phyin 'jig rten gsum gyi mgon //
NK021(zha)001:4336: mdzad pa mthar phyin dbang mchog nyi shu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4338: de ltar byang sems kyi theg pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:4339: mdo rang lugs kyi sbyor lam gnyis pa mtshan ma
NK021(zha)001:4340: rtags kyi rnal 'byor bslab pa rgyun gyis non pa
NK021(zha)001:4341: dang rigs 'dra ba'i yon tan gsos thebs /
NK021(zha)001:4342: mngon du rgyu'i bag chags 'bring po dag /
NK021(zha)001:4343: srid zhi las rnam par grol ba'i rgyu dang //
NK021(zha)001:4344: lam gong ma la sbyor ba byang chub kyi sems skye ba'i stegs su gyur /
NK021(zha)001:4345: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab chen po sa
NK021(zha)001:4346: bcu pa'i byang sems kyi rtogs rigs dang 'dra ba'i
NK021(zha)001:4347: yon tan khyad par can thob pa'i skal pa can
NK021(zha)001:4349: rjes kyi bya ba la spyi don gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:4352: gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid gdab pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4353: spyi don dang po lam khyer la bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:4354: dang po theg pa lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:4355: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:4358: bden pa gnyis kyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK021(zha)001:4359: don dam par chos thams cad dbyings rang bzhin gyis
NK021(zha)001:4360: spros pa dang bral ba'i gshis lugs rtogs pa'i ngang
NK021(zha)001:4361: nas / kun rdzob tu rten 'brel ma 'gags pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4362: 'char sgo sgyu ma ltar snang tsam du byams snying
NK021(zha)001:4363: rje byang chub kyi sems kyis zin par byas te
NK021(zha)001:4364: nas / / dge mi dge la 'jug ldog gi
NK021(zha)001:4365: tshul gyis thabs shes zung 'brel gyi spyod pas 'jug
NK021(zha)001:4368: de'ang kun rdzob tu chos thams cad med bzhin du snang ba chu zla ltar rtogs shing /
NK021(zha)001:4369: don dam par spros pa thams cad zhi ba'i tshul
NK021(zha)001:4370: du rtogs pas na bden gnyis kyi gnas lugs rtogs
NK021(zha)001:4372: mnyam pa'i don nyid mi shes shing //
NK021(zha)001:4373: kun rdzob don dam gnyis 'byed la //
NK021(zha)001:4374: chos dang gang zag bdag med na //
NK021(zha)001:4375: 'di ni byang chub sa pa yin //
NK021(zha)001:4378: nyes spyod las ldog pa sdom pa'i tshul khrims /
NK021(zha)001:4379: bsam sbyor thams cad gzhan don du spyod pa sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims /
NK021(zha)001:4380: phyin drug gis bsdus pa'i legs spyod sgrub pa dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims so //
NK021(zha)001:4382: spyir slob pa'i lam bzhir byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun dang /
NK021(zha)001:4383: mthar lam du gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya dang /
NK021(zha)001:4384: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum 'phrag la sogs pa sgom pa yin mod /
NK021(zha)001:4386: zhi lhag zung du 'brel ba'i rnam par mi rtog pa'i lam sgom pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:4388: zhi gnas rab tu ldan pa'i lhag mthong gis //
NK021(zha)001:4389: nyon mongs rnam par 'joms par shes bya ste //
NK021(zha)001:4392: phar phyin bcu dang bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi gzhan don du spyod pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4394: rang lam gyis bskal pa grangs med gsum nas mi
NK021(zha)001:4395: slob pa'i lam kun tu 'od kyi sa thob par
NK021(zha)001:4396: 'dod mod / sngags kyi theg pa las ni /
NK021(zha)001:4397: phar phyin theg pa'i lam gyis mthar phyin par bsgrubs
NK021(zha)001:4398: kyang sa bcu pa'i byang sems kyi go 'phang las
NK021(zha)001:4400: skabs der sngags lam la nges par zhugs nas sangs rgyas thob pas na /
NK021(zha)001:4401: mthar thug theg pa gcig tu grub par gsungs so //
NK021(zha)001:4402: gnyis pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:4403: don dam par 'phags bzhi'i yum so so rang rig
NK021(zha)001:4404: pa'i ye shes kyi spyod yul dbyings spros pa dang
NK021(zha)001:4405: bral ba'i ngang las bsal bzhag med par bskyangs pas
NK021(zha)001:4407: kun rdzob tu brda'i yum shes rab kyi pha rol
NK021(zha)001:4408: tu phyin ma la sras phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis
NK021(zha)001:4409: bskor ba'i sku'i rnam pa gsal btab nas /
NK021(zha)001:4410: phyag mchod 'bul ba la sogs pas bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4411: gsum pa snying po lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:4412: lha rnams kyi sku las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK021(zha)001:4413: 'phags pa rnams sems can gyi don la bskul zhing /
NK021(zha)001:4414: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyi sdig sgrib sbyangs nas lam dang 'bras bu'i bde ba la bkod /
NK021(zha)001:4415: 'od zer des bdag la reg pas gzhan don sgrub mthu thob par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:4417: ga te ga te sogs bzla ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:4418: bzhi pa bslab bya lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:4419: 'di byang chub sems dpa'i mdzad pa nyi shu'i dbang yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:4420: de dang rjes su mthun par byang chub kyi spyod pa la bslab dgos /
NK021(zha)001:4421: de la spang bya byang sdom gyi mi mthun phyogs rtsa ba'i ltung ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:4423: rgyal po la nges pa lnga /
NK021(zha)001:4424: blon po la nges pa lnga /
NK021(zha)001:4425: phal pa la nges pa brgyad /
NK021(zha)001:4426: thun mong du smon sems btang ba dang bcu dgu gsungs /
NK021(zha)001:4428: rnyed dang bkur stir chags pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:4429: bdag bstod gzhan la smod pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:4430: sdug bsngal mgon med gyur pa la //
NK021(zha)001:4431: ser snas chos nor mi ster dang //
NK021(zha)001:4432: gzhan gyis bshags kyang mi nyan par //
NK021(zha)001:4433: khro bas gzhan la 'tshogs pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:4434: theg pa chen po spong byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:4438: bslab btus su brgyad cu dang /
NK021(zha)001:4439: sdom pa nyi shu par zhe drug gsungs te /
NK021(zha)001:4442: shes bzhin gsum dang ldan pas ltung ba de dag gis mi gos pa la bslab pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:4443: nyin mtshan dus drug tu rgyun bshags bya zhing /
NK021(zha)001:4444: smon pa'i bslab bya bdag gzhan mnyam pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:4446: gzhan gces par 'dzin pa'i byang chub kyi sems gsum sgom pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:4447: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol tu phyin pa drug la bslab par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:4448: spyi don gnyis pa 'gag drug bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4450: gang gis gang la gang du ci yi phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4451: tshul dang dgos par bcas pa rnam drug ste //
NK021(zha)001:4452: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa'i 'gag drug yin //
NK021(zha)001:4453: zhes gsungs pa ltar gang du bshad pa'i gnas ni /
NK021(zha)001:4454: rgyal po'i khab kyi bya rgod phung po'i ri'o //
NK021(zha)001:4455: gang gis bshad pa'i ston pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4456: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas so //
NK021(zha)001:4458: byang chub sems dpa' don grub la sogs pa rnams so //
NK021(zha)001:4459: gang bshad pa'i theg pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4460: shes rab dang snying rje chen pos gzhan don rlabs
NK021(zha)001:4461: po che spyod pa'i thabs byang chub sems dpa'i theg
NK021(zha)001:4463: 'gro ba 'dul ba byang sems kyi mdzad pa nyi
NK021(zha)001:4464: shu'i dbang bskur bas blo mchog tu gyur pa rnams
NK021(zha)001:4465: mdzad pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i ched du'o //
NK021(zha)001:4466: de ltar bstan pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4467: bdud dpung bcom nas chos kyi rgyal srid 'dzin pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4468: spyi don gsum pa gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid ni /
NK021(zha)001:4469: bsam gtan gyi 'dug stangs chos bdun dang ldan pas /
NK021(zha)001:4470: rang gi snying dkyil du thig le cog sgong tsam
NK021(zha)001:4471: pa 'od kyi rnam pa kha dog gang du yang
NK021(zha)001:4474: thig le stong pa skye ba med //
NK021(zha)001:4475: ces pas thig le de la brtags pa na kha
NK021(zha)001:4476: dog gi rnam pa ma 'gags par cir yang snang
NK021(zha)001:4477: la / kha dog de dag la brtags pas gang
NK021(zha)001:4478: du'ang ma grub pa'i ngang la rtse gcig tu 'jog
NK021(zha)001:4479: la / go // de ltar dpyad cing bsgoms pas blo gnas pa na /
NK021(zha)001:4481: dbang bskur bya skur byed bskur ba la sogs pa'i bya byed kyis mtshon /
NK021(zha)001:4482: phyi nang gi snang ba'i dngos po 'di dag rten 'brel tsam du ma 'gags par shar yang /
NK021(zha)001:4483: snang tsam nyid nas don la cung zad kyang grub
NK021(zha)001:4484: pa med pa rmi lam gyi snang ba lta bu
NK021(zha)001:4485: dang / de ltar nyams su myong mkhan rang sems
NK021(zha)001:4486: kyi ngo bo la cer gyi bltas shing btsal ba
NK021(zha)001:4487: na dbyibs kha dog sogs ci'i ngo bor yang ma
NK021(zha)001:4488: grub pas 'dzin med stong par thag bcad nas /
NK021(zha)001:4489: yul dngos med stong gzugs dang /
NK021(zha)001:4490: yul can 'dzin sems skad cig cha med do //
NK021(zha)001:4491: zhes myong mkhan gyi gnyen po kho rang gi ngo
NK021(zha)001:4492: bo la'ang ce re bltas pas gtad med du sangs
NK021(zha)001:4493: te / gzung 'dzin gang du'ang ma grub pa'i stong
NK021(zha)001:4494: gsal nam mkha' lta bu'i rig pa smra bsam brjod
NK021(zha)001:4496: de ka'i ngang la bsal bzhag med par glod pas bdag med gnyis kyi don rtogs par 'gyur la /
NK021(zha)001:4497: de ltar mnyam bzhag tu bdag med gnyis rtogs pa
NK021(zha)001:4498: de rjes thob tu dran shes kyis bskyang ba ni
NK021(zha)001:4499: / snang ba gang shar kyang med pa gsal snang sgyu ma lta bur thag bcad nas /
NK021(zha)001:4500: de nyid lha rjes dran gyi sgor dag pa'i snang
NK021(zha)001:4501: ba yum sher phyin gyi sku'i rnam par wal gyis
NK021(zha)001:4502: gsal btab nas rgyun chags su bskyang bar bya ba
NK021(zha)001:4503: yin no // des byang sems kyi theg pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:4504: bskur ba'i man ngag dang bcas pa grub pas ji
NK021(zha)001:4505: ltar gdams pa rnams tshul bzhin du bsgrub snyam pas
NK021(zha)001:4506: yin no // / gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blang ngo //
NK021(zha)001:4508: deng nas brtsams te sogs kyis yon dbul zhing /
NK021(zha)001:4509: dge ba bsngo ba rnams sngar ltar dang /
NK021(zha)001:4510: rjes chog rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:4511: zab don man ngag bdud rtsi'i chus //
NK021(zha)001:4512: shes rab dbang po'i za ma tog /
NK021(zha)001:4513: yongs bkang brtse bas chos sbyin rgyun //
NK021(zha)001:4514: dad ldan gdung sel dpal du spel //
NK021(zha)001:4515: byang sems theg pa'i dbang chog gi le tshan no //
NK021(zha)001:4518: ye shes gcig nyid rigs gsum gyi //
NK021(zha)001:4520: ston mdzad rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK021(zha)001:4521: btud nas kri ya'i dbang chog bshad //
NK021(zha)001:4522: da ni lnga pa bya spyod thun mong gi theg pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:4524: dngos gzhi dkyil 'khor bris sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa grub nas /
NK021(zha)001:4525: dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:4526: dang po slob dpon 'jug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4527: slob ma ji ltar 'jug pa'i cho gas bdag nyid zhugs te dbang blang ba'am /
NK021(zha)001:4529: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang bla ma gnyis su
NK021(zha)001:4530: med par mos la rig pa'i me tog phul bas
NK021(zha)001:4531: dkyil 'khor pa'i rdo rje gsum dang rang gi sgo
NK021(zha)001:4532: gsum gnyis med du gyur par bsam ste /
NK021(zha)001:4533: slob dpon gyi las la rjes su gnang ba thob par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:4534: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4535: las bum gyi chus khrus byas /
NK021(zha)001:4536: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad /
NK021(zha)001:4537: sems bskyed dang chos nyan pa'i kun spyod gsal 'debs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK021(zha)001:4538: 'dir gang gsan par bya ba'i chos ni //
NK021(zha)001:4540: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil
NK021(zha)001:4541: 'khor zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar las skabs babs kyi
NK021(zha)001:4542: spro bsdu ji ltar rigs pa byas rjes /
NK021(zha)001:4543: lnga pa kri ya'i tan+t+ra ste bya ba'i rgyud /
NK021(zha)001:4544: de la'ang tsam khyad gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:4545: 'dir bya ba khyad par can spyod rgyud dang thun
NK021(zha)001:4546: mong pa'i dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba skabs su
NK021(zha)001:4547: babs pa yin / de la slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams sngon du grub pas /
NK021(zha)001:4548: da slob ma rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa
NK021(zha)001:4549: la thog mar dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang zhu
NK021(zha)001:4550: ba'i yon du man+dala 'bul du bcug nas /
NK021(zha)001:4552: snyim pa me tog dang bcas pas thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:4553: bla ma dkon mchog rnam gsum po //
NK021(zha)001:4554: 'gro ba sems can don slad du //
