NK021(zha)001:4555: bdag la dgongs shing gzigs su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:4556: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:4557: rigs gsum gtso 'khor dgongs su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:4558: lha dang byin rlabs dam tshig dang //
NK021(zha)001:4559: dbang rnams rim par bskur du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:4561: de ltar gsol ba btab pa'i lan du gnang ba sbyin pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4563: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK021(zha)001:4565: khyod la dam tshig dbang bskur sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:4566: gus pa'i sems kyis sgrub par gyis //
NK021(zha)001:4567: nyes pa dag gis ma gos na //
NK021(zha)001:4571: tree lokya bi dza ya h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:4574: ces bzla zhing las bum gyis chus bsang gtor bya /
NK021(zha)001:4575: tsak+shu ban+d+ha wa ra m+aa na ya h+aum gis mig dar bcing /
NK021(zha)001:4577: zhes pas me tog 'dzin du bcug /
NK021(zha)001:4578: de nas sdom pa bzung ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:4579: bla ma dang tha mi dad pa'i rigs gsum gyi
NK021(zha)001:4580: dkyil 'khor la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i
NK021(zha)001:4581: tshogs kyis bskor ba mngon sum du bzhugs par mos
NK021(zha)001:4583: thun mong pa skyabs sems kyi sdom pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4584: sta gon gyi dus blangs ma thag pa yin pas 'dir ma blangs kyang chog la /
NK021(zha)001:4586: thun mong ma yin pa ni rigs gsum spyi'i dam tshig bzung ba'i bsam pas /
NK021(zha)001:4587: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK021(zha)001:4588: dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:4589: bla med dkon mchog gsum po la //
NK021(zha)001:4590: deng nas bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK021(zha)001:4591: bdag gis sangs rgyas bstan pa'i gzhung //
NK021(zha)001:4592: spyi dang mi 'gal legs gnas te //
NK021(zha)001:4593: theg chen gsang sngags bya ba'i gzhung //
NK021(zha)001:4594: khyad par dam tshig bdag gis blang //
NK021(zha)001:4595: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:4596: theg chen gsang ba sngags kyi lha //
NK021(zha)001:4597: don gcig gnyis med ye shes don //
NK021(zha)001:4598: yang dag nyid du bdag gis bzung //
NK021(zha)001:4599: sku yi rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:4600: dam tshig sdom pa la gnas te //
NK021(zha)001:4601: sgrub pa dag kyang ci nus brtsam //
NK021(zha)001:4602: pad+ma'i rigs mchog dag pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:4603: phyi nang gsang ba'i gsung sgrags te //
NK021(zha)001:4604: dam pa'i chos kyang ma lus bzung //
NK021(zha)001:4605: rdo rje rigs mchog dam tshig ni //
NK021(zha)001:4606: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya yang //
NK021(zha)001:4607: bla ma rdo rje rigs bsten bya //
NK021(zha)001:4608: mtha' yas sems can don gyi phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4609: gsang sngags dam tshig bdag gis blang //
NK021(zha)001:4610: yang dag par ni bzung bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:4611: byang chub sems mchog sgrub par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:4612: zhes lan gsum brjod du gzhug /
NK021(zha)001:4613: de nas chos bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4614: 'o skol gyi ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4615: sangs rgyas kyis gdul bya'i bsam pa dang 'tshams par
NK021(zha)001:4616: theg pa'i sgo mtha' yas pa gsungs pa las /
NK021(zha)001:4617: ngan song las nges par 'byung ba lha mi //
NK021(zha)001:4618: 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba'i byang chub chung ngu nyan thos dang /
NK021(zha)001:4620: mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung ba'i byang chub chen po byang sems kyi theg pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:4621: de ltar nges 'byung gi theg pa bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:4622: 'dir 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa khyad par du 'phags te /
NK021(zha)001:4624: don gcig na yang ma rmongs dang //
NK021(zha)001:4625: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:4626: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:4627: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK021(zha)001:4629: de'i don ni rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po
NK021(zha)001:4630: gnyis sems can gyi don du bla na med pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4633: lha sngags sogs thabs kyi cha la ma rmongs dang //
NK021(zha)001:4634: de'ang dbang po'i rim pa dang mthun par rgyud sde'i sgo mtha' yas pas thabs mang ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:4635: de'ang dus ring por mi thogs pas dka' ba med pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:4636: de nyid sngags kyi theg pa dngos kyi gdul bya dbang rnon la dgongs nas gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK021(zha)001:4638: bskal pa bye ba du ma ru //
NK021(zha)001:4639: sdig pa gang zhig sngon byas pa //
NK021(zha)001:4641: de dag thams cad zad 'gyur na //
NK021(zha)001:4642: grags pa mtha' yas sngags spyod pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4643: tshul la gnas rnams smos ci dgos //
NK021(zha)001:4644: skyob pa'i gsang sngags bzlas na ni //
NK021(zha)001:4646: zhes mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor mthong ba tsam gyis bskal pa mang po'i las sgrub 'dag par 'gyur na /
NK021(zha)001:4647: lam bde zhing myur pa'i theg pa 'dir zhugs nas
NK021(zha)001:4648: nyams su blang du yod pa ni rnyed pa'i mchog
NK021(zha)001:4649: rab tu rnyed par gyur to snyam du spro ba
NK021(zha)001:4650: khyad par can bskyed par mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:4651: de nas kri ya'i dam tshig bcu gsum bsgrag pa yin pas gsan 'tshal //
NK021(zha)001:4652: de ring phyin chad khyed rnams kyis //
NK021(zha)001:4653: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK021(zha)001:4654: rig sngags gsang sngags tshogs rnams la //
NK021(zha)001:4655: dad pa rab tu brtan par bya //
NK021(zha)001:4656: rtag tu phyag rgya chen po la //
NK021(zha)001:4657: khyad par du ni mos par bya //
NK021(zha)001:4658: dam tshig can dang mdza' bo dang //
NK021(zha)001:4659: bla ma la yang gus par bya //
NK021(zha)001:4660: lha rnams kun la dad mos bya //
NK021(zha)001:4661: dus 'tshams dag tu mchod pa bya //
NK021(zha)001:4662: ston pa gzhan gyi gzhung mi mchod //
NK021(zha)001:4663: rtag par glo bur mgron mchod bya //
NK021(zha)001:4664: srog chags rnams la byams pa'i sems //
NK021(zha)001:4665: rab tu brtan pa nye bar gzhag /
NK021(zha)001:4666: theg pa la ni dga' rnams kyis //
NK021(zha)001:4667: bsod nams dag la nan tan bskyed //
NK021(zha)001:4668: bzlas brjod la ni 'bad pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:4669: gsang sngags spyod la brtson par bya //
NK021(zha)001:4670: gsang sngags rgyud las bstan pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:4671: dam tshig rnams kyang bsrung bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:4672: dam tshig med pa rnams la ni //
NK021(zha)001:4673: sngags dang phyag rgya mi sbyin no //
NK021(zha)001:4674: gsang sngags rgyud ni legs bsrung zhing //
NK021(zha)001:4675: de yang bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:4677: de ltar dam tshig dang sdom pa de dag nan
NK021(zha)001:4678: gyis bsrung bar gdams pa'i phyir mna' chu blud pa
NK021(zha)001:4679: ni / 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK021(zha)001:4680: dam tshig 'das na bsreg par byed //
NK021(zha)001:4681: dam tshig bsrungs na dngos grub ni //
NK021(zha)001:4683: ces las bum gyi chu khar sbyin no //
NK021(zha)001:4684: de nas dngos su yol ba yod na bsal zhing /
NK021(zha)001:4685: slob dpon gyi lag gi rdo rje la 'jus te /
NK021(zha)001:4686: +aa kham w+ai ra h+aum zhes 'khrid pa /
NK021(zha)001:4687: dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes sgo bzhi nas zhugs //
NK021(zha)001:4688: gtso bo'i mdun ngos kyi khyams la 'khod pas byang
NK021(zha)001:4689: chub kyi sems yid la byed bzhin du 'di'i rjes
NK021(zha)001:4690: zlos dang bcas te me tog dor mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:4691: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes phul ba gang la babs pa'i rigs ngos bzung nas ming gdags shing /
NK021(zha)001:4693: de ltar gtso bos me tog bzhes nas slar yang
NK021(zha)001:4694: khyod rang gi spyi bor bcings pa'i mos pa mdzod
NK021(zha)001:4695: / pra ti grih+na t+wam i mam sat+wa ma h+aa ba la /
NK021(zha)001:4697: de bzhin gshegs kun deng khyod kyi //
NK021(zha)001:4698: mig 'byed par ni brtson par mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:4699: phye bas thams cad mthong 'gyur ba //
NK021(zha)001:4700: rdo rje'i mig ni bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:4701: badz+ra ne tra a pa ha ra pa tra lam hri tram /
NK021(zha)001:4703: de ltar rdo rje'i mig thob pa de la mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:4705: de yang 'di na rigs gsum gyi dkyil 'khor mngon sum du bzhugs pa yin te /
NK021(zha)001:4706: yang dag pa'i smon lam gyi stobs las byung ba'i
NK021(zha)001:4707: zhing khams rnam par dag pa'i dbus su de bzhin
NK021(zha)001:4708: gshegs pa thams cad kyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i chos
NK021(zha)001:4709: kyi dbyings kyi pho brang rin po che sna bdun
NK021(zha)001:4710: las grub pa yon tan mtha' yas pa'i rgyan gyis
NK021(zha)001:4711: spras pa'i gzhal yas khang gi lte bar gdan gsum
NK021(zha)001:4712: sgrigs kyi dbus mar 'jam dpal dbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:4713: de'i g.yas logs su spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK021(zha)001:4714: g.yon du phyag na rdo rje /
NK021(zha)001:4715: mtha' bskor gyi pad+ma 'dab ma drug la rim par
NK021(zha)001:4716: sbyong spel sgyur thob tshim pa dbang du byed pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4717: lha drug / lha snam la sgeg sogs lha mo brgyad dang //
NK021(zha)001:4718: sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi sogs dkyil 'khor du 'du
NK021(zha)001:4719: bar 'os pa'i lha thams cad bzhugs pa mngon sum
NK021(zha)001:4720: bzhin du mthong bar gyur snyam pa'i mos pa mdzod
NK021(zha)001:4722: dngos gzhi'i slad du slob dpon 'di ni bdag gi
NK021(zha)001:4723: ston pa'o snyam du mos pas thal mo sbyar te
NK021(zha)001:4724: gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:4725: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid //
NK021(zha)001:4726: brtse bas dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK021(zha)001:4727: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK021(zha)001:4728: de ring rab tu stsal du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:4730: de nas khyed rang rnams dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i
NK021(zha)001:4731: mdun phyogs su dbang stegs kyi steng du 'khod pa
NK021(zha)001:4732: la / ji ltar 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por
NK021(zha)001:4733: bum pa'i rgya rtags kyi dbang bskur ba ltar chos
NK021(zha)001:4734: thams cad la dbang thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:4735: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis mgrin gcig tu rin po
NK021(zha)001:4736: che'i bum pa dang bdud rtsi'i gang ba'i chu rgyun
NK021(zha)001:4737: gyis dbang bskur ba'i mos pa mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:4739: nyin mo bde legs mtshan bde legs //
NK021(zha)001:4740: zhes pa lta bu'i dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis
NK021(zha)001:4741: sngon du 'gro bas bum pa spyi bor 'jog cing
NK021(zha)001:4744: don dam bden pa'i chos nyid las //
NK021(zha)001:4745: mi g.yo sems dpa' mngon sum du //
NK021(zha)001:4746: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang gnas pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4747: rigs gsum kri ya'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:4752: zhes bum chus bkru zhing 'thung du'ang gzhug /
NK021(zha)001:4753: dkon mchog gsum dang rigs gsum mgon po'i dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:4754: gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis
NK021(zha)001:4755: rigs kyi bu la bum pa chu'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4756: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa thob
NK021(zha)001:4757: par gyur cig / thal mo bkan pa las mdzub
NK021(zha)001:4758: rtse gnyis cung zad bkug pa'i rgya slob ma'i spyi
NK021(zha)001:4759: par gyur cig / bor bzhag la / ta th+aa ga tod+b+ha ba s+w+aa h+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:4760: rigs kyi bu la cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas chos kyi rgyal po chen po gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4761: de nas lha dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:4762: dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i lha rnams las rang 'dra
NK021(zha)001:4763: ba'i lha re re chad nas so so rang rang
NK021(zha)001:4764: gi spyi bo nas thim pa'i byin rlabs kyis rigs
NK021(zha)001:4765: de dang de'i las dang dngos grub kyi skal ba
NK021(zha)001:4766: thams cad rgyud la thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:4767: lha tsaka rnams rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:4768: d+h+aih gzhon nu sku lus 'chang ba po //
NK021(zha)001:4769: ye shes sgron me rab rgyas shing //
NK021(zha)001:4770: 'jig rten gsum gyi mun sel ba //
NK021(zha)001:4771: 'jam dpal dbyangs kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:4774: h+r+aih sangs rgyas kun gyis rab tu basngagasa //
NK021(zha)001:4775: yon tan dam pa kun bsags pa //
NK021(zha)001:4776: spyan ras gzigs zhes mtshan gsol ba //
NK021(zha)001:4777: rtag par brtse ba'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:4781: stobs po che la drag shul ldan //
NK021(zha)001:4782: rigs sngags rgyal po dge ba can //
NK021(zha)001:4783: gdul dka' mtha' dag 'dul ba po //
NK021(zha)001:4784: phyag na rdo rje'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:4787: sbyangs spel bsgyur bas mchod sbyin gnas //
NK021(zha)001:4788: thob tshim dbang byed sngags kyi lha //
NK021(zha)001:4789: snang mdzad bdud rtsi rin 'byung thub //
NK021(zha)001:4790: don grub phyag rdor dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:4791: a kham dza tram ha dza a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:4792: gzugs mdzes phreng ba dbyangs snyan gar //
NK021(zha)001:4793: nyer spyod bzhi dang phyag rgya bzhis //
NK021(zha)001:4794: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:4795: lha mo bcu gnyis dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:4796: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah d+h+au pu a gan /
NK021(zha)001:4797: dzahh+aum bam hoh a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:4798: de dag gis rtsa ba'i lha'i dbang song nas /
NK021(zha)001:4799: da mgron thabs kyi lha rnams kyi dbang ni //
NK021(zha)001:4800: rigs bdag sku mchog rnam snang mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:4801: nyes pa'i skyon bral sku mdog dkar //
NK021(zha)001:4802: byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK021(zha)001:4803: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4804: 'jam dpal dbyangs ni sku yi rigs //
NK021(zha)001:4806: phyag na ral gri ut+pala bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4807: rigs kyi yum mchog sangs rgyas spyan //
NK021(zha)001:4808: dkar mo phyag na spyan 'bras bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4809: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed //
NK021(zha)001:4810: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje rno //
NK021(zha)001:4811: lha mo dpal dang mdzod sprul ma //
NK021(zha)001:4812: lha chen tshangs pa la sogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:4813: sku yi rigs kyi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:4816: +aah rigs bdag gsung mchog snang mtha' yas //
NK021(zha)001:4817: thugs rje chags pas sku mdog dmar //
NK021(zha)001:4818: ting 'dzin mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK021(zha)001:4819: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4820: spyan ras gzigs dbang gsung gi rigs //
NK021(zha)001:4821: dmar po phyag na pad+ma bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4822: yum chen gos dkar sku mdog dmar //
NK021(zha)001:4823: phyag na 'dam skyes dkar po bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4824: khro rgyal rta mgrin rta skad sgrog /
NK021(zha)001:4825: rigs kyi pho nya rdo rje phur //
NK021(zha)001:4826: grags ldan ma dang lu gu rgyud //
NK021(zha)001:4827: ma h+aa de ba la sogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:4828: gsung gi rigs kyi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:4829: +aa mi t+aa b+ha +aah a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:4831: rigs bdag thugs mchog rdo rje sems //
NK021(zha)001:4832: chos nyid mi 'gyur sku mdog sngo //
NK021(zha)001:4833: sa gnon mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK021(zha)001:4834: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4835: phyag na rdo rje thugs kyi rigs //
NK021(zha)001:4836: sngon po phyag na rdo rje bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4837: yum chen bzang mo sku mdog sngo //
NK021(zha)001:4838: phyag na rdo rje rtse gsum can //
NK021(zha)001:4839: khro bo'i rgyal po bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK021(zha)001:4840: pho nya rdo rje khro bo ste //
NK021(zha)001:4841: stobs chen ma dang rnam rgyal ma //
NK021(zha)001:4842: lha chen khyab 'jug la sogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:4843: thugs kyi rigs kyi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:4846: dpal bar 'gro ba ral gri ste //
NK021(zha)001:4847: kun tu bzang po rin chen bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4849: bzang skyong bum pa can dang bzhi //
NK021(zha)001:4850: shar gyi phyogs bzhugs sku mdog dkar //
NK021(zha)001:4851: lho phyogs sems dpa' bzhi po sngo //
NK021(zha)001:4853: nam mkha' mdzod ni rin chen sgrom //
NK021(zha)001:4854: nam snying rdo rje rtse gsum ste //
NK021(zha)001:4856: nub phyogs sems dpa' byi ru'i mdog /
NK021(zha)001:4858: ye shes tog ni rin chen tog /
NK021(zha)001:4859: spobs pa brtsegs ni rin chen 'bar //
NK021(zha)001:4860: blo groos mi zad glegs bam can //
NK021(zha)001:4861: byang gi sems dpa' ljang khu ste //
NK021(zha)001:4862: byams pa klu shing spyi blugs can //
NK021(zha)001:4863: spos kyi glang po dung dkar 'bud //
NK021(zha)001:4865: don kun grub byed rgya gram 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:4866: bskal bzang sems dpa' bcu drug gi //
NK021(zha)001:4867: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4868: bo d+hi sat+wa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:4869: shar du dus ldan pad+ma can //
NK021(zha)001:4870: dkar mo dpal be'u 'khor lo bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:4873: nub tu mdangs can dri med ma //
NK021(zha)001:4874: dmar mo gdugs dang bum pa 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:4875: byang du rgyal bzung yid bzang ma //
NK021(zha)001:4876: ljang khu dung dang gser nya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:4877: phyogs bzhi dus bzhir bkra shis pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4878: lha mo brgyad kyi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:4879: tram mam ga la de w+ai a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:4881: de nas mtshan ma rtags kyi dbang du grags pa
NK021(zha)001:4882: phyag rdor dbang bskur gyi rgyud las bkol ba kri
NK021(zha)001:4883: ya'i rdzas dbang nyi shu rtsa drug bskur bas sngon
NK021(zha)001:4884: ston pas phyag na rdo rje sogs la ji ltar
NK021(zha)001:4885: dbang bskur ba dang rjes su mthun pa'i yon tan
NK021(zha)001:4886: khyad par can rgyud la thob par gyur snyam pa'i
NK021(zha)001:4887: mos pa mdzod / de la rdzas dbang nyer drug las /
NK021(zha)001:4888: dang po ri rab thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:4889: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zom la chos
NK021(zha)001:4890: kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus su dpal phyag na
NK021(zha)001:4891: rdo rje la rin po che sna lnga'i ri rab
NK021(zha)001:4892: kyi dbang bskur bas mthu stobs phun sum tshogs pa
NK021(zha)001:4893: dang ldan te mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:4894: to // de bzhin du rin po che sna lnga'i
NK021(zha)001:4895: ri rab kyi dbang bskur bas mthu stobs phun sum
NK021(zha)001:4896: tshogs pa dang ldan te mi 'gyur ba'i sku thob
NK021(zha)001:4897: to // par gyur cig / gzi brjid lhun sdug ri rab mchog gi sku //
NK021(zha)001:4898: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i bang rim mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4899: thams cad gnas pa'i ri bo chen po la //
NK021(zha)001:4900: mthu stobs mi 'gyur sku rnams rdzogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4901: skye shi 'gro drug khams gsum yongs kyi srog /
NK021(zha)001:4902: kha dog mdzes ldan rin chen sna tshogs gzhi //
NK021(zha)001:4903: phyogs bzhi dbus dang rigs kyi skur bstan pa //
NK021(zha)001:4904: 'di ni rin chen sna lnga'i ri rab kyi //
NK021(zha)001:4905: dbang gi bkra shis le'u dang po'o //
NK021(zha)001:4907: sngon bcom ldan 'das mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyin
NK021(zha)001:4908: pa'i dus su u dum+ba ra'i me tog dang sbyar
NK021(zha)001:4909: nas dpal phyag na rdo rje la rang bzhin gyi
NK021(zha)001:4910: mchod rten dang sprul pa'i mchod rten la sogs pas
NK021(zha)001:4911: dbang bskur bas rnam par mi rtog pa chos kyi
NK021(zha)001:4913: de bzhin du mchod rten chen po'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4914: chos kyi sku thob pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur
NK021(zha)001:4915: cig / dran pa nye bar bzhag pa'i bang rim la //
NK021(zha)001:4916: skye 'gag med pa'i bum pa zlum pos brgyan //
NK021(zha)001:4917: chos kyi 'khor lo ma 'dres tog la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:4918: rnam par mi rtog chos sku thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4919: lta ba'i sa dang mngon par byang chub mtshungs pa mi mnga' yang //
NK021(zha)001:4920: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor dang cho 'phrul chen po ston la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:4921: lha yul nas gshegs pa dang ston pa zhi ba'i dbyings su bzhugs //
NK021(zha)001:4922: stobs bcu'i byin mnga' mchod rten dbang gi bkra shis gnyis pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4923: gsum pa dpag bsam gyi shing /
NK021(zha)001:4924: sngon bcom ldan 'das gyad yul gyi nye 'khor na
NK021(zha)001:4925: bzhugs pa'i dus su dpal phyag na rdo rje la
NK021(zha)001:4926: dpag bsam shing gi dbang bskur bas dgongs pa'i don
NK021(zha)001:4927: thams cad yid bzhin du grub par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:4928: de bzhin du dpag bsam shing gi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4929: dgos 'dod thams cad yid bzhin du grub par gyur
NK021(zha)001:4930: cig / gang la ci 'dod dpag bsam shing lta bu //
NK021(zha)001:4931: yon tan yid bzhin zad med gter dang ldan //
NK021(zha)001:4932: brtan pa'i rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul yin te //
NK021(zha)001:4933: dgongs pa'i don rnams yid bzhin 'grub par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4934: lha yi re skongs dpag bsam ljon shing ltar //
NK021(zha)001:4935: 'phags pa'i yon tan brjod kyis mi lang ste //
NK021(zha)001:4936: re ba yid bzhin phun sum tshogs pa'i rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:4937: 'dod dgu'i 'byung gnas rin chen dpag bsam shing //
NK021(zha)001:4938: dbang gi bkra shis le'u gsum pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4940: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgya mtsho chen po'i gling du
NK021(zha)001:4941: gshegs pa'i dus su dpal phyag na rdo rje la
NK021(zha)001:4942: rgya mtsho chen pos dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:4943: skye ba med pa'i chos zab cing rgya che ba rgyud la rtogs par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:4944: de bzhin du rgya mtsho chen po'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:4945: skye ba med pa'i chos zab cing rgya che ba'i
NK021(zha)001:4946: don rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:4947: / gting dpag zab cing rgya che yangs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:4948: kun tu snyoms pa'i yon tan chen po ste //
NK021(zha)001:4949: skye 'gag med pa'i rgya mtsho chen po la //
NK021(zha)001:4950: zab cing rgya che'i chos don rtogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:4951: chos nyid rgya mtsho lta bur thugs chud pas //
NK021(zha)001:4952: zab cing gting dpag dka' ba'i rgya mtsho la //
NK021(zha)001:4953: yid bzhin nor bu kha dog mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK021(zha)001:4954: rgya mtsho dbang gi bkra shis bzhi pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4956: sngon bcom ldan 'das rdo rje gdan drung na bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:4957: pa'i tshe dpal phyag na rdo rje la sa gzhi
NK021(zha)001:4958: chen po gnas kyi dbang bskur bas bkra shis la
NK021(zha)001:4959: byin chags pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur to
NK021(zha)001:4960: // de bzhin du sa gzhi gnas kyi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:4961: bas gnas bkra shis shing byin chags pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:4963: rab tu dben pa'i gnas mchog dam pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:4964: me tog dri bsung mang po skye ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:4965: yon tan ma lus tshang bar kun rdzogs te //
NK021(zha)001:4966: dben pa'i bkra shis 'byor ba'i gnas su shog /
NK021(zha)001:4967: me tog mdzes ldan yid 'ong brgyan pa'i gnas //
NK021(zha)001:4968: bkra shis sgra snyan bya skad sna tshogs sgrog /
NK021(zha)001:4969: yon tan kun ldan ston pas byin brlabs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:4970: gnas gzhi dbang gi bkra shis lnga pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4972: sngon bcom ldan 'das w+aa r+aa na s+ai na bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:4973: pa'i tshe dpal phyag na rdo rje la bdud rtsi'i
NK021(zha)001:4974: chus dbang bskur bas skye shi mi mnga' ba'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:4976: de bzhin du bdud rtsi bum pa'i chus dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:4977: bas skye shi med pa rdo rje sku'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:4979: bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun 'gro ba'i gsos kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:4980: nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad rnams ma lus sel //
NK021(zha)001:4981: ma rig dag byed bdud rtsi'i chu mchog ste //
NK021(zha)001:4982: skye shi med pa dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:4983: bum pa'i kha rgyan dpag bsam shing //
NK021(zha)001:4984: dbang bskur bum chu spyi blugs pas //
NK021(zha)001:4985: bdud rtsi dam pa 'dir stsol cig /
NK021(zha)001:4986: 'di ni bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun gyi //
NK021(zha)001:4987: dbang gi bkra shis drug pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:4988: zhes bum chu spyi bor gtigs shing 'thung du'ang gzhug /
NK021(zha)001:4989: bdun pa dar gyi zar tshags /
NK021(zha)001:4990: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi zom la bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:4991: pa'i tshe lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis chos zhu
NK021(zha)001:4992: ba'i phyir dar bu khad kyi za ra tshags phul
NK021(zha)001:4993: bas chos sgra chen po sgrog pa'i byin dang ldan
NK021(zha)001:4994: par gyur to // de bzhin du dar gyi zar
NK021(zha)001:4995: tshags kyi dbang bskur bas chos kyi sgra chen po
NK021(zha)001:4996: sgrog pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:4997: chos kyi rgyal srid che la mnga' brnyes shing //
NK021(zha)001:4998: ma rig mun pa ma lus bsal ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:4999: brgya byin shes pa ma lus 'grol ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5000: chos rnams thams cad go zhing sgrog par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5001: 'jam mnyen reg bde dar gyi za ra tshags //
NK021(zha)001:5002: rigs kyi kha dog sna bdun shin tu mdzes //
NK021(zha)001:5003: yid 'ong legs par brgyan pa'i bkra shis rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:5004: lhab lhub dbang gi bkra shis bdun pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5006: sngon bcom ldan 'das sum cu rtsa gsum gyi gnas
NK021(zha)001:5007: su brgya byin la chos 'khor bskor ba'i tshe rin
NK021(zha)001:5008: po che'i khri rkang phul ba la bzhugs pas chos
NK021(zha)001:5009: shes pa'i rgyud la go zhing bsgrags par gyur to
NK021(zha)001:5010: // de bzhin du rin po che'i khri rkang gi
NK021(zha)001:5011: dbang bskur bas ma nor bar go zhing sgrog pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5012: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:5013: rin chen gser gyi khri steng du //
NK021(zha)001:5014: chos sgra chen po bsgrags pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:5015: 'gro ba rnams kyi mi shes dgrol //
NK021(zha)001:5016: chos rnams go zhing sgrogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5017: tshad med bzhi ldan 'degs byed gser gyi khri //
NK021(zha)001:5018: yon tan tshogs rdzogs rat+na sna tshogs spras //
NK021(zha)001:5019: 'gro ba'i yid bzhin zad med dgos 'dod skong //
NK021(zha)001:5020: khri mchog dbang gi bkra shis brgyad pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5022: sngon bcom ldan 'das kyis chos kyi 'khor lo bskor
NK021(zha)001:5023: ba'i tshe brgya byin gyis me tog gi chun po
NK021(zha)001:5024: bres pas sems can 'khor ba las bslu zhing brid
NK021(zha)001:5026: de bzhin du me tog gi chun pos dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:5027: bas 'khor ba las yid 'byung ba mdzes pa'i rgyan
NK021(zha)001:5028: mchog dam pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:5029: sdug bsngal mdzes pa'i me tog dam pa 'di /
NK021(zha)001:5030: kha dog ma 'dres so sor gsal ba'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5031: sems can kun gyis lta bar 'os pa'i gnas //
NK021(zha)001:5032: mdzes pa'i rgyan mchog dam pa thob pa shog /
NK021(zha)001:5033: me tog chu skyes thang skyes dam pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5034: shing dang nags skyes 'bru mchog dam pa 'di //
NK021(zha)001:5035: rin chen phreng ltar mkha' la char 'bebs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5036: me tog dbang gi bkra shis dgu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5038: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri rab kyi rtse khang pa
NK021(zha)001:5039: brtsegs par chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe sum
NK021(zha)001:5040: cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu nyi 'od dam pas
NK021(zha)001:5041: rnga yab kyis g.yabs pas dgyes pa chen po'i gzi
NK021(zha)001:5042: mdangs dang ldan par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5043: de bzhin du rnga yab kyi dbang bskur bas dgyes
NK021(zha)001:5044: pa chen po'i gzi mdangs dang ldan pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:5046: snyan pa'i sgra rnams myur du sgrogs pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5047: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma ma lus sel //
NK021(zha)001:5048: thams cad myur du go ba'i blo thob nas //
NK021(zha)001:5049: bkra shis gzi mdangs mchog dang ldan par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5050: rgyal ba'i sku la nyes pas ma gos kyang //
NK021(zha)001:5051: dag cing bsang bar bya ba'i rnga yab 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:5052: sku yi dri ma ljan ljin dag par byed //
NK021(zha)001:5053: rnga yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5055: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5056: tshe sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu kun nas
NK021(zha)001:5057: 'od zer 'byung bas rdul yab kyis rdul g.yabs pas
NK021(zha)001:5058: chos nyid la skyon gyis ma gos pa'i don rtogs
NK021(zha)001:5059: par gyur to // de bzhin du lha'i rdul yab
NK021(zha)001:5060: kyi dbang bskur bas chos nyid zab mo'i don la
NK021(zha)001:5061: 'jug pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:5062: nyon mongs rdul rnams ma lus 'phyi ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:5063: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK021(zha)001:5064: bag chags skyon gyi dri ma bsal ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5065: chos nyid zab mo'i don la 'jug par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5066: rgyal ba'i sku la dri ma mi mnga' yang //
NK021(zha)001:5067: log rtog rdul gyi bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5068: bkra shis gtsang ma'i rdzas kyis sku 'phyi ba //
NK021(zha)001:5069: rdul yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gcig pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5071: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal dgon pa na bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:5072: pa'i tshe sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i bu zhig
NK021(zha)001:5073: gis sbrang yab kyis g.yabs pas sems can du 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:5074: pa'i skyon las grol bar gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5075: de bzhin du lha'i sbrang yab kyi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:5076: 'dzin chags kyi skyon las grol ba'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:5078: nyon mongs sems can ma rig bsal ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:5079: 'bras bu thar pa'i go 'phang thob pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5080: bde bar gshegs pa'i drung du 'khor ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5081: 'dzin chags skyon gyi dri ma dag par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5082: drang srong chen po bsam gtan gnas pa la //
NK021(zha)001:5083: srog chags gdug pa'i gzugs brnyan bsal ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:5084: rnga yab rgyal ba'i ring bsrel bskor ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5085: sbrang yab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5087: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal po'i khab na bzhugs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5088: tshe 'khor rnams bzhis bla re bres pas nyon mongs
NK021(zha)001:5089: pa'i gdung ba zhi bar gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5090: de bzhin du bla re'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs
NK021(zha)001:5091: pa'i rdul gyi dri mas mi gos par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:5092: / chos kyi 'khor lo bskor phyir bla re bres //
NK021(zha)001:5093: mi yi seng ge bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK021(zha)001:5094: dbang phyug dam pa'i mnga' bdag chen po ste //
NK021(zha)001:5095: nyon mongs rdul gyi dri ma med par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5096: dpag bsam ljon shing me tog lo 'dab rgyas //
NK021(zha)001:5097: nyi zla gza' skar mang po'i sprin gseb nas //
NK021(zha)001:5098: bkra shis bya skad mang po 'phur zhing lding //
NK021(zha)001:5099: dar zab dbang gi bkra shis bcu gsum pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5101: sngon bcom ldan 'das bya rgod phung po'i ri bor
NK021(zha)001:5102: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe 'khor rnams bzhis
NK021(zha)001:5103: rgyal mtshan chen po btsugs pas che ba'i yon tan
NK021(zha)001:5105: de bzhin du rgyal mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas che
NK021(zha)001:5106: ba'i yon tan nub pa med pa'i dbang thob par
NK021(zha)001:5107: gyur cig / lhun grub sku brnyes rdzogs pa'i rgyal mtshan te //
NK021(zha)001:5108: nub pa'i dus med zad pa med pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:5109: yon tan mchog gyur kun las khyad par 'phags //
NK021(zha)001:5110: che ba'i yon tan nub pa med par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5111: dpal brjid mdzes pas 'jig rten yongs kyi rgyan //
NK021(zha)001:5112: bdud dang mu stegs mthu dpung 'joms par byed //
NK021(zha)001:5113: rgyal ba'i sku dang dbyer med tshul gcig pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5114: rgyal mtshan dbang gi bkra shis bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5116: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du gshegs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5117: tshe 'khor rnams kyis tsha ba'i gdung skyob gdugs kyis
NK021(zha)001:5118: bkab pas tsha ba'i gdung ba zhi bar gyur to
NK021(zha)001:5119: // de bzhin du gdugs kyi dbang bskur bas nyon
NK021(zha)001:5120: mongs pa'i gdung ba thams cad zhi ba'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:5122: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i gdung ba kun sel zhing //
NK021(zha)001:5123: grang zhing bsil ba'i gdugs mchog dam pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:5124: 'gro ba'i nyon mongs tsha gdung zhi ba'i gsos //
NK021(zha)001:5125: rims nad tsha ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:5126: ji ltar nyi ma'i 'od kyis gdungs pa na //
NK021(zha)001:5127: gdugs kyis tsha ba'i gdung ba skyob pa ltar //
NK021(zha)001:5128: 'khor ba'i nyes pa sdug bsngal skyob pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5129: gdugs mchog dbang gi bkra shis bco lnga pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5130: bcu drug pa dar gyi lda ldi /
NK021(zha)001:5131: sngon bcom ldan 'das yangs pa can gyi grong khyer
NK021(zha)001:5132: spre'u rdzing gi 'gram khang bu brtsegs pa na bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:5133: pa'i tshe bram ze kham pa gsos sngon gyi nyes
NK021(zha)001:5134: pas brdas nas nya pa rnams kyis zin pa'i tshe
NK021(zha)001:5135: / nya pa rnams 'gyod pa rjes su dran nas
NK021(zha)001:5136: nya rgya che chung phul bas nya pa lnga brgya
NK021(zha)001:5138: de bzhin du nya rgya'i rtags dar gyi lda ldis
NK021(zha)001:5139: dbang bskur bas ngan song du skye nges yin kyang
NK021(zha)001:5140: de las thar te 'tshang rgya ba'i dbang thob pa
NK021(zha)001:5141: gyur cig / dar gyi lda ldi nyon mongs kun spangs te //
NK021(zha)001:5142: legs pa'i yon tan ma lus yongs rdzogs nas //
NK021(zha)001:5143: ma rig 'khrul pa'i shes pa blo dag cing //
NK021(zha)001:5144: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i gnas las thar par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5145: 'khor ba'i nyes pa dag bya'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5146: sdug bsngal rgya mo bkra shis rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:5147: bag chags kun dag lda ldi yi //
NK021(zha)001:5148: dbang gi bkra shis bcu drug pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5150: sngon bcom ldan 'das skyed mos tshal du gshegs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5151: tshe khyim bdag lha'i bu mo bzang ldan mas a
NK021(zha)001:5152: par se'i sku rags gsol bas sku brtan pa'i mchog
NK021(zha)001:5154: de bzhin du sku rags kyi dbang bskur bas lus brtan pa'i mchog dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:5155: dri med dag pa'i sku rags gtsang ma'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5156: khyim bdag dad pas phul ba'i sku chings 'di //
NK021(zha)001:5157: sku la dkris shing rab tu bsdams pas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:5158: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i sku mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5159: thar pa mchog gis legs par gang gsungs pa //
NK021(zha)001:5160: mi dmigs dag pa'i ye shes chen po yis //
NK021(zha)001:5161: nyon mongs dri med bde ba'i sku rten pa //
NK021(zha)001:5162: sku rags dbang gi bkra shis bcu bdun pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5164: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri bo gangs can na bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:5165: pa'i tshe gnod sbyin rnams kyis spos rnams pa lnga
NK021(zha)001:5171: de rnams phul bas dbang po tshim zhing bkra shis par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5172: de bzhin du spos rnam pa lnga'i dbang bskur bas dbang po tshim zhing bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:5173: dbang po tshim byed bdug pa'i spos mchog 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:5174: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa mchod pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5175: 'gro ba ma lus dbang po kun tshim zhing //
NK021(zha)001:5176: dri zhim 'phags pa'i sku dang ldan par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5177: dri zhim ngad ldang yon tan phun sum tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:5178: mkha' la mchod pa'i sprin phung gtibs byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:5179: yongs su khyab pa'i bdug spos dam pa 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:5180: tshim byed dbang gi bkra shis bco brgyad pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5181: bcu dgu pa snying po lnga /
NK021(zha)001:5182: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po na bzhugs pa'i tshe klu'i rgyal po rnams kyis tsh+wa /
NK021(zha)001:5186: til te snying po lnga phul bas tshe'i snying po
NK021(zha)001:5187: mi zad pa'i mdzod du bkra shis par gyur to
NK021(zha)001:5188: // de bzhin du snying po rnam pa lngas dbang
NK021(zha)001:5189: bskur bas tshe mi zad pa'i mdzod du bkra shis
NK021(zha)001:5190: // par gyur cig / snying po lnga ni gsos kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5191: mi zad pa yi dbyig thob ste //
NK021(zha)001:5192: legs pa'i yon tan mthar phyin nas //
NK021(zha)001:5193: tshe dang longs spyod 'phel bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:5194: tsh+wa yis ro sgyur mar gyi mdangs dang ldan //
NK021(zha)001:5195: sbrang rtsis stobs rgyas ka ras nad rnams zhi //
NK021(zha)001:5196: til gyis sdig zhi dge tshogs rnam par 'phel //
NK021(zha)001:5197: snying po dbang gi bkra shis bcu dgu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5198: nyi shu po rin chen lnga /
NK021(zha)001:5199: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri bo gru 'dzin na bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:5200: pa'i tshe gnod sbyin gter 'chang rnams kyis gser dngul
NK021(zha)001:5201: zangs lcags mu men te rin po che rnam pa
NK021(zha)001:5202: lnga phul bas zad mi shes pa'i dkor mdzod dang
NK021(zha)001:5204: de bzhin du rin po che rnam pa lngas dbang
NK021(zha)001:5205: bskur bas longs spyod zad mi shes pa'i dkor mdzod
NK021(zha)001:5207: rin chen gser dngul zangs lcags sogs //
NK021(zha)001:5208: mi zad nor gyi mchog 'di yis //
NK021(zha)001:5209: 'phags pa'i nor bdun dang ldan te //
NK021(zha)001:5210: 'gro ba'i dbul ba sel bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:5211: dgos pa'i nor 'byung rin chen sna tshogs mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5212: zad mi shes pa re ba skong ba'i gter //
NK021(zha)001:5213: bkres shing dbul 'phongs sdug bsngal sel byed pa //
NK021(zha)001:5214: dgos 'byung dbang gi bkra shis nyi shu pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5216: sngon bcom ldan 'das yul ang+ga ma ga d+ha na bzhugs pa'i tshe rgyal po gsal rgyal gyis /
NK021(zha)001:5220: mon sran dre'u ste 'bru lnga phul bas mu ge med cing bkra shis par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5221: de bzhin du 'bru rnam pa lnga'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:5222: mu ge'i bskal pa las thar te bkra shis par
NK021(zha)001:5223: gyur cig / rin chen 'bru mchog 'gro ba kun gyi gsos //
NK021(zha)001:5224: mu ge'i sdug bsngal kun las thar byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:5225: sbyin pas longs spyod rtag tu 'phel ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5226: zas gos mi zad gter dang ldan par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5227: longs spyod tshogs ldan 'byor ba kun tshang ba //
NK021(zha)001:5228: gang la ci 'dod yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK021(zha)001:5229: phun sum tshogs pa dge ba'i stobs bskyed pa //
NK021(zha)001:5230: longs spyod dbang gi bkra shis nyer gcig pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5231: nyer gnyis pa sman stag tsher /
NK021(zha)001:5232: sngon bcom ldan 'das tsan+dana gyi nags su gshegs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5233: tshe gcan gzan gyi rgyal po stag gis sman b+y+aa
NK021(zha)001:5234: gri phul bas bkra shis par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5235: de bzhin du sman stag tsher gyi dbang bskur bas bkra shis par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:5236: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5237: byol song gti mug gis kyang go mdzad pas //
NK021(zha)001:5238: b+y+aa gri sman mchog gcan gzan stag gis phul //
NK021(zha)001:5239: sman gyis nad rnams ma lus zhi bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:5240: sems can gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5241: thabs kyi cho 'phrul kun la cir yang ston //
NK021(zha)001:5242: thugs rje chen pos gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5243: cho 'phrul dbang gi bkra shis nyer gnyis pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5245: sngon bcom ldan 'das seng ldeng gi nags su gshegs
NK021(zha)001:5246: pa'i tshe gcan gzan gyi rgyal po seng ges seng
NK021(zha)001:5247: gri phul bas sman gyi mchog tu bkra shis par
NK021(zha)001:5248: gyur to // de bzhin du sman seng tsher gyi
NK021(zha)001:5249: dbang bskur bas sman mchog dam pa'i yon tan gyis
NK021(zha)001:5251: seng gri sman mchog gcan gzan seng ges phul //
NK021(zha)001:5252: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5253: byol song gti mug gis kyang go mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5254: sman mchog dam pas nad las thar par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5255: gzi brjid 'gro mkhas 'gying ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK021(zha)001:5256: glal zhing 'gying ba dud 'gro'i rgyal po ste //
NK021(zha)001:5257: sgra skad sgrog pas sder chags zil gyis gnon //
NK021(zha)001:5258: 'dul byed dbang gi bkra shis nyer gsum pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5260: sngon bcom ldan 'das ri btang bzung chen por bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:5261: pa'i tshe klu'i rgyal po 'jog pos bri ha ti
NK021(zha)001:5262: phul bas sman gyi mchog tu bkra shis par gyur
NK021(zha)001:5263: to // de bzhin du shu dag dkar po'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:5264: bskur bas sman mchog dam pas bkra shis par gyur
NK021(zha)001:5265: to // cig / shu dag sman mchog klu yis phul ba ste //
NK021(zha)001:5266: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5267: klu rigs gti mug gis kyang go mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5268: sman gyis nad rnams rab tu sel bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:5269: rig pa'i cha ldan byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK021(zha)001:5270: 'gro ba'i re skong gtsug na rin chen mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5271: thabs kyis don mdzad mthu dpung che ba'i klu //
NK021(zha)001:5272: nad sel dbang gi bkra shis nyer bzhi pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5274: sngon bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal
NK021(zha)001:5275: na bzhugs pa'i tshe lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis
NK021(zha)001:5276: sman ha sa de ba phul bas sman mchog gi
NK021(zha)001:5277: snying por bkra shis par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5278: de bzhin du dbang po lag pa'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:5279: sman mchog dam pa'i don gyis bkra shis pa gyur
NK021(zha)001:5280: cig / dbang po lag pa brgya byin dbang pos phul //
NK021(zha)001:5281: bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5282: brgya byin lha yi sems kyang go mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5283: sman mchog nad kun rab tu zhi bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:5284: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi gnas mchog nas //
NK021(zha)001:5285: longs spyod ldan pa lha dbang brgya byin mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5286: sum cu rtsa gsum lha gnas rnam rgyal ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:5287: longs spyod dbang gi bkra shis nyer lnga pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5288: nyer drug pa kan+d+ha ka ri /
NK021(zha)001:5289: sngon bcom ldan 'das nags tshal chen po'i tshal du
NK021(zha)001:5290: gshegs pa'i tshe shing gi lha mo 'od 'chad mas
NK021(zha)001:5291: kan+d+ha ka ri phul bas sman mchog snying por bkra
NK021(zha)001:5293: de bzhin du kan+d+ha ka ri'i dbang bskur bas snying
NK021(zha)001:5294: po don gyi dbang du bkra shis par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:5295: / bcom ldan thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5296: shing gi lha mo'i sems kyang go mdzad pas //
NK021(zha)001:5297: kan+d+ha ka ri shing gi lha mos phul //
NK021(zha)001:5298: sman mchog de yis nad kun zhi bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:5299: nags tshal chen po'i ljon shing las //
NK021(zha)001:5300: bde zhing dgos pa'i re skong ba //
NK021(zha)001:5301: lha mo'i dang bas rab phul ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:5302: dbang mchog bkra shis nyer drug pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5304: glan rdor 'od kyi phyag len ltar 'gos kyi las
NK021(zha)001:5305: thor 'dis sngags kyi rjes gnang kyang ster bar gsungs
NK021(zha)001:5306: pas / dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i thugs kar zla
NK021(zha)001:5307: dkyil gyi steng du sngags phreng 'od zer 'bar ba
NK021(zha)001:5308: bkod pa la rtse gcig tu dmigs te 'di'i rjes
NK021(zha)001:5309: pas / zlos / w+aa gi shwa ri mum /
NK021(zha)001:5311: badz+ra p+aa ni h+aum rnams lan gsum /
NK021(zha)001:5312: bus lha la me tog 'thor bzhin du /
NK021(zha)001:5313: bcom ldan bdag gis gzung lags kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5314: bdag la 'go bar mdzad du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:5317: bcom ldan 'di la stsal lags kyi //
NK021(zha)001:5319: zhes slob ma'i spyi bor me tog gtor ro //
NK021(zha)001:5320: de ltar kri ya dang u pa ya'i theg pa gnyis kyi dbang thun mong du bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:5321: mdo rang lugs kyi sbyor lam gsum pa spyod pa
NK021(zha)001:5322: rgyun gyi rnal 'byor bsod nams rten gyi sa dang
NK021(zha)001:5323: / mthong lam dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor brten
NK021(zha)001:5324: pas khyad par 'gro ba'i sa gnyis po ci rigs
NK021(zha)001:5325: non pa dang rigs 'dra'i yon tan gsos thebs /
NK021(zha)001:5326: mngon du rgyu phra mo dang kun 'gro'i sgrib pa gnyis po ci rigs dag /
NK021(zha)001:5327: rang sa'i lam gong ma gong ma la sbyor ba'i
NK021(zha)001:5328: 'jug pa dang dga' ba byang chub kyi sems gang
NK021(zha)001:5329: rung skye / gnas skabs su bya spyod kyi sngags dang rgyud rnams spyod pa la dbang zhing /
NK021(zha)001:5330: mthar thug rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rgyal tshab rigs
NK021(zha)001:5331: gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rtogs rigs dang 'dra ba'i
NK021(zha)001:5332: yon tan khyad par can thob pa'i skal pa can
NK021(zha)001:5334: rjes kyi bya ba la spyi don gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:5337: gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid gdab pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5338: spyi don dang po lam khyer la bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:5339: dang po theg pa lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:5340: kri ya khyad par can spyod rgyud dang thun mong bzhii theg pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:5343: khrus dang gtsang sbra'i spyod pa dang dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug go //
NK021(zha)001:5345: don dam mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag pa stong gsal gyi ye shes chen por rtogs pas /
NK021(zha)001:5346: de'i yon tan kun rdzob rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du dag par 'dod de /
NK021(zha)001:5348: gnyis med mnyam pa ma shes pas //
NK021(zha)001:5349: don dam dag pa chos nyid tsam //
NK021(zha)001:5350: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK021(zha)001:5353: gsang ba spyi rgyud du spyi'i dam tshig gsum dang /
NK021(zha)001:5354: bye brag gi dam tshig bcu gsum du bshad pa sogs so //
NK021(zha)001:5356: bya rgyud tsam po rnams su bdag nyid lhar sgom pa mi 'byung yang /
NK021(zha)001:5357: 'dir bya rgyud khyad par can spyod rgyud dang thun mong ba'i sgrub tshul la /
NK021(zha)001:5358: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK021(zha)001:5359: phyag rgya mtshan ma drug yin te //
NK021(zha)001:5360: zhes pa ltar lha drug gi sgo nas dam tshig
NK021(zha)001:5361: pa bskyed pa bran nam 'bangs lta bu'i mdun du
NK021(zha)001:5362: / lha ye shes pa spyan drangs pa rje dpon rgyal po lta bur bltas te mchod la /
NK021(zha)001:5363: dam tshig gi phyag rgyas btab nas /
NK021(zha)001:5364: bzlas brjod la sogs pa byed pa'am /
NK021(zha)001:5365: blo chen spyod rgyud khyad par can yo ga tsam
NK021(zha)001:5366: po dang thun mong gi sgrub tshul dam tshig pa
NK021(zha)001:5367: dang mdun gyi ye shes pa gnyis grogs po'i tshul
NK021(zha)001:5368: du mchog dman med par lta ba gang rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:5369: sgo nas dngos grub sgrub pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5377: bzlas brjod sngags kyi bya ba rnams so //
NK021(zha)001:5379: rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa sku gsum ye
NK021(zha)001:5380: shes lnga'i bdag nyid can gyi go 'phang mi tshe
NK021(zha)001:5381: bdun dang ring na'ang bskal pa gsum mam brgyad nas
NK021(zha)001:5382: thob par 'dod mod 'dir yang gsang sngags bla med
NK021(zha)001:5383: las ni / bya spyod kyi theg pa'i rang lam
NK021(zha)001:5384: gyis sa bcu pa'i byang sems la sangs rgyas su
NK021(zha)001:5385: las ni / brjod pa las / mthar thug gi rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob par mi bzhed do //
NK021(zha)001:5386: yang u pa ya'i theg pa'i khyad par ni /
NK021(zha)001:5388: gnyis ka rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:5389: lta spyod gong 'og rjes su mthun //
NK021(zha)001:5390: zhes kri yog gnyis ka brten pa'i theg pa yin par ma zad /
NK021(zha)001:5391: 'dir shing rta chen po slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad dang /
NK021(zha)001:5392: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba'i bzhed pas phyi rgyud
NK021(zha)001:5393: la kri yog gnyis su 'gyed pa'i lugs yin pas
NK021(zha)001:5395: gnyis pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:5396: chos can snang ba kun rdzob kyi bden ngor lha
NK021(zha)001:5397: drug gi sgo nas rigs gsum mgon po'i skur sgoms
NK021(zha)001:5398: la / ye shes pa spyan drangs nas rje khol lam grogs po lta bu'i tshul gyis sgrub cing /
NK021(zha)001:5399: lha sgom pa de'ang mi dmigs pa mtha' bzhi dang
NK021(zha)001:5400: bral ba'i stong gsal gyi ngang la 'jog pa ni
NK021(zha)001:5401: don dam bden pa'i nyams len te /
NK021(zha)001:5402: bden gnyis snga phyi res 'jog tu nyams su len pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5403: gsum pa snying po lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:5404: bdag mdun gyi lha gnyis ka'i thugs kar zla dkyil
NK021(zha)001:5405: gyi steng du sngags phreng bkod pa sgra gdangs sgrog
NK021(zha)001:5406: pa la rtse gcig tu dmigs te /
NK021(zha)001:5410: zhes bzlas pas thugs rgyud bskul ba'o //
NK021(zha)001:5411: bzhi pa dbang lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:5412: kri ya'i dbang nyi shu rtsa drug ste /
NK021(zha)001:5413: de dang rjes su 'brel pa'i kri ya'i dam tshig
NK021(zha)001:5414: bcu gsum sogs bslab bya rnams la tshul bzhin du
NK021(zha)001:5416: spyi don gnyis pa 'gag drug bshad pa la /
NK021(zha)001:5417: gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni sngon byung w+aa r+aa na s+ai dang /
NK021(zha)001:5418: rjes 'jug me tog 'ja' tshon gyi tshal du'o //
NK021(zha)001:5419: gang gis bskur ba'i ston pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5420: sngon byung bcom ldan 'das dang rjes 'jug tu slob dpon sh+aan+tisa so //
NK021(zha)001:5421: gang la bskur ba'i yul ni /
NK021(zha)001:5422: sngon byung du phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK021(zha)001:5423: rjes 'jug tu rdo rje zla 'bar rtsal la'o //
NK021(zha)001:5425: ri rab dang mchod rten sogs kri ya'i dbang nyi shu rtsa drug go //
NK021(zha)001:5427: sngon byung du phyag rdor la bcom ldan 'das kyi thugs rjes bzung ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:5428: rjes 'jug tu snod bcud 'dzom pa'i dus su bstan te /
NK021(zha)001:5429: dam tshig dang ldan pa rjes su bzung ba'i ched du'o //
NK021(zha)001:5430: de ltar bskur ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5431: ri rab kyi dbang bskur bas mthu stobs khyad par
NK021(zha)001:5432: can du 'gyur ba sogs dbang so so'i yon tan
NK021(zha)001:5433: rnams thob par dgos pa yod do //
NK021(zha)001:5434: spyi don gsum pa gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid ni /
NK021(zha)001:5435: 'dir rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa ltar /
NK021(zha)001:5436: kun rdzob snang tshod du bden par mi 'jog par
NK021(zha)001:5437: btags yod tsam du snang ba de lhar bsgyur nas
NK021(zha)001:5439: blo chung na rang rnam smin gyi lus 'di dwangs
NK021(zha)001:5440: gsal sgrib thogs med pa 'ja' tshon lta bu'i lus
NK021(zha)001:5441: su bsam pa'am / blo chen de nyid 'jam dpal dbyings lta bu'i lha'i skur bsgom mo //
NK021(zha)001:5442: dmigs pa'i gzhi de gnyis gang rigs gsal thebs pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:5443: de'i spyi bor yas nas mar thig le dkar dmar
NK021(zha)001:5444: mthing gsum brtsegs mar bsam pa la mnyam par bzhag
NK021(zha)001:5446: thig le dkar po las 'od zer 'phros /
NK021(zha)001:5447: sems can thams cad kyi lus kyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:5448: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams la sku mnyes pa'i mchod pa phul /
NK021(zha)001:5449: 'od de tshur 'dus nas rang gi spyi bor thim pas /
NK021(zha)001:5450: spyi bor 'jam dbyangs gser btso ma'i mdangs can ral
NK021(zha)001:5451: gri dang ut+pala glegs bam gyis mtshan pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:5452: zhig sgom / yang thig le dmar po las 'od 'phros /
NK021(zha)001:5453: sems can gyi ngag sgrib sbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:5455: tshur 'dus pas rang gi mgrin par spyan ras gzigs dkar po phyag bzhi'i dang po gnyis thal sbyar /
NK021(zha)001:5456: 'og gnyis shel 'phreng dang pad dkar 'dzin pa zhig sgom /
NK021(zha)001:5457: yang thig le mthing ga las 'od 'phroos /
NK021(zha)001:5458: sems can gyi yid sgrib sbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:5460: tshur 'dus pas rang gi snying gar phyag rdor sngon
NK021(zha)001:5461: po rdo rje dang sdigs mdzub can khros pa'i nyams
NK021(zha)001:5463: de ltar lus ngag yid gsum la de bzhin gshegs
NK021(zha)001:5464: pa'i sku gsung thugs kyis rgyas btab nas mnyam par
NK021(zha)001:5467: lha'i snang ba de yang mi dmigs par sbyangs nas /
NK021(zha)001:5468: sems nyid dag pa stong gsal gyi ye shes mtha'
NK021(zha)001:5469: bzhi dang bral ba'i ngang la bsal bzhag med par
NK021(zha)001:5472: snang stong rim gyis brtan par byed //
NK021(zha)001:5473: ces pa ltar bden gnyis res 'jog tu nyams su len pa yin no //
NK021(zha)001:5474: des bya spyod thun mong gi dkyil 'khor du dbang
NK021(zha)001:5475: bskur bas man ngag dang bcas pa grub pas ji
NK021(zha)001:5476: ltar gdams pa rnams tshul bzhin du bsgrub par bya'o
NK021(zha)001:5477: snyam pas / gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blang /
NK021(zha)001:5479: deng nas brtsams te sogs kyis yon dbul zhing /
NK021(zha)001:5480: dge ba bsngo ba rnams sngar ltar dang /
NK021(zha)001:5481: rjes chog rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:5482: rtsa ba'i man ngag las tho dang //
NK021(zha)001:5483: dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa sogs //
NK021(zha)001:5485: dpal ldan bla ma'i gsung bzhin spel //
NK021(zha)001:5486: bya spyod thun mong gi theg pa'i dbang chog gi le tshan no //
NK021(zha)001:5489: 'gyur bcas sgrib kun mngon byang lngas //
NK021(zha)001:5490: sgrib med ye shes rigs lnga'i skur //
NK021(zha)001:5491: yongs dag rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK021(zha)001:5492: gus btud yo ga'i dbang chog bshad //
NK021(zha)001:5493: da ni drug pa yo ga'i theg pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:5494: sta gon sngon du 'gro bas dngos gzhi dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:5495: bri sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa sgrub thabs ltar
NK021(zha)001:5496: bya zhing / sbyin sreg byed dam /
NK021(zha)001:5498: de ltar zin nas dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa la gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:5499: dang po slob dpon 'jug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5500: slob ma ji ltar 'jug pa'i cho gas bdag nyid zhugs te dbang blang ba'am /
NK021(zha)001:5501: yang na sgo phye nas dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo
NK021(zha)001:5502: bsgyur ba nyid bla ma dang tha mi dad par
NK021(zha)001:5503: mos la rig pa'i me tog phul bas /
NK021(zha)001:5504: bdag dang dkyil 'khor pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan
NK021(zha)001:5505: phrin las rnams gnyis med du gyur par bsam ste
NK021(zha)001:5506: / slob dpon gyi las la rjes su gnang ba thob par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:5507: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5508: las bum gyi chus khrus bya /
NK021(zha)001:5509: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad /
NK021(zha)001:5510: sems bskyed dang chos nyan pa'i kun spyod gsal 'debs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK021(zha)001:5511: 'dir gang gsan par bya ba'i chos ni /
NK021(zha)001:5513: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor /
NK021(zha)001:5514: zhes pa'i bar sngar ltar ram /
NK021(zha)001:5515: spro bsdu ji ltar rigs pa 'dod na'ang byas rjes /
NK021(zha)001:5516: drug pa rnal 'byor phyi pa'i theg pa yo ga
NK021(zha)001:5517: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba
NK021(zha)001:5520: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams grub nas /
NK021(zha)001:5521: 'dir slob ma rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa la /
NK021(zha)001:5522: thog mar dkyil 'khor du 'jug cing dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala 'bul du bcug /
NK021(zha)001:5523: de nas slob dpon gyi zhabs la phyag byas te /
NK021(zha)001:5524: snyim pa me tog dang bcas pas thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:5525: bcom ldan nam mkha'i sangs rgyas kun //
NK021(zha)001:5526: theg pa chen po'i mthu ldan la //
NK021(zha)001:5527: bdag ni rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5528: rang bzhin ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan lhas //
NK021(zha)001:5529: bdag la dbang mchog deng stsol cig /
NK021(zha)001:5530: sangs rgyas bka' yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK021(zha)001:5531: bdag nyid dad pas 'jug lags na //
NK021(zha)001:5532: dkyil 'khor bcas pa'i lha tshogs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5533: bdag la byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:5534: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK021(zha)001:5535: bsod nams can du bdag nyid 'gyur //
NK021(zha)001:5536: sngon las bzang pos 'brel ba lags //
NK021(zha)001:5537: thugs kyi sras su dgongs par mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:5539: de nas slob ma rnams kyis tshe 'khor ba thog
NK021(zha)001:5540: ma med pa nas rgyu nyon mongs pa dug gsum
NK021(zha)001:5541: dang rkyen mi dge ba'i las bsags pas 'bras bu
NK021(zha)001:5542: ngan song gsum du skye 'gyur gyi sdig sgrib bag
NK021(zha)001:5543: chags dang bcas pa thams cad sbyangs par gyur snyam
NK021(zha)001:5545: sngar basngagasa pa'i yungs thun gyi brab cing /
NK021(zha)001:5546: da ha da ha sarba na ra ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:5547: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:5548: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ka ga te he tum h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:5550: de nas thun mong gi sdom pa bzung ba'i phyir
NK021(zha)001:5551: bla ma dang tha mi dad pa'i rdo rje dbyings
NK021(zha)001:5552: kyi dkyil 'khor la sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems
NK021(zha)001:5553: dpa'i tshogs kyis bskor ba mngon sum lta bur bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:5554: pa'i spyan sngar rgyun bshags sngon du 'gro ba can
NK021(zha)001:5555: gyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed par bagyi'o snyam
NK021(zha)001:5556: pas 'di'i dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:5557: dkon mchog gsum la bdag skyabs mchi //
NK021(zha)001:5558: sdig pa mi dge so sor bshags //
NK021(zha)001:5559: 'gro ba'i dge la rjes yi rang //
NK021(zha)001:5560: sangs rgyas byang chub yid kyis bzung //
NK021(zha)001:5561: sangs rgyas chos dang tshogs mchog la //
NK021(zha)001:5562: byang chub bar du bdag skyabs mchi //
NK021(zha)001:5563: rang gzhan don gnyis rab bsgrub phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5564: byang chub sems ni bskyed par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5565: byang chub mchog gi sems ni bskyed bgyis nas //
NK021(zha)001:5566: sems can thams cad bdag gis mgron du gnyer //
NK021(zha)001:5567: byang chub spyod mchog yid 'ong spyod par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5568: 'gro la phan phyir sangs rgyas 'grub par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5570: de nas thun mong ma yin pa rigs lnga'i sdom
NK021(zha)001:5571: pa bzung snyam pas 'di'i sangs rgyas byang chub sems
NK021(zha)001:5572: dpa' dang // dkyil 'khor lha tshogs dgongs su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:5573: bdag gis dus 'di nas bzung ste //
NK021(zha)001:5574: ji srid byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK021(zha)001:5575: ji ltar dus gsum mgon po rnams //
NK021(zha)001:5576: byang chub tu ni nges mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5577: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:5578: dam pa bdag gi bskyed par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5579: tshul khrims kyi ni bslab pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5580: dge ba'i chos ni sdud pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5581: sems can don byed tshul khrims gsum //
NK021(zha)001:5582: bdag gis brtan por bzung bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5583: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun te //
NK021(zha)001:5584: bla na med pa'i dkon mchog gsum //
NK021(zha)001:5585: sangs rgyas rnal 'byor las skyes pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5586: sdom pa deng nas brtan por bzung //
NK021(zha)001:5587: rdo rje rigs mchog chen po la //
NK021(zha)001:5588: rdo rje dril bu phyag rgya yang //
NK021(zha)001:5589: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5590: slob dpon dag kyang bzung bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5591: rin chen rigs mchog chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:5592: dam tshig yid du 'ong ba la //
NK021(zha)001:5593: nyin re bzhin ni lan drug tu //
NK021(zha)001:5594: sbyin pa rnam bzhi rtag tu sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:5595: byang chub chen po las byung ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:5596: pad+ma'i rigs mchog dag pa la //
NK021(zha)001:5597: phyi nang gsang ba'i theg pa gsum //
NK021(zha)001:5598: dam pa'i chos ni bzung bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5599: las kyi rigs mchog chen po la //
NK021(zha)001:5600: sdom pa thams cad ldan par ni //
NK021(zha)001:5601: yang dag nyid du bzung bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5602: mchod pa'i las kyang ci nus bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5603: byang chub sems ni bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:5604: dam pa bdag gis bskyed bgyis nas //
NK021(zha)001:5605: sems can kun gyi don gyi phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5606: bdag gis sdom pa ma lus bzung //
NK021(zha)001:5607: ma grol ba rnams dgrol bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5608: ma sgrol ba rnams bsgral bar bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5609: dbugs ma phyin rnams dbugs dbyung zhing //
NK021(zha)001:5612: de nas nang gi mi shigs pa'i sems bskyed pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5613: phyir sa ma ya a zhes pas khyed rang rnams
NK021(zha)001:5614: kyi snying gar kun rdzob byang sems zla ba'i dkyil
NK021(zha)001:5615: 'khor gyi steng du h+aum las don dam byang chub
NK021(zha)001:5616: kyi sems kyi ngo bo rdo rje dkar po rtse
NK021(zha)001:5617: lnga pa'i rnam par sgoms la 'di'i rjes zlos /
NK021(zha)001:5618: sarba yo ga tsit+ta ut+pa da y+aa mi /
NK021(zha)001:5619: slob dpon gyis rdo rjes reg ste /
NK021(zha)001:5620: su ra te sa ma ya s+t+wam ho sid+d+hi badz+ra ya th+aa su kham /
NK021(zha)001:5622: badz+ra sat+wa zhes pas khyed rang rnams rdo rje'i sems
NK021(zha)001:5623: dpa'i skur gyur pa la mchod pa'i mos pa mdzod
NK021(zha)001:5627: +aa lo ke bcug pas mchod nas chos bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5628: don gcig na'ang ma rmongs dang //
NK021(zha)001:5629: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5630: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:5631: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK021(zha)001:5633: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis
NK021(zha)001:5634: gdul bya'i blo'i rim pa dang 'tshams par theg pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5635: sgo mtha' yas par gsungs pa las /
NK021(zha)001:5636: 'dir nges 'byung gi theg pa lha mi /
NK021(zha)001:5637: nyan rang byang sems bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:5640: thabs la mkhas pa'i khyad par gyis mchog tu gyur
NK021(zha)001:5641: pa gsang sngags kyi dkyil 'khor chen por zhugs nas
NK021(zha)001:5642: nyams su blang du yod pa 'di ni rnyed pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5643: mchog rab tu rnyed par gyur to //
NK021(zha)001:5644: snyam du dga' zhing spro ba'i sems bskyed 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:5645: de nas a kham w+ai ra h+aum gis mig dar bcings /
NK021(zha)001:5646: badz+ra m+aa le h+aum gis me tog gi phreng ba
NK021(zha)001:5647: gtad pa sems ma rdo rje ma'i dam rgyas 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:5648: du bcug la / sgo dbye bar gsol ba gdab
NK021(zha)001:5649: pa 'di'i rjes rab gnas sgo 'di ma rig pas
NK021(zha)001:5650: du bcug la / // thogs med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK021(zha)001:5651: tshad med bzhi ldan phyag rgya bzhis //
NK021(zha)001:5652: de ring thar pa'i sgo dbye gsol //
NK021(zha)001:5653: shar nas badz+ra kro d+ha ta th+aa ga tot+sa ma
NK021(zha)001:5654: ye ta th+aa pra we sh+r+ai kram s+pha ra na
NK021(zha)001:5656: de bzhin du lho sogs nas badz+ra gyi gnas su /
NK021(zha)001:5657: rat+na pad+ma karma bcug pa'i sngags tshan bzhis gsol ba
NK021(zha)001:5658: btab pas sgo bzhi rim pa phye bar bsam la
NK021(zha)001:5659: / dngos su yol ba yod na bsal /
NK021(zha)001:5660: de nas dkyil 'khor du 'jug par gsol ba gdab
NK021(zha)001:5661: pa 'di'i rjes snying po'i dkyil 'khor dam pa 'dir
NK021(zha)001:5662: // bla med byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK021(zha)001:5663: dngos grub dam pa thob bya'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5664: bdag nyid dad pas 'jug tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:5665: zhes gsol ba btab pa'i lan du gnang ba sbyin pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5668: byang chub rin chen sems bskyed de //
NK021(zha)001:5669: 'khor ba'i nang nas rab drangs nas //
NK021(zha)001:5670: bde gshegs sras su bskyed pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:5671: bla med 'bras bu smin bya'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5672: bdag gis slob ma gzhug par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:5674: de nas slob dpon gyi lag gi rdo rje la 'jur bcug nas /
NK021(zha)001:5677: sgo bzhi nas tshad med bzhi'i 'jug pas zhugs te
NK021(zha)001:5678: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la phyag 'tshal bar mos la
NK021(zha)001:5680: rgyal ba rigs lnga 'khor bcas la //
NK021(zha)001:5681: skal ldan rgyal sras dag pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:5682: rab tu gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK021(zha)001:5683: de nas khe nyen brjod pa'i sgo nas dam la bzhag pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5684: rdo rje sems dpa' deng khyod kyi //
NK021(zha)001:5685: snying la yang dag zhugs par mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:5686: gal te tshul 'di smras na ni //
NK021(zha)001:5687: de ma thag tu bral te gshegs //
NK021(zha)001:5689: zhes dung chos kyi chu blud /
NK021(zha)001:5690: bka' gnyan pa'i sgo nas dam la bzhag pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5691: spyi bor rdo rje bzhag ste /
NK021(zha)001:5692: deng nas brtsams te bu khyod kyi //
NK021(zha)001:5693: phyag na rdo rje nga yin gyi //
NK021(zha)001:5694: nga yis ji ltar bsgo ba'i bka' //
NK021(zha)001:5695: khyod kyis skyo ba med par bsgrubs //
NK021(zha)001:5696: gal te gus par ma byas na //
NK021(zha)001:5697: bdud kyis bcom nas ngan 'gror ltung //
NK021(zha)001:5699: de nas ye shes dbab pa'i phyir bla ma a
NK021(zha)001:5700: las byung ba'i rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs kar zla
NK021(zha)001:5701: ba la rdo rje'i dbus su as mtshan pa /
NK021(zha)001:5702: khyed rang rnams h+aum las rdo rje sems dpa'i sku
NK021(zha)001:5703: rdul bral dwangs pa shel ltar gyur pa'i snying gar
NK021(zha)001:5705: dpral bar t+r+aam las rin chen /
NK021(zha)001:5707: spyi bor kam las sna tshogs rdo rjes mtshan par
NK021(zha)001:5708: bsam nas gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i bdag ni rdo
NK021(zha)001:5710: rdo rje sems dpa' yin pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5711: rdo rje ye shes bla med ni //
NK021(zha)001:5712: de ring bdag la dbab tu gsol //
NK021(zha)001:5715: badz+rod+g+ha ta sa ma ya pra we sha ya h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:5716: zhes brjod pas slob dpon dang slob ma'i snying ga'i sgo phye /
NK021(zha)001:5717: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i a yig las a yig 'od zer 'bar ba dpag tu med pa byung /
NK021(zha)001:5718: khyed rang rnams kyi snying ga'i rdo rje'i lte bar thim /
NK021(zha)001:5719: 'od zer gyis lus thams cad gang /
NK021(zha)001:5720: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs gnyis su med pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5721: ye shes h+aum yig gi rnam pa char ltar babs
NK021(zha)001:5722: pa lus la zhugs pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:5723: slob dpon gyis rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu gsil bas /
NK021(zha)001:5724: 'di ni rdo rje'i dam tshig ste //
NK021(zha)001:5725: rdo rje sems dpa' yin par grags //
NK021(zha)001:5726: rdo rje ye shes bla med ni //
NK021(zha)001:5727: de ring nyid du 'bab par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5728: badz+ra +aa be sha ah zhes mang du brjod pas dbab /
NK021(zha)001:5729: phebs pa na brtan pa'i phyir spyi bor rdo rje rgya gram du bzhag la /
NK021(zha)001:5730: a sa me tri sa me ma h+aa sa ma ya h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:5731: de nas sngar gzung ba'i me tog rang gi lha
NK021(zha)001:5732: la 'bul ba'i bsam pas 'di'i sangs rgyas dngos grub
NK021(zha)001:5733: thob bya'i phyir // bdag la thugs brtser dgongs nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:5734: 'gro la phan phyir gtso chen gyis //
NK021(zha)001:5735: sman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:5736: pra t+aits+tsha badz+ra hoh zhes me tog dor /
NK021(zha)001:5737: gang la babs pa'i lha des me tog rang gi mgo bor bcings par mos su bcug ste /
NK021(zha)001:5738: pra ti grih+na t+wam i mam sat+wa ma h+aa ba la /
NK021(zha)001:5739: zhes me tog mgor bcings la //
NK021(zha)001:5740: rdo rje sems dpa' deng khyod kyis //
NK021(zha)001:5741: mig 'byed par ni brtson par mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:5742: phye bas thams cad mthong 'gyur ba //
NK021(zha)001:5743: rdo rje'i mig ni bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:5744: badz+ra h+aa s+ya ung+g+ha ta ya h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:5746: de ltar rdo rje'i mig thob pa de la mthong ba bstan pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:5748: de yang 'di na rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor chen po mngon sum du bzhugs pa yin te /
NK021(zha)001:5749: bsrung ba'i 'khor los mi phyed par bcings pa'i nang
NK021(zha)001:5750: pad+ma la gnas pa'i sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar
NK021(zha)001:5751: rdzogs pa'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa
NK021(zha)001:5752: nyis rim mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su tshang ba'i
NK021(zha)001:5753: lte ba ling tshe dgu'i dbus dang phyogs bzhir 'khor
NK021(zha)001:5754: lo rtsibs bzhi pa re re /
NK021(zha)001:5755: lha so so'i gdan dang bcas pa /
NK021(zha)001:5756: ling tshe dbus ma'i lte bar bcom ldan 'das rnam
NK021(zha)001:5757: par snang mdzad ser po kun tu zhal byang chub
NK021(zha)001:5758: mchog gi phyag rgya can rtsibs bzhir sbas yum bzhi
NK021(zha)001:5759: / phyogs bzhi ling tshe bzhi'i lte bar shar du mi bskyod pa /
NK021(zha)001:5763: so so'i rtsibs la rang rigs kyi sems dpa' bzhi bzhis bskor ba /
NK021(zha)001:5766: sgo rnams su sgeg sogs bcu gnyis //
NK021(zha)001:5767: gzhal yas khang phyi ma'i snam bu la sems dpa'
NK021(zha)001:5768: bcu drug rnams bzhugs pa mngon sum bzhin du mthong
NK021(zha)001:5769: bar gyur snyam pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:5771: dngos gzhi'i slad du gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rjes bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:5772: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du bdag la dbang bskur du gsol /
NK021(zha)001:5774: de nas khye rang rnams dbang stegs kyi khri'i steng
NK021(zha)001:5775: du rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam pas dkyil 'khor la
NK021(zha)001:5776: mngon par phyogs pa'i tshul gyis 'khod pa'i mos pa
NK021(zha)001:5777: mdzod / slob dpon gyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha la
NK021(zha)001:5778: 'dud pa dang bcas pas mkhyen par gsol ba ni
NK021(zha)001:5779: mdzod / / bdag rdo rje slob dpon 'di zhes
NK021(zha)001:5780: bgyi ba thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang thob par
NK021(zha)001:5781: mdzod / / bya ba dang / sangs rgyas kyi
NK021(zha)001:5782: che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa sgrub cing sems
NK021(zha)001:5783: can gyi don yongs su rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir
NK021(zha)001:5784: mdzod / / bya ba dang / / rdo rje
NK021(zha)001:5785: dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur bar 'tshal gyis
NK021(zha)001:5787: ldan 'das ye shes kyi gtso bo thugs rje'i mnga'
NK021(zha)001:5788: bdag rnams kyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i che ba'i yon
NK021(zha)001:5789: tan gyi dbang rnams rim pa bzhin du bskur zhing
NK021(zha)001:5792: slob dpon dang lhan cig par dkyil 'khor pa'i thugs
NK021(zha)001:5793: ka nas spros pa'i lha sogs nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:5794: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis dbang bskur bas sdig sgrib
NK021(zha)001:5795: bag chags dang bcas pa thams cad byang zhing dag
NK021(zha)001:5797: rnam rgyal bum pa bteg ste /
NK021(zha)001:5798: rin chen mdzes pa'i bum pa 'di //
NK021(zha)001:5799: gnyis med byang chub sems chus gang //
NK021(zha)001:5800: skal ldan khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:5801: las nyon sdig sgrib dag gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:5805: pad+ma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah
NK021(zha)001:5806: zhes bum pa mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag cing bum
NK021(zha)001:5808: rin po che'i dbu rgyan dar dpyangs dang bcas pa bskon la /
NK021(zha)001:5809: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:5810: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kun 'dus pa //
NK021(zha)001:5811: gzi brjid rigs sngags rgyal ba'i dbu //
NK021(zha)001:5812: bu khyod gtsug na nor bur 'bar //
NK021(zha)001:5813: badz+ra d+h+aa t+w+ai shwa r+ai h+aum badz+r+ai ni a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK021(zha)001:5814: badz+ra badz+ri ni a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK021(zha)001:5815: rat+na badz+r+aa ni a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK021(zha)001:5816: d+harma badz+r+ai ni a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK021(zha)001:5817: karma badz+r+ai ni a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK021(zha)001:5819: badz+ra tush+ya hoh lag tu rdo rje dang lhan cig tu dril bu'ang gtod cing /
NK021(zha)001:5820: sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:5821: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:5822: sangs rgyas kun tu rab bsgrub phyir //
NK021(zha)001:5823: rdo rje 'di ni khyod kyis longs //
NK021(zha)001:5824: badz+ra a d+hi pa ti s+t+wam a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam /
NK021(zha)001:5825: tish+tha badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK021(zha)001:5826: zhes rdo rje gsor zhing snying gar bzung /
NK021(zha)001:5827: dril bu snyims tshul gyis dkur brten du gzhug go //
NK021(zha)001:5828: rdor dril rgya gram du bzung ba spyi bor dkrol la /
NK021(zha)001:5829: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:5830: byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK021(zha)001:5831: cis kyang mi phyed mi shigs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:5832: ming gi dbang bskur bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:5833: badz+ra sat+wa s+t+wam a b+hi shiny+tsa m+aam badz+ra n+aa ma
NK021(zha)001:5834: a b+hi she ka tah kye dpal rdo rje dbyings
NK021(zha)001:5835: zhes bya ba'i de bzhin gshegs pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:5836: de nas gang spyad kyang 'khor ba'i spyod pa hrul por byed pa brtul zhugs kyi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:5837: h+aum las skyes pa'i rdo rje gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:5838: 'di de sangs rgyas thams cad yin //
NK021(zha)001:5839: phyag na rdo rje'i phyag na 'dug /
NK021(zha)001:5840: khyod kyis kyang ni lag tu bcang //
NK021(zha)001:5841: phyag na rdo rje'i brtul zhugs brtan //
NK021(zha)001:5842: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid+d+hi badz+ra sa ma ya
NK021(zha)001:5843: tish+tha e sha s+t+wam d+ha ra y+aa mi badz+ra sat+wa
NK021(zha)001:5844: h+ai / hi hi hi hi h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:5845: zhes rdo rje gsor zhing snying gar bzung ngo //
NK021(zha)001:5846: dbang bskur tshul 'di ni glan rdo rje 'od kyi
NK021(zha)001:5847: phyag bzhes kyi las tho rnams las bshad pa ltar
NK021(zha)001:5849: phal che ba bum dbang tsam las mi bskur ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:5850: 'ga' zhig kun rig gi dbang skabs 'dir sbyor bar
NK021(zha)001:5851: mdzad pa rnams ni zor yang tsam du zad do
NK021(zha)001:5852: // de nas lha dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:5853: slob dpon dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams kyi thugs ka dang /
NK021(zha)001:5854: 'og min gyi gnas nas rdo rje dbyings kyi lha
NK021(zha)001:5855: tshogs rnams rim par byon nas khyed rang rnams kyi
NK021(zha)001:5856: spyi bo nas thim pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:5857: lha tsaka rnams rim par thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:5859: snang stong rdo rje nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK021(zha)001:5860: chos dbyings ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:5861: rdo rje mchog gi phyag rgya can //
NK021(zha)001:5862: rnam par snang mdzad dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:5863: bud+d+ha be ro tsa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:5864: gzung 'dzin rdo rje brtan pa'i sa //
NK021(zha)001:5865: me long ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:5866: rdo rje sa gnon phyag rgya can //
NK021(zha)001:5867: rdo rje mi bskyod dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:5868: badz+ra ak+sho b+h+yahh+aum a b+hi rin chen rdo rje 'bar ba'i me //
NK021(zha)001:5869: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:5870: rdo rje mchog sbyin phyag rgya can //
NK021(zha)001:5871: rin chen 'byung ldan dbang rat+na sam b+ha wa t+r+aam a b+hi mtha' yas rdo rje chos kyi chu //
NK021(zha)001:5872: kun rtog ye shes rdo rje'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:5873: rdo rje ting 'dzin snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma a
NK021(zha)001:5874: mi t+aa b+ha h+r+aiha b+hi don yod rdo rje bskyod
NK021(zha)001:5875: pa'i rlung // bya grub ye shes rdo rje skyabs
NK021(zha)001:5876: sbyin rdo rje don grub karma a mo g+ha sid+d+hi
NK021(zha)001:5878: me long ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK021(zha)001:5879: sems ma rdo rje'i phyag rgya ste //
NK021(zha)001:5880: rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa //
NK021(zha)001:5881: de yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:5882: sat+wa badz+ri h+aum a b+hi mnyam nyid ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK021(zha)001:5883: rin chen sems ma'i phyag rgya ste //
NK021(zha)001:5884: rin chen ser po zur brgyad pa //
NK021(zha)001:5885: de yi dbang mchog rat+na badz+ri t+r+aam a b+hi kun rtog ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK021(zha)001:5886: chos kyi sems ma'i pad dkar 'dab ma bcu drug pa //
NK021(zha)001:5887: de yi dbang mchog pad+ma badz+ri h+r+aiha b+hi bya grub
NK021(zha)001:5888: ye shes byin las kyi sems ma'i phyag rdo rje
NK021(zha)001:5890: de yi dbang mchog karma badz+ri aha b+hi rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK021(zha)001:5891: rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa kun //
NK021(zha)001:5892: rdo rje dang po kun tu bzang //
NK021(zha)001:5893: phyag na rdo rje'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:5894: badz+ri sat+wa h+aum a b+hi rdo rje rgyal po sangs rgyas mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5895: rdo rje lcags kyu de bzhin gshegs //
NK021(zha)001:5896: nges pa'i rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5897: rdo rje 'gugs khyod dbang badz+ra r+aa dza dza a b+hi rdo rje chags pa bde chen po //
NK021(zha)001:5898: rdo rje mda' ni dbang byed pa //
NK021(zha)001:5899: bdud kyi 'dod pa rdo rje che //
NK021(zha)001:5900: rdo rje gzhu khyod dbang badz+ra r+aa ga hoha b+hi rdo rje legs pa sems dpa' mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5901: rdo rje mgu ba dga' ba che //
NK021(zha)001:5902: rab dgyes rgyal po rdo rje mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5903: rdo rje dgyes khyod dbang badz+ra s+aa d+hu d+hu a b+hi rdo rje rin chen rdo rje don //
NK021(zha)001:5904: rdo rje nam mkha' nor bu che //
NK021(zha)001:5905: nam mkha'i snying po rdo rje phyug /
NK021(zha)001:5906: rdo rje snying khyod dbang badz+ra rat+na t+r+aam a b+hi rdo rje gzi brjid 'bar ba che //
NK021(zha)001:5907: rdo rje nyi ma rgyal ba'i 'od //
NK021(zha)001:5908: rdo rje 'od zer gzi brjid che //
NK021(zha)001:5909: rdo rje 'od khyod dbang badz+ra te dzar+ya a b+hi rdo rje sems can don rab dpal //
NK021(zha)001:5910: rdo rje rgyal mtshan rab dga' byed //
NK021(zha)001:5911: rdo rje chen po rin chen dpal //
NK021(zha)001:5912: rdo rje dpal khyod dbang badz+ra ke tu b+h+ri a b+hi rdo rje bzhad mo bzhad pa che //
NK021(zha)001:5913: rdo rje 'dzum pa ngo mtshar che //
NK021(zha)001:5914: dga' zhing rab dga' rdo rje ston //
NK021(zha)001:5915: rdo rje dga' khyod dbang badz+ra ha sa ha a b+hi rdo rje chos rab de nyid ston //
NK021(zha)001:5916: rdo rje pad+ma rab dga' byed //
NK021(zha)001:5917: 'jig rten dbang phyug rab mdzes spyan //
NK021(zha)001:5918: rdo rje spyan khyod dbang badz+ra d+harma h+r+aiha b+hi rdo rje rnon po theg pa chen //
NK021(zha)001:5919: rdo rje ral gri mtshon chen po //
NK021(zha)001:5920: 'jam dpal rdo rje rab tu zab //
NK021(zha)001:5921: rdo rje blo khyod dbang badz+ra t+aik+sh+na d+h+ai a b+hi rdo rje rgyu dang snying po che //
NK021(zha)001:5922: rdo rje 'khor lo tshul chen po //
NK021(zha)001:5923: rab bskor rdo rje las byung ba //
NK021(zha)001:5924: rdo rje snying po'i dbang badz+ra he tu krum a b+hi rdo rje gsung ba rang rig mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5925: rdo rje zlos pa rab sgrub sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:5926: mi gsung rdo rje mchog grub pa //
NK021(zha)001:5927: rdo rje gsung khyod dbang badz+ra b+h+aa sha b+h+aa a b+hi rdo rje las rab rdo rje dka' //
NK021(zha)001:5928: las kyi rdo rje kun rab sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:5929: rdo rje nges par rgya che ba //
NK021(zha)001:5930: rdo rje las khyod dbang badz+ra karma kam a b+hi rdo rje bsrung ba brtan pa che //
NK021(zha)001:5931: rdo rje go cha sra ba che //
NK021(zha)001:5932: rdo rje brtson 'grus thub dka' ba //
NK021(zha)001:5933: rdo rje brtson 'grus dbang badz+ra rak+sha ham a b+hi rdo rje gnod sbyin thabs chen po //
NK021(zha)001:5934: rdo rje mche ba 'jigs pa che //
NK021(zha)001:5935: bdud 'joms rdo rje mi bzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:5936: rdo rje drag po'i dbang badz+ra yak+sha h+aum a b+hi rdo rje mtshams sbyor rab tu sdud //
NK021(zha)001:5937: rdo rje 'ching ba rnam grol byed //
NK021(zha)001:5938: rdo rje khu tshur dam tshig mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5939: rdo rje khu tshur dbang badz+ra san+d+he bam a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:5940: rnam dag rdo rje thugs kyi yum //
NK021(zha)001:5941: mi dmigs rdo rje mtshan ma 'joms //
NK021(zha)001:5943: rdo rje sgeg mo'i dbang badz+ra l+aa s+ya h+aum a b+hi rnam dag rdo rje yon tan yum //
NK021(zha)001:5944: yid bzhin re ba skong bar mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:5945: rdo rje phreng ba'i phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:5946: rdo rje phreng ma'i dbang badz+ra m+aa le tram a b+hi rnam dag rdo rje gsung gi yum //
NK021(zha)001:5947: gsung rab rgya mtsho sgrog pa'i don //
NK021(zha)001:5948: rdo rje pi wam phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:5949: rdo rje dbyangs mkhan dbang badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aiha rnam dag rdo rje las kyi yum //
NK021(zha)001:5950: las kyi rdo rje 'gro don mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:5951: bdud 'dul rdo rje phyag rgya gar //
NK021(zha)001:5952: rdo rje gar mkhan dbang badz+ra n+ri t+ye aha b+hi sprin lding rdo rje bdug pa mo //
NK021(zha)001:5953: rdo rje tshim byed kun tu tshim //
NK021(zha)001:5954: rdo rje spos khang phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:5955: rdo rje spos ma'i dbang badz+ra d+h+au pe h+aum a b+hi lta mdzes rdo rje thams cad mdzes //
NK021(zha)001:5956: rdo rje me tog kun tu mdzes //
NK021(zha)001:5957: rdo rje me tog phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:5958: me tog ma yi dbang badz+ra push+pe tram a b+hi 'od gsal rdo rje mda' yi me //
NK021(zha)001:5959: rdo rje can gyis ma rig sel //
NK021(zha)001:5960: rdo rje gsal byed phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:5961: rdo rje mar me'i badz+ra +aa lo ke h+r+aiha b+hi rdo rje tsan+dana bdud rtsi'i chu //
NK021(zha)001:5962: rdo rje bdud rtsis rnam rtog 'khru //
NK021(zha)001:5963: rdo rje dag byed phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:5964: rdo rje dri ma'i badz+ra gan+d+he aha b+hi rnam dag bskul byed thugs rje'i don //
NK021(zha)001:5967: rdo rje lcags kyu'i badz+ra am ku sha dzah a b+hi mi gtong rdo rje chos kyi don //
NK021(zha)001:5970: rdo rje zhags ma'i dbang badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum a b+hi rdo rje chos nyid mi 'gyur don //
NK021(zha)001:5971: rdo rje mgyogs byed glog ltar myur //
NK021(zha)001:5972: rdo rje lcags sgrog phyag rgya 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:5973: rdo rje lcags sgrog dbang badz+ra s+pho ta bam a b+hi rdo rje 'bebs pa brtan pa'i mchog /
NK021(zha)001:5974: rdo rje bskyod mdzad kun gyi las //
NK021(zha)001:5976: rdo rje dril bu'i badz+ra a be sha ya aha b+hi sgo yi khyams kyi nang gnas pa //
NK021(zha)001:5977: byams pa la sogs bcu drug ni //
NK021(zha)001:5978: dang po rab dga' la sogs gnas //
NK021(zha)001:5979: sa gnas rnams kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:5980: sarba sams+k+aa ra pa ra shud+d+ha d+harma te ga ga
NK021(zha)001:5981: na sa mut+ga te swa b+h+aa ba bi shud+d+he ma
NK021(zha)001:5982: h+aa na ya pa ri w+aa re s+w+aah+aa a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:5984: de nas yo ga'i rdzas dbang rnams rim par bskur
NK021(zha)001:5985: bas sngon rnam par snang mdzad kyis ji ltar dbang
NK021(zha)001:5986: bskur ba dang rjes su mthun pa'i yon tan khyad
