NK021(zha)001:8824: hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK021(zha)001:8825: bdag rdo rje slob dpon 'di zhes bya bas slob
NK021(zha)001:8826: bu 'di rnams la 'dus pas chen po'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:8827: bar 'tshal bas / phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK021(zha)001:8831: slob bu rnams la dbang bskur ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:8832: sems can don la bdag brtson na //
NK021(zha)001:8833: bzod par mdzad de dgongs su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:8834: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK021(zha)001:8835: dbang gi lha phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs
NK021(zha)001:8836: pa sras dang bcas pa thams cad mdun gyi nam
NK021(zha)001:8837: mkha'i gnas su sprin 'thib pa bzhin sad nas bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:8838: pas dbang ci dga' bar bskur cig /
NK021(zha)001:8839: ces gnang ba byin par bsam nas /
NK021(zha)001:8840: dbu rgyan sogs 'khor los sgyur ba'i chas su zhugs te /
NK021(zha)001:8841: bskur rlob kyi sngags brjod pas /
NK021(zha)001:8842: bdag nyid sku gsung thugs kyi gzi byin dang ldan par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:8843: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad kun //
NK021(zha)001:8845: dang ba'i yid kyis zhugs nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:8846: byin brlabs dbang mchog nod par mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:8847: ces brjod cing dkyiil 'khor gyi dbus su 'dug par mos te /
NK021(zha)001:8848: rang nyid dbang khri la snyems pa dang bcas pas 'dug go //
NK021(zha)001:8849: de nas slob bu rnams gnas su dkri zhing lhar bskyed pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:8850: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i h+aum las h+aum yig 'bar
NK021(zha)001:8851: ba re chad pa snying gar thim pas ma dag
NK021(zha)001:8853: khyed rang rnams skad cig gis rdo rje sems dpa'
NK021(zha)001:8854: rdul bral dwangs pa'i sku gyur pa dkyil 'khor gyi
NK021(zha)001:8855: shar sgor dbang stegs pad+ma'i stan la 'khod pa'i mos
NK021(zha)001:8856: pa mdzod / slob dpon gyis rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i phyag rgya snying gar gtugs te /
NK021(zha)001:8857: badz+ra sa t+wa +aah zhes pas gsal zhing brtan par byas pa la /
NK021(zha)001:8858: bskur byed dkyil 'khor pa las spros pa dang nam
NK021(zha)001:8859: mkhar bzhugs pa'i dbang lha rnams kyis dbang rim par
NK021(zha)001:8860: bskur ba'i mos pa byed du bcug ste /
NK021(zha)001:8861: bskur bya phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo'am phan pa'i dbang bcu las /
NK021(zha)001:8862: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:8864: h+aum big+h+n+aan+ta krita phata kyis bsang /
NK021(zha)001:8866: dbang rdzas mi dmigs pa las de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i skur gyur /
NK021(zha)001:8867: ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis su med par byas pa /
NK021(zha)001:8868: slob ma'i gnas lngar thim pas phung po lnga rigs lnga'i skur dag par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:8869: zhi ba rigs lnga'i tsakli spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK021(zha)001:8870: kun gyis 'da' bar dka' ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:8871: tshig btsan yul la dbang bsgyur ba //
NK021(zha)001:8872: rgyal po'i bka' rtags phyag rgya'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:8873: sku lnga yongs su rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK021(zha)001:8874: h+aum s+w+aa h+r+aihh+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:8876: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:8877: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyed rnams la lha
NK021(zha)001:8878: sku phyag rgya chen po'i dbang bskur bas sku lnga
NK021(zha)001:8879: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:8880: cig / gnyis pa rtags kyi mtshan pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:8882: dbang rdzas mi dmigs pa las rigs lnga'i skur gyur /
NK021(zha)001:8883: ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis med du byas
NK021(zha)001:8884: pa zhu ba las byung ba'i phyag mtshan lag g.yas
NK021(zha)001:8885: su gtad pa snying ga'i rtsa chen bzhi la thim
NK021(zha)001:8886: pas rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag par
NK021(zha)001:8887: mos la / rigs rnams so so'i rgyud 'dzin cing //
NK021(zha)001:8888: rtags kyi mtshan ma chen po ni //
NK021(zha)001:8889: sbyor ba chen po'i phyag mtshan te //
NK021(zha)001:8890: dam tshig phyag rgyas dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:8892: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:8894: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na a b+hi rin chen gtad la /
NK021(zha)001:8895: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na a b+hi pad+ma gtad la /
NK021(zha)001:8896: ma h+aa pra t+ya ba k+sh+ae na dz+ny+aa na a b+hi ral gri gtad la /
NK021(zha)001:8897: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na a na mo /
NK021(zha)001:8898: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:8899: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyed rnams la rigs
NK021(zha)001:8900: lnga'i phyag mtshan dam tshig gi phyag rgya'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:8901: bas rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dbang dam pa thob
NK021(zha)001:8902: par gyur cig / gsum pa shes rab gzungs kyi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:8904: dbang rdzas mi dmigs pa las rigs kyi yum lngar gyur /
NK021(zha)001:8905: ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hoh zhu ba las byung
NK021(zha)001:8906: ba'i gzungs kyi phyag rgya lag g.yon par gtad pa
NK021(zha)001:8907: dbu ma'i thig le la thim pas khams lnga dbyings
NK021(zha)001:8908: su dag ste 'od gsal rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK021(zha)001:8909: shes rab mthar phyin par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:8910: rig ma'i tsakli 'am dril bu gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:8911: shes rab gzungs kyi dbang mchog ni //
NK021(zha)001:8912: don dang ldan par gyur pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:8913: mtha' gnyis dag tu mi gtong ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:8914: gzungs ma'i rgyal mo chen po yin //
NK021(zha)001:8915: gnyis med yongs su rdzogs pas na //
NK021(zha)001:8916: thams cad bde ba chen po'i ngang //
NK021(zha)001:8917: byang chub sems dang don du 'brel //
NK021(zha)001:8918: shes rab chen po rdzogs dbang sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:8919: ma h+aa mu d+r+aa a b+hi na mo /
NK021(zha)001:8920: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:8921: khyed rnams la shes rab gzungs ma'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:8922: rtogs pa'i gzungs kyis mtha' gnyis su mi gtong ba'i
NK021(zha)001:8923: dbang dam pa bzhi pa bkra shis bum pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:8925: dbang rdzas mi dmig pa las /
NK021(zha)001:8926: ye shes rin po che'i bum pa mtshan nyid yongs
NK021(zha)001:8927: su rdzogs pa'i gzhal yas khang du dkyil 'khor gyi
NK021(zha)001:8928: lha tshogs thams cad gsal bar gyur /
NK021(zha)001:8929: ye shes pa dzahh+aum bam hohs bstim /
NK021(zha)001:8930: til gyi gang bu kha bye ba bzhin du nam
NK021(zha)001:8931: mkha' gang bar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams
NK021(zha)001:8933: rol mo'i sgra sgrog cing me tog gi char 'bebs
NK021(zha)001:8934: pa sogs ngo mtshar ba'i dge mtshan gyi rnam pa
NK021(zha)001:8935: du ma dang ldan par dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:8936: bum nang gi lha tshogs thams cad rjes chags kyis
NK021(zha)001:8937: snyoms par zhugs pa las babs pa'i byang sems ye
NK021(zha)001:8938: shes lnga'i rang bzhin bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun rtsa gnas
NK021(zha)001:8939: kun gyi thig le la thim zhing 'phel bas lus
NK021(zha)001:8940: thams cad skya mer gyis khengs /
NK021(zha)001:8941: ngag ma dag pa'i rlung gi 'gyu ba thams cad dang bral /
NK021(zha)001:8942: sems bde ba chen po rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK021(zha)001:8943: ye shes nyams su myong bas rgyud rlan par byas
NK021(zha)001:8944: / phung khams nyon mongs pa lnga sogs rtog tshogs
NK021(zha)001:8945: thams cad sku dang ye shes su dag par mos
NK021(zha)001:8946: / la / bum pa lnga'am dgu yod na gzhan rnams kyi chu dbus kyi bum par bsdus nas /
NK021(zha)001:8947: spos 'thul zhing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas bum pa spyi bor bzhag la /
NK021(zha)001:8948: bkra shis chen po'i bum pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:8949: bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i pho brang ste //
NK021(zha)001:8950: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par gyur pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:8951: dbang mchog de yang sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:8952: badz+ra ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:8953: bud+d+ha ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK021(zha)001:8954: rat+na ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa s+w+aa /
NK021(zha)001:8955: pad+ma ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih karma ka la sha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:8956: zhes bum chu mgo bo'i gnas lngar gtigs shing blud do //
NK021(zha)001:8958: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK021(zha)001:8959: kyi skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyed rnams la
NK021(zha)001:8960: bum pa byang chub sems kyi chu rgyun gyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:8961: bskur bas phyi nang gi sgrib pa ma lus pa
NK021(zha)001:8962: dag nas dkyil 'khor yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:8963: pa lnga pa bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang ni
NK021(zha)001:8964: / mam las byung ba'i bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad
NK021(zha)001:8965: gtad pas gsang ba'i bstan pa 'phel zhing yun du
NK021(zha)001:8966: btsan pas bkra shis pa'i rten 'brel sgrigs par bsam
NK021(zha)001:8967: / la / gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyas nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:8968: yun ring gnas par 'gyur ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:8969: bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang mchog kyang //
NK021(zha)001:8970: gnang ba chen po sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:8971: rdzas brgyad rim par gtod cing /
NK021(zha)001:8972: yungs kar dngos grub bgegs kyi sbyor ba rnam 'joms shog /
NK021(zha)001:8973: sar+sha pa dra bya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:8974: zho yis rgyas byed ting 'dzin bcud kyis 'tsho bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:8975: da d+hi dra bya a b+hi durbasa dge ba'i rtsa ba dpag med tshogs ldan shog /
NK021(zha)001:8976: dur+b+aa dra bya a b+hi li khris lha mi ma lus dbang du 'du bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:8977: sin+d+h+au ra dra bya a b+hi me long gis ni chos kun gzugs brnyan ltar rtogs shog /
NK021(zha)001:8978: +aa dar+sha dra bya a b+hi dung gis 'jig rten gsum du grags pa thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:8979: shang+kha dra bya a b+hi gi'u wam dug gsum zhi byed chos srog 'tsho bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:8980: go ro tsa na dra bya a b+hi bilbasa bla med byang chub snying po thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:8981: bilba dra bya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:8983: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:8984: khyed rnams la bkra shis pa'i rdzas kyis dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:8985: bas ji ltar bshad pa'i yon tan de rnams kyis
NK021(zha)001:8986: / gnas skabs su bstan pa 'phel zhing yun du btsan pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:8987: mthar thug 'phags lam yan lag brgyad mngon du byed
NK021(zha)001:8988: pa'i dbang dam pa drug pa rin chen sna bdun
NK021(zha)001:8989: gyi dbang ni / las byung ba'i rin po che
NK021(zha)001:8990: sna bdun lag tu gtad pas chos kyi 'khor los
NK021(zha)001:8991: sgyur ba'i rten 'brel sgrigs par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:8992: don rnams grub par gyur ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:8993: 'dod dgu'i re skongs rin po che //
NK021(zha)001:8994: rgyal srid rin chen sna bdun gyis //
NK021(zha)001:8995: rgyal po mchog tu dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:8996: rin chen bdun rim par gtod cing /
NK021(zha)001:8997: tsakra rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:8998: ma ni rat+na a b+hi wa ti rat+na ma h+aa
NK021(zha)001:8999: ta rat+na hasti rat+na tu rang+ga rat+na khang+ga rat+na na
NK021(zha)001:9000: mo / phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa
NK021(zha)001:9001: 'dzin pa khyed rnams la rin po che sna bdun
NK021(zha)001:9002: gyi dbang bskur bas gnas skabs su 'khor los sgyur
NK021(zha)001:9003: ba'i rgyal srid dang mthar thug byang chub yan lag
NK021(zha)001:9004: bdun gyis chos kyi rgyal po chen po'i go 'phang
NK021(zha)001:9005: la mnga' bsgyur ba'i dbang dam pa bdun pa gdan
NK021(zha)001:9006: mo / khri'i dbang ni / b+h+r+aum las byung ba'i
NK021(zha)001:9007: gdan khri bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa 'og tu
NK021(zha)001:9008: bting bas bla na med pa'i go 'phang la dbang
NK021(zha)001:9009: bsgyur ba'i rten 'brel sgrigs par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:9011: rin chen pad+ma seng ge'i khri //
NK021(zha)001:9012: bla mar gyur pa'i gdan mchog ste //
NK021(zha)001:9013: khyad par chen por gyur pa'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:9014: khri chen dag la bzhag par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9016: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:9017: khyed rnams la gdan khri'i dbang bskur bas mi 'jigs
NK021(zha)001:9018: pa bzhi dang / stobs bcu dang /
NK021(zha)001:9019: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang /
NK021(zha)001:9021: thogs pa med pa'i phrin las dang /
NK021(zha)001:9022: dgos 'dod yid bzhin du 'grub pa'i dbang thob ste //
NK021(zha)001:9023: bla na med pa'i chos kyi rgyal po chen por gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:9024: brgyad pa rgyan chas rtags kyi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9025: tram las byung ba'i rgyan cha rnams bskon pas 'bras
NK021(zha)001:9026: bu'i chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i rten 'brel
NK021(zha)001:9029: dar gyi cod pan me tog phreng ba sogs //
NK021(zha)001:9030: dbang mchog brjid pa'i rgyan gyis klubs //
NK021(zha)001:9031: dbu rgyan do shal se mo do //
NK021(zha)001:9032: dpung rgyan rkang gdub lag gdub rnams //
NK021(zha)001:9033: dbang thob rgyal po de la sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:9035: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:9036: khyed rnams la mdzes pa rgyan chas kyi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:9037: bas / mi brjid pa'i gzungs dang /
NK021(zha)001:9038: gzungs kyi sgo lnga brgya dang /
NK021(zha)001:9039: ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum phrag dang /
NK021(zha)001:9040: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos rnams dang /
NK021(zha)001:9041: mtshan dang dpe byad la sogs pa 'bras bu'i chos
NK021(zha)001:9042: thams cad la dbang bsgyur ba'i dam pa dgu pa
NK021(zha)001:9043: dbang bsgyur ming gi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9045: rin chen dbang phyug sogs dbang phyug gi mtha' can rigs kyi ming btags shing /
NK021(zha)001:9046: de nyid slob dpon dang nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de
NK021(zha)001:9047: bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu btags par
NK021(zha)001:9048: bsam la / lag g.yas skyabs sbyin gyi rdo rje thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:9049: dbang thob mdzes pas brjid pa'i rgyal po de //
NK021(zha)001:9050: dbang phyug yin pas de la gus phyag 'tshal //
NK021(zha)001:9051: rdo rje dbang phyug dbang phyug ces par ni //
NK021(zha)001:9052: kun gyis sgra cher 'bod cing bsgrag par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9054: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:9055: khyod la che ge dbang phyug ces bya ba rdo
NK021(zha)001:9056: rje ming gi dbang bskur bas sangs rgyas dang rig
NK021(zha)001:9057: pa 'dzin pa'i zhing khams kun tu yongs su grags
NK021(zha)001:9058: pa'i dbang dam pa ces dril bus sna drangs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:9060: bcu pa rgyal thabs 'khor lo'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9061: b+h+r+aum las byung ba'i gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs stong
NK021(zha)001:9062: dang ldan pa lag tu byin pas chos kyi 'khor
NK021(zha)001:9063: los sgyur ba'i rgyal thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul ba'i
NK021(zha)001:9066: gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs khyud ldan pa zhig /
NK021(zha)001:9067: rgyal po de yi lag tu bskur nas ni //
NK021(zha)001:9068: 'jig rten kun la kha lo bsgyur ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:9069: dbang mchog rgyal po 'di yang sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9070: badz+ra tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9072: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:9073: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyed rnams la 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:9074: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal thabs kyis 'jig rte gyi
NK021(zha)001:9075: kha lo gyen du bsgyur ba'i dbang dam pa thob
NK021(zha)001:9076: par gyur cig / ces bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:9077: de rnams kyis ni phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bor grags pa phan pa'i dbang bcu thob /
NK021(zha)001:9078: phyi 'khor skyong ba'i rgyal por gyur cing /
NK021(zha)001:9079: bla na med pa'i byang chub mchog gi rigs can du phyin pas nang dbang bskur rung du smin /
NK021(zha)001:9080: gtso bor las kyi sgrib pa dang lus kyis dri ma rags pa 'khrud /
NK021(zha)001:9081: rnal 'byor phyi pa man chad kyi theg pa mtha' dag bshad cing sgrub pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:9082: de rnams dang thun mong par gyur pa a nu
NK021(zha)001:9083: rang lugs kyi chos drang don gtso bor ston pa
NK021(zha)001:9084: rnams mnyan pa dang sgrub pa la dbang /
NK021(zha)001:9085: rnal 'byor bzhi las yo ga dang /
NK021(zha)001:9086: mthar thug bdun pa dmigs pa 'bras bu skye ba'i
NK021(zha)001:9087: sa man chad non pa sgom lam lung chen thob
NK021(zha)001:9088: pa'i rnal 'byor mngon du byed pa'i skal ba can
NK021(zha)001:9089: du byas so // gnyis pa nang dbang 'byung ba'i
NK021(zha)001:9090: chu bo'am nus pa'i dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala
NK021(zha)001:9092: lus thams cad sa la phab pa'i brkyang phyag sngon
NK021(zha)001:9093: du 'gro bas thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab
NK021(zha)001:9094: pa 'di'i gsang ba chen po'i rigs tshogs su /
NK021(zha)001:9095: deng nas bdag ni 'jug par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9096: phyir mi ldog par lung thob phyir //
NK021(zha)001:9097: bdag la gsang sgo dbye bar gsol //
NK021(zha)001:9100: phyi 'khor skyong ba'i rgyal por gyur phan chad //
NK021(zha)001:9101: bla med mchog gi rtags dang ldan gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9102: gsang sgo phye nas nang du gzhug par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9105: phyi dbang bcu po rdzogs pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:9106: rdo rjes nang du gzhug bya ba //
NK021(zha)001:9107: zhes pas dmigs pa 'di ltar mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:9108: bla ma dang gnyis su med pa'i dpal chen po
NK021(zha)001:9109: yab yum mnyam par sbyor ba'i mkha' gsang las nyi
NK021(zha)001:9110: zla byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyi sprin 'phros
NK021(zha)001:9111: pas nang dkyil mthong ba la sgrib pa'i dri ma
NK021(zha)001:9112: thams cad phral te don la nges par 'jug pa'i
NK021(zha)001:9114: slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas las kyi rdo rje
NK021(zha)001:9115: he ru ka'i rnam par spros pa'i phyag gi rdo
NK021(zha)001:9117: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i mdun phyogs kyi khyams nang
NK021(zha)001:9118: du dbang stegs seng khri pad+ma'i stan steng rdo rje
NK021(zha)001:9119: sems dpa'i rnam pas 'khod pa la /
NK021(zha)001:9120: bskur bya nang dbang bcu gcig las /
NK021(zha)001:9121: dang po dad pa dang sri zhu tshad du phyin
NK021(zha)001:9122: pa la gsang ba'i don nyan cing slob pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:9123: bskur ba ni / slob bu'i rna ba gnyis su
NK021(zha)001:9124: nyan shes kyi thig le nyid tram yig zung las
NK021(zha)001:9125: rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum ser po rin po
NK021(zha)001:9126: che dang dril bu 'dzin pa'i skur gyur /
NK021(zha)001:9127: gnas gsum las 'phros pa'i 'od kyis tshig dang don
NK021(zha)001:9128: gyi gzungs la sogs pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon
NK021(zha)001:9129: tan rin po che'i gter thams cad 'od kyi rnam
NK021(zha)001:9131: chos nyan pa la sgrib pa'i dri ma thams cad dag /
NK021(zha)001:9132: slob ma lha dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba
NK021(zha)001:9133: las rin chen 'byung ldan gyi skur gyur pas nyan
NK021(zha)001:9135: t+r+aam las byung ba'i rin 'byung gi ngo bo rgyud kyi glegs bam gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:9137: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog rnam gsum gyi //
NK021(zha)001:9138: gsang ba'i don la mnyan zhing slob pa'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:9139: dbang thob skal ldan khyod la sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9140: bdud rtsi'i chu 'dis rna ba'i gsang sgo dbye //
NK021(zha)001:9141: sarba ta th+aa ga ta d+harma sid+d+hi hoh zhes bsgrag /
NK021(zha)001:9143: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:9144: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la nyan pa'i
NK021(zha)001:9145: dbang bskur bas gsang ba'i bka' mtha' dag nyan pa'i
NK021(zha)001:9146: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:9147: gnyis pa las rnam bzhi tshad du phyin par nus pa la phrin las kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:9148: slob bu'i lag mthil gnyis su bskyod byed kyi thig
NK021(zha)001:9149: le nyid h+aa yig zung las don yod grub pa
NK021(zha)001:9150: yab yum ljang khu rgya gram dang dril bu 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:9151: pa'i skur gyur / gnas gsum las 'phros pa'i 'od
NK021(zha)001:9152: kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis phrin las
NK021(zha)001:9153: 'od kyi rnam par bsdus te thim pas /
NK021(zha)001:9154: 'gro ba 'dul ba'i phrin las sgrib pa'i dri ma thams cad dag /
NK021(zha)001:9155: slob ma lha dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba
NK021(zha)001:9156: las don yod grub pa'i skur gyur pas phrin las
NK021(zha)001:9157: kyi dbang thob par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:9158: h+aam las byung ba'i don grub kyi ngo bo sna tshogs rdo rje gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:9160: khyed kyi 'gro ba'i don byed nus pas na //
NK021(zha)001:9161: las rnams rgya mtsho thams cad 'grub pa'i rtags //
NK021(zha)001:9162: rdo rje rgya gram zhi sogs rnam bzhi'i rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:9163: bu mchog khyod la thabs kyis sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9165: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:9166: khyod la bya ba phrin las kyi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:9167: 'gro ba'i don la thogs pa med par spyod pa'i
NK021(zha)001:9168: dbang dam pa gsum pa ma 'gags pa'i shes rab
NK021(zha)001:9169: tshad du phyin pa la rgyal thebs 'chad pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:9170: bskur ba ni / slob bu'i lce la smra byed
NK021(zha)001:9171: kyi thig le nyid h+r+aihyiga zung las snang ba mtha'
NK021(zha)001:9172: yas yab yum dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:9173: bskur ba ni / pa'i skur gyur / gnas gsum
NK021(zha)001:9174: las 'phros pa'i 'od kyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK021(zha)001:9175: cad kyi gsung rdo rje 'od kyi rnam par bsdus
NK021(zha)001:9176: te thim pas chos 'chad pa sgrib pa dri ma
NK021(zha)001:9177: bskur ba ni / pa'i skur gyur / thams cad
NK021(zha)001:9178: dag / slob ma lha dang bcas pa 'od du
NK021(zha)001:9179: zhu ba las snang ba mtha' yas kyi skur gyur
NK021(zha)001:9180: pas 'chad pa'i dbang thob par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:9181: h+r+aihls byung ba snang mtha'i ngo bo 'khor lo gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:9182: h+r+aih gzhan gyi re 'dod skong ba'i bu mchog de //
NK021(zha)001:9183: rgyal po rgyal rigs rgyud du byung ba bzhin //
NK021(zha)001:9184: rgyal tshab chos kyi rgyud du byung bas na //
NK021(zha)001:9185: tan+t+ra la sogs dam pa'i mdzod gsum sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:9187: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:9188: khyod la chos 'chad pa'i dbang bskur bas bka' gsang
NK021(zha)001:9189: ba'i theg pa mtha' dag 'chad pa'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:9190: / bzhi pa dam pa'i mdzod gsum la phyogs med
NK021(zha)001:9191: 'chad par mkhas pa la rdo rje rgyal por rab
NK021(zha)001:9193: rje sgro phug pas spyi bor rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK021(zha)001:9194: dbang don rgyas par de bzhin gshegs rigs rnam snang
NK021(zha)001:9195: bsgom par gsungs pa ltar byas kyang mi 'gal mod
NK021(zha)001:9196: / de lta na'ang rngam glog las /
NK021(zha)001:9197: de nas rab 'byams rgyal po'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:9198: yan lag lnga la rigs lngas bskur //
NK021(zha)001:9201: kun bzang du bskyed par gsungs pa ltar /
NK021(zha)001:9202: rdo rje rgyal po rigs thams cad kyi bdag po yin pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:9203: rigs spyi'i dbang bskur ba 'brel chags pas na 'dir /
NK021(zha)001:9204: slob bu'i mgo la las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo /
NK021(zha)001:9205: lag g.yas la h+aum las mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo rje /
NK021(zha)001:9206: lag g.yon par s+w+aa las rin 'byung ser po rin po che /
NK021(zha)001:9207: rkang pa g.yon par +aam las snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma /
NK021(zha)001:9208: rkang pa g.yas par h+aa las don grub ljang khu rgya gram /
NK021(zha)001:9209: lnga ka g.yon dril bu 'dzin zhing rang 'od kyi yum dang 'khril ba'i skur gyur /
NK021(zha)001:9210: de rnams kyi gnas gsum las 'phros pa'i 'od kyis
NK021(zha)001:9211: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga so so'i byin rlabs
NK021(zha)001:9212: 'od kyi rnam par bsdus te thim pas /
NK021(zha)001:9213: don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa spyod cing sgrub pa la sgrib pa'i dri ma thams cad dag /
NK021(zha)001:9214: slob ma lha dang bcas pa 'od du zhu ba
NK021(zha)001:9215: las rigs thams cad kyi bdag po kun tu bzang
NK021(zha)001:9217: rdo rje slob dpon gyi las rab 'byams la spyod pa'i dbang thob par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:9218: dang a las byung ba kun bzang yab yum gyi
NK021(zha)001:9219: ngo bo rdo rje rtse dgu pa dang dril bu
NK021(zha)001:9220: gtad de // khyod kyis slob ma'i tshogs kun slob nus pas //
NK021(zha)001:9221: bstan pa sgrog pa'i sar gnas bya ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:9222: rdo rje rgyal po dpal gyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK021(zha)001:9223: theg chen dgu yi rtags dang bcas te byin //
NK021(zha)001:9225: phyogs bcu dus skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod
NK021(zha)001:9226: la rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang bskur bas thabs mkhas
NK021(zha)001:9227: thugs rje'i rlabs kyis 'gro ba 'dren pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:9228: pa lnga pa gdan khri'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9229: rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang thob pas bla na med
NK021(zha)001:9230: pa'i chos kyi rgyal po chen po'i sa non pa'i
NK021(zha)001:9231: rtags su zil gnon gdan khri'i bkod pa phun sum
NK021(zha)001:9232: tshogs pa 'og tu bting bar bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:9234: khyod ni bla med rgyal por gyur pas na //
NK021(zha)001:9235: sa rnams non pa'i dbang mchog gdan khri'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:9236: lha chen la sogs zhing chen nyi zlar bcas //
NK021(zha)001:9237: khyu mchog seng ge ma he gzig dang stag /
NK021(zha)001:9238: gtum pa dom gyis 'phags te byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9240: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la /
NK021(zha)001:9241: khams gsum gyi dregs pa can zil gyis gnon pa lha chen po'i gdan dang /
NK021(zha)001:9242: thabs shes 'brel bas 'gro don byed pa nyi zla'i gdan dang /
NK021(zha)001:9243: rgol ba zil gyis gnon pa khyu mchog glang seng gi gdan dang /
NK021(zha)001:9244: brtul zhugs chen po thogs pa med par 'jug pa dom gyi gdan dang /
NK021(zha)001:9245: yon tan phun sum tshogs pas brjid pa ma he'i gdan dang /
NK021(zha)001:9246: mthun 'jug gi las la mkhas pa gzig gi gdan dang /
NK021(zha)001:9247: sa rnams mngon sum du 'bar ba stag gi gdan
NK021(zha)001:9248: rnams kyi dbang bskur bas yon tan de dag yongs
NK021(zha)001:9249: su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa drug pa thun mong
NK021(zha)001:9250: ma yin pa'i rin chen bdun gyi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9251: rdzas rnams mi dmigs pa las lha so sor gyur
NK021(zha)001:9252: pa zhu ba las byung ba'i lha de dang de'i
NK021(zha)001:9253: ngo bo chos kyi rgyal po'i rtags rin po che
NK021(zha)001:9254: bdun du gyur pa gtad pas gsang ba bla na
NK021(zha)001:9255: med pa'i chos kyi rgyal srid la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK021(zha)001:9256: nus pa thob par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:9257: rgyal po yin pa'i rtags ni rnam pa bdun //
NK021(zha)001:9258: skye la dbang sgyur rgyal po mnyes pa'i gzungs //
NK021(zha)001:9259: pha rol dpung 'joms srid thub 'dzin pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:9260: bdag gzhan don sgrub rdzu 'phrul rkang par ldan //
NK021(zha)001:9261: dgos 'dod yid bzhin skong ba'i rin po che //
NK021(zha)001:9262: rgyal po khyod la thabs kyis byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9263: rdzas rnams re re nas gtod cing /
NK021(zha)001:9265: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la /
NK021(zha)001:9266: yi dam gyi lha yab rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo
NK021(zha)001:9267: bo rus pa'i 'khor lo'i dbang bskur bas skye ba
NK021(zha)001:9268: rnam pa bzhi la dbang bsgyur ba'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:9270: yum dbyings phyug ma'i ngo bo btsun mo'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:9271: bas 'byung ba rnam bzhir rang dbang thabs kyis spyod
NK021(zha)001:9272: pa la 'jug pa'i dbang khro bo stobs po che'i
NK021(zha)001:9273: ngo bo dmag dpon gyi dbang bskur bas tshul dgus
NK021(zha)001:9274: bdud bzhi'i dpung 'joms pa'i dbang dam pa sems dpa'
NK021(zha)001:9275: rdo rje'i ngo bo khyim bdag gi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:9276: tshad med bzhi'i blo gros phun sum tshogs pas chos
NK021(zha)001:9277: kyi chab srid 'dzin pa'i dbang dam pa byang sems
NK021(zha)001:9278: spos kyi glang po'i ngo bo glang chen gyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:9279: bskur bas stobs bcu'i rtsal gyis bdag dang gzhan gyi
NK021(zha)001:9280: don thams cad sgrub pa'i dbang dam pa khro bo
NK021(zha)001:9281: rta mgrin gyi ngo bo rta'i dbang bskur bas thogs
NK021(zha)001:9282: pa med pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang ldan
NK021(zha)001:9283: pa'i dbang dam pa byang sems rdo rje rin chen
NK021(zha)001:9284: gyi ngo bo nor bu rin po che'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:9285: bas sbyin pa rnam pa bzhis gdul bya'i re 'dod
NK021(zha)001:9286: yid bzhin du skong ba'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK021(zha)001:9287: gyur cig / bdun pa phyag rgya gzugs brnyan gyi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9289: de nas rgyal ba'i sras po yin pas na //
NK021(zha)001:9290: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang mchog byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:9291: ras sam 'bur ram lugs su blugs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:9292: phyag rgya'i gzugs brnyan de yi spyi bor bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:9293: ces pa'i don rgya bdun 'grel dang rje sgro phug
NK021(zha)001:9294: pa'i dbang chog tu khro bo'i lha dbang nyid bskur
NK021(zha)001:9296: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du rgyud lugs kyi chu bo bzhi kho na bskur ba'i lugs yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:9297: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gcig tu dril ba'i skabs 'dir 'dren pa'i las byang che le dang /
NK021(zha)001:9298: dbang don rgya cher 'byed par zhi khro'i lha lnga
NK021(zha)001:9299: brgya dang brgyad cu rtsa gsum bskur bar gsungs pas
NK021(zha)001:9300: zhi ba'i lha dbang yang bskur dgos shing /
NK021(zha)001:9301: de'i lha grangs dbang don rgya cher 'byed par /
NK021(zha)001:9302: bde chen gcig dang brgyad cu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK021(zha)001:9304: bde chen gcig dang bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK021(zha)001:9305: zhes dpe mi 'dra ba gnyis byung ba ltar zur
NK021(zha)001:9306: ham gyi phyag bzhes kyi rgyun la snga ma ltar
NK021(zha)001:9307: mdzad na'ang / 'dir glan gyi yig rnying dang zur
NK021(zha)001:9308: mo dge 'dun 'bum gyi phyag bzhes rgyun la phyi
NK021(zha)001:9309: ma ltar 'byung ba nyid dag par mngon te /
NK021(zha)001:9311: zhi khro'i lha spyi grangs lnga brgya gya gsum dang /
NK021(zha)001:9312: bye brag zhi ba'i lha grangs la bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK021(zha)001:9313: yang zur ham gyi phyag len la rig 'dzin bla
NK021(zha)001:9314: ma'i dbang rnams sgrub dbang gi rjes su bskur bar
NK021(zha)001:9316: skabs 'dir bskur dgos par dbang don gyi lung sngar gyi 'phros las /
NK021(zha)001:9317: dkyil 'khor tha ma byin rlabs slob dpon dbang //
NK021(zha)001:9320: de nas byin pa slob dpon gyi dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9321: dus gsum gyi rdo rje slob dpon gyi mtshan dang /
NK021(zha)001:9322: gsang mtshan dang bcas pas bskur te /
NK021(zha)001:9323: de'ang dam tshig dbang gi slob dpon dang /
NK021(zha)001:9324: shes rab rgyud kyi slob dpon dang /
NK021(zha)001:9325: man ngag 'bras bu'i slob dpon gyi rim pas dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:9327: des na 'dren pa'i las byang chen pos dbang bskur ba la gsum gyi /
NK021(zha)001:9329: byin pa slob dpon gyi dbang gnyis bskur ba'i skabs yin /
NK021(zha)001:9330: de la phan pa lha'i dbang la'ang /
NK021(zha)001:9333: dang po zhi ba'i lha dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:9334: khyed rang rnams rigs drug pa bcom lda 'das dpal
NK021(zha)001:9335: kun tu bzang po mthing ka zhal gsum phyag drug
NK021(zha)001:9336: pa yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo dang 'khril
NK021(zha)001:9338: slob dpon gyis lha so so'i tsaklisa dbang bskur ba'i
NK021(zha)001:9339: dus su dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs las lha de
NK021(zha)001:9340: dang de mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi rnam
NK021(zha)001:9341: par spyi bo nas so so'i rtog pa la thim
NK021(zha)001:9342: pas rtog tshogs zhe gnyis ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa
NK021(zha)001:9343: gnyis su grol ba'i nus pa thob pa'i rtags su
NK021(zha)001:9344: gzhi lus kyi gnas so so lha de dang de
NK021(zha)001:9345: lus dkyil gyi rnam par bkra lam gyis grub pa'i
NK021(zha)001:9346: mos pa mdzod / tsakli rnams rim par thogs nas /
NK021(zha)001:9347: rigs bdag kun bzang yab yum dbyings rig la thim
NK021(zha)001:9348: pas gzhi lus kyi lha nyid gsal zhing 'bar bar
NK021(zha)001:9349: gyur / e ma ho kun bzang rdo rje yid //
NK021(zha)001:9350: rig pa tshul snang sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9351: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK021(zha)001:9352: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9353: phyi yi yul snang sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9354: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK021(zha)001:9355: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yum //
NK021(zha)001:9356: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9358: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9359: rigs lnga yab yum phung khams la thim pas thugs
NK021(zha)001:9360: kar 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la bzhugs par mos nas
NK021(zha)001:9362: rnam shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9363: rdo rje rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK021(zha)001:9364: sangs rgyas kun gyi thugs yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9365: rdo rje sems dpa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9366: 'byung ba nam mkha' sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9367: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:9368: rdo rje rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9369: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9372: a b+hi gzugs kyi phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9373: de bzhin gshegs rigs lhun gyis grub //
NK021(zha)001:9374: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9375: rnam par snang mdzad dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9376: 'byung ba sa ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9377: rdo rje dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:9378: bde gshegs rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9379: sangs rgyas spyan ma'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9382: a b+hi tshor ba'i phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9383: rin chen rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK021(zha)001:9384: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan mchog /
NK021(zha)001:9385: rin chen 'byung ldan dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9386: 'byung ba chu yis sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9387: rin chen dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:9388: rin chen rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9389: m+aa ma k+ai yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9392: a b+hi 'du shes phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9393: pad+ma rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK021(zha)001:9394: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9395: snang ba mtha' yas dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9396: 'byung ba me ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9397: pad+ma dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:9398: pad+ma rigs kyi yum yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9399: gos dkar mo yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9402: a b+hi 'du byed phung po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9403: las kyi rigs su lhun gyis grub //
NK021(zha)001:9404: sangs rgyas phrin las mchog yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:9405: don yod grub pa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9406: 'byung ba rlung gi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9407: las kyi dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:9408: sna tshogs 'dul ba'i yum yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:9409: dam tshig sgrol ma'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9412: a b+hi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad shes yul dbang dus /
NK021(zha)001:9413: so sor thim pas mig sogs dbang rten g.yas g.yon bzhi bzhi la bzhugs par mos te /
NK021(zha)001:9414: mig gi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9415: byang chub chen po mthong ba'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:9416: bdag gi mig las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9417: sa yi snying po'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9418: gzugs su snang ba sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9419: byang chub lha mo dkar mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9420: phyi yul gzugs las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9421: lha mo l+aa s+ye'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9423: h+aum l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK021(zha)001:9424: a b+hi sna yi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9425: byang chub chen po snom pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:9426: bdag gi sna las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9427: nam mkha' snying po'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9428: dri yi yul ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9429: byang chub lha mo bee d+aur+ya //
NK021(zha)001:9430: dri yi yul las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9431: lha mo m+aa le'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9434: tram m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoh a b+hi lce yi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9435: byang chub chen po myong ba'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:9436: bdag gi lce las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9437: spyan ras gzigs kyi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9438: ro yi yul ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9439: byang chub lha mo r+aa ga'i mdog /
NK021(zha)001:9440: dro ba'i yul las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9441: lha mo g+airti'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9442: h+r+aihh+aa h+aum pad+ma pa da ma /
NK021(zha)001:9444: a b+hi rna ba'i rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9445: byang chub chen po thob pa'i dpal //
NK021(zha)001:9446: rna ba nyid las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9447: phyag na rdo rje'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9448: sgra yi yul ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9449: byang chub lha mo n+ai len+d+ra //
NK021(zha)001:9450: sgra yi yul las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9451: lha mo nirti'i dbang mchog sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:9453: am nirti r+aa ga y+aa myi /
NK021(zha)001:9454: a b+hi mthong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9455: byang chub chen po mthong bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:9456: de nyid las ni bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9457: byams pa mee tri'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9458: dbyar dgun ston dpyid sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9459: dus bzhi'i yul rnams sems ma'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:9460: 'das dus las ni bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9461: badz+ra d+h+au pe'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9462: me d+h+aa ra ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9464: a b+hi thos pa'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9465: byang chub chen po thos par byed //
NK021(zha)001:9466: thos pa'i dbang po las bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9467: sgrib pa rnam sel dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9468: dus bzhi nyid ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9469: lha mo 'od ldan mdzes pa'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:9470: da lta'i dus las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9472: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9474: a b+hi snom pa'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9475: byang chub chen po snom par byed //
NK021(zha)001:9476: snom byed nyid las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9477: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9478: dus bzhi'i yul ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9479: lha mo mun sel 'od kyi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:9480: ma 'ongs dus las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9481: badz+ra lo ke'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9482: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9483: bam d+h+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK021(zha)001:9484: a b+hi myong ba'i dbang po sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9485: byang chub chen po myong byed dpal //
NK021(zha)001:9486: dbang po de las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9487: 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i dbang mchog byin /
NK021(zha)001:9488: dus bzhi'i dus ni sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9489: lha mo 'jam des bde ldan ma //
NK021(zha)001:9490: ma nges dus las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9492: mum sh+r+ai am r+aa ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9494: a b+hi mthar byed yab yum lus kyi chos bzhi
NK021(zha)001:9495: dang mu bzhi'i chos nyid la bstim pas rkang lag
NK021(zha)001:9496: gi mthil bzhir bzhugs par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:9497: phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9498: 'joms byed khro bo reg shes te //
NK021(zha)001:9499: reg shes nyid las sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9500: gshin rje gshed po'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9501: de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9502: rtag par ma yin khro mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9503: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9504: ro langs ma yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9506: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:9507: a b+hi phyin ci log bzhi'i sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9508: 'joms byed khro bo reg bya ste //
NK021(zha)001:9509: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9510: gzhan gyis mi thub dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9511: de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9512: chad par ma yin khro mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9513: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9514: mi pham ma yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9516: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa a b+hi phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9517: 'joms byed khro bo reg byed de //
NK021(zha)001:9518: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9519: khro chen rta mgrin dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9520: de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9521: bdag tu ma yin khro mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9522: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9523: khro gnyer ma yin dbang mchog sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:9525: pad+ma d+ha ra a b+hi phyin ci log bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9526: 'joms byed khro bo reg pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:9527: reg pa nyid las sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9528: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9529: de yi yul bzhi sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9530: mtshan mar ma yin khro mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9531: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pa //
NK021(zha)001:9532: ral gcig ma yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9534: karma d+ha ra a b+hi bya byed gnyis yid chos
NK021(zha)001:9535: la bstim pas snying ga'i mdun rgyab tu bzhugs par
NK021(zha)001:9536: mos la / yid kyi rnam shes sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9537: byed po kun tu bzang po ste //
NK021(zha)001:9538: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9539: kun tu bzang po'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9541: a b+hi chos kyi skye mched sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9542: bya ba kun tu bzang mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9543: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9544: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9545: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK021(zha)001:9546: a b+hi thub drug nyon mongs drug gi rtog pa la bstim pas /
NK021(zha)001:9547: dpral lce snying lte gsang gnas rkang mthil drug tu gsal bar mos la /
NK021(zha)001:9548: nga rgyal thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9549: brgya byin lha yi dbang po byung //
NK021(zha)001:9550: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9551: lha yi thub pa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9553: a b+hi phrag dog thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9554: lha ma yin la thag bzang ris //
NK021(zha)001:9555: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9556: lha min thub pa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9557: mu ne h+aum t+r+au s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9558: a b+hi 'dod chags thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9559: bcom ldan sh+aakya thub pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:9560: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9561: mi yi thub pa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9563: a b+hi gti mug nyid la sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9564: sangs rgyas seng ge rab brtan byung //
NK021(zha)001:9565: de nyid las ni sku bskyed pa //
NK021(zha)001:9566: byol song thub pa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9568: a b+hi ser sna thams cad sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9569: sangs rgyas kha 'bar sku byung ste //
NK021(zha)001:9570: ser sna nyid las bskyed byas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9571: yi dwags thub pa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9573: a b+hi zhe sdang ye nas sangs rgyas pas //
NK021(zha)001:9574: ston pa chos kyi rgyal po byung //
NK021(zha)001:9575: zhe sdang rgyu las sku bskyed pas //
NK021(zha)001:9576: dmyal ba'i thub pa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9580: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la /
NK021(zha)001:9581: kun gyi spyi dpal kun bzang bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK021(zha)001:9582: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu
NK021(zha)001:9583: rtsa gnyis kyi phyag rgya'i dbang bskur bas rtog tshogs
NK021(zha)001:9584: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du yongs su
NK021(zha)001:9585: dag pa'i dbang dam pa gnyis pa khro bo'i lha
NK021(zha)001:9586: dbang ni / khyed rang rnams kun tu bzang por gsal ba gnas bsgyur te /
NK021(zha)001:9587: dpal chen po che mchog he ru ka mthing nag
NK021(zha)001:9588: dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK021(zha)001:9589: pa / gsang ba'i rdo rje dang zhabs brgyad yum
NK021(zha)001:9590: gnam zhal dbyings phyug ma dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad
NK021(zha)001:9591: zhabs bzhi pa'i zhal dgu dang sbyar ba'i skur gyur
NK021(zha)001:9592: pa / pa la / dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs
NK021(zha)001:9593: rnams mar me gcig las gnyis chad kyi rnam par
NK021(zha)001:9594: pa / pa la / byon te / spyi bo
NK021(zha)001:9595: nas rtog tshogs so so la thim pas tha mal
NK021(zha)001:9596: gyi rtog pa dbyings su dag nas dpal chen po'i
NK021(zha)001:9597: sku dang ye shes su rtogs pas gnyis 'dzin gyi
NK021(zha)001:9598: mtha' la zhen pa'i 'gro ba rnams sgrol ba'i nus
NK021(zha)001:9600: gzhi lus kyi gnas so sor lha de dang de skad cig gis grub pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:9601: che mchog dang dbang mchog gnyis gzhi lus la bstim pas gsal zhing 'bar bar mos te /
NK021(zha)001:9603: ston pa kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK021(zha)001:9604: khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsan yab //
NK021(zha)001:9605: sku dang phyag rgya mngon rdzogs par //
NK021(zha)001:9606: che mchog he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9607: kun tu bzang mo gnas gyur pa //
NK021(zha)001:9608: khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK021(zha)001:9609: shes rab dbyings las sku bskyed pa //
NK021(zha)001:9610: kro d+he shwa r+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9611: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9612: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:9614: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK021(zha)001:9616: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:9617: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK021(zha)001:9618: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu /
NK021(zha)001:9619: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK021(zha)001:9620: dbu gsum bar du rngams pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:9621: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK021(zha)001:9622: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK021(zha)001:9623: srid gsum dbyings su sgrol ba'i zhal //
NK021(zha)001:9624: dbu gsum tha mar rngams pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:9625: g.yas g.yon dbus gsum mthing ga'i zhal //
NK021(zha)001:9626: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu /
NK021(zha)001:9627: khams gsum re ba skong ba'i zhal //
NK021(zha)001:9628: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:9629: stong pa bco brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK021(zha)001:9630: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:9631: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK021(zha)001:9632: b+hany+dza zhing chung ti ra g.yon //
NK021(zha)001:9633: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK021(zha)001:9634: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK021(zha)001:9635: me dang rgya mtsho ga'u g.yas //
NK021(zha)001:9636: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK021(zha)001:9637: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK021(zha)001:9638: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK021(zha)001:9639: kro d+h+ai mthing nag 'khril ba'i tshul //
NK021(zha)001:9640: rdo rje dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK021(zha)001:9641: khro rgyal dpal chen he ru ka /
NK021(zha)001:9642: dbang mchog sku yi dbang 'di byin //
NK021(zha)001:9643: sarba ta th+aa ga te sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9644: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9645: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+he shwa r+ai sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK021(zha)001:9646: a b+hi yab kyi snying gar 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad
NK021(zha)001:9647: kyi lte ba dang rtsibs la he ru ka dgu
NK021(zha)001:9649: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9652: mchod cing byin rlabs gsal sgrubs pa //
NK021(zha)001:9653: badz+ra he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9654: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9655: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK021(zha)001:9656: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK021(zha)001:9657: yab yum mchod cing gsal sgrubs pa //
NK021(zha)001:9658: badz+ra kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9659: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+he shwa ri sa ma ya h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9660: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9661: a b+hi rnam par snang mdzad gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9664: mchod cing sgrubs te byin rlabs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:9665: bud+d+ha he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9666: sangs rgyas spyan ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9667: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal ba //
NK021(zha)001:9668: thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems //
NK021(zha)001:9669: spyan drangs mchod cing sgrubs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:9670: bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9671: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9672: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9673: a b+hi rin chen 'byung ldan gnas gyur pas /
NK021(zha)001:9676: spyan drangs mchod cing sgrub pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:9677: rat+na he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9678: m+aa ma k+ai las gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9679: 'jigs byed khro mo'i sku byung ba //
NK021(zha)001:9680: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK021(zha)001:9681: spyan drangs mchod nas bsnyen sgrubs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:9682: rat+na kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9683: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+he shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK021(zha)001:9684: ru lu ru lu a b+hi snang ba mtha' yas gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9686: dmar nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK021(zha)001:9687: bsgoms shing mchod de sgrubs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:9688: pad+ma he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9689: na bza' dkar mo gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9690: 'jigs byed khro mo'i skur snang ba //
NK021(zha)001:9691: thabs shes byang chub sems sgrubs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:9692: pad+ma kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9693: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+he shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK021(zha)001:9694: ru lu a b+hi don yod grub pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9697: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod sgrubs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:9698: karma he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9699: dam tshig sgrol ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9701: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK021(zha)001:9702: lhag ma byang chub sems 'phros pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:9703: karma kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9704: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+he sh+aa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK021(zha)001:9705: ru lu a b+hi mthu stobs mnga' bdag gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9706: sgrol byed chen po bdud rnams 'joms //
NK021(zha)001:9707: thod g.yag srin po sgrol la brtson //
NK021(zha)001:9708: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK021(zha)001:9709: rak+sha he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9710: lha mo ral gcig gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9711: khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK021(zha)001:9712: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK021(zha)001:9713: rak+sha kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9714: ma h+aa rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK021(zha)001:9715: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK021(zha)001:9716: phata / ru lu ma h+aa rak+sha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:9717: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9718: e sha ra si ti na ma s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9719: a b+hi mkhyen rab bdag po gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9721: ser nag mdog can 'jigs pa'i gzugs //
NK021(zha)001:9722: gang sgrubs mthu dang dbang stsol ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:9723: sa nu he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9724: 'jig rten bdag mo gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9725: khro mo dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK021(zha)001:9726: sprul pa yang sprul kun gyi ma //
NK021(zha)001:9727: sa nu kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9728: ma h+aa sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa
NK021(zha)001:9729: tsan+da sarba ngush+t+aana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK021(zha)001:9730: tsa h+aum phata / ma h+aa sa nu kro d+h+ai sha r+ai h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:9731: a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9732: e sha ra si ti na mah ru lu a b+hi thugs rje'i bdag po gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9733: gsang ba'i don la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:9734: dmar nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK021(zha)001:9735: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK021(zha)001:9736: gu h+ya he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9737: gsung gi bdag mo gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9738: khro mo chen mo gsang ba'i lha //
NK021(zha)001:9739: gsang ba'i don la bskul byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9740: gu h+ya kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9741: gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK021(zha)001:9742: gu h+ya kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9743: ru lu a b+hi she ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9744: a b+hi badz+ra yak+sha gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9745: dpal chen dam tshig mnga' mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:9746: ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK021(zha)001:9747: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig lha //
NK021(zha)001:9748: yak+sha he ru ka'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9749: yum chen dam tshig gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9750: khro mo dam tshig bya ra mkhan //
NK021(zha)001:9751: sangs rgyas sems can 'da' mi byed //
NK021(zha)001:9752: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9753: yak+sha kro d+h+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9754: ma h+aa yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK021(zha)001:9755: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK021(zha)001:9756: phata / ma h+aa yak+sha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dz+wa li ni h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:9757: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9758: e sha ri si ti na mah bi she tsa ni mam ga la na sh+aa pa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9759: ru lu a b+hi goo r+ai ma brgyad mig sogs
NK021(zha)001:9760: g.yas g.yon gyi dbang rten bzhi bzhi'i rtsa nang du
NK021(zha)001:9761: bstim zhing de dang der bskyed la /
NK021(zha)001:9762: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:9763: 'khor lo brgyad kyi phyi rol na //
NK021(zha)001:9764: gru chad bzhi dang glo 'bur du //
NK021(zha)001:9765: khro mo brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:9766: sa yi snying po gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9767: srin mo chen mo keng thod btul //
NK021(zha)001:9768: dkar mo'i mthu rtsal 'gugs byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9769: badz+ra goo r+ai'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9771: a b+hi nam mkha'i snying po gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9772: srin mo chen mo mda' 'phen btul //
NK021(zha)001:9773: rkun mo'i mthu rtsal len byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9774: badz+ra tsoo r+ai'i dbang badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha /
NK021(zha)001:9775: a b+hi spyan ras gzigs dbang gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9776: srin mo chen mo 'dzin byed btul //
NK021(zha)001:9777: rmongs mo'i mthu rtsal 'bral byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9778: badz+ra pra mo h+aa'i dbang badz+ra pra mo he ha /
NK021(zha)001:9779: a b+hi phyag na rdo rje gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9780: srin mo be ta nag mo btul //
NK021(zha)001:9781: thal byed mthu rtsal nyams byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9782: badz+ra be ta l+ai'i dbang badz+ra be ta l+ai ha /
NK021(zha)001:9783: a b+hi 'phags pa byams pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9784: srin mo nang khrol 'dren ma btul //
NK021(zha)001:9785: sbos mo'i mthu rtsal 'ching byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9786: puk+ka s+ai yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9788: a b+hi sgrib pa rnam sel gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9789: lho nub srin mo rab 'jigs btul //
NK021(zha)001:9790: sme sha'i mthu rtsal smyo byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9791: gasma r+ai yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9793: a b+hi kun tu bzang po gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9794: nub byang srin mo srog gcod btul //
NK021(zha)001:9795: gtum mo'i mthu rtsal dbang byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9796: sma sha n+ai yi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9798: a b+hi 'jam dpal gzhon nu gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9799: byang shar srin mo smyon ma btul //
NK021(zha)001:9800: ma tshogs mthu rtsal smyo byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9801: tsan+da l+ai yi dbang badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha /
NK021(zha)001:9802: a b+hi ha ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9803: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9804: e sha ri si ti na mah bi she tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9806: yul gyi phra men brgyad dbang rten gyi rtsa'i phyir bstim zhing bskyed la /
NK021(zha)001:9807: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:9808: gru chad glo 'bur phyi rol gyi //
NK021(zha)001:9809: bar khyams phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi ru //
NK021(zha)001:9810: phra men brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:9811: rdo rje sgeg mo gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9812: shar phyogs srin mo seng gdong btul //
NK021(zha)001:9813: phra men mthu rtsal 'byin byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9814: sid+ha mu kh+aa'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9816: a b+hi rdo rje phreng ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9817: lho phyogs srin mo stag mgo btul //
NK021(zha)001:9818: phra men mthu rtsal 'joms byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9819: bya g+h+ri mu kh+ai'i dbang badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK021(zha)001:9820: a b+hi rdo rje glu ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9821: nub phyogs srin mo srog len btul //
NK021(zha)001:9822: phra men mthu rtsal 'dzin byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9823: sh+ri ga la mu kh+ai'i dbang badz+ra sh+ri g+aa la mu kh+ai he /
NK021(zha)001:9824: a b+hi rdo rje gar ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9825: byang phyogs srin mo ra ro btul //
NK021(zha)001:9826: phra men mthu rtsal 'dri byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9827: shwa na mu kh+ai'i badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK021(zha)001:9828: a b+hi rdo rje sbos ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9829: shar lho'i srin mo khrag 'thung btul //
NK021(zha)001:9830: phra men mthu rtsal 'gyogs byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9831: grid+d+ha mu kh+aa'i dbang badz+ra grid+d+ha a b+hi rdo rje me tog gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9832: lho nub srin mo rkang za btul //
NK021(zha)001:9833: phra men mthu rtsal khyab byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9834: kang+ka mu kh+aa'i badz+ra kang+ka mu kh+aa he /
NK021(zha)001:9835: a b+hi rdo rje sgron me gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9836: nub byang srin mo 'joms byed btul //
NK021(zha)001:9837: phra men mthu rtsal za byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9838: k+aa ka mu kh+aa'i dbang badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK021(zha)001:9839: a b+hi rdo rje dri ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9840: byang shar srin mo skem ma btul //
NK021(zha)001:9841: phra men mthu rtsal myos byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9842: u l+au mu kh+ai'i dbang badz+ra u l+au ka mu kh+ai he /
NK021(zha)001:9843: a b+hi he he he ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9844: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9845: e sha ri si ti na mah bi she tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9846: a b+hi sgo skyong gdong mo bzhi rkang lag gi mthil bzhi la bstim zhing bskyed la /
NK021(zha)001:9847: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:9848: gru chad bar khyams phyi rim gyi //
NK021(zha)001:9849: rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK021(zha)001:9850: sgo ma bzhi yis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:9851: lha mo byams ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9852: shar gyi srin mo rta mgo btul //
NK021(zha)001:9853: byams chen rnal 'byor mgon mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:9854: ang+ku sha yi dbang badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga
NK021(zha)001:9855: dzah a b+hi lha mo snying rje gnas gyur pas
NK021(zha)001:9856: // lho sgo'i srin mo phag mgo btul //
NK021(zha)001:9857: thugs rjes gzhan la phan 'dogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:9858: badz+ra p+aa sha'i dbang badz+ra a mu khe h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9859: a b+hi dga' ba chen mo gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9860: nub sgo'i srin mo dred mgo btul //
NK021(zha)001:9861: dga' bas rnal 'byor stongs mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:9862: lo ka ma yi dbang badz+ra lo ka bam /
NK021(zha)001:9863: a b+hi btang snyoms chen mo gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9864: byang sngo'i srin mo spyang mgo btul //
NK021(zha)001:9865: btang snyoms chen pos don mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:9866: thal byed ma yi badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hoh a b+hi phata phata phata /
NK021(zha)001:9868: a b+hi she ka te s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9869: e sha ri si ti na mah bi she tsa ni swa ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9871: spor ma brgyad snying ga nas g.yas bskor gyi nu ma /
NK021(zha)001:9874: sog phrag sogs lus kyi gnas brgyad la bstim zhing bskyed la /
NK021(zha)001:9875: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:9876: rnam thar sgo bzhi'i phyi rol tu //
NK021(zha)001:9877: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:9878: snam bu phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi ru //
NK021(zha)001:9879: spor ma brgyad kyis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:9880: nang gi yid shes gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9881: sring mo 'bar ma nyi zhags btul //
NK021(zha)001:9882: mi bzad sna tshogs nyi zer zhags //
NK021(zha)001:9883: shar gyi spor ma'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9884: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra phata rak+mo h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9885: a b+hi yi dwags ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9886: 'bar ma srin mo me khyer btul //
NK021(zha)001:9887: me khyer dmar nag glog phreng 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:9888: shar lho'i spor ma'i badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya
NK021(zha)001:9889: ni a b+hi mi yi ston pa gnas gyur pas
NK021(zha)001:9890: // srin mo 'bar ma gtum mo btul //
NK021(zha)001:9891: gtum mo sngo nag mdun thung 'phen //
NK021(zha)001:9892: lha yi spor ma'i dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:9893: badz+ra a pra ti a b+hi dmyal ba'i ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9894: srin mo 'bar ma ral gri btul //
NK021(zha)001:9895: gshin rje sngo nag ral gri'i skra //
NK021(zha)001:9896: lho nub spor ma'i dbang phyi yi yul chos gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9898: rdo rje dril bu 'khrol byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:9899: nub kyi spor ma'i badz+ra a pra a b+hi lha yi ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9900: 'bar ma srin mo gnod sbyin btul //
NK021(zha)001:9901: gnod sbyin mthing nag khyung thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:9902: nub byang spor ma'i badz+ra a pra ti a b+hi lha min ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9903: srin mo 'bar ma thogs med btul //
NK021(zha)001:9904: thogs med sngon nag skar mda' gtong //
NK021(zha)001:9905: byang gi spor ma'i badz+ra a pra ti a b+hi byol song ston pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9907: 'jig rten smug nag glag sha gdengs //
NK021(zha)001:9908: byang shar spor ma'i badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata rak+mo h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9911: a b+hi she ka ta s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:9912: e sha ri si ti na mah bi shi tse ni swa ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:9914: gsang yum bzhi nam tshong rtsib ma bzhir bstim zhing bskyed la /
NK021(zha)001:9915: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:9916: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis pa de'i //
NK021(zha)001:9917: snam bu'i phyi rim sgo bzhi ru //
NK021(zha)001:9918: gsang ba'i yum bzhis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:9919: dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs ma //
NK021(zha)001:9920: dpal chen sku la sbyor ba'i yum //
NK021(zha)001:9921: shar phyogs mdun nas 'khril ba yis //
NK021(zha)001:9922: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzungs mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:9923: gsang ba'i yum 'di'i dbang sh+r+ai badz+ra mang+ga ra mu
NK021(zha)001:9924: kha shwa ra y+aa ya na mah a b+hi ser
NK021(zha)001:9926: dpal chen sku la sbyong ba'i yum //
NK021(zha)001:9927: lho phyogs g.yas nas 'khril ba yis //
NK021(zha)001:9928: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzungs mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:9929: gsang ba'i yum 'di'i sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa
NK021(zha)001:9930: ra y+aa ya na mah a b+hi dmar mo za
NK021(zha)001:9932: dpal chen sku la sbyor ba'i yum //
NK021(zha)001:9933: nub phyogs rgyab nas 'khril ba yis //
NK021(zha)001:9934: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzungs mdzad ma /
NK021(zha)001:9935: gsang ba'i yum 'di'i badz+ra kha t+w+aam ka pra dz+wa
NK021(zha)001:9936: la y+aa ya na mah a b+hi nag mo ral
NK021(zha)001:9938: dpal chen sku la sbyor ba'i yum //
NK021(zha)001:9939: byang phyogs g.yon nas 'khril ba yis //
NK021(zha)001:9940: sangs rgyas kun gyi gzungs mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:9941: gsang ba'i yum 'di'i sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la
NK021(zha)001:9942: ya y+aa na mah a b+hi dbang mo nyer brgyad
NK021(zha)001:9943: mjing mjug rtsis pa'i sgal tshigs nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK021(zha)001:9945: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:9946: phyi rim gsum pa khrag khyams kyi //
NK021(zha)001:9947: sgo dang snam bu'i ngos bzhi la //
NK021(zha)001:9948: dbang phyug tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:9949: srin po'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9950: dbang phyug chen mo mi'i srin mo //
NK021(zha)001:9951: sku mdog smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK021(zha)001:9952: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9953: dmar ser tri sh+au zhing chen g.yang //
NK021(zha)001:9954: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK021(zha)001:9955: ma nu rak+sha'i dbang ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo a b+hi tshangs pa'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9956: dbang phyug chen mo tshangs ma ste //
NK021(zha)001:9957: sku mdog dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:9958: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9959: dmar skya rtse lnga b+han dmar sprul //
NK021(zha)001:9960: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK021(zha)001:9961: brah+ma n+ai'i dbang mchog bra h+ma ni b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:9962: a b+hi lha chen chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9963: dbang phyug chen mo 'khrug mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9964: sku mdog dkar mo tri sh+au la //
NK021(zha)001:9965: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9966: dmar ser zhing dbyug snying 'byin gzig /
NK021(zha)001:9967: rol pa'i rdzu 'phrul byin rlabs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:9968: badz+ra roo t+r+ai dbang roo t+r+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:9969: a b+hi khyab 'jug chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9971: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9972: ser mo pha wam 'khor lo ril //
NK021(zha)001:9973: dregs pa'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:9974: bish+na be yi bish+na bee b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:9975: a b+hi gzhon nu'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9976: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9977: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK021(zha)001:9978: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9979: dbang mo dmar skya bam dbyug dred //
NK021(zha)001:9980: yon tan mthu rtsal bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:9981: badz+ra ku m+aa'i dbang ku m+aa r+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:9982: a b+hi brgya byin chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9983: dbang phyug chen mo dbang mo che //
NK021(zha)001:9984: sku mdog dmar mo en+d+ra gdengs //
NK021(zha)001:9985: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9986: dkar dmar dung dmar sre mong mgo //
NK021(zha)001:9987: che ba'i yon tan bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:9989: a b+hii lha mo khyo med gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9990: dbang phyug chen mo dmar mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:9992: de nyid las ni gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:9993: dmar mo dung dmar rgyu zhags dom //
NK021(zha)001:9994: yid kyi 'dod pa bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:9995: ping+ga la yi dbang badz+ra ping+ga lam b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:9996: a b+hi nyi ma'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK021(zha)001:9997: dbang phyug chen mo bdud rtsi mo //
NK021(zha)001:9998: sku mdog dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:9999: de nyid las ni bdud rtsi sngon mo chu srin bum //
NK021(zha)001:10000: sman gyi mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:10001: badz+ra mri ta'i dbang a mri tam b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10002: a b+hi zla ba'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10003: dbang phyug chen po zhi ba mo //
NK021(zha)001:10004: sku mdog dkar mo pun+d+aa ri //
NK021(zha)001:10005: de nyid las ni sngo skya bam ril khog smad sding //
NK021(zha)001:10006: bdud rtsi byang chub sems kyi mthus //
NK021(zha)001:10007: badz+ra soo mya'i dbang soo mya b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10008: a b+hi be con chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10009: dbang phyug chen mo be con ma //
NK021(zha)001:10010: sku mdog sngon mo dbyug to 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10011: de nyid las ni be con nag mo thod rlon khra //
NK021(zha)001:10012: dug shul 'joms pa'i mthu stobs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:10013: badz+ra dan+d+aa'i dbang dan+d+aa dam b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10014: a b+hi srin mo khyo med gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10015: dbang phyug chen mo srin mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:10016: sku mdog dmar ser thod khrag 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:10017: de nyid las ni dmar nag zhing gi rgyu 'dren wa //
NK021(zha)001:10018: drag po'i mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:10019: badz+ra rak+sha'i dbang mchog rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10020: a b+hi nag chen chung ma dbang phyug chen mo za ba mo //
NK021(zha)001:10021: sku mdog dmar nag ba su 'dren //
NK021(zha)001:10022: de nyid las za byed nag mo snying 'byin stag /
NK021(zha)001:10023: mthu stobs gzhan gyis mi thub pa //
NK021(zha)001:10024: badz+ra b+hak+sha'i dbang b+hak+sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10025: a b+hi b+h+ring gi'i chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo dga' mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:10026: sku mdog dkar mo ka tar 'chang //
NK021(zha)001:10027: de nyid las ni dmar mo 'khor lo ral gri rgod //
NK021(zha)001:10028: mthu dang longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK021(zha)001:10029: badz+ra ra ti'i dbang ra ti badz+ra b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10030: a b+hi stobs bzang chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10031: dbang phyug chen mo khrag 'thung mos //
NK021(zha)001:10032: sku mdog dkar mo gshol 'chang ba //
NK021(zha)001:10033: de nyid las ni dmar nag rdor dbyug dung dmar rta //
NK021(zha)001:10034: mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:10035: ru d+hirmat+ta'i dbang ru d+hi ra mat+t+aa b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10036: a b+hi rnam thos chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10037: dbang phyug chen mo gcig pur spyod //
NK021(zha)001:10038: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //
NK021(zha)001:10039: de nyid las ni dkar dmar rdo rje b+hany+dza khyung //
NK021(zha)001:10040: 'byor ba'i longs spyod bsam mi khyab //
NK021(zha)001:10041: e ka tsa ri'i dbang e ka tsa ri n+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10042: a b+hi 'dod lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10043: dbang phyug chen mo yid 'phrog ma //
NK021(zha)001:10044: sku mdog dmar mo mda' gzhu thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10045: de nyid las ni dmar ser zhing za khyi gdong can //
NK021(zha)001:10046: 'dod pa'i yon tan kun rdzogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:10047: ma no ha ra'i dbang na mo ha ram b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10048: a b+hi nor srung chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo grub mor byung //
NK021(zha)001:10049: sku mdog dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10050: de nyid las ni dkar dmar pad+ma pu shud gdong //
NK021(zha)001:10051: lhag par nor gyi longs spyod che //
NK021(zha)001:10052: sid+d+hi kam gi dbang mchog byin //
NK021(zha)001:10054: a b+hi rlung lha'i chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo rlung mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:10055: sku mdog sngo nag ba dan 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10056: de nyid las ni dmar skya ro za sha ba'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:10057: mgyogs byed shugs 'chang dngos grub can //
NK021(zha)001:10058: w+aa ya w+ai yi dbang w+aa ya w+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10059: a b+hi skyong ma khyo med gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10060: dbang phyug chen mo khyo med ma //
NK021(zha)001:10061: sku mdog dmar nag ral gris gcod //
NK021(zha)001:10062: de nyid las ni ljang nag bam chen rnge'u chung spyang //
NK021(zha)001:10063: sgrol byed mthu stobs bsam yas pa //
NK021(zha)001:10064: m+aa ra na yi dbang ma h+aa m+aa ra na badz+ra b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10065: a b+hi me lha'i chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo me mor byung //
NK021(zha)001:10066: sku mdog dmar mo gsal shing 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10067: de nyid las ni ljang dmar mes sreg rgyu 'dren skyin //
NK021(zha)001:10068: rnam rtog bag chags kun sreg pa //
NK021(zha)001:10070: a b+hi sa bdag chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo phag mor byung //
NK021(zha)001:10071: sku mdog dmar nag mche zhags bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:10072: de nyid las ni ljang ser rtse gsum byis ro phag /
NK021(zha)001:10073: 'jig rten khams kyi dpal gcig ma //
NK021(zha)001:10074: w+aa ra h+ai yi dbang w+aa ra h+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10075: a b+hi gshin rje'i chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo rgan byed mo //
NK021(zha)001:10076: dmar smug byis ro'i rgyu ma za //
NK021(zha)001:10077: de nyid las ni ljang sngon rgyu 'dren khrag 'thor khra //
NK021(zha)001:10078: ma mo mthu dbang kun rdzogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:10079: tsa mun+d+ai yi dbang tsa mun+d+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10080: a b+hi bgegs kyi chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10081: dbang phyug chen mo sna chen mo //
NK021(zha)001:10082: sku mdog dmar nag thod khrag 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:10083: de nyid 'jigs pa'i skur sprul pa //
NK021(zha)001:10084: ljang dmar bam chen longs spyod glang //
NK021(zha)001:10085: bgegs chen kun 'dul mthu stobs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:10086: su ta na yi dbang mchog su ta nam b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10087: a b+hi chu lha'i chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10088: dbang phyug chen po chu lha mo //
NK021(zha)001:10089: sku mdog dkar mo sprul zhags 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10091: ljang nag dung dmar sprul zhags sprul //
NK021(zha)001:10092: rat+na gter gyi longs spyod ma //
NK021(zha)001:10093: wa ru na yi dbang mchog wa ru n+ai b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10094: a b+hi nag chen chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10095: dbang phyug nag mo chen mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:10096: sku mdog nag mo ang+ku sha /
NK021(zha)001:10098: nag mo lcags kyu khu byug gdong //
NK021(zha)001:10099: thams cad 'dzin byed mthu rdzogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:10100: ma h+aa k+aa la'i dbang mchog badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10101: a b+hi ra gdong chung ma gnas dbang phyug chen mo ra mgo ma //
NK021(zha)001:10102: sku mdog dmar ser zhags pa bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:10104: ra gdong sngon mo rgyu zhag 'dren //
NK021(zha)001:10105: 'khor bar mi gtong dbang mo che //
NK021(zha)001:10106: tsa k+aa la yi dbang mchog badz+ra tsa k+aa la b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10107: a b+hi bum rna'i chung ma gnas dbang phyug bum rna sngo nag ma //
NK021(zha)001:10108: sku mdog sngo nag lcags sgrog sdom //
NK021(zha)001:10110: bum rna dmar po lcags sgrog seng //
NK021(zha)001:10111: bgegs bdud srin sdom dbang mo che //
NK021(zha)001:10112: kum+b+ha kar+na'i dbang badz+ra ku m+b+ha kar+na b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10113: a b+hi gsus chen chung ma gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10114: dbang phyug gsus 'dzin chen mor gyur //
NK021(zha)001:10115: sku mdog ljang nag dril bu 'khrol //
NK021(zha)001:10117: ljang nag dril b+han skya kha'i gdong //
NK021(zha)001:10118: nga rgyal dregs pa gnas spor ma //
NK021(zha)001:10119: lam+bo da ra'i dbang badz+ra lam+bo da ra b+h+yo /
NK021(zha)001:10121: de yan gyis rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbang song nas /
NK021(zha)001:10122: da khro bo bka' nyan gyi dkyil 'khor rnams kyi lha dbang las /
NK021(zha)001:10123: mkha' 'gro so gnyis kyi sku so sum cu rtsa gnyis la bstim zhing der bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:10124: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:10125: phyi rim lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK021(zha)001:10126: phyogs bzhi khyams dang sgo bzhi du //
NK021(zha)001:10127: d+aa ki'i tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:10128: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10129: mkha' 'gro dga' byed rdo rje bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:10130: d+aa ki rdo rje'i rigs dbang phyug /
NK021(zha)001:10131: de yi dbang mchog khyod la byin //
NK021(zha)001:10132: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:10133: rdo rje rgyal po gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10134: 'dren byed dkar skya lcags kyu ma //
NK021(zha)001:10135: d+aa ki 'dren byed chen mo stas //
NK021(zha)001:10136: de yi dbang mchog khyod la byin //
NK021(zha)001:10137: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum a b+hi rdo rje chags pa gnas gyur pas //
NK021(zha)001:10138: gsod byed thabs kyi mda' 'geng dkar //
NK021(zha)001:10139: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK021(zha)001:10140: de yi dbang mchog badz+ra ma h+aa he ma ba
NK021(zha)001:10141: ti h+aum a b+hi rdo rje legs pa gnas gyur
NK021(zha)001:10142: pas // spor byed dkar skya spu gri thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10143: d+aa ki nyon mongs gcod mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:10144: de yi dbang mchog badz+ra ku m+aa ra pra ye
NK021(zha)001:10145: h+aum a b+hi rdo rje rin chen gnas gyur pas
NK021(zha)001:10147: d+aa ki dgos 'dod kun skong ma //
NK021(zha)001:10148: de yi dbang mchog ma h+aa badz+ra ma ti h+aum
NK021(zha)001:10149: a b+hi rdo rje nyi ma gnas mkha' 'gro gzi
NK021(zha)001:10151: rnam rtog mun sel mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK021(zha)001:10152: de yi dbang badz+ra tri sh+r+ai sma ra ya h+aum
NK021(zha)001:10153: a b+hi rdo rje rgyal mtshan gnas khro gnyer mthing
NK021(zha)001:10155: bdud bzhi 'dul byed dbang ldan ma //
NK021(zha)001:10156: de yi dbang mchog badz+ra tsag+ne na h+aum a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:10157: shiny+tsa rdo rje bzhad pa gnas 'joms byed dkar skya
NK021(zha)001:10158: zhing kha gdengs // dur khrod bgegs 'joms za byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10159: de yi dbang mchog ma h+aa badz+ra kro d+h+aa h+aum
NK021(zha)001:10160: a b+hi rdo rje chos rab gnas chags byed dmar
NK021(zha)001:10162: nyes pa'i skyon bral legs rdzogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10163: de yi dbang mchog ma h+aa a mri tot+pa ti
NK021(zha)001:10164: h+aum a b+hi rdo rje rnon po gnas chags bral
NK021(zha)001:10166: mkha' 'gro sgrol byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK021(zha)001:10167: de yi dbang mchog ma h+aa soo ma h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10168: b+hi rdo rje 'khor lo gnas 'khor lo dmar ser
NK021(zha)001:10169: 'khor lo 'phen // mkha' 'gro gcod byed mthu dbang rdzogs //
NK021(zha)001:10170: de yi dbang mchog ma h+aa badz+ra tsan+di h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10171: b+hi rdo rje smra ba gnas rgyas 'debs lce 'bebs
NK021(zha)001:10172: lcags kyu dmar // thogs med ljags kyis dbang bsgyur ma //
NK021(zha)001:10173: de yi dbang mchog ma h+aa ra ma ni h+aum
NK021(zha)001:10174: a b+hi rdo rje phrin las gnas sna tshogs lus
NK021(zha)001:10176: mkha' 'gro phrin las rdzogs byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10177: de yi dbang mchog ma h+aa smri ti ka pa
NK021(zha)001:10178: la hasti ta ki h+aum a b+hi rdo rje bsrung
NK021(zha)001:10179: ba gnas bsrung ba mo ljang go cha thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10180: 'jigs kun srung byed d+aa ki ma //
NK021(zha)001:10181: de yi dbang mchog badz+ra su ma h+aum a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:10182: rdo rje gnod sbyin gnas gnod sbyin mo ljang mche
NK021(zha)001:10183: ba 'dzin // dam nyams gsod pa'i d+aa ki ma //
NK021(zha)001:10184: de yi dbang mchog mri ta su ta dan+da ri
NK021(zha)001:10185: h+aum a b+hi rdo rje kun tshur gnas yang dag
NK021(zha)001:10187: rdul du rlog byed mkha' 'gro ma //
NK021(zha)001:10188: de yi dbang mchog badz+ra bi la ke h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10189: b+hi dpal bar 'gro ba gnas bya rog gdong la
NK021(zha)001:10190: mig 'byin ma // nag mo gri dang mkhar gzhong thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10191: rnam shes 'joms pa'i mkha' gro ma //
NK021(zha)001:10192: de yi dbang bi b+ha ri ram h+aum a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:10193: kun bzang sems dpa' gnas 'jigs byed dkar sngo mche
NK021(zha)001:10194: gtsigs ma // thams cad 'joms dbang mkha' 'gro ma //
NK021(zha)001:10195: de yi dbang sha ni k+sha h+aum a b+hi zla
NK021(zha)001:10196: 'od gzhon nu gnas bzhad gdong dkar mo snying 'byin
NK021(zha)001:10197: ma // thams cad sgrol ba'i d+aa ki ma //
NK021(zha)001:10198: de yi dbang sha ni ta ka h+aum a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:10199: byang sems bzang skyong gnas 'ug mgo dkar sngo keng
NK021(zha)001:10200: rus 'dzin // las byed lhag sdud d+aa ki ma //
NK021(zha)001:10201: de yi dbang pi ta ka h+aum a b+hi byang
NK021(zha)001:10202: sems d+r+wa 'od gnas khyi mgo mthing nag keng rus
NK021(zha)001:10203: 'cha' // dur khrod 'joms pa'i mthu ldan ma //
NK021(zha)001:10204: de yi dbang badz+ra a na ya h+aum a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:10205: rdo rje snying po gnas mthing nag phag mgo m+aam
NK021(zha)001:10206: sa za // gtsang rme med par rtog bral ma //
NK021(zha)001:10207: de yi dbang pe k+ae ni h+aum a b+hi nam
NK021(zha)001:10208: mkha' mdzod ni gnas sngo nag glo 'dren rnga mo'i
NK021(zha)001:10209: mgo // yi dwags 'dod 'joms d+aa ki ma //
NK021(zha)001:10210: de yi dbang mchog dza du la ya h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10211: b+hi 'od dpag med pa gnas thod dbyung dgra s+t+wa
NK021(zha)001:10212: bong bu'i mgo // dbang byed 'joms pa'i d+aa ki ma //
NK021(zha)001:10213: de yi dbang ta ki bi ka te h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10214: b+hi mya ngan kun 'joms gnas ra mgo dmar nag
NK021(zha)001:10215: spu gri 'dzin // dgra bgegs 'joms gcod mkha' 'gro ma //
NK021(zha)001:10216: de yi dbang badz+ra tar+shi ta h+aum a b+hi rgyal
NK021(zha)001:10217: ba ye shes gnas dmar nag rus 'cha' byi la'i
NK021(zha)001:10218: mgo // ma lus sgrol byed d+aa ki ma //
NK021(zha)001:10219: de yi dbang mchog k+aa li pra be sha h+aum
NK021(zha)001:10220: a b+hi blo gros mi zad gnas dmar ljang seng
NK021(zha)001:10223: de yi dbang mchog ustim+mas h+aum a b+hi spobs pa
NK021(zha)001:10224: brtsegs pa gnas dmar ser rus 'phreng lce spyang mgo
