NK021(zha)001:10226: de yi dbang mchog ka rany+dza h+aum a b+hi ngan
NK021(zha)001:10227: song kun 'dren gnas mkha' 'gro srin mo bum sna
NK021(zha)001:10228: ma // rdo rje lcags kyu ka ta re //
NK021(zha)001:10229: de yi dbang mchog sarba a ta ri h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10230: b+hi byams pa brtsegs pa gnas mkha' 'gro gshin rje
NK021(zha)001:10231: rnam 'joms ma // zhags pa gri thogs 'dzin cing sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:10232: de yi dbang mchog sa la ta gi h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10233: b+hi spos kyi glang po gnas mkha' 'gro da sha
NK021(zha)001:10234: g+r+ai wa stee // lcags sgrog spu gri za byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10235: de yi dbang mchog badz+ra sarba b+han+d+ha a h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:10236: b+hi sems dpa' don grub gnas gyur mkha' 'gro chen
NK021(zha)001:10238: dril bu dgra s+t+was spor zhing sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:10239: de yi dbang mchog khyod la byin //
NK021(zha)001:10240: badz+ra s+aa b+han a ki h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:10241: ma mo bdun mgo dang gzugs drug la bstim zhing bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:10242: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:10243: phyi rim snam bu'i phyogs bzhi ru //
NK021(zha)001:10244: ma mo bdun gyis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:10245: rgya mtsho chen mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK021(zha)001:10246: dpal ldan shugs sgrol gtso mo ste //
NK021(zha)001:10247: ri rab bsnyil ba'i mthu mo che //
NK021(zha)001:10248: rdo rje kun grags dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10249: ma ma d+h+aa tu kro d+h+ai shwa ri h'u a b+hi nam mkha' stong gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK021(zha)001:10250: thams cad kun tu khyab mdzad cing //
NK021(zha)001:10251: ma lus yongs la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK021(zha)001:10252: kun tu bzang mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10253: ma ma d+h+aa tu kro d+h+ai shwa ri h+aum a b+hi 'ja' tshon 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK021(zha)001:10255: ma rig mun pa sel mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:10256: rdo rje kun gsal dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10257: ma ma d+h+aa tu kro d+h+ai a b+hi dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK021(zha)001:10258: pho nya ma ste drug cu'i gtso //
NK021(zha)001:10259: sha chen khrag la longs spyod ma //
NK021(zha)001:10260: rdo rje ye shes dbang ma ma d+h+aa tu kro
NK021(zha)001:10261: d+h+ai a b+hi khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor nas
NK021(zha)001:10262: // rdo rje d+r+wa ba'i phreng thogs shing //
NK021(zha)001:10264: rdo rje 'od chags dbang ma ma d+h+aa tu a b+hi me dpung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK021(zha)001:10265: zhags pa stong gi gdengs ldan zhing //
NK021(zha)001:10267: rdo rje 'od 'phro'i dbang ma ma d+h+aa tu a b+hi dbang phyug chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK021(zha)001:10268: dam tshig nyams pa gsod byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:10270: rdo rje g.yu sgron dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10271: ma ma d+h+aa tu kro d+h+ai shwa ri h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:10272: sring mo bzhi rkang lag gi gseg ne bzhi la bstim zhing bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:10273: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:10274: phyi rim snam bu'i sgo bzhi ru //
NK021(zha)001:10275: sring mo bzhi yis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:10276: gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha yi sring //
NK021(zha)001:10277: sku la bya rgod thul pa gsol //
NK021(zha)001:10278: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK021(zha)001:10279: lha yi sring mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10280: badz+ra dun+tinga b+h+yo ab+hi mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring //
NK021(zha)001:10281: sku la stag gi thul pa gsol //
NK021(zha)001:10282: thugs dam rnal 'byor grogs la brtson //
NK021(zha)001:10283: gshin rje'i sring mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10284: badz+ra dun+tinga b+h+yo a b+hi dmar mo g.yag thod klu yi sring //
NK021(zha)001:10285: na bza' chu srin lpags pa gsol //
NK021(zha)001:10286: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10287: klu yi sring mo'i dbang badz+ra dun+tinga b+h+yo a b+hi nag mo sngar chen gnod sbyin sring //
NK021(zha)001:10288: sku la rma bya'i thul pa gsol //
NK021(zha)001:10289: dam tshig can la brtser dgongs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10290: gnod sbyin sring mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10291: badz+ra dun+tinga b+h+yo a b+hi king+ka ra bco brgyad gur rtsib bco brgyad la bstim zhing bskyed de /
NK021(zha)001:10292: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:10293: phyi rim snam bu'i phyogs bzhi ru //
NK021(zha)001:10294: dpal chen bzhad zhal sprul pa las //
NK021(zha)001:10295: khro bo king gis bskor ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:10296: dpal chen las rnams kun byed pa //
NK021(zha)001:10297: mthing nag ral gri b+hany+dza thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10298: gang la dmigs pa sgrol byed pa //
NK021(zha)001:10299: rdo rje king gi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10300: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum a b+hi khro mo khams gsum dbugs sdud ma //
NK021(zha)001:10301: sngo nag thod khrag ral gri thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10302: sgrol ba 'ba' zhig las la dgyes //
NK021(zha)001:10303: rdo rje king mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10304: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum a b+hi rdo rje ka tar king+ka ra //
NK021(zha)001:10306: ma thogs myur du sgrol bar byed //
NK021(zha)001:10307: rdo rje 'byung po'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10308: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum a b+hi rdo rje king chen gnod sbyin ni //
NK021(zha)001:10309: ljang nag phyag gnyis sdigs mdzub 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10310: dam tshig nyams rnams sgrol byed pa //
NK021(zha)001:10311: rdo rje king gi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10312: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum a b+hi rdo rje king chen spyang ki ni //
NK021(zha)001:10313: dmar nag spyang mgo spu gri thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10314: gsod pa'i las la shin tu dgyes //
NK021(zha)001:10315: rdo rje king gi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10316: badz+ra ka ta ri sha shwa ri h+aum a b+hi rdo rje king chen gshin rje ni //
NK021(zha)001:10317: mthing nag be con dgra s+t+wa 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10318: ma lus sgrol ba'i king chen te //
NK021(zha)001:10319: rdo rje king gi dbang badz+ra ka ta ri a b+hi rdo rje king chen rol pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:10320: dmar nag b+hany+dza dpal tshab bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:10321: dgra bgegs ma lus nyal thag gcod //
NK021(zha)001:10322: rdo rje king gi dbang badz+ra ka ta ri a b+hi rdo rje king chen 'chi bdag ni //
NK021(zha)001:10323: ljang ser rdo rje gsor zhing brdeg /
NK021(zha)001:10324: drag shul sgrol ba'i mthu stobs can //
NK021(zha)001:10325: rdo rje king gi dbang badz+ra ka ta ri a b+hi rdo rje king chen dus mtshams ni //
NK021(zha)001:10328: rdo rje king gi dbang badz+ra ka ta ri a b+hi rdo rje king chen ro langs ni //
NK021(zha)001:10329: ser nag zhing gi dbyug pa 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10330: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'joms //
NK021(zha)001:10331: rdo rje king gi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10332: badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rdo rje king chen 'joms pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:10333: smug nag rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10334: bgegs kyi dpung rnams yud kyis 'joms //
NK021(zha)001:10335: rdo rje king gi dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rdo rje king lcam dbang sdud ni //
NK021(zha)001:10336: ljang nag rdo rje lcags kyu 'dren //
NK021(zha)001:10337: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:10338: rdo rje king lcam dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rdo rje king lcam dbang bskur ma /
NK021(zha)001:10339: khams gsum zhing gi g.yab mos 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:10340: mthu dang rdzu 'phrul bsam mi khyab //
NK021(zha)001:10341: rdo rje king lcam dbang badz+ra ka ta ri sha
NK021(zha)001:10342: shwa ri h+aum a b+hi rdo rje king lcam 'phrul
NK021(zha)001:10343: mo che // gzugs med rlung ltar rgyu byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:10344: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'brub //
NK021(zha)001:10345: rdo rje king lcam dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rdo rje king lcam glog 'gyu ma //
NK021(zha)001:10347: cir yang bsgyur ba'i mthu mo che //
NK021(zha)001:10348: rdo rje king mo'i dbang badz+ra a b+hi rdo rje king lcam mthu mo che //
NK021(zha)001:10349: ljang nag lcags kyi tho ba thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10350: rbod gtong bcol ba len par byed //
NK021(zha)001:10351: rdo rje king mo'i dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:10352: badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rdo rje king lcam rtsal mo che //
NK021(zha)001:10353: mthing nag rdo rje dgra s+t+wa thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10354: phrin las rna nyan phra ma zer //
NK021(zha)001:10355: rdo rje'i king mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta ri a b+hi rdo rje king lcam sgrol byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10356: smug nag b+hany+tsa gri thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10357: phrin las srid gsum sgrol byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10358: rdo rje king mo'i dbang badz+ra a b+hi 'dir mgron
NK021(zha)001:10359: thabs su king lcam za myong gnyis kyi dbang yang
NK021(zha)001:10360: sbyor bar mdzad pas rtsib thung gnyis la bstim zhing
NK021(zha)001:10361: bskyed de / rdo rje king lcam za byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10362: mthing nag phyag na longs spyod bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:10363: phrin las tshogs kyi phyag tshang byed //
NK021(zha)001:10364: rdo rje king mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta a b+hi rdo rje king lcam myong byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10365: smug nag longs spyod gzhong pa thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10366: phrin las tshogs kyi phyag tshang mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:10367: rdo rje king mo'i dbang badz+ra ka ta ri sha
NK021(zha)001:10368: shwa ri h+aum a b+hi steng gi pho nya khro
NK021(zha)001:10369: bo yab yum ya drug cu rkang lag gi sor
NK021(zha)001:10370: tshigs mgo'i rus pa drug cu la zug pa'i rgyab
NK021(zha)001:10371: rtsa re dang bcas pa la bstim zhing bskyed de
NK021(zha)001:10373: sku yi 'od zer rnam drug las //
NK021(zha)001:10374: sum brgya drug cu'i gdon bsgral phyir //
NK021(zha)001:10375: pho nya sum brgya drug cur sprul //
NK021(zha)001:10376: de las steng gi pho nya ni //
NK021(zha)001:10377: phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gi //
NK021(zha)001:10378: dgra gdon ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:10379: sku yi 'od zer mthing nag las //
NK021(zha)001:10380: khro bo khro mo drug cu sprul //
NK021(zha)001:10381: rnam rgyal rdo rje tho ba dkar //
NK021(zha)001:10382: rdo rje snyems ma thod khrag thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10383: dri za'i gdon 'dul mthu rtsal can //
NK021(zha)001:10384: khro bo khro mo'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:10385: kro d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:10386: dbyug sngon sdigs mdzub rin chen sngo //
NK021(zha)001:10387: rdo rje sder mo dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10388: mthu ldan drang srong gdon 'dul ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:10389: khro bo khro mo'i dbang kro d+ha kro d+h+ai a b+hi gshin rje gshed mthing dbyug tho zhags //
NK021(zha)001:10390: rdo rje dur khrod dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10391: nga rgyal mthu chen gshin rje 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10392: khro bo khro mo'i kro d+ha kro d+h+ai a b+hi mi g.yo ral gri khu tshur smug /
NK021(zha)001:10393: rdo rje gtun khung dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10395: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi rta mgrin mda' gzhu pad+ma dmar //
NK021(zha)001:10396: rdo rje gtum mo dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10397: gti mug klu 'dul thugs rje'i rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:10398: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi gzhan gyis mi thub dgra s+t+wa gtun //
NK021(zha)001:10399: rdo rje mda' snyems dung dmar sngo //
NK021(zha)001:10401: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi bdud rtsi 'khyil ljang rgya gram 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10402: rdo rje rlung 'byin dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10403: drag po'i mthu yis gnod sbyin 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10404: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi sum rgyal rdo rje tho ba nag /
NK021(zha)001:10405: rdo rje gsod byed dung dmar stob //
NK021(zha)001:10407: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi stobs chen dud kha rnga yab dung //
NK021(zha)001:10408: rdo rje bskyed byed dung dmar stob //
NK021(zha)001:10409: mthu stobs ldan pas sa gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10410: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi h+aum mdzad dmar skya mda' gzhu 'gengs //
NK021(zha)001:10411: rdo rje sgra 'byin dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10412: nyi zla gza' skar gnam gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10413: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi rdo rje phur mthing phur bu 'dril //
NK021(zha)001:10414: khro mo rgyas 'debs dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10415: mthu dbang dgra dang lha gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10416: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi rme brtsegs mthing nag rdo rje thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10419: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi yak+sha phur bu sdigs mdzub ljang //
NK021(zha)001:10420: yak+mo dung chen snying khrag bcas //
NK021(zha)001:10421: dam tshig nyams dang dam sri 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10422: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi khro bo dmar nag rdo rje thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10424: mthu rtsal chen pos ma gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10425: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi khro bo sa 'og thod sprul ljang //
NK021(zha)001:10426: sa 'og mo ni rdo rje thod //
NK021(zha)001:10428: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi khro bo rab 'khrug ral gri sngo //
NK021(zha)001:10429: khro mo rab 'jigs thod khrag thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10430: mthu rtsal gdon chen bco brgyad 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10431: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi ma h+aa k+aa la dmar nag zhags //
NK021(zha)001:10432: khro mo ral sgreng thod khrag 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10433: mthu chen ya bdud 'dul bar mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:10434: khro bo kro d+ha mi 'chi thabs sbyor thal rdeb sngo //
NK021(zha)001:10435: khro mo 'joms chen dung dmar can //
NK021(zha)001:10436: mthu chen sri can rdul du rlog /
NK021(zha)001:10437: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi gu lang smug nag gtun shing brdeg /
NK021(zha)001:10438: khro mo las kun b+han dmar bkang //
NK021(zha)001:10439: mthu rtsal khams gsum gsad gso mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:10440: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi rab rngams ljang nag rdo rje dung //
NK021(zha)001:10441: gtum chen thod khrag tsit+ta bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:10442: mthu chen brjed byed gdon rnams 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10443: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi gsum snang be con sdigs mdzub mthing //
NK021(zha)001:10444: mi pham sngo nag dung chen thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10445: mthu rtsal che bas shar gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10446: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi gsum 'dul dmar nag tho ba 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10447: khro mo lcags kyu ma lcags kyu //
NK021(zha)001:10448: shar sgo bsrung zhing shar gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10449: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi rngams chen smug nag be con sdigs //
NK021(zha)001:10450: khro mo dbang sdud thod khrag 'chang //
NK021(zha)001:10451: rtsal chen bdud dang srin po 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10452: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi gsum 'jigs dmar nag tho ba 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10453: khro gnyer can ma thod khrag thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10454: mthu rtsal che bas lho gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10455: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi gsum 'ching sngo nag dbyug tho 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10456: khro mo zhags pa dung dmar zhags //
NK021(zha)001:10457: lho sgo bsrung zhing lho gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10458: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi pad rgyal dmar nag ral gri 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10459: ro langs can ma thod khrag 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10460: mthu rtsal che bas nub gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10461: khro bo kro d+ha a b+hi be con rat+na'i be con sngo //
NK021(zha)001:10462: khro mo lcags sgrog de bzhin du //
NK021(zha)001:10463: nub sgo bsrung zhing nub gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10464: khro bo khro mo'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:10465: kro d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:10466: rdo rje tho ba dud kha tho //
NK021(zha)001:10467: khro mo za byed dung dmar thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10468: mthu rtsal ma mo gshin rje 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10469: khro bo khro mo'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:10470: kro d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK021(zha)001:10471: ka ti dmar nag gri sdigs mdzub //
NK021(zha)001:10472: khro mo ral gcig dung khrag thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10473: mthu rtsal chen pos byang gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10474: khro bo khro mo dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:10475: kro d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum a b+hi rdo rje go cha mthing nag go //
NK021(zha)001:10476: khro mo dril 'khrol thod khrag dril //
NK021(zha)001:10477: byang sgo bsrung zhing byang gdon 'dul //
NK021(zha)001:10478: khro bo khro mo'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:10479: kroo d+ha kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:10480: sku'i pho nya mo drug cu lag g.yas kyi sor
NK021(zha)001:10481: tshigs bco lnga'i g.yas g.yon gyi rtsa gnyis gnyis te
NK021(zha)001:10484: dri za'i dgra gdon 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:10485: shar phyogs 'od zer dkar po las //
NK021(zha)001:10486: dung gi mi mo drug cu sprul //
NK021(zha)001:10487: rdo rje 'bar ba'i pho nya mo //
NK021(zha)001:10488: dkar mo mthong byed lcags kyu ma //
NK021(zha)001:10489: yid kyis phyin cing bsam pas 'grub //
NK021(zha)001:10490: dbang 'di bu la bskur bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:10491: b+ha na b+ha na ang+ku sha dzah a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:10492: rdo rje sder mo pho nya mo //
NK021(zha)001:10494: gar yang thogs med glog 'gyu ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:10495: dbang 'di bu la bskur b+ha na b+ha na a b+hi pho nya rdo rje k+ai la ya //
NK021(zha)001:10496: dkar mo thog med dmigs gsal ma //
NK021(zha)001:10498: dbang 'di bu la b+ha na pho nya rdo rje 'bigs pa mo //
NK021(zha)001:10499: dkar mo shel gyi mda' 'phen ma //
NK021(zha)001:10500: gang la dmigs pa grub byed ma /
NK021(zha)001:10501: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya ro langs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10502: dkar mo lag na gri thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10503: mgyogs byed dur khrod khyab 'gro ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10504: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje drag mo pho nya mo //
NK021(zha)001:10505: dkar mo lag na mdung thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10506: gang la mngags pa grub byed ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10507: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya mgyogs pa mo //
NK021(zha)001:10508: dkar mo mi srin g.yab mos 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:10509: ting 'dzin yid kyi pho nya ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10510: dbang 'di b+ha na pho nya rdo rje gtum mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:10512: sgrol byed pho nya tsit+ta yi //
NK021(zha)001:10513: dbang 'di b+ha na pho nya rdo rje 'bebs ma ni //
NK021(zha)001:10514: dkar mo gar byed glu len mkhan //
NK021(zha)001:10515: las la 'drid pa'i pho nya ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10516: dbang 'di b+ha na pho nya rdo rje gsal ma ni //
NK021(zha)001:10517: dkar mo dung phreng klad la bskor //
NK021(zha)001:10518: sa ma ya yi khus 'debs ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10519: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya bstod ma ni //
NK021(zha)001:10520: dkar skya dar dkar g.yab 'dor ma //
NK021(zha)001:10521: rgyal bas yon tan cher bstod pas //
NK021(zha)001:10522: rdo rje pho nya chen mo yi //
NK021(zha)001:10523: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya 'gugs byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10524: dkar mo bdud kyi rnying 'byin ma //
NK021(zha)001:10525: grub par mi 'gyur gang yang med //
NK021(zha)001:10526: rdo rje pho nya skur bcas kyi //
NK021(zha)001:10527: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya thogs pa med //
NK021(zha)001:10528: dkar dmar lag na zangs gri 'chang //
NK021(zha)001:10529: dpa' bo chen mo thogs med ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10530: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya bskyod ma ni //
NK021(zha)001:10531: dkar dmar rlung gi zhags pa thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10532: rnal 'byor phrin las bskyod byed ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10533: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya 'chang bdag mo //
NK021(zha)001:10534: dkar dmar 'dzin byed zhag thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10536: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya phra men ma //
NK021(zha)001:10537: dkar dmar me yi sgron khyer ma //
NK021(zha)001:10538: don dang rtags su bcas nas 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10539: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya myur byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10540: dkar dmar glog gi zhags thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10541: gang bzung yud kyis 'debs par byed //
NK021(zha)001:10542: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10544: thugs dam bskul zhing phrin las mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:10545: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya gsal bkra mo //
NK021(zha)001:10546: dkar dmar rdo rje'i zhags 'phen ma //
NK021(zha)001:10547: sus kyang mi bzlog thub par dka' //
NK021(zha)001:10548: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya yang dag mo //
NK021(zha)001:10549: dkar dmar dung gi lan phran 'debs /
NK021(zha)001:10550: khams gsum sa dgu yid kyis khyab //
NK021(zha)001:10551: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya che ba mo //
NK021(zha)001:10552: dkar ser rdo rje rtse gcig 'phen //
NK021(zha)001:10553: thugs dam dbang gis rtags ston ma //
NK021(zha)001:10554: rdo rje thugs kyi pho nya mo'i //
NK021(zha)001:10555: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya gnon mdzad mo //
NK021(zha)001:10556: dkar ser rdo rje'i brag 'phen mo //
NK021(zha)001:10557: ri rab rtse yang gnon byed ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10558: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya dbang phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:10559: dkar ser tri shul gze mo 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10560: dug gsum nad rnams 'joms mdzad ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10561: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya sre mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:10562: dkar ser lcags kyu dmar po thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10563: brdabs pa tsam gyis gang yang khug /
NK021(zha)001:10564: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya kha 'bar ma //
NK021(zha)001:10565: dmar ser sprin gyi go zu can /
NK021(zha)001:10566: kha nas me 'bar rgya mtsho skyems //
NK021(zha)001:10567: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya gsal byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10569: gang la bya ba sa ler gsal //
NK021(zha)001:10570: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya khro mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:10571: dkar ser khro mo'i gzugs 'chang ma //
NK021(zha)001:10572: de bzhin lag na g.yang gzhi rdeb //
NK021(zha)001:10573: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya 'chang ma ni //
NK021(zha)001:10574: dkar ser rdo rje phur bu 'chang //
NK021(zha)001:10575: gang la bya ba'i snying la 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:10576: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya gtum mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:10577: dkar ser rdo rje tho ba thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10578: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis 'joms //
NK021(zha)001:10579: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya khros ma ni //
NK021(zha)001:10580: dmar ser rdo rje be con 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10581: khros bzhin gdong la dpa' brtul che //
NK021(zha)001:10582: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya las byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10583: dmar ser gcod pa'i ral gri 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10584: sems can skye shi rtsad gcod ma //
NK021(zha)001:10585: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya dus mtshan ma //
NK021(zha)001:10586: dmar ser lag na shak+ti thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10587: ma lus 'joms pa'i las mdzad ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10588: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya thar pa mo //
NK021(zha)001:10589: dmar ser lag na gtun shing 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:10590: rdul du rlog pa'i las mdzad ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10591: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya kun ma la //
NK021(zha)001:10592: dmar ser lag na lcags kyu 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:10593: ma lus 'dzin pa'i king chen ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10594: dbang b+ha na rdo rje pho nya dpal 'bar ma //
NK021(zha)001:10595: dmar ser ras kyi zhags pa 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:10596: dpal chen sku la sbyor mdzad ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10597: dbang b+ha na rdo rje pho nya bskyod chen ma //
NK021(zha)001:10598: dmar ser rlung gi rkyal pa thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10599: bskal pa'i me chen gtor ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:10600: dbang b+ha na rdo rje pho nya lus 'phrog ma //
NK021(zha)001:10601: dkar ser lcags kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro //
NK021(zha)001:10602: ba spu sra mkhregs rdo rje'i spu //
NK021(zha)001:10603: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya ngag 'phrog ma //
NK021(zha)001:10604: dmar ser lkugs byed lcags kyu can //
NK021(zha)001:10605: smra ba ngag gi lce 'phrog ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10606: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya yid gtum ma //
NK021(zha)001:10607: dkar ser sen mos snying 'byin ma //
NK021(zha)001:10608: thugs rjes bdud srin myos shing rlam //
NK021(zha)001:10609: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya bde chen mo //
NK021(zha)001:10610: dmar ser ral pa'i g.yab mos 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:10611: thugs rjes bsgral ba'i zhing bcu sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:10612: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya gsod byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10613: dkar sngo dung gi zhags pa can //
NK021(zha)001:10614: thugs rjes zhing bcu sgrol la brtson //
NK021(zha)001:10615: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya rlangs pa mo //
NK021(zha)001:10616: dkar sngo dung gi rlangs pa bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:10617: thugs rjes bdud dang srin po sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:10618: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya gsod pa mo //
NK021(zha)001:10619: dkar sngo shel gyi gri thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10620: gsod pa 'ba' zhig las la dgyes //
NK021(zha)001:10621: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya za ba mo //
NK021(zha)001:10622: dkar sngo m+aam sa zas su za //
NK021(zha)001:10623: gti mug gtan nas zad mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:10624: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya khrag 'thung ma //
NK021(zha)001:10626: 'dod chags gtan nas zad mdzad pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:10627: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya 'cha' ba mo //
NK021(zha)001:10628: dkar sngo keng rus khral khrol 'cha' //
NK021(zha)001:10629: zhe sdang gtan nas zad mdzad ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10630: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya tshe len ma //
NK021(zha)001:10631: dkar sngo dar gyi g.yab 'dor bas //
NK021(zha)001:10632: sdang ba dgra yi tshe 'phrog ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10633: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya mdangs len ma //
NK021(zha)001:10634: dkar sngo dung gi par bu thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10635: gang la dmigs pa'i mdangs 'phrog ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10636: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya srog 'phrog ma //
NK021(zha)001:10638: skad cig yud la nyams pa len //
NK021(zha)001:10639: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya snying 'byin ma //
NK021(zha)001:10640: dkar sngo snying gi phreng ba 'dren //
NK021(zha)001:10641: rnam shes phung po gtan stob pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:10642: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya gcod byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10643: dkar ljang shel gyi dgra s+t+wa 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:10644: rgyud drug 'khor ba rtsad gcod ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10645: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya bskul byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10646: dkar mo phyag na lcags kyu can //
NK021(zha)001:10647: zhing bcu bsgral nas thugs dam bskul //
NK021(zha)001:10648: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya sna tshogs gzugs //
NK021(zha)001:10649: bse yi ldan dkar zab slog gsol //
NK021(zha)001:10650: ma lus sgrol byed bya ra ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10651: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya smyon ma ni //
NK021(zha)001:10652: dkar ljang shel gyi rdo rje 'phen //
NK021(zha)001:10653: gzhan gyis mi thub drag shul che //
NK021(zha)001:10654: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya 'jug byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10655: dkar ljang phyag na khra thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:10657: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya yid 'phrog ma //
NK021(zha)001:10658: dkar ljang tshon gyi gru gu thogs //
NK021(zha)001:10660: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya ro rkun ma //
NK021(zha)001:10661: dkar ljang zhing gi ro khur ma //
NK021(zha)001:10662: dur khrod bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:10663: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya rdzu byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10664: dkar ljang rlung gi zhags pas 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:10665: cir yang sprul pa'i sku gcig ma //
NK021(zha)001:10666: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya 'jigs byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:10667: dkar ljang dung gi mche ba 'byin //
NK021(zha)001:10669: dbang 'di b+ha na rdo rje pho nya bcud len ma //
NK021(zha)001:10670: dkar ljang g.yu yi za ma tog /
NK021(zha)001:10671: khams gsum tshe sdud pho nya mo'i //

NK021(zha)001:11257: sbas mo thal mdog thod khrag 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:11258: g.yang gzhi dur khrod rgyan mdzes klubs //
NK021(zha)001:11259: srid gsum mthu che rtsal drag pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:11260: ma mo 'di yi dbang ma me shwa ra dur khrod tshogs kyi ral can ma //
NK021(zha)001:11261: mi thod phreng bas sku rgyan brjid /
NK021(zha)001:11262: khams gsum 'di na mthu chen can //
NK021(zha)001:11263: ma mo 'di yi ma me shwa za byed rngams pa'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11264: mthing skya khrag ral gos su gyon //
NK021(zha)001:11266: ma mo 'di yi ma me shwa ra khams gsum sdud pa'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11267: dmar mo thod khrag skom du 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:11269: ma mo ma me rgyud drug sgrol ba'i ma mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11270: smug nag me 'bar rgya mtsho gyon //
NK021(zha)001:11271: mi snying phreng ba klad la bskor /
NK021(zha)001:11272: ma mo 'di ma me srid gsum za byed ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11273: dmar nag gnam sa gos su gyon //
NK021(zha)001:11275: ma mo 'di ma me srid gsum yongs la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK021(zha)001:11276: ser nag nyi zla thod du bcings //
NK021(zha)001:11277: gnam sa gnyis la dbang byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11278: ma mo 'di ma me mthu rtsal snyems pa'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11279: ljang nag zhing gi go zu gyon //
NK021(zha)001:11280: lag pa g.yas pas nam mkha' 'degs //
NK021(zha)001:11282: khros chen sha khrag gsur la dga' //
NK021(zha)001:11283: mi sha rta sha zas su za //
NK021(zha)001:11284: mi khrag rta khrag skom du 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:11285: ma mo ma me sgrol byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11286: mthing nag nang rol glo snying 'byin //
NK021(zha)001:11287: phrin las dam nyams sgrol la brtson //
NK021(zha)001:11288: ma mo ma me za byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11289: sngo nag g.yu yi za ma tog /
NK021(zha)001:11290: nyams pa len cing sgrub la stob //
NK021(zha)001:11291: ma mo 'di yi ma me rngams byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11292: dmar nag 'brug sngon chibs su chibs //
NK021(zha)001:11293: dgra dang nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK021(zha)001:11294: ma mo ma me 'dzin byed ma mo chen mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11295: ser nag thod khrag lcags kyu thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11296: ma lus sgrol ba'i king chen mo //
NK021(zha)001:11297: ma mo ma me bgegs chen 'joms pa'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11298: sngo nag spu gri tho ba thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11299: bgegs kyi rgyal po'i snying la 'debs //
NK021(zha)001:11300: ma mo ma me zhing bcu sgrol ba'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11301: ljang nag b+hany+dza gri thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:11302: 'jig rten khams kyi dbang mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11303: ma mo ma me chad pas gcod pa'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11304: sngo nag zhing gi g.yang gzhi rdeb //
NK021(zha)001:11305: dam tshig nyams pa'i snying 'byin ma //
NK021(zha)001:11306: ma mo ma me 'byung po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11308: shar gyi phyogs kyi las byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11309: ma mo ma me gshin rje sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11310: b+hany+dza gri thogs gshin rje sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:11311: lho yi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11312: ma mo ma me nub phyogs klu sgrol chen mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11313: b+hany+dza gri thogs klu chen sgrol //
NK021(zha)001:11314: nub kyi phyogs kyi las byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11315: ma mo ma me gnod sbyin sgrol byed chen mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11316: ljang nag b+hany+dza gri thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:11317: byang gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11318: ma mo ma me srin po sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11319: sngo nag b+hany+dza gri thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:11320: steng gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11321: ma mo ma me srin mo sgrol byed ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11322: smug nag b+hany+dza gri thogs ma //
NK021(zha)001:11323: 'og gi phyogs nas las byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11324: ma mo ma me gzugs la mnga' mdzad dbang mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11325: dkar mo zhing gi dbyug pa bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:11326: dgra bo'i gzugs rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11327: ma mo ma me khrag la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11328: sngon mo thod khrag 'khrug cing gsol //
NK021(zha)001:11329: dgra bo'i khrag rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11330: ma mo ma me drod la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11331: dmar mo lag na tsit+ta thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11332: sdang ba dgra yi drod 'phrog ma //
NK021(zha)001:11333: ma mo ma me dbugs la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11334: ljang nag thod khrag zhags pa thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11335: dgra yi dbugs rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11336: ma mo ma me bkrag la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11337: ser nag ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:11338: dgra yi mdangs rnams 'jib byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11339: ma mo ma me srog la dbang ba'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11340: smug nag gri dang thod khrag 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:11341: dgra yi srog rnams 'phrog byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11342: ma mo ma me ma mo khrag 'thung bya rgod mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11343: ser ljang ral gri thod khrag 'thung //
NK021(zha)001:11344: 'jig rten khyab pa'i mthu mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11345: ma mo ma me ma mo za byed stag gi mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11346: dmar ser thod khrag zhal du gso //
NK021(zha)001:11348: ma mo ma me ma mo 'jigs byed chu srin mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11349: sha khrag gsur la dga' byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11351: ma mo ma me ma mo chen mo dur khrod rgyan //
NK021(zha)001:11352: mi lpags rlon pa na bzar gsol //
NK021(zha)001:11353: dur khrod bgegs chen 'dul mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:11354: ma mo ma me rdo rje gar dbang chen mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11355: dbu brgya spyan stong kun la khyab //
NK021(zha)001:11356: ma lus sgrol ba'i king chen ma //
NK021(zha)001:11357: ma mo 'di ma me pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:11358: lag na mi mgo'i phor pa ru //
NK021(zha)001:11359: mi snying tshil bus bkang zhing gsol //
NK021(zha)001:11360: ma mo ma me sa bdag chen mo pad+ma phreng //
NK021(zha)001:11361: dmar nag b+hany+dza khrag gis bkang //
NK021(zha)001:11362: mig rtsa dmar zhing rngam pa che //
NK021(zha)001:11363: ma mo ma me srid pa gsum gyi mnga' bdag mo //
NK021(zha)001:11364: ri rab rtse nas bsnyil byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:11365: rgya mtsho gting nas rnyog byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11366: ma mo ma me rgya mtsho'i gting gi dbang mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11367: na bza' chu srin lpags pa gsol //
NK021(zha)001:11368: sbrul nag stong gi gdengs ka can //
NK021(zha)001:11369: ma mo ma me ma mo rdo rje tho ba ma //
NK021(zha)001:11370: sngo nag mi bsrun tho ba thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11371: srin po'i tshogs kyang 'dar zhing g.yo //
NK021(zha)001:11372: ma mo ma me ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma //
NK021(zha)001:11373: mthing nag dgra bo gtun du brdung //
NK021(zha)001:11374: gang la bya ba rdul du rlog /
NK021(zha)001:11375: ma mo ma me ma mo rdo rje dur khrod bdag /
NK021(zha)001:11376: sngo nag mi mgo rdo rje dbyug /
NK021(zha)001:11377: gdug pa tshogs rnams 'joms par byed //
NK021(zha)001:11378: ma mo 'di ma me ma mo rdo rje gdengs pa mo //
NK021(zha)001:11379: sngo nag rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:11380: gdug cing gtum la drag shul che //
NK021(zha)001:11381: ma mo ma me ma mo rdo rje gsal bkra ma //
NK021(zha)001:11382: dmar nag me yi rgyu zhags 'phen //
NK021(zha)001:11384: ma mo ma me ma mo rdo rje khrag 'thung ma //
NK021(zha)001:11387: ma mo ma me ma mo nag mo drel zhon ma //
NK021(zha)001:11388: nad kyi rkyal pa gong du btags //
NK021(zha)001:11389: tshon gyi gru gu klad la bskor //
NK021(zha)001:11390: ma mo ma me dus bzhi'i rgyal mo mthu mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11391: srid pa gsum la dbang byed cing //
NK021(zha)001:11392: cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' ba //
NK021(zha)001:11393: ma mo 'di yi ma me ma mo gnas nyul spyang ki'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11394: mi sha za zhing bdud khyim 'joms //
NK021(zha)001:11395: bltas pas bdud rnams rlog byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11396: ma mo ma me ma mo rdzu byed stag dang dom //
NK021(zha)001:11397: gcan gzan gdug pa'i gzugs su sprul //
NK021(zha)001:11398: ma lus 'joms pa'i mthu mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11399: ma mo ma me ma mo 'jums byed pho nya mo //
NK021(zha)001:11400: khra ltar 'jums shing khyi ltar zug /
NK021(zha)001:11401: gang la dmigs pa yud kyis len //
NK021(zha)001:11402: ma mo ma me ma mo gnam sa phyed kyi bdag /
NK021(zha)001:11403: ri klungs med pa gzugs kyis khebs //
NK021(zha)001:11404: che chung med pa 'joms par byed //
NK021(zha)001:11405: ma mo ma me ma mo pho nya rgyug byed mo //
NK021(zha)001:11406: bud med lus la 'ja' tshon gos //
NK021(zha)001:11407: bang ni ri klungs med par rgyug /
NK021(zha)001:11408: ma mo ma me ma mo pho nya za byed ma //
NK021(zha)001:11409: bud med lus la stag gi mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11410: zas su gtsang rme med par za //
NK021(zha)001:11411: ma mo 'di yi ma me rdo rje ya byin pho nya mo //
NK021(zha)001:11412: dkar khra lcags kyu phur bu 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11413: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK021(zha)001:11414: ma mo ma me rdo rje bse byin rtsal mo che //
NK021(zha)001:11415: sngo nag zhags pa phur bu thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11416: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK021(zha)001:11417: ma mo 'di ma me rdo rje phag byin thogs pa med //
NK021(zha)001:11418: dmar nag lcags sgrog phur bu thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11419: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK021(zha)001:11420: ma mo ma me rdo rje de byin dbang grub ma //
NK021(zha)001:11422: gang la bya ba grub par byed //
NK021(zha)001:11423: ma mo ma me sa bdag rgyal mo chen mo 'di //
NK021(zha)001:11424: ser nag gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK021(zha)001:11425: tshe srog kun la dbang bsgyur ma //
NK021(zha)001:11426: ma mo ma me phyi 'khor skyong ba'i mnga' bdag mo //
NK021(zha)001:11427: rgyan dang cha lugs mdzes pa'i tshul //
NK021(zha)001:11428: gnas ni g.ya' ri gangs la gnas //
NK021(zha)001:11429: ma mo ma me 'brog sring rnams kyi rje mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11430: bud med bzang sdug 'od chags ma //
NK021(zha)001:11431: skra bshig ral pa gyen du bardzesa //
NK021(zha)001:11432: ma mo ma me khro tshig myur ba'i ma mo ni //
NK021(zha)001:11433: bud med khrag gi lan phran can //
NK021(zha)001:11434: nag mo lag na thod pa thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11435: ma mo 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:11436: ma me shwa ra h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11437: srung 'khor gyi dbus dang phyogs bcu nas khrag 'thung
NK021(zha)001:11438: sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor phur pa'i lha zhe gnyis yang
NK021(zha)001:11439: sprul bye ba phrag sa ya dang bcas pa chad
NK021(zha)001:11440: de ba spu'i bu ga rnams su thim pas khro
NK021(zha)001:11441: bo'i rdul phra rab kyis go mtshams med par gtams
NK021(zha)001:11442: par bsam zhing / rdo rje gzhon nu mthing nag phur bu 'dril //
NK021(zha)001:11443: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs gtso 'khyud dung dmar stob //
NK021(zha)001:11444: phrin las gdug can dregs pa 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:11445: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la bskur bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:11446: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aam bam h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:11447: d+aip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:11449: h+aum chen mthing skya 'khor lo thod dbyug thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11450: sgra 'byin gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stob //
NK021(zha)001:11451: sprul pa'i phra men phag dang rmig bu'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11452: phrin las nyi zla'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:11453: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la skur bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:11454: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11456: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai d+ai pa ya ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11457: badz+ra u ya ka mu kha u i shi mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11458: a b+hi rnam rgyal dkar po rtse lnga zhing dbyug 'phyar //
NK021(zha)001:11459: snyems ma gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stob //
NK021(zha)001:11460: sprul pa'i phra men stag dang bya rgod mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11461: phrin las dri za'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i skal ldan
NK021(zha)001:11462: rigs kyi bu la badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya
NK021(zha)001:11463: h+aum ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:11464: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai l+aa s+ya ki h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11465: badz+ra b+h+aa g+h+ri mu kha gri d+ha mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11466: a b+hi dbyug sngon sngo skya me dbal drang srong 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11467: sder mo gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stob //
NK021(zha)001:11468: sprul pa'i phra men g.yag dang bya rog mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11469: phrin las drang srong gdon tshogs skal ldan rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:11470: bu badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum da ha
NK021(zha)001:11472: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai t+aa t+aa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11473: badz+ra tsa ma ra mu kha k+aa ka mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11474: a b+hi gshed po ser nag be con gshin rje 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11475: dur khrod gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stob //
NK021(zha)001:11476: sprul pa'i phra men sha ba 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11477: phrin las gshin rje'i gdon tshogs skal ldan rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:11478: bu la badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum pa
NK021(zha)001:11480: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sma sha pa ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11481: badz+ra ha ri na mu kha u l+au ka mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11482: a b+hi mi g.yo ljang sngon ral gri srin po 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11483: gtun khung gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab sprul pa'i phra men gzig dang khwa ta'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11484: phrin las srin po'i gdon tshogs skal ldan rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:11485: bu badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum ban+d+ha
NK021(zha)001:11486: ban+d+ha h+aum phata / kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai mu ha la h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11487: badz+ra a t+ya mu kha pre ti mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11488: a b+hi rta mgrin dmar nag zhing dbyug khyung gshog 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11489: gtum mo gtso 'khyud dung khrag sprul pa'i phra men byi la pu shud mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11490: phrin las klu yi gdon tshogs skal ldan rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:11491: bu badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum hu
NK021(zha)001:11493: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai dza ya ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11494: badz+ra bi r+aa la mu kha pak+sha ti mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11495: a b+hi 'dod rgyal dmar ljang ba dan rlung lha 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11496: mda' snyems gtso 'khyud dung khrag sprul pa'i phra men spyang ki khra yi mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11497: phrin las rlung lha'i gdon tshogs skal ldan rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:11498: bu badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h+aum
NK021(zha)001:11500: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sa bya ti h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11501: badz+ra sri ga la mu kha sany+tsa ra na mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11502: a b+hi bdud rtsi ljang nag dbyug to gnod sbyin 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11503: rlung 'byin gtso 'khyud dung khrag sprul pa'i phra men seng ge pha wang mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11504: phrin las gnod sbyin gdon tshogs skal ldan rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:11505: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum tshin+d+ha
NK021(zha)001:11506: tshin+d+ha h+aum phata / kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai sa bya mi ta h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11507: badz+ra sim ha mu kha ti ti la mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11508: a b+hi sum rgyal dkar po rdo rje 'byung po 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11509: gsod ma gtso 'khyud dung khrag sprul pa'i phra men dom dang sre mo'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11510: phrin las 'byung po'i gdon tshogs skal ldan rigs kyi badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11512: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai m+aa ra ni h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11513: badz+ra rik+sha sa mu kha na ku la mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11514: a b+hi stobs chen dud kha thong gshol zhing dbyug thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11515: bskyod ma gtso 'khyud dung khrag yab la stob //
NK021(zha)001:11516: sprul pa'i phra men dred dang byi ba'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11517: phrin las sa bdag gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:11518: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la bskur bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:11519: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h+aum s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK021(zha)001:11520: kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai mun+de mam h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11521: badz+ra rik+sha sa mu kha k+aa shi ka mu kh+ai h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11524: h+aum chen mthing ga 'khor lo thod dbyug thogs //
NK021(zha)001:11525: sgra 'byin gtso 'khyud dung khrag gtso la stob //
NK021(zha)001:11526: phrin las nyi zla'i gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:11527: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:11528: h+aum zhes sgra 'byin phag dang rmig bu'i mgo //
NK021(zha)001:11530: khro bcu zhal gsum phyag drug mngon par rol //
NK021(zha)001:11532: khro bcu rnams zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'am /
NK021(zha)001:11533: yang na zhal gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:11534: za gsod kyang yod med 'dam ka can du mdzad pa las /
NK021(zha)001:11536: za gsod kyang med pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:11537: khro bcu zhal gcig phyag gnyis par mdzad pa'i rjes su 'brang na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:11538: 'dir zhal phyag rgyas bsdus yin pas gang ltar byas kyang rung mod /
NK021(zha)001:11539: za gsod nges par dgos te /
NK021(zha)001:11541: rdo rje me ri lag chu ha //
NK021(zha)001:11542: phyi rol khro bcu yab yum ste //
NK021(zha)001:11543: phra men nyi shu yang sprul dag /
NK021(zha)001:11544: bye ba phrag ni sa ya 'phro //
NK021(zha)001:11547: rig 'dzin bla ma ma gtogs pa'i lha dbang la
NK021(zha)001:11548: 'dir zhi khro'i lha lnga brgya gya gsum yod par
NK021(zha)001:11549: bshad cing / de la 'dren pa'i las byang che
NK021(zha)001:11550: ler phur pa'i lha zhe gnyis bgrang dgos par gsungs
NK021(zha)001:11551: bshad cing / pa'i phyir / za gsod yod pa'i
NK021(zha)001:11552: phyogs dag par mthong nas 'dir kha bskang ba yin
NK021(zha)001:11553: bshad cing / pa'i phyir / no // na mo /
NK021(zha)001:11554: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:11555: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la /
NK021(zha)001:11556: che mchog yab yum chos sku rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK021(zha)001:11557: khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bdun cu rtsa brgyad /
NK021(zha)001:11558: khro bo bka' nyan dang sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhi
NK021(zha)001:11559: brgya re gsum rnams kyi phyag rgya'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:11560: / rtog tshogs thams cad dbyings su dag nas dpal
NK021(zha)001:11561: chen po'i sku dang ye shes su rtogs par gnyis
NK021(zha)001:11562: 'dzin gyi mtha' la zhen pa'i 'gro ba rnams dus
NK021(zha)001:11563: gcig la sgrol ba'i dbang dam pa des phan pa
NK021(zha)001:11565: da byin pa slob dpon gyi dbang zhes grags pa
NK021(zha)001:11566: rdo rje 'chang gi dkyil 'khor rig 'dzin rnams kyi
NK021(zha)001:11569: mdo yongs rdzogs kyi brgyud lugs gnyis gang ltar kyang ro langs bde ba la bka' babs pas /
NK021(zha)001:11570: de phyin chad gcig 'dres su gyur mod //
NK021(zha)001:11572: a nu la bskyed rdzogs gsum du phye ba'i ma h+aa dang a ti gnyis kyang /
NK021(zha)001:11573: theg pa de gnyis kyi lam dang cha 'dra bar bkral bas /
NK021(zha)001:11574: de dang de'i byin rlabs kyi bka' babs kyang du ma zhig gnubs chen la babs pas na /
NK021(zha)001:11575: mdo rang gi nang gses bskyed rdzogs gsum du phye
NK021(zha)001:11576: ba'i bla brgyud gcig nas gcig tu brgyud pa'i rim
NK021(zha)001:11577: pa kho na ma yin kyang /
NK021(zha)001:11578: rig 'dzin de rnams kyi byin rlabs 'pho ba'i chu
NK021(zha)001:11579: rgyun gcig tu 'dril bas slob ma'i rgyud byin gyis
NK021(zha)001:11580: rlob pa'i sgor bka' babs tha dad pa'i brgyud pa'ang
NK021(zha)001:11581: mgron thabs su byas te ngo mtshar sgrigs lta bur
NK021(zha)001:11582: mdzad nas bskur ba yin la /
NK021(zha)001:11583: de yang gab pa'i dbang ler dus gsum gyi slob dpon zhes /
NK021(zha)001:11586: man ngag 'bras bu'i slob dpon rnams so so'i gsang
NK021(zha)001:11587: mtshan dang bcas te go rim de ltar bskur bar
NK021(zha)001:11588: gsungs shing / bskyed rdzogs gsum re re la'ang dbang rgyud man ngag gsum gyi brgyud srol tshang yang /
NK021(zha)001:11589: gtso che ba'i dbang du byas nas /
NK021(zha)001:11590: de gsum rim pa ltar ma h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:11592: a ti gsum la sbyar du rung bas /
NK021(zha)001:11593: de'i dgongs pa ltar na 'jug rim bzhin mas 'dzegs kyis bskur bar 'gyur na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:11594: bla ma rnams kyi phyag bzhes su mchog dman gyi
NK021(zha)001:11595: rim pas bskur bar mdzad pa la'ang 'gal ba ma
NK021(zha)001:11596: mthong bas / 'dir de bzhin du bskur bar bya ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:11597: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs las dgongs rig gi rgyal ba sras bcas dang /
NK021(zha)001:11598: rgyu'i rta babs kyi phyi rol khor yug zlum po
NK021(zha)001:11599: la bzhugs pa'i dus gsum gyi rig 'dzin bla ma
NK021(zha)001:11600: rnams las rang 'dra ba re re chad de mgo
NK021(zha)001:11601: bo'i skra la thim pas rig 'dzin bla ma bye
NK021(zha)001:11602: ba sa ya'i tshogs su skad cig gis grub pa'i
NK021(zha)001:11603: mos pa mdzod / de la gsum las /
NK021(zha)001:11604: dang po man ngag 'bras bu'i slob dpon a ti yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:11605: tsakli rnams rim par thogs la /
NK021(zha)001:11606: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:11607: ston pa kun bzang yab yum ni //
NK021(zha)001:11608: 'og min gnas bzhugs byin rlabs can //
NK021(zha)001:11609: 'dir gshegs dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs //
NK021(zha)001:11610: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11611: ye shes rang rtsal mtshan dpe'i sku //
NK021(zha)001:11612: longs sku rdo rje sems dpa' yang //
NK021(zha)001:11613: 'og min gnas bzhugs 'dir gshegs dbang ma h+aa gu ru bde gshegs sku yi rigs 'chang ba //
NK021(zha)001:11614: mkhyen rab mnga' bdag 'jam dpal dbyangs //
NK021(zha)001:11615: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa bde gshegs gsung gi rigs 'chang ba /
NK021(zha)001:11616: thugs rje'i mnga' bdag spyan ras gzigs /
NK021(zha)001:11617: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa bde gshegs thugs kyi rigs 'chang ba //
NK021(zha)001:11618: mthu stobs mnga' bdag rdo rje 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11619: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje ni //
NK021(zha)001:11620: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11621: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ni //
NK021(zha)001:11622: gsang mtshan rdo rje gzhon nu rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11623: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rgyal po d+ha he na ta lo //
NK021(zha)001:11624: gsang mtshan rdo rje dga' byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11625: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa thu bo r+aa dza hasti ni //
NK021(zha)001:11626: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal ba rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11627: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rgyal po'i sras mo w+aa ra ni //
NK021(zha)001:11628: gsang mtshan rdo rje mdzes ma rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11629: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa klu yi rgyal po 'jog po ni //
NK021(zha)001:11630: gsang mtshan rdo rje rdzu 'phrul can //
NK021(zha)001:11631: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa sras mo gnod sbyin byang chub mo //
NK021(zha)001:11632: gsang mtshan rdo rje g.yung drung rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11633: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa smad 'tshong gzungs ma a ra li'i //
NK021(zha)001:11634: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbyings ma rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11635: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa kha che'i slob dpon ak+sho b+h+yah /
NK021(zha)001:11636: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11637: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa mkhan po ku ku r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11638: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11639: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa smad 'tshong bud+d+ha sa ma ya'i //
NK021(zha)001:11640: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dag rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11641: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa smad 'tshong bud+d+ha sa ma t+ai //
NK021(zha)001:11642: gsang mtshan rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11643: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa o rgyan rgyal po ma h+aa r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11644: gsang mtshan rdo rje rdzu 'phrul rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11645: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa sras mo go ma de w+ai yi //
NK021(zha)001:11646: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11647: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon chen po +aa lo ke'i //
NK021(zha)001:11648: gsang mtshan rdo rje g.yung drung rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11649: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma yi //
NK021(zha)001:11650: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11651: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon ma h+aa r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11652: gsang mtshan rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11653: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon drang srong b+ha shi ti'i //
NK021(zha)001:11654: gsang mtshan rdo rje lhun grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11655: 'og miin 'dir gshegs ma h+aa gzungs ma smad 'tshong bdag nyid ma'i //
NK021(zha)001:11656: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'od mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11657: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon n+aa gardzu na yi //
NK021(zha)001:11658: gsang mtshan rdo rje thogs med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11659: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon de ba r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11660: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsang brtsal ba //
NK021(zha)001:11661: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma yi //
NK021(zha)001:11662: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11663: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rig 'dzin dge bsnyen legs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:11664: gsang mtshan rdo rje mchog rab rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11665: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon bud+d+ha gu h+ya yi //
NK021(zha)001:11666: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsang rdzogs rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11667: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon sh+r+ai sid+d+ha yi //
NK021(zha)001:11668: gsang mtshan rdo rje bzhad pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11669: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa dge slong ma gzugs kun dga' mo'i //
NK021(zha)001:11670: gsang mtshan rdo rje shes rab rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11671: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon bi ma la mi tra'i //
NK021(zha)001:11672: gsang mtshan rdo rje gro lod rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11673: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa lo chen bee ro tsa na yi //
NK021(zha)001:11674: gsang mtshan rdo rje khyung gshog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11675: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11676: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde 'byams rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11677: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa gnyags lo ye shes gzhon nu yi //
NK021(zha)001:11678: gsang mtshan dri med zla shar rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11679: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa sog po dpal gyi ye shes kyi //
NK021(zha)001:11680: gsang mtshan rdo rje gzhad pa'i gter //
NK021(zha)001:11681: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa gnyis pa shes rab rgyud
NK021(zha)001:11682: kyi slob dpon a nu yo ga'i brgyud pa ni
NK021(zha)001:11683: // 'og min chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK021(zha)001:11684: rgyal mchog kun bzang yum dang bcas //
NK021(zha)001:11685: 'dir gshegs dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs //
NK021(zha)001:11686: dbyings rig dbyer med rtogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:11687: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:11688: ye shes rang snang zhing khams nas //
NK021(zha)001:11689: rgyal tshab rdo rje sems dpa' yang //
NK021(zha)001:11690: 'dir gshegs dbang rang byung ye shes rtogs par shog /
NK021(zha)001:11691: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri dbus phyogs rnam dag zhing khams nas //
NK021(zha)001:11692: sku mchog rnam par snang mdzad kyang //
NK021(zha)001:11693: 'dir gshegs chos dbyings ye shes rtogs ma h+aa shar phyogs rnam dag zhing khams nas //
NK021(zha)001:11694: thugs mchog rdo rje mi bskyod pa //
NK021(zha)001:11695: 'dir gshegs me long ye shes ma h+aa lho phyogs rnam dag yon tan rin chen 'byung gnas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:11696: 'dir mnyam nyid ma h+aa nub phyogs rnam dag gsung mchog snang ba mtha' yas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:11697: 'dir sor rtog ma h+aa byang phyogs rnam dag las mchog don yod grub pa yang //
NK021(zha)001:11698: 'dir bya grub ye shes ma h+aa chos nyid zhi las ma g.yos par //
NK021(zha)001:11699: bdud 'dul khro bo'i skur snang ba //
NK021(zha)001:11700: tshogs rje tshogs bdag he ru ka /
NK021(zha)001:11701: 'dir ma h+aa rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang du //
NK021(zha)001:11703: dbang bskur dam pa tog dkar yang //
NK021(zha)001:11704: 'dir ma h+aa gzhon tshul mdzes pa'i skur bstan nas //
NK021(zha)001:11705: lha rnams rgyal ba'i gdung tshab tu //
NK021(zha)001:11706: dbang bskur byed po 'jam dpal dbyangs //
NK021(zha)001:11707: 'dir gshegs ma h+aa bdud rtsi sman gyi skur bstan nas //
NK021(zha)001:11708: klu rnams rgyal ba'i gdung tshab tu //
NK021(zha)001:11709: 'dren mdzad spyan ras gzigs dbang yang //
NK021(zha)001:11710: 'dir ma h+aa drag shul 'jigs pa'i skur bstan nas //
NK021(zha)001:11711: gnod sbyin tshogs rnams rgyal tshab tu //
NK021(zha)001:11712: dbang bskur byed po rdo rje 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:11713: 'dir ma h+aa lha dbang grags ldan mchog skyong gi //
NK021(zha)001:11714: gsang mtshan thig le chags med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11715: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa gnod sbyin rig 'dzin skar mda' gdong //
NK021(zha)001:11716: gsang mtshan rdo rje glog 'byin rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11717: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa srin po lang+ka mgrin bcu yi //
NK021(zha)001:11718: gsang mtshan blo gros thabs ldan stsal //
NK021(zha)001:11720: 'dir ma h+aa rig 'dzin klu rgyal 'jog po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11721: gsang mtshan dbang phyug lhun grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11722: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa mi yi rig 'dzin li tsa b+ai //
NK021(zha)001:11723: gsang mtshan dri med grags pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11724: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK021(zha)001:11725: mi las skal ldan rigs can zhes //
NK021(zha)001:11726: rgyal bas lung bstan rgyal po dzah /
NK021(zha)001:11727: lag na rdo rjes rjes bzung zhing //
NK021(zha)001:11728: bka' brgyud rtags kyi dbang rdzogs thob //
NK021(zha)001:11729: gsang mtshan rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11730: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon u pa r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11731: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dag rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11732: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rgyal po in dra bo d+hi yi //
NK021(zha)001:11733: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal mdzes rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11734: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rgyal po n+aa ga pu tra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11735: gsang mtshan thig le bskyod med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11736: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rgyal po gu h+ya pu tri yi //
NK021(zha)001:11737: gsang mtshan rdo rje gsal 'phro can //
NK021(zha)001:11738: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma rgyal po sid+ha pu tra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11739: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'od zer rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11740: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma yi //
NK021(zha)001:11741: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11744: ma h+aa slob dpon ro langs bde ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:11745: gsang mtshan bdud 'dul drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11746: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:11747: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11748: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa za hor rgyal po pra hasti'i //
NK021(zha)001:11749: gsang mtshan thig le bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11750: 'og 'dir ma slob dpon sh+aakya seng ge yi //
NK021(zha)001:11751: gsang mtshan rdo rje thod phreng rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11752: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon sh+aakya pra b+h+aa yi //
NK021(zha)001:11753: gsang mtshan rdo rje thig le rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11754: 'og 'dir slob dpon sh+aakya mu dra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11755: gsang mtshan rdo rje thogs med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11756: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon d+ha na rak+shi ta'i //
NK021(zha)001:11757: gsang mtshan seng ge sgra sgrog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11758: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon h+aum chen k+aa ra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11759: gsang mtshan rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11760: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon s+thi ra ma ti'i //
NK021(zha)001:11761: gsang mtshan yang dag rdzogs pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11762: 'og 'dir slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi //
NK021(zha)001:11763: gsang mtshan dbang phyug 'jigs med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11764: 'og 'dir slob dpon d+harma bo d+hi yi //
NK021(zha)001:11765: gsang mtshan shes rab mthar phyin rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11766: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa mkhan po d+harma r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11767: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11768: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa bal po ba su d+ha ra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11769: gsang mtshan rdo rje thugs mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11770: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge yi //
NK021(zha)001:11771: gsang mtshan rdo rje gtsug tor rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11772: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa bru sha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes //
NK021(zha)001:11773: gsang mtshan rdo rje legs thob rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11774: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa gsum pa dam tshig dbang
NK021(zha)001:11775: gi slob dpon ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud pa ni
NK021(zha)001:11776: / bya byed yid chos gnas dag pa //
NK021(zha)001:11777: drug pa kun bzang yab yum sku //
NK021(zha)001:11778: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa gzugs kyi phung po gnas dag pa //
NK021(zha)001:11779: rnam par snang mdzad bcom ldan 'das //
NK021(zha)001:11780: 'og min gnas bzhugs 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rnam shes phung po gnas dag pa //
NK021(zha)001:11781: mi bskyod rdo rje bcom ldan 'das //
NK021(zha)001:11782: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa tshor ba'i phung po
NK021(zha)001:11783: rin chen 'byung gnas 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa
NK021(zha)001:11784: 'du shes phung po snang ba mtha' yas 'og min
NK021(zha)001:11785: 'dir ma h+aa 'du byed phung po don yod grub
NK021(zha)001:11786: pa 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rang byung ye
NK021(zha)001:11788: rigs 'dus rgyal tshab rdo rje sems //
NK021(zha)001:11789: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa gsang sngags sdud por dbang bskur ba //
NK021(zha)001:11790: rdo rje chos zhes gsang ba'i bdag /
NK021(zha)001:11791: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa spong len brtul zhags spyod pa'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:11792: dge bar bskur thob skal ldan dzah /
NK021(zha)001:11793: gsang mtshan rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11794: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rnam dag mchod rten drug bsgrubs pas //
NK021(zha)001:11795: rdor sems zhal mthong tan+t+ra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11796: don rtogs ku ku r+aa dza che //
NK021(zha)001:11797: gsang mtshan rdo rje che mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11798: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rgyal po sha tra pu tra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11799: gsang mtshan rdo rje rab mdzes rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11800: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rgyal po sid+ha r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11801: gsang mtsham rdo rje grags pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11802: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rgyal po u pa r+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11803: gsang mtshan yang dag grub pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11804: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa sras mo go ma de w+ai yi //
NK021(zha)001:11805: gsang mtshan rdo rje zla mdzes rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11806: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon mee t+r+ai ka ma la'i //
NK021(zha)001:11807: gsang mtshan rdo rje khyung chen rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11808: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon dzi na mi tra yi //
NK021(zha)001:11809: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11810: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:11811: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11812: 'og min gnas bzhugs byin rlabs can //
NK021(zha)001:11813: 'dir gshegs dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs //
NK021(zha)001:11814: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri slob dpon nyin byed seng ge yi //
NK021(zha)001:11815: gsang mtshan rdo rje rtsal chen rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11816: 'og min 'dir slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi //
NK021(zha)001:11817: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'gyur med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11818: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa slob dpon sh+aakya bo d+hi yi //
NK021(zha)001:11819: gsang mtshan rdo rje grub mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11820: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon so kya de ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:11821: gsang mtshan rdo rje dad pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11822: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rje yi //
NK021(zha)001:11823: gsang mtshan rdo rje sgeg pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11824: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa slob dpon chos blon bde ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:11825: gsang mtshan rdo rje nges chen rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11826: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa mkhan po chos rgyal skyong ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:11827: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11828: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa zhar byung theg drug gi babs so yang /
NK021(zha)001:11829: phar phyin slob dpon king+ka ra //
NK021(zha)001:11830: kri ya'i klu sgrub tsan+di ka /
NK021(zha)001:11831: yo ga'i ku ma ti gsum gyis //
NK021(zha)001:11832: rjes bzung ro langs bde ba sogs //
NK021(zha)001:11833: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo yi //
NK021(zha)001:11834: bka' babs brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams //
NK021(zha)001:11835: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa de nas rgyud lung
NK021(zha)001:11836: man ngag gsum theg drug dang bcas pa thams cad
NK021(zha)001:11837: gcig tu 'dril ba'i brgyud pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:11838: bdag 'dra gnubs kyi ban chung gis //
NK021(zha)001:11839: g.yung drung rin chen gter gnas su //
NK021(zha)001:11840: yi dam gsal bar bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:11841: stobs po che yi rdzas mchog 'di //
NK021(zha)001:11842: nam mkha'i mthongs nas yas mar babs //
NK021(zha)001:11843: bdag gi lag pa g.yas pas zin //
NK021(zha)001:11844: ye shes rdo rje'i dbang mchog thob //
NK021(zha)001:11845: 'ol mo tshal du bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:11846: mngon sum dri za phru gu byung //
NK021(zha)001:11847: sangs rgyas khyod yin mtshan yang btags //
NK021(zha)001:11848: dam pa'i don la dam tshig bsres //
NK021(zha)001:11849: rdo rje ming gi dbang yang thob //
NK021(zha)001:11850: gang bzang gnas su bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:11851: gnod sbyin phru gu mngon du byung //
NK021(zha)001:11852: 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa bstabs //
NK021(zha)001:11853: yun gyi 'khor du dam yang bcas //
NK021(zha)001:11854: che ba'i yon tan dbang yang thob //
NK021(zha)001:11855: gling dgu'i mtsho 'gram bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:11856: klu phrug spun gsum mngon gyur ste //
NK021(zha)001:11857: ro brgya ldan pa'i mchod pa drangs //
NK021(zha)001:11858: yang dag slob mar dam tshig nos //
NK021(zha)001:11859: gdug pa sel ba'i dbang yang thob //
NK021(zha)001:11860: dur khrod lhas su bsgoms pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:11861: yi dwags phru gu mngon du byung //
NK021(zha)001:11862: zhabs la gtugs te mchi ma phyungs //
NK021(zha)001:11863: ci bsgos nyan par gnyer dam bskos //
NK021(zha)001:11864: mthu rtsal snyems pa'i dbang yang thob //
NK021(zha)001:11865: phyi rabs slob ma gang byung rnams //
NK021(zha)001:11867: phan pa lha yi dbang nos la //
NK021(zha)001:11868: bskur thabs dbang bskur rgyal po bzhin //
NK021(zha)001:11869: dbang mchog 'di rnams thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:11870: de skad rdo rje'i bden tshig tu //
NK021(zha)001:11871: gsung mdzad sangs rgyas ye shes zhabs //
NK021(zha)001:11872: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dbang gter //
NK021(zha)001:11873: 'og min gnas bzhugs 'dir gshegs dbang bskur ma h+aa
NK021(zha)001:11874: gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h+aum a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:11875: gnubs sras yon tan rgya mtsho yi //
NK021(zha)001:11876: gsang mtshan rdo rje rig 'dzin gter //
NK021(zha)001:11877: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa gnubs rton ye shes rgya mtsho yi //
NK021(zha)001:11878: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11879: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa rgya ston blo gros byang chub kyi //
NK021(zha)001:11880: gsang mtshan rdo rje las grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11881: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa bka' babs tho kar nam mkha'i lde'i //
NK021(zha)001:11882: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub gter //
NK021(zha)001:11883: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa yang na gnubs chen nas /
NK021(zha)001:11884: sru ston legs pa'i sgron me yi //
NK021(zha)001:11885: gsang mtshan ut+pala dbang chen rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11886: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa zhu ston bsod nams sh+aakya yi //
NK021(zha)001:11887: gsang mtshan phrin las mthar phyin rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11888: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa de dang tho dkar nas /
NK021(zha)001:11890: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11891: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa lta dgongs rtse mo zur chung ba //
NK021(zha)001:11892: gsang mtshan rdo rje lhun grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11893: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rdzogs chen ka ba skyo sh+aaka ye //
NK021(zha)001:11894: gsang mtshan rdo rje snying po rtsa la //
NK021(zha)001:11895: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa mdo yi ka ba yang khyed bla //
NK021(zha)001:11896: gsang mtshan thig le 'gyur med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11897: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa sgyu 'phul ka ba klan sh+aaka bzang //
NK021(zha)001:11898: gsang mtshan rdo rje myu gu rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11899: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa phrin sgrub ka ba mda' chos sh+aaka /
NK021(zha)001:11900: gsang mtshan rdo rje dngos grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11901: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa glan ston sh+aakya byang chub ni //
NK021(zha)001:11902: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11903: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa gsang bdag sh+aakya seng ge yi //
NK021(zha)001:11904: gsang mtshan dbang phyung rdzogs pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11905: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa 'og gdong lha rje 'gar zung nge //
NK021(zha)001:11906: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11907: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa sregs ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11908: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'jigs med rtsal /
NK021(zha)001:11909: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa mkhas pa glan ston rdo rje 'od //
NK021(zha)001:11910: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11911: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa glan ston brtson 'grus seng ge yi //
NK021(zha)001:11912: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11913: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa glan ston bsod nams rgyal po ni //
NK021(zha)001:11914: gsang mtshan phrin las mthar phyin rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11915: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa sprul sku lha rje lha 'bum ni //
NK021(zha)001:11916: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11917: 'og 'dir ma glan ston chos kyi seng ge ni //

NK021(zha)001:11919: 'og 'dir ma h+aa glan ston bud+d+ha sh+r+ai yi //
NK021(zha)001:11920: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11921: 'og 'dir ma nya tshal glan chen bsod nams mgon //
NK021(zha)001:11922: gsang mtshan theg le drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11923: 'og min 'dir ma gzi ston sh+aakya bzang po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11924: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11925: 'og 'dir ma sgrol chen bsam grub rdo rje yi //
NK021(zha)001:11926: gsang mtshan rdo rje bde byed rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11927: 'og 'dir ma h+aa sgrol byed sangs rgyas rin chen gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11928: gsang mtshan rdo rje thugs mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11929: 'og 'dir ma h+aa rlung sems mthar phyin gnam sdings pa //
NK021(zha)001:11930: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang drag ste //
NK021(zha)001:11931: 'og 'dir ma sha mi rdo rje rgyal mtshan gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11932: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11933: 'og 'dir rig 'dzin la rgu rdos dgon pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:11934: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11935: 'og 'dir mkhas grub blo gros bzang po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11936: gsang mtshan dri med zla shar rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11937: 'og min 'dir ma mkhas btsun gzhan phan rdo rje yi //
NK021(zha)001:11938: gsang mtshan rdo rje ye shes rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11939: 'og min 'dir gshegs ma h+aa gsang bdag phrin las lhun grub kyi //
NK021(zha)001:11940: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11941: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa dwags ston chos rgyal bstan 'dzin gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11942: gsang mtshan rdo rje yongs grol rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11943: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa yang na sgrol chen bsam grub rdo rje nas //
NK021(zha)001:11945: gsang mtshan rdo rje thod phreng rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11946: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa lang gro tshe dbang rgyal po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11947: gsang mtshan rdo rje thogs med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11948: 'og 'dir ma brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal bzang gi //
NK021(zha)001:11949: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang sdud rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11950: 'og 'dir ma lha btsun glo bo ma thang pa //
NK021(zha)001:11951: 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan yang //
NK021(zha)001:11952: 'og 'dir ma h+aa rig 'dzin bdud 'joms rdo rje yi //
NK021(zha)001:11953: gsang mtshan rdo rje gro lod rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11954: 'og 'dir ma skyi ston tshe ring dbang po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11955: gsang mtshan rol ba'i rdo rje ste //
NK021(zha)001:11956: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa gnyags ston chos rgyal rdo rje yi //
NK021(zha)001:11958: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa nyang ston blo gros mchog gi sde //
NK021(zha)001:11959: gsang mtshan rig pa'i rdo rje rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11960: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa rig 'dzin pad+ma phrin las kyi //
NK021(zha)001:11961: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'joms rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11962: 'og min 'dir ma yang na gzhan phan rdo rje la /
NK021(zha)001:11964: blo mchog rdo rje gnyis kas gsan pas /
NK021(zha)001:11965: de las kyang brgyud chog go //
NK021(zha)001:11966: yang brgyud lugs gcig ltar na /
NK021(zha)001:11967: sgrol chen bsam 'grub rdo rje nas //
NK021(zha)001:11969: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbyings phyug ma //
NK021(zha)001:11970: 'og min 'dir ma h+aa zur ston sh+aakya bshes gnyen gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11971: gsang mtshan rdo rje thugs mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11972: 'og 'dir ma h+aa mkhas grub bra'o chos 'bum gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11973: gsang mtshan rdo rje thogs med rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11974: 'og 'dir ma h+aa bshes gnyen dkon mchog bzang po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11975: gsang mtshan rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11976: 'og 'dir ma rmog ston rdo rje bzang po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11977: gsang mtshan rdo rje yang dag rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11978: 'og 'dir ma sems dpa' chen po dar lung ba //
NK021(zha)001:11979: rdo rje rnam rgyal mi bskyod rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11980: 'og 'dir ma h+aa 'khrul zhig blo gros dpal ldan gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11981: gsang mtshan rdo rje lhun grub rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11982: 'og 'dir ma h+aa dpang ston karma gu ru yi //
NK021(zha)001:11983: gsang mtshan rdo rje dbang phyug rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11984: 'og 'dir ma sngags 'chang kun bzang dpal 'byor gyi //
NK021(zha)001:11985: gsang mtshan rdo rje che mchog rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11986: 'og 'dir ma h+aa yang na kahthoga pa nas /
NK021(zha)001:11987: 'phags mchog bya btang chen po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11988: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11989: 'og 'dir ma de dang gnam sdings pa nas /
NK021(zha)001:11990: sha mi badz+ra d+h+w+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11991: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11992: 'og 'dir ma mthu chen g.yu 'brug rdo rje yi //
NK021(zha)001:11993: gsang mtshan rdo rje drag po rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11995: 'dir ma h+aa kun mkhyen ma ti d+h+w+aa dza yi //
NK021(zha)001:11996: gsang mtshan dri med zla shar rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11997: 'og 'dir ma h+aa zab lung dbang gi rgyal po yi //
NK021(zha)001:11998: gsang mtshan rdo rje rol pa rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:11999: 'og 'dir ma lha btsun kun bzang rnam rgyal gyi //
NK021(zha)001:12000: gsang mtshan rnam mkha' 'jigs med rtsal /
NK021(zha)001:12001: 'og 'dir ma de dang kun bzang dpa' 'byor nas /
NK021(zha)001:12002: gsang bdag phrin las lhun grub kyi //
NK021(zha)001:12003: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12004: 'og 'dir dwags ston chos rgyal bstan 'dzin gyi //
NK021(zha)001:12005: gsang mtshan rdo rje yongs grol rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12006: 'og 'dir yang na ma ti d+h+w+aa dza nas gzhan phan rdo rje sogs so //
NK021(zha)001:12007: de ltar rig 'dzin pad+ma phrin las dang /
NK021(zha)001:12008: drags ston chos rgyal bstan 'dzin gnyis la gter chen
NK021(zha)001:12009: rin po ches gsan te brgyud srol de thams cad
NK021(zha)001:12012: gsang mtshan 'gyur med rdo rje rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12013: 'og 'dir lo chen chos dpal rgya mtsho yi //
NK021(zha)001:12014: gsang mtshan rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12015: 'og 'dir rgyal sras rin chen rnam rgyal gyi //
NK021(zha)001:12016: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal /
NK021(zha)001:12019: gsang mtshan gar dbang rdo rje rtsal /
NK021(zha)001:12020: 'og 'dir mkhan chen oo di y+aa na yi //
NK021(zha)001:12021: gsang mtshan bstan 'dzin rdo rje rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12022: 'og 'dir smyos ston phrin las rnam rgyal gyi //
NK021(zha)001:12023: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal /
NK021(zha)001:12025: gsang mtshan rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal /
NK021(zha)001:12026: 'og 'dir khri chen sangs rgyas kun dga' yi //
NK021(zha)001:12027: gsang mtshan rdo rje mi 'gyur rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12028: 'og 'dir ma mdo sngags bstan 'dzin nor bu yi //
NK021(zha)001:12029: gsang mtshan rdo rje sems dpa' rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12031: lo chen nas bdag gi 'dren mchog phan bde'i 'od
NK021(zha)001:12032: zer bar gyi brgyud pa'i zhal skong dz+ny+aa nas so
NK021(zha)001:12034: gsang mtshan rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12035: 'og 'dir spyi gtsug nyi zla'i gdan steng du //
NK021(zha)001:12036: rtsa ba'i bla ma bka' drin can //
NK021(zha)001:12037: byin rlabs brgyud par ldan pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:12038: 'dir gshegs dbang bskur byin gyis rlobs //
NK021(zha)001:12039: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12041: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rigs pa'i 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:12042: khyod la rdo rje 'chang gi dkyil 'khor brgyud gsum
NK021(zha)001:12043: rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs kyi phyag rgya'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:12044: bas // bskyed rdzogs gsum gyis dgongs pa'i don rtog
NK021(zha)001:12045: nas rgyud lung man ngag lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:12046: dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12047: brgyad pa ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur ba ni //
NK021(zha)001:12049: dbang rdzas mi dmigs pa las t+r+aam las byung ba'i
NK021(zha)001:12050: thod pa'i dbu rgyan rin po che'i khang bu lnga
NK021(zha)001:12052: ye shes rin chen dbu rgyan mchog /
NK021(zha)001:12053: gzi brjid phung po bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:12054: sangs rgyas rin chen kun 'dus pas //
NK021(zha)001:12055: rnam par rgyal bar dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:12056: rat+na ka p+aa la mu ku ta a b+hi shiny+tsa tram tram /
NK021(zha)001:12058: de nas rigs lnga'i tsakli spyi bo dang mar me lnga lag tu gtad la /
NK021(zha)001:12059: dbang rdzas rnam shes tshogs brgyad la bstim pas //
NK021(zha)001:12060: spyi bo'i gnas lngar de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga
NK021(zha)001:12061: yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i rjes chags kyi mes
NK021(zha)001:12062: zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun gyis dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:12064: chu lhag ma spyi bo'i gnas lngar 'khyil ba las /
NK021(zha)001:12065: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar dag ste /
NK021(zha)001:12066: khams gsum chos kyi rgyal por gyur pa'i rtags rigs
NK021(zha)001:12067: lnga dbu rgyan gyi khang bu la bzhugs pa'i mos
NK021(zha)001:12068: pa mdzod / ye shes chen po'i don dang de ldan pas //
NK021(zha)001:12069: ye shes lnga yi rtags mchog phyag rgya yi //
NK021(zha)001:12070: gnas lngar gtugs te thugs kyi dbang mchog sbyin //
NK021(zha)001:12071: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swab+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK021(zha)001:12073: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa sa ma
NK021(zha)001:12074: t+aa dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa
NK021(zha)001:12075: na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+th+aa
NK021(zha)001:12076: na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham
NK021(zha)001:12078: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK021(zha)001:12079: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la thugs ye
NK021(zha)001:12080: shes lnga'i rtags kyi phyag rgya'i dbang bskur bas rnam
NK021(zha)001:12081: shes tshogs brgyad ma spangs gnas su dag nas ye
NK021(zha)001:12082: shes lnga'i don rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa dgu pa
NK021(zha)001:12083: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:12084: rigs lnga so so'i sku sgo gsum nyer spyod bya ba dang bcas pa la bstim pas /
NK021(zha)001:12085: spyi mgrin snying lte gsang bar zla ba pad+ma nyi
NK021(zha)001:12086: ma rin chen ral gri la gnas pa'i +aam h+aum
NK021(zha)001:12088: rdo rje lnga'i lha tshogs spyan drangs te thim pas /
NK021(zha)001:12089: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK021(zha)001:12090: yon tan phrin las dang gnyis su med par gyur
NK021(zha)001:12091: pa'i rtags su / spyi bor rnam snang /
NK021(zha)001:12095: gsang bar don grub rnams kyis rgyas btab pa'i mos pa mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:12096: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK021(zha)001:12097: rnal 'byor bde mchog de yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:12098: sku gsung thugs kyi dbang mchog 'di //
NK021(zha)001:12099: rdo rje can la sbyin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12100: rigs so so'i tsakli gnas lngar 'jog cing /
NK021(zha)001:12101: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma kony+aa ham /
NK021(zha)001:12103: sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ka badz+ra sarba ta
NK021(zha)001:12104: th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK021(zha)001:12105: a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra sarba ta th+aa ga
NK021(zha)001:12106: ta p+au dza badz+ra na mo /
NK021(zha)001:12107: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la 'bras chos lnga'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12108: khams drug gnyis gnyis ro gcig pa gnyug ma'i sgo gsum du dag ste /
NK021(zha)001:12109: rdo rje gsum gyi don rtogs pa'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:12110: bcu pa bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas brgyad kyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:12111: bskur ba ni / mam las byung ba'i thun mong
NK021(zha)001:12112: ma yin pa'i rdzas brgyad lag tu gtad byed lus
NK021(zha)001:12113: kyi gnas so sor bstim pas bdud kyi g.yul las
NK021(zha)001:12114: rnam par rgyal te don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa
NK021(zha)001:12115: la mnga' 'byor ba'i rten 'brel sgrigs pa'i mos pa
NK021(zha)001:12116: bskur ba ni / mdzod / dbang mchog thob pa'i bu mchog des //
NK021(zha)001:12117: don rnams grub pa'i bkra shis phyir //
