NK021(zha)001:12118: bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas mchog rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12119: rtags kyis brgyan te byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12120: rus pa dang zhing lpags kyi rgyu las grub pa'i rdzas brgyad re re nas gtod cing /
NK021(zha)001:12122: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la /
NK021(zha)001:12123: sngon ston pa thub pa'i dbang po 'tshang rgya ba'i
NK021(zha)001:12124: tshe bdud kyi g.yul las rnam par rgyal ba'i rtags
NK021(zha)001:12125: bkra shis pa'i rdzas brgyad las /
NK021(zha)001:12126: dpal be'u'i dbang bskur bas thugs dpal be'ura bkra shis
NK021(zha)001:12127: par thams cad mkhyen pa'i go 'phang la dbang 'byor
NK021(zha)001:12128: ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12129: rgyal mtshan gyi dbang bskur bas sku mi nub pa
NK021(zha)001:12130: rgyal mtshan du bkra shis pas bdud bzhi las rgyal
NK021(zha)001:12131: ba'i dbang dam pa dung gi dbang bskur bas gsung
NK021(zha)001:12132: dbyangs dung gi sgrar bkra shis pas rgol ba thams
NK021(zha)001:12133: cad spa bkong ba'i dbang dam pa 'khor lo'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:12134: bskur bas phyag zhabs kyi mthil bzhi 'khor lor bkra
NK021(zha)001:12135: shis pas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:12136: pa bum pa'i dbang bskur bas mgul bum par bkra
NK021(zha)001:12137: shis pas thugs rjes thams cad 'dzin pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:12138: pa gser nya'i dbang bskur bas phyag zhabs kyi nywa
NK021(zha)001:12139: bzhi nyar bkra shis pas 'khor bar don mdzad kyang
NK021(zha)001:12140: nyam nga med pa'i dbang dam pa pad+ma'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:12141: bas ljags pad+mara bkra shis pas cis kyang gos pa
NK021(zha)001:12142: med pa'i dbang dam pa gdugs kyi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:12143: dbu skra gdugs su bkra shis pas gdung ba thams
NK021(zha)001:12144: cad sel ba'i dbang dam pa bcu gcig pa gsang
NK021(zha)001:12145: ba ming gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:12146: thig le dang rtsal gyi bar du rigs gang yin gyi ming sbyar ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:12147: dper na rdo rje'i rigs la /
NK021(zha)001:12155: snying po sogs bcug pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:12156: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la /
NK021(zha)001:12174: bdud 'joms sogs bcug pa btags la /
NK021(zha)001:12175: ming de nyid slob dpon dang nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12176: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis mgrin gcig tu btags
NK021(zha)001:12177: pa'i mos pa byed du bcug ste /
NK021(zha)001:12178: rdo rje lag tu gtod cing /
NK021(zha)001:12179: don rnams grub pa'i bu mchog de //
NK021(zha)001:12180: rdo rje'i dbang mchog thob pas na //
NK021(zha)001:12181: zhing khams kun tu grags pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12182: rtsal gyi thig le rdo rje byin //
NK021(zha)001:12184: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:12185: khyod la thig le che ge rtsal zhes bya ba
NK021(zha)001:12186: don dang mi 'gal ba'i ming gi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:12187: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:12188: cig / ces dril bus sna drangs pa'i rol mo 'khrol lo //
NK021(zha)001:12189: de rnams kyis ni nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bor grags pa nus pa'i dbang bcu gcig thob /
NK021(zha)001:12190: nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i spangs thob dang rigs 'dra'i yon tan gyi sa bon thebs pas /
NK021(zha)001:12191: rang 'bras sgrub dbang bskur rung du smin /
NK021(zha)001:12192: gtso bor las sgrib dang lus kyi dri ma 'bring po 'khrud /
NK021(zha)001:12193: dmigs med kun gsal gyi ye shes g.yo bas bag
NK021(zha)001:12194: la nyal rags la sbyangs nas rig pa byang chub
NK021(zha)001:12195: kyi sems skye ba'i rgyu sgrubs /
NK021(zha)001:12196: nang pa ma h+aa yo ga man chad kyi theg pa mtha' dag bshad cing sgrub pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:12197: ma h+aa dang thun mong du gyur pa'i a nu
NK021(zha)001:12198: rang lugs kyi bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa'i chos
NK021(zha)001:12199: rnams nyan bshad byed pa la dbang /
NK021(zha)001:12200: rnal 'byor bzhi las ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK021(zha)001:12201: mthar thug brgyad pa gnas pa mi 'gyur ba'i sa
NK021(zha)001:12202: non pa mthar lam dang po rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12203: rnal 'byor mngon du byed pa'i skal ba can du
NK021(zha)001:12204: byas so // gsum pa sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo ni /
NK021(zha)001:12206: nang du 'jug pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK021(zha)001:12207: de dag kun la spyod sgrub pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12208: dbang mchog dam pa byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12209: zhes pas nang dbang thob nas /
NK021(zha)001:12210: de dag gi don khyad par can sgrub pa'i thabs
NK021(zha)001:12211: spyod pa'i dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala 'bul du
NK021(zha)001:12212: bcug nas / slob dpon gyi thugs ka nas las
NK021(zha)001:12213: kyi rdo rje he ru ka'i rnam par spros pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12214: phyag gi rdo rjes rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK021(zha)001:12215: bcug nas / du drangs te / lus thams cad
NK021(zha)001:12216: sa la phab pa'i phyag sngon du 'gro bar mos
NK021(zha)001:12217: nas thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i
NK021(zha)001:12218: rjes gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK021(zha)001:12219: de ring nges par zhugs nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:12220: thabs kyis spyod pa'i dbang mchog rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12221: slob dpon chen pos bdag la stsol //
NK021(zha)001:12224: bla ma yab yum mnyam par rol pa'i byang chub
NK021(zha)001:12225: sems kyi 'od zer gyis slob bu rnams bkug ste
NK021(zha)001:12226: zhal du bcug / sku'i dbyibs brgyud /
NK021(zha)001:12227: rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi mkha' nang du gnas par gyur /
NK021(zha)001:12228: slar yang mkha' khyab kyi sangs rgyas sras dang bcas pa spyan drangs /
NK021(zha)001:12230: byang chub kyi sems su zhu ba'i 'od zer rdo rje'i lam nas byung ba des /
NK021(zha)001:12232: shes pa skad cig gis che chog he ru kar gyur pa /
NK021(zha)001:12233: mkha' nang nas phyir thon te /
NK021(zha)001:12234: rang gi mdun tu dbang stegs zil gnon gdan khri'i
NK021(zha)001:12235: bkod pa phun sum tshogs pa'i steng du 'khod pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12236: mos pa mdzod / de la bskur bya sgrub dbang bcu gsum las /
NK021(zha)001:12237: dbang po shes rab rig pa'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:12238: shes bya phyi nang gis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK021(zha)001:12239: kyi gshis lugs dkyil 'khor rnam gsum ma 'dres yongs
NK021(zha)001:12241: de'i ngang la rtsol bral bsal bzhag med par skyong
NK021(zha)001:12242: ba'i ting nge 'dzin sems lon rig pa'i gtan tshigs
NK021(zha)001:12243: kyis / sems nyid ci yang ma yin pa nyid /
NK021(zha)001:12244: cir yang ma 'gags par snang la //
NK021(zha)001:12245: snang stong gnyis su med cing /
NK021(zha)001:12246: de yang 'di kho na'o zhes brjod bral du nyams
NK021(zha)001:12247: su myong ba ni bdag zhal bdag gis mthong ba
NK021(zha)001:12248: ste / de'i rtags las byung ba'i rdo rje'am gtan tshigs kyi sgron me gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12249: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK021(zha)001:12250: sems kyi dbang bskur thob pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12251: shes rab chen po rig pa'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:12252: sems lon don gyi gtan tshigs byin //
NK021(zha)001:12253: pradz+ny+aa bid+y+aa a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12255: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la shes rab rig pa'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12256: rtog dpyod kyi rjes su 'jug pa lta ba gtan la phebs shing /
NK021(zha)001:12257: don gyi rjes su 'jug pa rnam par mi rtog
NK021(zha)001:12258: pa de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin mthar phyin
NK021(zha)001:12259: pa'i dbang dam pa gnyis pa snying rje rtags kyi
NK021(zha)001:12260: dbang ni / chos nyid snying po ye ji bzhin
NK021(zha)001:12261: pa las sgom byed kyi blo ma bcos par 'jog
NK021(zha)001:12262: pa don dam byang sems rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12263: dbang ni / ngang las / de ltar ma rtogs
NK021(zha)001:12264: pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i sems can la snying rje
NK021(zha)001:12265: rig pa'i rtsal snang ma 'gags par snang ba kun
NK021(zha)001:12266: rdzob byang sems kyis khams gsum la dbang bsgyur ba'i
NK021(zha)001:12267: nus pa thob par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:12268: de'i rtags +aahls byung ba'i nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12269: bya ba'i mtshan ma kun bral zhing //
NK021(zha)001:12270: rtsol med gnas pa'i byang chub sems //
NK021(zha)001:12271: snying rje chen po'i bde mchog gis /
NK021(zha)001:12272: khams gsum kun la dbang bsgyur byin //
NK021(zha)001:12273: a ma tsakra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12275: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la
NK021(zha)001:12276: snying rje rtags kyi dbang bskur bas don dam byang
NK021(zha)001:12277: sems rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang las kun rdzob
NK021(zha)001:12278: byang sems snying rje kun tu snang ba'i ting nge
NK021(zha)001:12279: 'dzin gyis khams gsum la dbang bsgyur ba'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:12280: pa gsum pa 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dbang la gnyis
NK021(zha)001:12281: las / bshad rgyud rngam glog ltar yi ge 'khor lo'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:12282: stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug pa'i rang rig
NK021(zha)001:12283: ye ger snang bas rgyu'i ting 'dzin mthar phyin par
NK021(zha)001:12285: nyon mongs lnga po gnas dag nas //
NK021(zha)001:12286: ye shes lnga po thob bya'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:12288: dbang thob de yi lag tu byin //
NK021(zha)001:12289: h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aahwar+na tsakra a b+hi rtsa rgyud dang dbang
NK021(zha)001:12290: don rnam par 'byed pa ltar thong gshol gyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:12291: ni / nyon mongs pa'i tha rgod bcom pas srid gsum 'gro ba'i don rdzogs par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:12292: h+aum las byung ba'i thong gshol gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12293: srid gsum 'gro ba'i don rnams kun //
NK021(zha)001:12294: thams cad rdzogs par nus pa yin //
NK021(zha)001:12295: rtags kyi dbang mchog dam pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:12296: thong gshol 'bar ba byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12297: a mo g+ha sid+d+hi ha la a b+hi 'dir yi
NK021(zha)001:12298: ge dang gshol gcig tu dril nas bskur bar dbang
NK021(zha)001:12299: chog nor bu'i phreng ba las kyang bshad ces zur
NK021(zha)001:12301: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la
NK021(zha)001:12302: yi ge 'khor lo dang thong gshol gyi dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:12303: bas zung 'jug rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin gyis nyon mongs
NK021(zha)001:12304: pa bcom ste 'gro don rdzogs pa'i dbang dam pa
NK021(zha)001:12305: bzhi pa drug gsum sprugs pa'i dbang ni chags sdang
NK021(zha)001:12306: rmongs gsum gnas su dag pas sku gsum lhun grub
NK021(zha)001:12307: lha sku phyag rgya gcig pa'i ting nge 'dzin mthar
NK021(zha)001:12309: a las byung ba'i thod pa tshar gsum dmar gyis gang ba gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12310: dug gsum gting nas sprugs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12311: rtags chen ga'u rnam pa gsum //
NK021(zha)001:12312: dmar chen dag gis bkang nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:12313: dbang thob de yi lag tu byin //
NK021(zha)001:12314: tri ka p+aa la a b+hi na mo /
NK021(zha)001:12315: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa ga'u rnam gsum gyi
NK021(zha)001:12316: dbang bskur bas cho ga gsum gyis dug gsum dbyings
NK021(zha)001:12317: su bcad pas rdo rje gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12318: dbang dam pa lnga pa srid gsum sgrol ba'i dbang
NK021(zha)001:12319: ni / 'khor ba'i rtogs tshogs dbyings su bcad pas
NK021(zha)001:12320: snang ba thams cad zung 'jug gi lhar spro ba'i
NK021(zha)001:12321: nus pa thob par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:12322: h+aa las byung ba'i mtshon cha gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12323: srid gsum sgrol bar bya ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:12324: dbang mchog chen po sbyin pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:12325: ka tar la sogs mtshon cha rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12326: dbang thob de yi lag tu byin //
NK021(zha)001:12327: shastra a b+hi 'dir rgyal ba g.yung gis mtshon cha drug gi grangs nges mdzad kyang /
NK021(zha)001:12328: rngam glog las mtshon cha sna tshogs zhes gsungs pa ltar phyag len du mdzad do //
NK021(zha)001:12330: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:12331: ka tar la sogs pa mtshon cha'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:12332: srid pa gsum gyi nyon mongs pa dbyings su bsgral
NK021(zha)001:12333: te snang spyod thams cad sku dang ye shes su
NK021(zha)001:12334: lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dam pa drug pa skyon
NK021(zha)001:12335: gyis ma gos pa'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:12336: yo byad lnga sogs 'dod pa'i yon tan la ci
NK021(zha)001:12337: dgar spyad kyang gos pa med pa'i thabs mkhas kyis
NK021(zha)001:12338: nye rgyu'i spyod pa mthar phyin par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:12339: pam las byung ba'i pad+ma gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12340: 'khor ba'i chos la cir spyad kyang //
NK021(zha)001:12341: skyon gyis gos par mi 'gyur ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:12342: rtags kyi phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK021(zha)001:12343: rnam dag rdzas kyi pad+ma byin //
NK021(zha)001:12345: phyogs bcu skal ldan pad+ma'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs
NK021(zha)001:12346: pa 'khor ba'i chos la spyad kyang gos pa med
NK021(zha)001:12347: pas nye rgyu'i spyod pa tshogs sgrub mthar phyin pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12348: dbang dam pa bdun pa las rnam bzhi rdzogs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12349: dbang ni / phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub
NK021(zha)001:12350: pas gang la gang 'dul gyi don byed pa'i nus
NK021(zha)001:12352: h+aam las byung ba'i ti ra'i dbyug pa lag tu gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12353: las rnams rdzogs par gyur pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12354: dbang mchog dam pa'i rtags chen ni //
NK021(zha)001:12355: ti ra'i dbyug pa chen po dag /
NK021(zha)001:12356: dbang thob de yi lag tu byin //
NK021(zha)001:12357: ti ra dan+da a b+hi na mo /
NK021(zha)001:12358: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa ti ra'i dbyug pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12359: dbang bskur bas phrin las rnam bzhi mthar phyin nas
NK021(zha)001:12360: bdag gzhan gyi don rdzogs par spyod pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:12361: pa brgyad pa gnyis med 'khril ba'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:12362: thabs shes gnyis su med pas chos nyid ma nor
NK021(zha)001:12363: ba dang gnyis su med pa'i don thob par bsam
NK021(zha)001:12364: la / h+aum a las byung ba'i sbrul chun gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12365: yum dang gnyis med 'khril ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:12366: chos nyid don dang gnyis med rtogs //
NK021(zha)001:12368: dbang thob de yi lag tu byin //
NK021(zha)001:12369: a dwa ya a b+hi na mo /
NK021(zha)001:12370: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa sbrul nag gi chun
NK021(zha)001:12371: po'i dbang bskur bas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su
NK021(zha)001:12372: med pa'i don blta bya lta byed med par dmigs
NK021(zha)001:12373: bral du rang gsal rjen par mthong ba'i lam sgrub
NK021(zha)001:12374: pa chen po mthar phyin pa'i dbang dam pa dgu
NK021(zha)001:12375: pa gsang ba sbyor ba'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:12376: gnyis med du sbyor ba'i rtags lha mo rang bzhin gsum gyi dbang thob par mos la /
NK021(zha)001:12377: byin gyis brlabs pa'i rig ma gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12378: gsang ba sbyor ba'i shes rab ma //
NK021(zha)001:12379: dri med rnam dag lha mo zhig /
NK021(zha)001:12380: mtshan ldan shin tu brgyan byas la //
NK021(zha)001:12381: dbang thob de la byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12382: d+ha ri pradz+ny+aa a b+hi na mo /
NK021(zha)001:12383: phyogs bcu dus skal ldan don dam spros bral rang
NK021(zha)001:12384: bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas dri ma med cing
NK021(zha)001:12385: zhi ba'i phyag rgya shes rab ma'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:12386: gsang sbyor zhu bde'i ye shes dbang po'i sdug bsngal
NK021(zha)001:12387: gyi rtog pa thams cad dbyings su bcad nas sbyor
NK021(zha)001:12388: sgrol gyi lam mchog yongs su rdzogs pa'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:12389: pa bcu pa 'dod yon longs spyod kyi dbang ni
NK021(zha)001:12390: / phyi nang sgrub pa'i dbang thob pas kun gyi
NK021(zha)001:12391: bdag nyid chen por gyur pa la 'dod pa'i longs
NK021(zha)001:12392: spyod rnams kyis mnga' gsol bar bsam zhing /
NK021(zha)001:12393: las byung ba'i 'dod yon gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12394: dbang thob rgyal po chen po de //
NK021(zha)001:12395: kun gyi bdag po yin pas na //
NK021(zha)001:12396: rol mo dri dang zhal zas dang //
NK021(zha)001:12397: 'dod yon lnga la sogs pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:12398: nye ba'i longs spyod rgyan rnams kun //
NK021(zha)001:12399: thams cad thams cad byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12400: sarba k+aa ma gu na a b+hi na mo /
NK021(zha)001:12401: phyogs bcu skal ldan 'dod yon longs spyod kyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:12402: bskur bas 'dod yon gyi snang ba thams cad bde
NK021(zha)001:12403: ba chen po ye shes rol pa'i rgyan du ma
NK021(zha)001:12404: spangs lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK021(zha)001:12405: bcu gcig pa sgrub pa'i rgyal po'i dbang ni /
NK021(zha)001:12406: sgrub dbang gi dkyil 'khor thun min la brten pa'i tshe /
NK021(zha)001:12407: skabs 'dir khrag 'thung re bzhi gtso bo dang bcas pa rnams kyi lha dbang bskur nas /
NK021(zha)001:12408: gnas ma sogs bka' nyan gyi 'khor dang rig 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:12409: rnams sgrub rdzas kyi rjes su bskur bar bshad na'ang
NK021(zha)001:12410: / sgrub dbang la dkyil 'khor logs sgrub ma byas pa'i lugs la /
NK021(zha)001:12412: de dag kun la spyod sgrub pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12413: zhes pa'i dgongs pas lha dbang sngar nang dbang du song bas go chod par byas te /
NK021(zha)001:12414: kha cig sgrub pa'i rgyal po'i dbang mi bskur ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:12415: bskur ba la'ang g.yung ston chen pos rigs lnga /
NK021(zha)001:12417: zur ham gyi mtha' dpyod du zhi ba kun bzang
NK021(zha)001:12418: dang khro bo che mchog la bsdus te bskur ba
NK021(zha)001:12419: sogs bzhed pa tha dad pa las /
NK021(zha)001:12420: 'dir phyi ma ltar sa khongs 'dzin byed tsam du /
NK021(zha)001:12421: zhi ba'i gtso bo kun bzang gi tsakli dang /
NK021(zha)001:12422: khro bo'i gtso bo dkyil 'khor la che mchog gi thod sku bkod yod na dang /
NK021(zha)001:12424: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las kyang /
NK021(zha)001:12425: bcu gcig sgrub pa'i rgyal po dkyil 'khor gtso bo sbyin /
NK021(zha)001:12427: dbang tshig tu rdo rje sems dpa' zhes pa'ang rigs
NK021(zha)001:12428: 'dus la dgongs pas gtso bo dang mi 'gal lo
NK021(zha)001:12429: // des na zhi khro'i lha mar me gcig las
NK021(zha)001:12430: gnyis chad kyi rnam par spyi bo nas thim pas
NK021(zha)001:12431: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams sgrub pa'i las la dbang
NK021(zha)001:12433: zhi khro'i gtso bo thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:12434: sgrub pa'i rgyal po khyod la ni //
NK021(zha)001:12435: sgrub pa'i las la dbang thob phyir //
NK021(zha)001:12436: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:12437: rgyal ba thams cad sgrubs shig ces //
NK021(zha)001:12438: bsgrub bya'i lha rnams byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12439: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su
NK021(zha)001:12440: kha h+aum h+aum a b+hi na mo phyogs bcu dus
NK021(zha)001:12441: skal ldan rig pa sgrub pa'i rgyal po dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:12442: gyi gtso bo'i dbang bskur ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:12443: thams cad sgrub pa'i dbang 'byor ba'i dbang bcu gnyis
NK021(zha)001:12444: pa sgrub rdzas kyi dbang la gsum gyi /
NK021(zha)001:12445: dang po rnal 'byor pa blo rab 'bring med pa
NK021(zha)001:12446: yongs la 'dren pa'i las byang chung dus bskur ba'i
NK021(zha)001:12447: sgrub rdzas thun mong ba bco lnga las /
NK021(zha)001:12449: tram las byung ba'i dbu rgyan bcings pas thod pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12450: khang bu lngar gyur pa'i nang du rigs lnga'i he
NK021(zha)001:12451: ru kas dbu brgyan par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:12452: sangs rgyas kun gyi rat+na che //
NK021(zha)001:12453: dpag tu med pa'i 'od dang ldan //
NK021(zha)001:12454: rigs mchog phyag rgya lngar ldan pas /
NK021(zha)001:12455: khams gsum bdag por dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:12456: badz+ra rat+na mu ku ta tram tram tram /
NK021(zha)001:12458: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa dbu rgyan gyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:12459: bskur bas dregs pa bdud dang srin po 'dul pa'i
NK021(zha)001:12460: dbang dam pa gnyis pa cod pan ni /
NK021(zha)001:12461: h+aum dang h+r+aihls byung ba'i dar mthing dmar gyi cod
NK021(zha)001:12462: pan dpyangs shing 'phur bas 'khor 'das kyi chos la
NK021(zha)001:12463: mnga' brnyes shing gdug pa can 'dul ba dang chos
NK021(zha)001:12464: kyi rgyal po chen por mnga' gsol bar bsam zhing
NK021(zha)001:12465: // cod pan mi 'gyur mnga' brnyes pas //
NK021(zha)001:12466: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po'i dbang /
NK021(zha)001:12467: khams gsum kun gyi dbang phyug chen //
NK021(zha)001:12468: chos kyi rgyal por dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:12469: d+h+aarma r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12471: phyogs bcu skal ldan cod pan gyi dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:12472: chos kyi rgyal srid chen po la mnga' brnyes nas
NK021(zha)001:12473: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dbang dam pa gsum
NK021(zha)001:12474: pa b+hany+dza ni / kam las byung ba'i thod pa
NK021(zha)001:12475: byin pas snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan par
NK021(zha)001:12476: pa b+hany+dza ni / mos la / mtshan ma'i rtog bral b+hany+dza'i rdzas mchog 'di //
NK021(zha)001:12477: sngon gyi skyes mchog sgrub pa'i rdzas yin te //
NK021(zha)001:12478: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dabaca snod bcud chos kyi sku dang ldan par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12479: d+harma k+aa ya sha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12481: phyogs bcu skal ldan b+hany+dza'i dbang bskur bas snod bcud
NK021(zha)001:12482: chos kyi sku dang ldan pa'i dbang dam pa bzhi
NK021(zha)001:12483: pa h+aum las byung ba'i byang sems dkar po gtad
NK021(zha)001:12484: de / skye med byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di //
NK021(zha)001:12485: dkar la dag pa'i gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK021(zha)001:12486: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12487: rdo rje rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12490: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12491: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang ldan te rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12492: lnga pa las byung ba'i dri chen /
NK021(zha)001:12493: dri chen bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin te //
NK021(zha)001:12494: rnam rtog dug sel bdud rtsi'i bdag nyid kyis //
NK021(zha)001:12495: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12496: de bzhin rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12497: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK021(zha)001:12499: phyogs bcu skal ldan dri chen gyi dbang bskur bas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang ldan te /
NK021(zha)001:12500: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi dngos grub thob drug pa s+w+aa las byung ba'i mam sa /
NK021(zha)001:12501: ma rig khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12502: gnas nas sgrol mdzad rdzas mchog sha chen 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:12503: skal ldan rin chen rigs kyi sid+d+hi sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na at+ma ko&a ham /
NK021(zha)001:12505: phyogs bcu skal ldan sha chen gyi dbang bskur bas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang ldan te /
NK021(zha)001:12506: rin chen rigs kyi dngos grub thob bdun pa +aam las byung ba'i rak+ta /
NK021(zha)001:12507: gsang ba'i dbang gi rdzas mchog rak+ta 'di //
NK021(zha)001:12508: chags med bde bar spyad pas dmar la dwangs //
NK021(zha)001:12509: skal ldan rnal 'byor pad+ma rigs kyi pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na na mo /
NK021(zha)001:12510: phyogs bcu skal ldan rak+ta'i dbang bskur bas so sor
NK021(zha)001:12511: rtog pa'i ye shes dang ldan te pad+ma'i rigs kyi
NK021(zha)001:12512: dngos grub brgyad pa ha las byung ba'i dri chu
NK021(zha)001:12513: / rang byung dag pa las mchog rigs kyi rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:12514: phyi nang gsos gyur bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:12515: skal ldan rnal 'byor las kyi rigs kyi sid+d+hi thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12516: kri t+ya nush+th+aa na dz+ny+aa na +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK021(zha)001:12518: phyogs bcu dus skal ldan dri chu'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:12519: bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes dang ldan te
NK021(zha)001:12520: / las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12521: dgu pa h+aum a las byung ba'i rdor dril /
NK021(zha)001:12522: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med pa //
NK021(zha)001:12523: thugs mchog rtogs pa rig pa'i rgyan //
NK021(zha)001:12524: rdo rje dril bus dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12525: thabs dang shes rab dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12526: badz+ra g+han+de sha ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12528: phyogs bcu skal ldan rdo rje dril bu'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:12529: bas sku dang ye shes ldan pa'i chos la longs
NK021(zha)001:12531: bcu pa h+aum las byung ba'i phur bu /
NK021(zha)001:12532: dpal chen yab yum thugs ka nas //
NK021(zha)001:12533: mthar byed bgegs rnams tshar gcod mtshon char ldan //
NK021(zha)001:12534: rdo rje k+ai la ya yi dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12535: log 'dren dgra bgegs tshogs rnams 'joms par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12536: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya +aa be sha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12538: phyogs bcu dus skal ldan phur bu'i dbang bskur bas
NK021(zha)001:12539: ya ma dam sri'i bar gcod sgrol ba'i dbang dam
NK021(zha)001:12540: pa bcu gcig pa dpal bo 'bru lnga las byung
NK021(zha)001:12541: ba'i bdud rtsi ra sa ya na /
NK021(zha)001:12542: thams cad sman yin bdud rtsi mchog /
NK021(zha)001:12543: rgyal ba kun gyis sgrub pa'i lam //
NK021(zha)001:12544: ra sa ya nas dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12545: bdud rtsi'i bcud dang 'phrad par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12546: sarba a mri t+ya shwa ra s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12548: phyogs bcu skal ldan bdud rtsi'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12549: skye shi med pa'i sku thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12550: bcu gnyis pa tram las byung ba'i phreng ba /
NK021(zha)001:12551: phreng ba mya ngan 'das pa'i chos la spyod //
NK021(zha)001:12552: 'gro kun yang dag chos kyi don la 'jug /
NK021(zha)001:12553: me tog phreng ba la sogs dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12554: gzungs dang ting 'dzin ldan pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12555: rat+na m+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12557: phyogs bcu skal ldan me tog phreng ba'i dbang bskur
NK021(zha)001:12558: bas gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur
NK021(zha)001:12559: cig / bcu gsum pa h+aum las byung ba'i yungs kar /
NK021(zha)001:12560: yungs kar rgyal po byin rlabs sha ri ram //
NK021(zha)001:12561: bar gcod bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms grub rdzas 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:12562: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12563: bar gcod bgegs rnams rdul du rlog par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12565: phyogs bcu skal ldan yungs kar gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12566: sprul pa 'gyed pa dang dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12567: bcu bzhi pa h+aum las byung ba'i mar me /
NK021(zha)001:12568: dpal chen yab yum gsang ba'i thugs bsdus pas //
NK021(zha)001:12569: skye med dbyings nas ye shes mar me gsal //
NK021(zha)001:12570: kun gzhi gnas gyur spyan gyi ye shes 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:12571: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:12572: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na +aa lo ke sha ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12574: phyogs bcu skal ldan mar me'i dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12575: dpal chen po'i thugs ye shes dgu dang ldan pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12576: bco lnga pa h+aum las byung ba'i rnge'u chung /
NK021(zha)001:12577: shes rab gsang ba'i rnga mchog 'di /
NK021(zha)001:12578: khams gsum kun tu chos sgra sgrog /
NK021(zha)001:12579: nga rgyal drag shul bdud 'joms pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12580: phyag mtshan 'di yi dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:12581: pradz+ny+aa tsa ma ra sha ri s+w+aa h+aa /
NK021(zha)001:12583: phyogs bcu skal ldan rnge'u chung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12584: chos sku skye ba med pa'i sgra bsgrags pas bdud dang srin po zil gyis mnan te /
NK021(zha)001:12585: ma mo dang d+aa ki dbang du sdud pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:12586: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i sgrub rdzas rol pa'i chas bcu las /
NK021(zha)001:12587: dang po stag sham gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12588: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK021(zha)001:12589: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK021(zha)001:12590: stag lpags sham thabs dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12591: bdud dang srin po kun bsgral nas //
NK021(zha)001:12592: ma tshogs mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdus /
NK021(zha)001:12593: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK021(zha)001:12594: stag gi sham thabs gsol ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:12595: dpa' bo bdud las rgyal ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:12596: rnam rtog 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12597: b+y+aa g+h+ri tsarma a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12598: gnyis pa glang chen ko rlon /
NK021(zha)001:12599: sngon tshe dpal chen phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas glang chen
NK021(zha)001:12600: ko rlon dbang gti mug gnas su dag pa dang
NK021(zha)001:12601: / khams gsum bdag por gyur pa ltar //
NK021(zha)001:12602: de ring rnal 'byor bu khyod la //
NK021(zha)001:12603: glang chen ko rlon dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12604: gti mug gnas su dag gyur nas //
NK021(zha)001:12605: bdud dpung chen po 'joms par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12606: hasti tsarma a b+hi gsum pa zhing gi g.yang gzhi /
NK021(zha)001:12607: sngon tshe bdud srin la sogs pas //
NK021(zha)001:12608: bcom ldan sku la bsdos pa'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12609: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK021(zha)001:12610: zhing gi g.yang gzhi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12611: bdud dang srin po btul pa ltar //
NK021(zha)001:12612: 'khor ba rdul du rlog pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:12613: de ring rdo rje'i slob bu la //
NK021(zha)001:12614: zhing gi g.yang gzhi'i dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12615: bdud dang srin po la sogs pa //
NK021(zha)001:12616: thams cad 'joms pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12617: na ra tsarma a b+hi bzhi pa thod phreng /
NK021(zha)001:12618: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK021(zha)001:12619: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK021(zha)001:12620: thod pa skam rlon ra ri yi //
NK021(zha)001:12621: thod phreng tshar gsum mnga' gsol bas //
NK021(zha)001:12622: sa gsum non nas sku gsum grub //
NK021(zha)001:12623: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK021(zha)001:12624: thod phreng tshar gsum dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12625: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:12626: dug gsum gnas su dag nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:12627: thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12628: ka p+aa la m+aa la a b+hi lnga pa sprul chun /
NK021(zha)001:12629: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK021(zha)001:12630: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK021(zha)001:12631: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12632: thugs rjes zhe sdang gnas su dag /
NK021(zha)001:12633: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK021(zha)001:12634: sbrul gyi chun pos dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12635: klu bdud srin po kun bcom nas //
NK021(zha)001:12636: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12637: n+aa ga d+aa ma a b+hi drug pa khyung gshog /
NK021(zha)001:12638: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kar //
NK021(zha)001:12639: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK021(zha)001:12640: rdo rje'i gshog pas dbang bdud dang srin po zil gyis non //
NK021(zha)001:12641: de bzhin skal ldan bu khyod la //
NK021(zha)001:12642: rdo rje'i khyung gshog dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12643: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bar shog /
NK021(zha)001:12644: badz+ra pak+sha a b+hi bdun pa me dpung /
NK021(zha)001:12646: 'bar zhing 'phro ba ye shes thugs rjer ldan //
NK021(zha)001:12647: ye shes gsal bas phyogs bcu'i mun nag sel //
NK021(zha)001:12648: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12649: mtshan ma'i 'dzin rtog sreg pa'i dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12650: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na dz+wa la ram h+aum a b+hi brgyad
NK021(zha)001:12651: pa gdong gi 'bur bzhir khrag gi thig le gdab
NK021(zha)001:12653: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK021(zha)001:12654: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK021(zha)001:12655: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK021(zha)001:12656: dmar gyi ar+g+ha rgya mtshor skyil //
NK021(zha)001:12657: khrag gi thig les mtshan pa ni //
NK021(zha)001:12658: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig la //
NK021(zha)001:12659: 'di yang rtags kyi phyag rgya ste //
NK021(zha)001:12660: 'dod chags gnas su dag pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12661: khrag gi thig les rtags mtshan nas //
NK021(zha)001:12662: khrag gi thig le'i dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12663: gtum po drag po 'joms pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:12664: nga rgyal dregs pa 'dul mdzad cing //
NK021(zha)001:12665: dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12666: ma h+aa rak+ta ti la ka h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12667: dgu pa mgrin par zhag gi zo ris zla gam du gdab cing /
NK021(zha)001:12669: he ru ka yi gnas dur khrod chen po'i gnas
NK021(zha)001:12670: zhing chen gsar rnying dmar gyi ar+g+ha rgya zhag gi
NK021(zha)001:12672: 'di yang sngon gyi dam 'di yang rtags kyi phyag chos nyid zhag gis brgyan pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12673: zhag gi tshom bu'i dbang bskur bas //
NK021(zha)001:12674: chos nyid dbyings su rgyal ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:12675: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:12676: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12677: chos nyid zhag gi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:12678: pa ta pa ga ta h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12679: bcu pa dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu rtse gsum pa'i dbyibs su gdab cing /
NK021(zha)001:12681: he ru ka yi gnas dur khrod chen po'i zhing
NK021(zha)001:12682: chen gsar rnying dmar gyi ar+g+ha thal ba'i mtshan mas
NK021(zha)001:12683: brgyan pa ni // gdug pa ma lus rab 'dul ba //
NK021(zha)001:12684: che ba'i rgyal po kun gyi bdag /
NK021(zha)001:12685: thams cad kun tu dpa' bo'i mtshan //
NK021(zha)001:12686: gdug pa zil gnon thal ba'i mtshan //
NK021(zha)001:12687: dbang mchog 'di yi dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12688: khams gsum gdug pa thal bar rlog /
NK021(zha)001:12689: de 'dra'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK021(zha)001:12691: gsum pa khyad par gyi sgrub rdzas la /
NK021(zha)001:12694: dang po 'das ma 'das kyi dngos grub thams cad sgrub pa'i rdzas spyir byin pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:12699: bkra shis gtsang ma dang dag pa lha'i rdzas kyi bam /
NK021(zha)001:12711: bgrang phreng ste sgrub rdzas thams cad gtad la /
NK021(zha)001:12712: sgrub pa'i rgyal po khyod la ni //
NK021(zha)001:12713: sgrub pa'i las la dbang thob phyir //
NK021(zha)001:12714: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12715: rgyal ba thams cad sgrub pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:12716: rdo rje tshe dang sman la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12717: sgrub pa ma lus sgrubs shig ces //
NK021(zha)001:12718: sgrub rdzas thams cad byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12719: sarba sid+d+hi a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12720: gnyis pa bye brag gi sgrub rdzas ni /
NK021(zha)001:12722: yang dag dur khrod brdal dang phur bu rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:12723: bdud rtsi pho brang bde chen dbang bskur ro //
NK021(zha)001:12724: zhes pa tsam las mi 'byung yang /
NK021(zha)001:12725: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che'i gsung las /
NK021(zha)001:12726: ban chung sangs rgyas ye shes kyis //
NK021(zha)001:12727: pan+di ta yi thugs mdzod bsdus //
NK021(zha)001:12728: rgya bod mkhas pa'i dgongs pa dril //
NK021(zha)001:12730: theg pa 'dus dang dbang bsdus dang //
NK021(zha)001:12733: yang dag thugs dang bdud rtsi phur //
NK021(zha)001:12734: ma mo mchod bstod drag sngags rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12735: cha rkyen yin phyir rig 'dzin brgyad //
NK021(zha)001:12736: tshe ni spyi yi kha skong yin //
NK021(zha)001:12737: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs skrod //
NK021(zha)001:12738: rdzas skongs mar me bdud rtsi sman //
NK021(zha)001:12739: mtshams phur gdab kha bsnyen phur rten //
NK021(zha)001:12740: dmar chen rak+tasa thugs dam skongs //
NK021(zha)001:12741: 'jig rten mchod rten drag zor gtod //
NK021(zha)001:12742: rig 'dzin gtor phud tshe zan rdzas //
NK021(zha)001:12743: zhes sgrub sde brgyad ka gsungs pa ltar /
NK021(zha)001:12744: dang po phyi'i sgo byang lhor bkod pa gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12746: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK021(zha)001:12747: mngags gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:12748: 'jam dpal gshin rje gshed po yis //
NK021(zha)001:12749: dgra bgegs sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK021(zha)001:12751: rgya gar dur khrod 'jigs byed tshal chen du //
NK021(zha)001:12752: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12753: rdo rje grub pa rtsal te rig 'dzin gtso //
NK021(zha)001:12754: 'jam dpal sku yi dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12755: 'dir gshegs skal ldan byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK021(zha)001:12756: rgya gar gnas dang sgrags kyi yang rdzong du //
NK021(zha)001:12757: yi dam dpal chen dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12758: yi dam ya m+aan+ta k+aa'i zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12759: lo chen bee ro tsa na srung ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:12760: gnubs chen sangs rgyas ye shes gsang ba'i mtshan //
NK021(zha)001:12761: rdo rje drag po rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12762: 'jam dpal sku yi dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12763: 'dir gshegs skal ldan a kro te ka ya m+aan+ta
NK021(zha)001:12764: ka ha na ma tha b+hany+dza h+aum phata a b+hi
NK021(zha)001:12765: shiny+tsa h+aum / gnyis pa nang gi sgo byang nub tu bkod pa gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12767: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK021(zha)001:12768: mngags gzhug pho nya'i spyan ras gzigs dbang rta mgrin gyis //
NK021(zha)001:12769: gdon bgegs sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK021(zha)001:12771: rgya gar pad+ma brtsegs pa'i dur khrod nas //
NK021(zha)001:12772: slob dpon n+aa gardzu na'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12773: rdo rje grub pa rtsal te rig 'dzin mchog /
NK021(zha)001:12774: pad+ma gsung gi dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12775: 'dir gshegs skal ldan bsam yas mchims phu dpal gyi yang dben du //
NK021(zha)001:12776: zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12777: pad+ma dbang chen dkyil 'khor zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12778: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12779: rdo rje pad+ma rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12780: pad+ma gsung gi dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12781: 'dir gshegs skal ldan h+r+aihpad+man+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha
NK021(zha)001:12782: ya g+r+ai wa hu lu hu lu h+aum phata a
NK021(zha)001:12783: b+hi gsum pa shar gyi mar me gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12785: dus gsum sangs rgyas mngags gzhug pho nya'i dpal chen yang dag he ru kas //
NK021(zha)001:12786: ye shes rtogs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK021(zha)001:12788: rgya gar yul gyi h+aum sgrog dur khrod du //
NK021(zha)001:12789: slob dpon rdo rje h+aum mdzad gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12790: rdo rje dngos grub rtsal te rig 'dzin gtso //
NK021(zha)001:12791: yang dag thugs kyi dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12793: lho brag mkhar chu dpal gyi phug ring du //
NK021(zha)001:12794: mar me dgu yi dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12795: yi dam dpal chen 'khor bcas zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12796: slob dpon nam mkha'i snying po'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12797: rdo rje thog 'bebs rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12798: yang dag thugs kyi dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12799: 'dir gshegs ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum a
NK021(zha)001:12800: b+hi bzhi pa pho brang dbus kyi sman gyi thod
NK021(zha)001:12801: pa'am de khyer mi bde na sman phud gtod cing
NK021(zha)001:12803: dus gsum sangs rgyas mngags gzhug kun bzang che mchog bdud rtsi yis //
NK021(zha)001:12804: nad sel sman gyi dngos grub stsol //
NK021(zha)001:12806: bdud rtsi rol pa'i dur khrod rtsal chen du //
NK021(zha)001:12807: slob dpon bi ma mi tra'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12808: rdo rje mi 'gyur rtsal te rig 'dzin gtso //
NK021(zha)001:12809: bdud rtsi yon tan dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12811: yar klungs ra mo sman sgang shel brag tu //
NK021(zha)001:12812: bdud rtsi sman gyi dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12813: sman gyi lha srung rig 'dzin zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12814: gnyags lo ye shes gzhon nu'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12815: dri med zla shar rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12816: bdud rtsi yon tan dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12817: 'dir gshegs skal ldan +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta
NK021(zha)001:12818: h+aum h+r+aihth+aa a b+hi lnga pa byang gi bsnyen phur
NK021(zha)001:12819: dang khro bcu'i mtshams phur gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12821: dus gsum mngags gzhug rdo rje gzhon nu gtso 'khor gyis //
NK021(zha)001:12822: dam sri'i phung sbyor rgyun chod cig /
NK021(zha)001:12824: dregs pa 'dul ba'i dur khrod rtsal chen du //
NK021(zha)001:12825: slob dpon pra b+ha ha sti'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12826: rdo rje drag po rtsal te rig 'dzin gtso //
NK021(zha)001:12827: phur pa phrin las dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12829: brag dkar seng ge rdzong gi phug pa ru //
NK021(zha)001:12830: gru gsum shel gyi dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12831: mkhar chen ye shes mtsho rgyal gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12832: rdo rje lcam gcig ma ste rig 'dzin gtso //
NK021(zha)001:12833: phur pa grub pas brag la phur bu btab //
NK021(zha)001:12834: mkhar mi'i mdze gdon rgyun yang gcod par mdzad //
NK021(zha)001:12835: ming po mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug kyang //
NK021(zha)001:12836: rdo rje drag po rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12837: phur pa phrin las dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12838: 'dir gshegs badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba bi
NK021(zha)001:12839: g+h+n+aam bam h+aum phata a b+hi drug pa shar lho'i
NK021(zha)001:12842: dus gsum sangs rgyas mngags gzhug mngon rdzogs rgyal po yab yum gyis //
NK021(zha)001:12843: chag nyams bgegs sol dngos grub stsol //
NK021(zha)001:12845: rgya gar dur khrod sna tshogs pad+ma'i gling //
NK021(zha)001:12846: slob dpon d+ha na samskri ta'i gsang mtshan //
NK021(zha)001:12847: rdo rje dbang phyug rtsal te rig 'dzin gtso //
NK021(zha)001:12848: ma mo rbod gtong dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12850: yar klungs sham po gangs kyi gnas mchog tu //
NK021(zha)001:12851: ma mo'i rgyud lung dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12852: ma mo'i zhal gzigs 'o bran dpal gzhon nu //
NK021(zha)001:12853: gsang mtshan rdo rje 'phrul rgod rtsal dang ni //
NK021(zha)001:12854: ma mo'i bka' babs rtsa rlung dbang bsgyur nas //
NK021(zha)001:12855: mi brjed gzungs thob 'brog mi dpal ye sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12856: mkha' dbyings ma mo'i dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12857: 'dir gshegs sh+r+ai he ru ka yum kro d+h+ai shwa
NK021(zha)001:12858: r+ai s+t+wam h+aum ha he phata ma ma yo gi
NK021(zha)001:12860: a b+hi bdun pa nub byang gi chos skyong spyi gtor dang sman phud gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12862: dus gsum mngags gzhug gsang bdag dregs pa kun 'dul gyis //
NK021(zha)001:12863: chos bsrung ma g.yel stongs grogs mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:12865: rgya gar dur khrod 'dam bu'i tshal chen du //
NK021(zha)001:12866: ram bu gu h+ya de ba tsan+d+ra yi //
NK021(zha)001:12867: gsang mtshan rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal du grags //
NK021(zha)001:12868: 'jig rten mchod bstod grub pa brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12870: spa gro stag tshang seng ge'i brag phug tu //
NK021(zha)001:12871: dregs pa kun 'dul dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12872: bcom ldan dpal chen dregs pa'i zhal gzigs pa //
NK021(zha)001:12873: slob dpon dpal gyi seng ge'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12874: rdo rje drag po rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12875: 'jig rten mchod bstod dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12876: 'dir gshegs skal ldan badz+ra tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha
NK021(zha)001:12877: na h+aum phata a b+hi brgyad pa byang shar gyi
NK021(zha)001:12883: dus gsum mngags gzhug stobs ldan sgrol ging khro bo yi //
NK021(zha)001:12884: phrin las mthar phyin grub par mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:12886: rgya gar dur khrod ro yi tshal chen du //
NK021(zha)001:12887: 'phung byed slob dpon sh+aan+tinga gar+b+ha yi //
NK021(zha)001:12888: gsang mtshan rdo rje gshog rgod rtsal zhes bya //
NK021(zha)001:12889: dmod pa drag sngags dngos grub brnyes pa'i rje //
NK021(zha)001:12891: brag dmar g.ya' ma lung gi dben gnas su //
NK021(zha)001:12892: stobs ldan dregs pa'i dkyil 'khor zhal phye tshe //
NK021(zha)001:12893: dpal chen stobs ldan nag po zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12894: pa gor bee ro tsa na'i gsang mtshan ni //
NK021(zha)001:12895: rdo rje grub pa rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12896: dmod pa drag sngags dngos grub brnyes pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12897: 'dir gshegs skal ldan badz+ra sarba dush+tam h+aum phata a
NK021(zha)001:12898: b+hi dgu pa shar lho'i rig 'dzin spyi gtor dang
NK021(zha)001:12901: bdun pa sems pa rigs chen 'byed pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:12902: dbugs 'byin lung thob rtsal chen rdzogs pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:12903: rnal 'byor sar bzhugs rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:12905: ma h+aa gu ru pad+ma 'byung gnas kyi //
NK021(zha)001:12906: gsang mtshan rdo rje thod phreng rtsal du grags //
NK021(zha)001:12907: rgyal ba'i rgyal tshab srid gsum zil gyis gnon /
NK021(zha)001:12908: khams gsum gdul bya kun 'dul spyi dpal rje //
NK021(zha)001:12909: 'dir gshegs mnga' bdag chos rgyal khri srong lde'u btsan gyi //
NK021(zha)001:12910: gsang mtshan dbang chen 'jam dpal rtsal du grags //
NK021(zha)001:12911: mu khri sad na legs dang khri ral sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12912: rgyal sras sprul pa gdung rab 'khor dang bcas //
NK021(zha)001:12913: 'dir gshegs skal ldan bo d+hi sat+wa zhi 'tsho'i gsang ba'i mtshan //
NK021(zha)001:12914: rdo rje nyi 'od rtsal te de la sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12915: gsang sngags phyi rgyud thub pa'i rgyud rnams dang //
NK021(zha)001:12916: dzi na mi tra rdo rje sems rtsal sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12917: mtshan nyid theg pa che chung bla brgyad rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12918: 'dir gshegs tsha ba rong gi rgyal po'i sgrub khang du //
NK021(zha)001:12919: rgya bod mkhas grub thugs kyi bcud 'chang zhing //
NK021(zha)001:12920: yi dam tshogs chen rnams kyi zhal gzigs pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12921: g.yu sgra snying po rdo rje bde rgod rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12922: 'dir gshegs chu bo bzhi 'dus gnyags lo ye shes gzhon //
NK021(zha)001:12923: gsang mtshan thig le rtsal rgod rtsal du grags //
NK021(zha)001:12924: sog po dpal ye rdo rje bzhad pa'i gter //
NK021(zha)001:12925: zhang ston rgyal yon dam tshig mthar phyin rtsal //
NK021(zha)001:12926: dar rje dpal grags yang dag grub rtsal sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12927: bshad sgrub bka' srol byin rlabs brgyud ldan rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12928: 'dir gshegs skal ldan e ma hoh nags tshal me tog lha bya'i skad snyan tshal //
NK021(zha)001:12929: phar phyin slob dpon chen po king+ka ra //
NK021(zha)001:12930: kri ya'i slob dpon klu sgrub tsan+di ka /
NK021(zha)001:12931: yo ga'i slob dpon pad+ma ku ma ti //
NK021(zha)001:12932: slob dpon ro langs bde ba'i slob dpon te //
NK021(zha)001:12933: yo ga la sogs phyi dbang brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK021(zha)001:12934: lha mi yan chad dbang bskur slob dpon dang //
NK021(zha)001:12935: rgyud lung man ngag theg dgu'i bla ma rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12936: 'dir gshegs bka' lung ma nor rnal 'byor dbang phyug ni //
NK021(zha)001:12937: rig 'dzin brgya dang rtsa brgyad dbang bskur 'dis //
NK021(zha)001:12938: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang sgrub bshad lung gi //
NK021(zha)001:12939: byin rlabs brgyud par ldan pa'i bla ma rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12940: 'di gshegs skal ldan ma h+aa gu ru sha ri
NK021(zha)001:12941: ram g+ai li h+aum a b+hi bcu pa shar gyi
NK021(zha)001:12942: tshe 'brang dang tshe chang thogs te /
NK021(zha)001:12944: bcom ldan 'das mgon po ye shes tshe dpag med //
NK021(zha)001:12945: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:12946: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku gsung thugs mnga' bas //
NK021(zha)001:12947: mi shigs rdo rje gsum gyi dngos grub stsol //
NK021(zha)001:12949: rgya gar a su ra yi brag phug tu //
NK021(zha)001:12950: slob dpon ku ku r+aa dzas tshe dbang grub //
NK021(zha)001:12951: tshom bu 'bum bcas rdo rje 'chang sar gshegs //
NK021(zha)001:12952: 'dir gshegs skal ldan pad+ma thod phreng bi ma mi tra sogs //
NK021(zha)001:12953: 'chi med dwangs ma'i 'od lus sku brnyes pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:12954: rtsa ba brgyud pa'i bla ma grub thob rnams //
NK021(zha)001:12955: 'dir gshegs skal ldan byin rlabs dngos grub stsol //
NK021(zha)001:12956: b+h+r+aum badz+ra +aa yu she h+aum ah a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12959: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig sgrub rdzas thams cad kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:12960: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i dngos grub
NK021(zha)001:12961: thams cad sgrub pa'i dbang dam pa bcu gsum pa
NK021(zha)001:12962: sangs rgyas dang tha mi dad pa'i rtags ming gi
NK021(zha)001:12963: dbang ni / rdo rje bdud 'dul rtsal /
NK021(zha)001:12964: rdo rje gzi 'bar rtsal lta bu rdo rjee dang rtsal gyi bar du khyung chen gshog rgod /
NK021(zha)001:12982: myu gu sogs bcug pa btags la /
NK021(zha)001:12983: ming de nyid slob dpon dang lhan cig tu nam
NK021(zha)001:12984: mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis kyang
NK021(zha)001:12985: btags pa'i mos pa byed du bcug la /
NK021(zha)001:12986: rdo rje lag tu gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:12987: rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK021(zha)001:12988: dbang thob denyida gcig pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:12989: rig 'dzin rdo rje rtsal gyi dbang //
NK021(zha)001:12990: rdo rje ming ni byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:12991: de ba a dwa ya a b+hi shi ny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:12993: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la
NK021(zha)001:12994: rdo rje che ge rtsal zhes pa ming gi dbang
NK021(zha)001:12995: bskur bas lha dang gnyis su med par grags pa
NK021(zha)001:12996: rdo rje ming gi dbang dam pa thob par gyur
NK021(zha)001:12997: cig / ces dril bus sna drangs pa'i rol mo'i sgra sbyar ro //
NK021(zha)001:12998: de rnams kyis ni sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo
NK021(zha)001:12999: zhes bya ba dngos grub sgrub byed thabs kyi spyod
NK021(zha)001:13000: pa'i dbang khyad par can thob /
NK021(zha)001:13001: a nu yo ga'i theg pa rang lugs kyis spangs
NK021(zha)001:13002: thob kyi rigs su gnas pa'i yon tan gyi sa
NK021(zha)001:13003: bon thebs pas / rang 'bras gsang dbang bskur rung du smin /
NK021(zha)001:13004: gtso bor las sgrib dang lus kyi dri ma phra ba 'khrud /
NK021(zha)001:13005: dmigs med kun gsal gyi ye shes thob pas bag
NK021(zha)001:13006: la nyal 'bring po dag ste gnas pa byang chub
NK021(zha)001:13007: kyi sems skye ba'i rgyu sgrubs /
NK021(zha)001:13008: gsang ba'i theg pa a nu rang lugs kyi dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs zab mo'i bskyed rim dang /
NK021(zha)001:13009: de dang thun mong ba zhu bde sgrub pa'i rdzogs rim rnams nyan bshad sgrub pa la dbang /
NK021(zha)001:13010: rnal 'byor bzhi las a nu yo ga dang /
NK021(zha)001:13011: mthar thug slob lam dgu pa brdal ba chos nyid
NK021(zha)001:13012: kyi sa non pa mthar lam gnyis pa bde ba
NK021(zha)001:13013: chen po'i rnal 'byor dang mi slob lam sku rdo
NK021(zha)001:13014: rje mngon du byed pa'i skal ba can du byas
NK021(zha)001:13015: so // bzhi pa gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo ni /
NK021(zha)001:13017: sgrub pa'i dbang mchog thob pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:13018: gsang ba'i bdag po yin pas na //
NK021(zha)001:13019: gsang ba'i dbang mchog byin par bya //
NK021(zha)001:13020: zhes pas sgrub dbang song nas /
NK021(zha)001:13021: da gsang ba'i dbang zhu ba'i yon du man+dala 'bul du bcug nas /
NK021(zha)001:13022: phyag sngon du 'gro bas thal mo sbyar te gsol
NK021(zha)001:13023: ba gdab pa 'di'i dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag
NK021(zha)001:13024: nyid // rdo rje bla ma bdag la dgongs //
NK021(zha)001:13026: de ring mngon du gyur par mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:13027: ces lan gsum gyis gsol ba btab nas /
NK021(zha)001:13028: bskur bya rdzogs pa'i chu bo la gnyis kyi /
NK021(zha)001:13029: dang po kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi dbang lus la bskur ba la'ang gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:13031: bla ma he ru ka yab yum snyoms par zhugs
NK021(zha)001:13032: pa'i nyi zla byang chub kyi sems lce thog tu
NK021(zha)001:13033: bzhag pa snying gar babs pas /
NK021(zha)001:13034: las dang bag chags kyi rtogs pa sbyangs te /
NK021(zha)001:13035: sems gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i rang bzhin
NK021(zha)001:13036: don dam spros med kyi ye shes nyams su myong
NK021(zha)001:13038: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK021(zha)001:13039: kun tu tshim par byed pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:13040: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK021(zha)001:13041: dbang thob khyod kyi lce la bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:13042: a ho ma h+aa su kha hoh zhes bdud rtsi myong du bcug go //
NK021(zha)001:13044: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:13045: khyod la gsang ba'i dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:13046: sgrib pa gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK021(zha)001:13047: shes kyi dbyings su dag pa'i dbang dam pa gnyis
NK021(zha)001:13048: pa shes rab ye shes ni /
NK021(zha)001:13049: bla mas gtad pa'i rig ma dang snyoms par zhugs
NK021(zha)001:13050: pas sems nyid don dam 'od gsal du dwangs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:13051: rtsal snang bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyi rol
NK021(zha)001:13053: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang mtshon byed chos 'byung gi
NK021(zha)001:13054: dbus su pad 'dab brgyad rdo rjes mtshan pa gtad
NK021(zha)001:13056: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi dbang //
NK021(zha)001:13057: dbang thob khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK021(zha)001:13058: don dam kun rdzob lhan cig skyes //
NK021(zha)001:13059: rang byung ye shes chen por shog /
NK021(zha)001:13060: a ho ma h+aa su kha hoh na mo /
NK021(zha)001:13061: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig shes rab ye shes kyi
NK021(zha)001:13062: dbang bskur bas shes sgrib lus bde stong rnam par
NK021(zha)001:13063: mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi dbyings su grol ba'i
NK021(zha)001:13064: dbang dam pa gnyis pa don dam byang sems kyi
NK021(zha)001:13065: dbang sems la bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:13066: shes rab ma las byung ba'i bde stong sgyu ma lta bu des mtshon te /
NK021(zha)001:13067: de ga'i rang ngo la bltas pas /
NK021(zha)001:13068: dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i rang bzhin /
NK021(zha)001:13069: brjod bral lhan cig skyes pa'i de kho na nyid /
NK021(zha)001:13070: sku dang ye shes zung du 'jug pa ni bde ba chen po'i dbang gi ngo bo yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:13071: de ka'i ngang bskyang du bcug la /
NK021(zha)001:13072: hoh gsang ba shes rab ye shes dang //
NK021(zha)001:13073: dbyer med bde ba chen po'i dbang //
NK021(zha)001:13074: btsal med byang chub sems chen po //
NK021(zha)001:13075: shes rab chen po'i rtsal gyis ni //
NK021(zha)001:13076: chos kun sgyu mar dbang bsgyur nas //
NK021(zha)001:13077: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i dbang yin pas //
NK021(zha)001:13078: rdzas dang tshig dang gang zag dang //
NK021(zha)001:13079: kun rdzob dbang de ma thob kyang //
NK021(zha)001:13080: chos la sems kyi dbang thob na //
NK021(zha)001:13081: rgyal ba rig 'dzin thams cad dang //
NK021(zha)001:13082: srid gsum dbang btsan thams cad kun //
NK021(zha)001:13083: de la dbang mchog bskur bar 'gyur //
NK021(zha)001:13084: a ho ma h+aa su kha hoh na mo /
NK021(zha)001:13085: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa
NK021(zha)001:13086: khyod la rig pa rtsal gyi dbang bskur bas 'pho
NK021(zha)001:13087: ba'i bag chags kyi sgrib pa nyid zung 'jug lhan
NK021(zha)001:13088: cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi dbyings su grol ba'i
NK021(zha)001:13089: dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:13090: de rnams kyis ni gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bor
NK021(zha)001:13091: grags pa kun rdzob dang don dam byang sems kyi
NK021(zha)001:13093: a ti yo gas spangs thob kyi yon tan dang
NK021(zha)001:13094: rigs 'dra'i a nu rang lugs kyi rdzogs rim mthar
NK021(zha)001:13095: thug zung 'jug gi ye shes skye rung gi nus
NK021(zha)001:13097: mchog dbang de gsum gyis gtso bor nyon sgrib //
NK021(zha)001:13099: bag chags kyi sgrib pa gsum dang /
NK021(zha)001:13100: ngag yid 'pho ba'i thig le gsum gyi dri ma 'khrud /
NK021(zha)001:13101: dmigs med kun gsal gyi ye shes brtan pas bag
NK021(zha)001:13102: la nyal phra mo sbyangs te 'bras bu la skad
NK021(zha)001:13103: cig gis sbyor ba'i rdzogs pa byang chub kyi sems
NK021(zha)001:13105: a nu rang lugs kyi zab mo'i rdzogs rim rnams nyan bshad sgrub pa la dbang /
NK021(zha)001:13106: rnal 'byor bzhi las a ti yo ga dang /
NK021(zha)001:13107: mthar thug slob lam bcu pa rdzogs pa cir chib
NK021(zha)001:13108: kyi sa non pa mthar lam gsum pa lhun gyis
NK021(zha)001:13109: grub pa'i rnal 'byor dang mi slob lam sku gsung
NK021(zha)001:13110: thugs ye shes rdo rje mngon du byed pa'i skal
NK021(zha)001:13112: rjes kyi bya ba la spyi don gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:13115: gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid gdab pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:13116: spyi don dang po lam khyer la bzhi las /
NK021(zha)001:13117: dang po theg pa lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:13118: a nu yo ga'i theg pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:13121: gsang dbang rnams yan lag gi dkyil 'khor so sor phye ba la ltos nas gsungs pa ltar /
NK021(zha)001:13122: zab mo'i bskyed rdzogs rang gzhung ltar bkra ba a nu dang /
NK021(zha)001:13123: mi zab pa'i bskyed rim dang shin tu zab pa'i
NK021(zha)001:13124: rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa'i cha rnams gong 'og
NK021(zha)001:13125: gi theg pa ma h+aa dang a ti gnyis dang
NK021(zha)001:13127: bskyed rdzogs gsum du phye ba las /
NK021(zha)001:13128: 'dir ma h+aa dang a nu gnyis 'chad par bya ste /
NK021(zha)001:13129: dang po ma h+aa yo ga la'ang drug las /
NK021(zha)001:13131: shes rab stong pa chen po dang /
NK021(zha)001:13132: thabs snying rje sgyu ma dang /
NK021(zha)001:13133: phyag rgya phra rags te ting nge 'dzin gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug /
NK021(zha)001:13135: lhag pa bden pa dbyer med spyod yul dang bral bar rtogs pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:13137: lhag pa'i mnyam nyid dbyer med don //
NK021(zha)001:13138: ming grangs cir yang bstan mod kyang //
NK021(zha)001:13139: don du smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK021(zha)001:13142: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig dang /
NK021(zha)001:13143: yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan lnga ste nyi
NK021(zha)001:13144: shu rtsa brgyad la sogs pa rnams bsrung zhing sgrub
NK021(zha)001:13147: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bos ting nge 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:13148: gsum gyi sgo nas ma dag pa'i snang ba dbyings
NK021(zha)001:13149: su sbyong ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo dang /
NK021(zha)001:13150: rdo rje'i lus la gnad du bsnun pa'i rdzogs rim sgom /
NK021(zha)001:13152: gtsang rme'i rtog pa ldog pa'i phyir blang dor med pa'i thabs kyis dam rdzas lnga sogs la spyod /
NK021(zha)001:13154: tshe 'adi'am bar dor lam gzhan la ma ltos par
NK021(zha)001:13155: pad+ma can gyi sa non te rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK021(zha)001:13156: kyi go 'phang mngon du byed pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:13157: gnyis pa a nu yo ga la'ang drug las /
NK021(zha)001:13159: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med kyi sgo nas 'jug /
NK021(zha)001:13161: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor rnam gsum dbyer med pa'i
NK021(zha)001:13162: rang bzhin rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:13163: du ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK021(zha)001:13165: thams cad de nyid der gcig pas //
NK021(zha)001:13166: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK021(zha)001:13167: skye 'gag med pa'i snying po yin //
NK021(zha)001:13168: bya byed med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK021(zha)001:13169: ye nas grub zin lhun gyis grub //
NK021(zha)001:13172: bsrung mtshams med pa chos nyid kyi dam tshig dang /
NK021(zha)001:13173: bsrung mtshams can snying rje'i dam tshig rnams bsrung zhing sgrub pa las mi 'da' bar sdom /
NK021(zha)001:13175: don gyi rjes su 'jug pa mtshan med rnam par mi rtog pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:13176: yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa mtshan bcas lha'i ting nge 'dzin sgom /
NK021(zha)001:13178: dbyings dang ye shes mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang nas spyod /
NK021(zha)001:13180: tshe gcig gis lam gzhan la ma ltos par yi
NK021(zha)001:13181: ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar mngon par rdzogs
NK021(zha)001:13183: gnyis pa lha lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:13184: 'dir nang dbang dang sgrub dbang gnyis dkyil 'khor gcig
NK021(zha)001:13185: tu bskur ba'i lugs la lha tha dad pa med
NK021(zha)001:13186: pas / rgyud lung 'dra bar sngar me tog gang la phog pa'i lha'am /
NK021(zha)001:13187: yang na dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dpal chen po
NK021(zha)001:13188: che mchog he ru ka nyid yi dam gyi lha
NK021(zha)001:13190: de yang rang sems dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med
NK021(zha)001:13191: nyid gdod nas lha yab yum zung 'jug gi ngo
NK021(zha)001:13192: bo yin pa la yin par shes pas /
NK021(zha)001:13193: snang ba thams cad lha dang lha mo'i rol par lam du khyer ro //
NK021(zha)001:13194: gsum pa snying po lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:13195: me tog phog pa'i lha'i snying po'am /
NK021(zha)001:13196: yang na spyi sngags gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na nyid bzla bya'i sngags su ngo sprad /
NK021(zha)001:13197: de yang sgrar grags thams cad grags stong gzhom med kyi sngags sgrar lam du khyer ro //
NK021(zha)001:13198: bzhi pa dbang lam khyer ni /
NK021(zha)001:13199: chu bo bzhis bsdus pa'i dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK021(zha)001:13200: de dang rjes su 'brel ba'i bslab bya spyi dang
NK021(zha)001:13201: khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams kyi bsrung mtshams
NK021(zha)001:13202: las mi 'da' ba la sogs pa ste /
NK021(zha)001:13203: mdo 'gag snang grags 'gyu gsum thams cad dbyings skye
NK021(zha)001:13204: ba med pa nyid cir yang ma 'gags pa'i ye
NK021(zha)001:13205: shes kyi rol rtsal du thag bcad nas /
NK021(zha)001:13206: snod bcud kyi snang ba thams cad rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK021(zha)001:13207: sgrar grags thams cad sngags kyi sgra gdangs /
NK021(zha)001:13208: dran rtogs thams cad chos nyid mnyam pa nyid du
NK021(zha)001:13209: blta zhing sgom pa'i spyod pa las mnyam rjes thams
NK021(zha)001:13210: cad du mi 'da' bas gang shar dag snang du
NK021(zha)001:13211: sbyong ba'i thabs la bslab cing /
NK021(zha)001:13212: de ston pa'i bla ma dam pa la dad gus
NK021(zha)001:13213: dang de ltar nyams su len pa'i mched rnams la
NK021(zha)001:13214: dung sems rgyun mi chad par bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:13215: spyi don gnyis pa 'gag drug bshad pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:13217: gang du gang gis gang la gang bstan pa //
NK021(zha)001:13218: ci yi phyir dang dgos pa ye gnas pa //
NK021(zha)001:13219: 'dir ni nang gi 'gag drug bstan pa yin //
NK021(zha)001:13220: zhes pa'i don sngon byung dang /
NK021(zha)001:13221: rjes 'jug gi dbang gnyis su sbyar te bshad na /
NK021(zha)001:13222: gang du bskur ba'i gnas ni /
NK021(zha)001:13223: sngon byung la spyir ye shes rang snang las grub pa'i rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK021(zha)001:13224: bye brag tshul bstan du chu bo bzhi'i gnas rim pa ji lta bar /
NK021(zha)001:13226: chu bo nee r+aany+dza na'i 'gram dang /
NK021(zha)001:13227: byang chub kyi shing drung dang /
NK021(zha)001:13228: dbang bsgyur gyi khang bzang rnams su bskur zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13229: rjes 'jug tu pad+ma me tog 'ja' tshon gyi tshal du'o //
NK021(zha)001:13230: gang gis bskur ba'i slob dpon ni /
NK021(zha)001:13231: sngon byung du spyir rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK021(zha)001:13232: bye brag tu sangs rgyas thams cad chos kyi rgyal po ltar bstan pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:13234: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba dpag med dang /
NK021(zha)001:13235: rnam snang dang thub dbang ste gzugs sku gnyis kyis bskur zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13236: rjes 'jug tu slob dpon chen po ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub kyis so //
NK021(zha)001:13237: gang la bskur ba'i slob ma ni /
NK021(zha)001:13238: sngon byung du spyir rgyu'i mi slob lam dang /
NK021(zha)001:13239: sngags rang lugs kyi mthar lam rgyun mthar gnas pa la /
NK021(zha)001:13240: bye brag tu dam pa tog dkar dang /
NK021(zha)001:13243: gsang bdag lag na rdo rje rnams la bskur zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13245: o rgyan gyi rgyal po d+harma k+aa ya dang /
NK021(zha)001:13248: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen sogs mngon shes lnga dang ldan pa rnams la'o //
NK021(zha)001:13252: bye brag tu dbu rgyan dang /
NK021(zha)001:13255: rdo rje pha lam lta bu'i rdzas rnams la brten nas chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13256: rjes 'jug tu phyi nang sgrub gsang bzhis bsdus pa'i dbang mchog sum cu rtsa drug go //
NK021(zha)001:13258: sngon byung du spyir mthar thug gi 'bras bu la sbyor ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:13260: rgyal tshab tu dbyung ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:13261: gzugs sku rnam snang du 'tshang rgya ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:13262: chos kyi sgron mar lung mngon par thob pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:13263: gsang ba'i snying po'i nges pa dus la bab pa'i phyir bskur zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13264: rjes 'jug tu mi lus lhar sgrub pa'i ched du ste /
NK021(zha)001:13265: rtog tshogs su snang ba'i chos can gang la'ang chos
NK021(zha)001:13266: nyid du song ba'i ye shes kyi lha nyid rtogs
NK021(zha)001:13267: goms kyi sbyor bas mngon du byed pa'i phyir bskur
NK021(zha)001:13268: bas so // de ltar bskur ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:13270: de'i rtags sngon byung du spyir rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'i dgos pa yod cing /
NK021(zha)001:13272: chos kyi rgyal tshab chen por mngon par snang ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:13273: longs spyod rdzogs pa nyid du gyur pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:13274: chos kyi mnga' bdag tu gyur pas chos 'khor bskor ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:13275: don zab mo mthar rdzogs pas gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:13276: cing ston pa'i nus pa mngon du snang ba'i dgos
NK021(zha)001:13278: dang por rgyud ma smin pa smin par bya ba dang /
NK021(zha)001:13279: bar dang tha mar tshogs sbyor gcig tu bsdus te slob lam bzhir bzhag nas /
NK021(zha)001:13280: de dang de la rim pa ji lta bar chu
NK021(zha)001:13281: bo bzhi bskur bas lam gong ma gong mas sbyor
NK021(zha)001:13282: ba'i sgo nas yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi
NK021(zha)001:13283: sa thob pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK021(zha)001:13284: spyi don gsum pa gdams ngag ngang sgom gyi khrid la gnyis te /
NK021(zha)001:13287: dang po lha sgom pa'i thabs ni /
NK021(zha)001:13289: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad bdag gi phung khams skye mched du 'du zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13290: de thams cad lha'i rang bzhin du ye nas sangs rgyas pa'o zhes dar cig mnyam par bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:13291: de'i ngang las me tog gang la phog pa'i lha'am
NK021(zha)001:13292: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo che mchog lta bu gang
NK021(zha)001:13294: rang gi bskyed sngags chos nyid kyi rang sgrar bsgrags
NK021(zha)001:13295: pa'i rkyen gyis dwangs pa'i mtsho la gzugs brnyan shar
NK021(zha)001:13296: ba ltar bkra lam gyis gsal btab nas lha'i snang
NK021(zha)001:13297: zhen la yun ring du bslab /
NK021(zha)001:13298: de gsal brtan du gyur pa na /
NK021(zha)001:13299: de'i spyi bor thig le dmar po dang /
NK021(zha)001:13300: de las khru gang tsam gyis mtho bar thig le dkar po ste /
NK021(zha)001:13301: gnyis ka sran ma tsam pa 'od 'bar ba zhig sgom /
NK021(zha)001:13302: de gsal ba dang sna bug g.yon nas 'od kyi thig le dmar po sran ma tsam zhig 'phros /
NK021(zha)001:13303: spyi bo'i thig le dmar po la phog pas /
NK021(zha)001:13304: de las kyang 'od zer mkha' khyab tu spros /
NK021(zha)001:13305: sangs rgyas mchod cing sems can gyi sdig sgrib sbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:13306: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba thams cad zhu ba 'od
NK021(zha)001:13307: dang 'grogs te tshur 'dus thig le dmar po la
NK021(zha)001:13308: thim pas / de yang 'od du zhu ste ltem me gnas par bsam /
NK021(zha)001:13309: yang sna bug g.yas nas 'od kyi thig le dkar po sran ma tsam zhig 'phros /
NK021(zha)001:13310: de'i steng gi thig le dkar po la phog pas /
NK021(zha)001:13311: de las 'od zer spros te don gnyis byas /
NK021(zha)001:13312: 'khor 'das zhu ba dang 'grogs te tshur 'dus pa thig le dkar po la thim pas /
NK021(zha)001:13314: thig le dkar po dmar po la zhugs pa tshangs
NK021(zha)001:13315: bug nas snying dkyil du bstim zhing bde stong gnyis
NK021(zha)001:13316: med kyi ngang la blo skyur te bzhag go //
NK021(zha)001:13317: gnyis pa man ngag sgom pa la gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:13318: dang po nang dbang dang 'brel ba ma h+aa yo ga dang thun mong ba'i sgom thabs ni /
NK021(zha)001:13322: rang lus stong chen sgrib thogs dang bral ba'i dbus
NK021(zha)001:13323: su rtsa a ba d+h+au ti mda' smyug 'bring po
NK021(zha)001:13324: tsam pa phyi dkar la nang dmar ba dwangs gsal
NK021(zha)001:13325: sbubs stong gi rnam pa can drang thal ler gnas
NK021(zha)001:13329: lte ba rnams su 'khor lo'i rtsa 'dab dngos su sgom pa'am /
NK021(zha)001:13331: dbu ma bsgom pas de 'khor lo bzhi ka'i lte ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:13332: don la bsgom par 'gyur ba yin /
NK021(zha)001:13333: lte 'og sor bzhi'i thad du me'i 'khor lo dang /
NK021(zha)001:13334: de'i 'og tu gshang kha rlung gi 'khor lo rnams kyang gsal btab /
NK021(zha)001:13335: de yang dbu ma srog shing /
NK021(zha)001:13341: lus mchod rten gyi ngo bor mos par bya /
NK021(zha)001:13342: de nas spyi bor mi shigs pa'i thig le ham
NK021(zha)001:13343: gi rang bzhin sran ma tsam pa zhig gsal btab
NK021(zha)001:13344: la / 'jam rlung rang babs su bzung bas /
NK021(zha)001:13345: gtum mo 'bar ba'i 'od gyen du song ba spyi bo'i thig le la phog pas /
NK021(zha)001:13346: de las 'od zer mkha' khyab tu 'phros /
NK021(zha)001:13347: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK021(zha)001:13348: 'khor 'das kyi snang ba thams cad zhu nas tshur 'dus te /
NK021(zha)001:13349: spyi bo'i thig le la thim /
NK021(zha)001:13350: de yang zhu ba las rang gi rtsa ba'i bla
NK021(zha)001:13351: ma sku bde ba'i nyams rgyas shing gzi byin 'bar
NK021(zha)001:13352: bar gyur pa tog gi tshul du bzhugs par bsgom
NK021(zha)001:13353: / de la sems yun ring du bzung bas /
NK021(zha)001:13354: bla ma yang bde ba chen po'i ngo bor ltem gyis zhu ba tshangs bug nas babs te /
NK021(zha)001:13356: bla ma'i thugs dang rang sems ro gcig tu 'dres
NK021(zha)001:13357: pa'i ngang la ma bcos par skyur bas snang ba
NK021(zha)001:13359: gnyis pa 'og sgo'i bde ba sgom thabs ni /
NK021(zha)001:13360: rang gi spyi bor thig le dmar po sran ma tsam pa /
NK021(zha)001:13361: de'i steng gi mda' gang tsam du'ang thig le dkar po sran ma tsam zhig gsal btab la /
NK021(zha)001:13363: spyi bo'i thig le dmar po la shes pa gtad pas /
NK021(zha)001:13364: de chags pa'i rang bzhin du 'dar khri li li g.yo zhing 'bar bas rkyen byas te /
NK021(zha)001:13365: thig le dkar po de'ang 'dar bzhin du ltem gyis zhu nas /
NK021(zha)001:13366: thig le dmar po la ro gcig tu 'dres /
NK021(zha)001:13367: de tshangs bug nas bde ril li li babs pa
NK021(zha)001:13368: snying dkyil du thim pa'i ngang la ma bcos par
NK021(zha)001:13369: bzhag pas bde stong dbyer med kyi nyams 'char ro
NK021(zha)001:13370: // gnyis pa sgrub dbang dang 'brel ba a nu'i man ngag sgom thabs ni /
NK021(zha)001:13372: rang gi snying gi dkyil du thig le dkar po
NK021(zha)001:13373: phug ron gyi sgo nga tsam pa 'od 'bar ba
NK021(zha)001:13374: zhig sgom / de gsal thebs pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:13375: de las 'od kyi thig le skar mda' 'phangs pa ltar yar spyi gtsug nas thon /
NK021(zha)001:13376: de las kyang thig phran bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK021(zha)001:13377: 'phros pas blos 'khyud tshad kyi nam mkha'i khyon gang
NK021(zha)001:13379: yang mkha' khyab kyi thig phran rnams tshur 'dus /
NK021(zha)001:13380: 'phro gzhi'i thig le dang ro gcig tu 'dres pa'i
NK021(zha)001:13381: ngang la blta bya lta byed med par bzhag pas
NK021(zha)001:13382: / yul dbyings dang yul can rig pa'i ye shes
NK021(zha)001:13383: dbyer med bde ba chen pos lhag lhag 'char te
NK021(zha)001:13384: / / de ka'i ngang la zhen 'dzin med par bskyang bar bya ba gnad do //
NK021(zha)001:13385: des rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du nang dbang sgrub dbang
NK021(zha)001:13386: gnyis mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs dang yang thun mong
NK021(zha)001:13387: bar gyur pa'i chu bo bzhi'i dbang rgyud lugs gtso
NK021(zha)001:13388: bor byas pa mtha' rten man ngag dang bcas pa
NK021(zha)001:13389: grub pas / ji ltar gdams pa ltar tshul bzhin du bsgrub par bagyi'o snyam pas /
NK021(zha)001:13390: gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blangs /
NK021(zha)001:13392: deng nas brtsams te sogs kyi yon dbul zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13393: dge ba bsngo ba rnams sngar ltar dang /
NK021(zha)001:13394: rjes chog rnams skabs ji lta ba'i khrigs bzhin bya ba yin no //
NK021(zha)001:13395: zab barlinga rgyud dag man ngag nam mkha'i khyon //
NK021(zha)001:13396: rnam 'byed rta bdun dbang pos gzhal ba na //
NK021(zha)001:13397: legs bshad chos kyi 'od zer bye ba'i gzis //
NK021(zha)001:13398: ska bzang mig la snang ba'i dpal du gyur //
NK021(zha)001:13400: tshur bzhin rtogs nas 'chad pa nyung //
NK021(zha)001:13401: de phyir gtsang dag yi ge 'di //
NK021(zha)001:13402: sngon med legs bshad nyid du bzung //
NK021(zha)001:13403: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang chog rdo rje'i them skas las /
NK021(zha)001:13404: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor du phyi gsang gnyis rgyud lugs thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:13405: nang sgrub gnyis rgyud dang man ngag thun mong par
NK021(zha)001:13406: gyur pa'i chu bo bzhi bskor ba'i dbang chog bshad
NK021(zha)001:13410: zhu bde'i 'gyur rtsis kun rtogs lcags //
NK021(zha)001:13411: 'pho med gser khams rdo rjera bsgyur //
NK021(zha)001:13412: der btud kun rdzob byang sems kyi //
NK021(zha)001:13413: gsang dbang lus la bskur thabs bstan //
NK021(zha)001:13414: da ni yan lag gi dkyil 'khor du man ngag
NK021(zha)001:13415: gi lugs kyi kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi dbang
NK021(zha)001:13416: bskur ba ni / mtshon bya lus dkyil dang /
NK021(zha)001:13417: mtshon byed kyi brda me long gi mkha' dkyil /
NK021(zha)001:13418: gsang rdzas bdud rtsi sgrub pa tshogs gtor dang bcas pa rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13419: de nas 'jug pa la gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:13420: dang po slob dpon 'jug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:13421: ru bdag nyid rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma yab
NK021(zha)001:13422: yum lhag pa'i lhar gsal ba'i lus dkyil du zhugs
NK021(zha)001:13424: phyag rgya ma 'khor lo'i gtso mor gsal ba'i mkha'
NK021(zha)001:13425: dkyil du zhugs nas sher dbang dang cho ga rgyas
NK021(zha)001:13426: bsdus ji ltar rigs pas blang pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:13427: gnyis pa slob ma gzhug cing dbang bskur ba gnyis las /
NK021(zha)001:13429: las rgya dngos yod na mtshan mo dben pa'i gnas
NK021(zha)001:13430: su yol bas sgribs te slob ma rnams dri chu
NK021(zha)001:13432: bgegs bskrad cing bsrung ba byas la /
NK021(zha)001:13433: sems bskyed dang chos nyan pa'i kun spyod gsal 'debs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK021(zha)001:13434: 'dir gangs gsan par bya ba'i chos na /
NK021(zha)001:13436: mdo yongs rdzogs kyi lugs gnyis gcig tu dril nas bskur ba las /
NK021(zha)001:13437: zhes pa'i bar spro bsdu ji ltar rigs pas mtshams sbyar rjes /
NK021(zha)001:13438: 'dir mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du byas pa'i gsang
NK021(zha)001:13439: dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:13440: dang por kun rdzob byang sems kyi dbang lus la
NK021(zha)001:13442: de la thog mar gsang dbang zhu ba'i slad du
NK021(zha)001:13443: bla ma rigs 'dus rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bor
NK021(zha)001:13444: bzhugs pa la phyag sngon du 'gro bas /
NK021(zha)001:13445: 'dod yon lnga'i mchod pa dang rgyud sbyangs pa'i las
NK021(zha)001:13446: kyi phyag rgya mtshan nyid dang ldan pa phul bar
NK021(zha)001:13448: de nas bla ma rigs 'dus rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK021(zha)001:13449: rnam par bzhugs pa'i gnas lngar de bzhin gshegs pa
NK021(zha)001:13451: yan lag bzhir sgo ba bzhi rnams gsal ba las /
NK021(zha)001:13452: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od kyis reg pas /
NK021(zha)001:13453: phul ba'i las rgya de'i sems kyi rtog pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:13454: de las byung ba'i lus ngag gi sgrib pa sbyangs te stong pa nyid du gyur /
NK021(zha)001:13455: de'i ngang las skad cig gis yum rdo rje dbyings
NK021(zha)001:13456: phyug mar gyur pa'i gnas lngar rigs kyi yum lnga
NK021(zha)001:13458: zhal dang b+ha ga'i sgor gsang yum bzhi rnams gsal bar mos la /
NK021(zha)001:13459: thal mo sbyar te gsol ba gdab pa 'di'i rdorje slob dpon yab yum dgongs //
NK021(zha)001:13461: dgyes pa chen po'i thabs lam gyis //
NK021(zha)001:13462: chu bo bzhi las bdag sgrol mdzod //
NK021(zha)001:13464: de ltar gsol ba btab pa'i lan du slob dpon
NK021(zha)001:13465: rig ma dang bcas pa rdor sems yab yum du
NK021(zha)001:13466: gsal bas / bu khyod smros dang thabs lam 'di //
NK021(zha)001:13467: rgyal ba yongs kyis sbas pa yin //
NK021(zha)001:13468: thabs chen gsang ba'i theg pa 'dir //
NK021(zha)001:13469: gtsang rme'i 'ching ba sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:13470: dri sha chu rnams bza' btung dang //
NK021(zha)001:13471: phyag rgya'i b+ha ga'i ye shes bzhi //
NK021(zha)001:13472: 'o dang gzhib dang drang ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:13473: sems chu 'thung bar khyod nus sam //
NK021(zha)001:13474: zhes dris pa'i lan du nus snyam pa'i 'di'i e ma'o thabs lam ye shes phyir //
NK021(zha)001:13475: bdag ni ci la'ang mi nus med //
NK021(zha)001:13476: de dag bdag gis spyad par bgyi //
NK021(zha)001:13477: ji ltar sad phyir bdag la stsol //
NK021(zha)001:13479: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ma mthong ba'i brdar +aahh+aum gis gdong g.yogs bcings la /
NK021(zha)001:13480: de nas bla ma yab yum lhar gsal ba'i yab
NK021(zha)001:13481: kyi gsang gnas h+aum las rdo rje dmar po rtse
NK021(zha)001:13484: bu gar +aahyiga ye shes kyi me 'bar ba dang bcas pa /
NK021(zha)001:13485: yum gyi mkha' +aahls pad+ma ze'u 'brur h+r+aihyiga dmar po
NK021(zha)001:13486: 'od zer 'bar bas mtshan pa'i nang du rtsa dgu'i
NK021(zha)001:13487: ngo bo rtsibs brgyad lte ba dang bcas par zla
NK021(zha)001:13488: gam dgu la gnas pa'i byang sems bde ba'i ye
NK021(zha)001:13489: shes kyi ngo bo he ru ka yab yum goo
NK021(zha)001:13490: r+ai ma brgyad kyis bskor bar mos la /
NK021(zha)001:13491: bla ma yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i dga' ba'i
NK021(zha)001:13492: sgras zhi khro rigs lnga yab yum spyan drangs te
NK021(zha)001:13493: / stong gsum 'gengs pa tsam gyis 'dod chags chen
NK021(zha)001:13494: pos byang chub sems kyi ngo bor zhu nas rang
NK021(zha)001:13495: / la thim pas / lus dkyil gyi lha rnams
NK021(zha)001:13496: kyang rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba dang lhan cig
NK021(zha)001:13498: rdo rje nor bur lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba brtan par byas la /
NK021(zha)001:13499: phata ces spros pas yum gyi pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor pa rnams mnyes par byas /
NK021(zha)001:13500: de las kyang spros pa'i sems sprin gyis sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs nas tshur 'dus te /
NK021(zha)001:13501: mkha' gsang gi dkyil 'khor pa rnams kyang bde ba
NK021(zha)001:13502: chen por zhu ba dang lhan cig tu mkha' la
NK021(zha)001:13503: ltems pa'i byang chub sems kyi rdul phra rab re
NK021(zha)001:13504: re bzhin yang rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bo h+aum
NK021(zha)001:13505: yig gi rnam par gyur pa /
NK021(zha)001:13506: yab kyi rdo rje nor bu'i rtse nas ba dang be'u'i tshul du len pa thabs kyi gsang dbang /
NK021(zha)001:13507: yum gyi mkha' las me tog dang bung ba'i tshul du len pa shes rab kyi gsang dbang /
NK021(zha)001:13508: yum gyi mkha' las yab kyi lce'am mtheb srin gyis
NK021(zha)001:13509: blangs pa bya dang byi'u'i tshul du byin pa thabs
NK021(zha)001:13510: shes gnyis med kyi gsang dbang ste /
NK021(zha)001:13511: rim pa ji lta ba de ltar rang gi lces blangs pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:13513: dga' ba byang chub sems chen po //
NK021(zha)001:13514: kun tu tshim par byed pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:13515: dkar dmar lhag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK021(zha)001:13516: dbang thob khyod kyi lce la bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:13517: rdo rje nyi zla rdul phran grangs //
NK021(zha)001:13518: rdo rje sems dpa' mngon gsal ba //
NK021(zha)001:13519: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pas /
NK021(zha)001:13520: rtse nas rtse ru thim pa las //
NK021(zha)001:13521: gnas ngan len pa kun sbyangs nas //
NK021(zha)001:13524: h+aum badz+ra sat+wa sh+r+ai ma h+aa su kha bo d+hi badz+ra h+aum hoham /
NK021(zha)001:13525: zhes lce la bdud rtsi lan gsum sbyin zhing /
NK021(zha)001:13526: des kyang sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i ngo bor mos te /
NK021(zha)001:13527: a ho ma h+aa su kha hoh zhes myang bas
NK021(zha)001:13528: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i rgyun snying gar babs pas
NK021(zha)001:13529: rtsa chen bzhi la gnas pa'i rigs drug gi sa
NK021(zha)001:13530: bon gnyid dang bcas pa sbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:13531: las nyon bag chags kyi rtog pa thams cad mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su grol te /
NK021(zha)001:13532: sems gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i rang bzhin
NK021(zha)001:13533: don dam spros med kyi ye shes nam mkha' dang
NK021(zha)001:13534: mnyam pa rgyud la skyes pa'i mos pa byed du
NK021(zha)001:13535: bcug la / dbang de thob pa'i brdar 'bru gsum gyis gdong g.yogs bsal bas /
NK021(zha)001:13536: yum gyi b+ha ga mthong ba'i rkyen gyis byang sems
NK021(zha)001:13537: cher g.yos nas 'dod chags chen pos byang chub sems
NK021(zha)001:13539: shes pa h+aum yig shel ltar dwangs pa las skad
NK021(zha)001:13540: cig gis che mchog he ru ka mthing nag rdo
NK021(zha)001:13541: rje dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK021(zha)001:13542: de'i thugs kar gu h+ya he ru ka sngon po rdor dril /
NK021(zha)001:13543: de'i thugs kar sa nu he ru ka dkar po
