NK021(zha)001:14895: byang phyogs khro bo chen po bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK021(zha)001:14896: log par lta spangs ye shes dbang mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:14897: shar lho khro bo chen po dbyug sngon can //
NK021(zha)001:14898: rdzun gyi skyon spangs mos la dbang mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:14899: lho nub khro bo chen po mi g.yo mgon //
NK021(zha)001:14900: ngag 'khyal skyon spangs sems la dbang mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:14901: nub byang khro bo chen po 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK021(zha)001:14902: gnod sems skyon spangs rdzu 'phrul dbang mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:14903: byang shar khro bo chen po khams gsum rgyal //
NK021(zha)001:14904: brnab sems skyon spangs smon lam dbang mdzad pa //
NK021(zha)001:14905: 'og phyogs khro bo chen po stobs po che //
NK021(zha)001:14906: zhes brjod pas nges shes bskyed nas /
NK021(zha)001:14907: 'di ltar yug dkar po la tshom bu bcu gsum
NK021(zha)001:14908: bkod pa 'di ni thar pa'i lam sa bcu gsum
NK021(zha)001:14909: mtshon pa ste / de dag gi ming don ni /
NK021(zha)001:14910: lha mo nag mo'i mdo gzungs las //
NK021(zha)001:14911: nam yang 'khor bar mi ltung zhing //
NK021(zha)001:14912: mya ngan 'das pa thob pa'i phyir //
NK021(zha)001:14913: nyan thos sa rnams non pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:14914: rten 'brel bcu gnyis shes par bya //
NK021(zha)001:14915: byang chub sems dpa'i sa rnams ni //
NK021(zha)001:14917: sbyang dka' mngon gyur ring du song //
NK021(zha)001:14918: mi g.yo legs pa chos kyi sprin //
NK021(zha)001:14919: sangs rgyas sa chen bla na med //
NK021(zha)001:14920: bcu gnyis po yang thob 'gyur te //
NK021(zha)001:14924: las kyi 'od dang dpe med pa //
NK021(zha)001:14925: dpe ldan pa dang shes rab 'od //
NK021(zha)001:14926: thams cad mkhyen dang rang rig ste //
NK021(zha)001:14927: bcu gnyis sangs rgyas sa rnams kyang //
NK021(zha)001:14928: 'di tsho byung na myur du thob //
NK021(zha)001:14930: sbyin pa tshul khrims bzod brtson 'grus //
NK021(zha)001:14931: ser sna 'chal ba le lo bral //
NK021(zha)001:14932: bsam gtan shes rab thabs stobs kyis //
NK021(zha)001:14933: g.yeng rmugs mi mkhas rgol ba sel //
NK021(zha)001:14934: smon lam ye shes pha rol phyin //
NK021(zha)001:14936: ye shes lnga dang chos kyi dbyings //
NK021(zha)001:14937: rang byung ye shes bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:14939: dkor bdun bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin //
NK021(zha)001:14940: bla ma'i sa dkor sku gsung thugs //
NK021(zha)001:14941: yon tan phrin las dbyings ye bdun //
NK021(zha)001:14942: zhes gsungs pa ltar rgyu'i theg pa la che chung ma phye ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK021(zha)001:14946: sangs rgyas kyi sa dang bcu gsum mo //
NK021(zha)001:14948: theg dman la thar pa'i lam stegs su gyur pa mngon mtho'i sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14949: nyan thos kyi tshogs lam dkar po rnam par mthong ba'i sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14950: sbyor lam rigs kyi sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14951: 'bras bu dang po la zhugs pa brgyud pa'i sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14952: de la gnas pa mthong ba'i sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14953: phyir 'ong 'bras gnas srabs pa'i sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14954: phyir mi 'ong 'bras gnas 'dod chags dang bral ba'i sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14955: dgra bcom pa 'bras gnas byas pa rtogs pa'i sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14956: phyir 'ong mi 'ong dgra bcom gyi zhugs pa gsum nyan thos kyi sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14957: bse ru lta bu dang tshogs spyod kyi 'phags pa rigs gnyis ni rang sangs rgyas kyi sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14958: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa dang bcu gcig las /
NK021(zha)001:14959: 'bras bu phyi ma gsum gyi zhugs pa so sor phye bas bcu gsum mo //
NK021(zha)001:14960: theg chen gyi mos pas spyod pa'i sa la tshogs lam dang /
NK021(zha)001:14962: 'phags pa'i lam la rab tu dga' ba sogs slob pa'i sa bcu dang /
NK021(zha)001:14963: mi slob pa sangs rgyas kyis kun tu 'od dang bcu gsum mo //
NK021(zha)001:14964: yang 'bras bu gsang sngags bla med kyi dbang du byas na /
NK021(zha)001:14965: las rlung nyi khri chig stog drug brgya las stong
NK021(zha)001:14966: brgyad brgya pa re 'gags pas 'khor lo drug gi
NK021(zha)001:14967: mas rim nas phyed phyed mi 'gyur ba'i byang sems
NK021(zha)001:14968: kyis gang bas sa bcu gnyis rim par bgrod nas
NK021(zha)001:14969: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi sa brnyes pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:14970: dbu ma la mdud pa nyer gcig gi gnyis gnyis
NK021(zha)001:14971: grol bas sa re re thob ste sa bcu dang
NK021(zha)001:14972: / sangs rgyas kyi sa la sku gsum gyi dbyee bas phye ste bcu gsum bshad cing /
NK021(zha)001:14973: de nyid rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su rgyud dang man ngag rnams su gsungs mod /
NK021(zha)001:14974: 'di ni ting nge 'dzin gyi sa zhes don la
NK021(zha)001:14975: mthong lam la rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su btags pa
NK021(zha)001:14976: ste / gsang sngags lam myur bas rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la shin tu nye zhing /
NK021(zha)001:14977: de dag rnam pa mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:14979: de nas mthong sgom gyis bsdus pa'i sa bcu lam
NK021(zha)001:14980: rigs 'dra kho nas bgrod nas sangs rgyas thob par
NK021(zha)001:14981: bshad cing / 'di dag tu sa bcu gnyis kyi
NK021(zha)001:14982: rnam bzhag gzhan kun tu 'od dang bdud rtsi 'od
NK021(zha)001:14983: sogs bcu gnyis po 'di rnams de bzhin gshegs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:14984: yon tan gyi skabs su gsungs na'ang /
NK021(zha)001:14985: ting nge 'dzin gyi sa bcu gnyis pa'i mthar thob ste /
NK021(zha)001:14986: gong ma'i yon tan gyi gzhir gyur pa'i ye shes kyi khyad par bcu gnyis thob pa yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:14987: rab dga' sogs sa bcu dang rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK021(zha)001:14988: kyi sa re re bzhin yang 'di dag bcu gnyis
NK021(zha)001:14990: de dag ni sngon gyi slob dpon rnams kyis lung drangs pa'i dgongs pa cung zad bkral ba ste /
NK021(zha)001:14991: gsang sngags spyi'i lugs yin la /
NK021(zha)001:14992: da res 'dir skabs su babs pa 'dus pa mdo'i rang skad la /
NK021(zha)001:14993: 'gyur ba ma nges pa'i sa sogs slob lam bzhis bsdus pa'i sa bcu dang /
NK021(zha)001:14994: mi slob lam gyis bsdus pa'i sa gsum ste bcu gsum mo //
NK021(zha)001:14995: de ltar nges par byas nas /
NK021(zha)001:14996: tshom bus mtshon pa'i sa re re bzhin yid kyi
NK021(zha)001:14997: 'jug pa'i sgo nas thabs shes kyi rkang pas bgrod
NK021(zha)001:14998: par bya ste / de yang khyed rang dpon slob
NK021(zha)001:14999: mched grogs gnyen 'dun sogs 'brel thogs rnams kyis thog
NK021(zha)001:15000: drang mkha' khyab kyi sems can thams cad thar pa'i
NK021(zha)001:15001: lam la rim par 'dren pa yin pas /
NK021(zha)001:15002: thog mar bla ma sprul pa'i sku'i bdag nyid can gyis khrid de /
NK021(zha)001:15003: sa dang po 'gyur ba ma nges pa /
NK021(zha)001:15005: gsum pa gal chen sbyong ba /
NK021(zha)001:15006: bzhi pa bslab pa rgyun gyi sa rnams la rim par drangs pas /
NK021(zha)001:15010: byang sems kyi sa rnams dang /
NK021(zha)001:15011: mdo rang lugs kyi tshogs lam bdun pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor gnyis dang /
NK021(zha)001:15012: sbyor lam rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor la gsum gyi gnyis pa man chad non /
NK021(zha)001:15013: de nas bla ma longs spyod rdzogs pa sku'i bdag nyid can gyis khrid de /
NK021(zha)001:15014: lnga pa bsod nams rten gyi sa /
NK021(zha)001:15015: drug pa brten pas khyad par du 'gro ba'i sa /
NK021(zha)001:15016: bdun pa dmigs pas 'bras bu skye ba'i sa rnams la rim par drangs pas /
NK021(zha)001:15020: mdo rang lugs kyi sbyor lam gsum pa dang /
NK021(zha)001:15021: mthong lam dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK021(zha)001:15022: sgom lam lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor gsum non /
NK021(zha)001:15023: de nas bla ma chos kyi sku'i bdag nyid can gyis khrid de /
NK021(zha)001:15024: brgyad pa gnas pa mi 'gyur ba'i sa /
NK021(zha)001:15025: dgu pa brdal pa chos nyid kyi sa //
NK021(zha)001:15026: bcu pa rdzogs pa cir chibs kyi sa rnams la drangs pas /
NK021(zha)001:15029: a ti yo ga rnams dang /
NK021(zha)001:15030: mdo rang lugs kyi mthar lam rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor gsum non /
NK021(zha)001:15031: de nas bla ma dbyer med rdo rje dang mngon
NK021(zha)001:15032: par byang chub pa'i sku gnyis dbyer mi phyed pa
NK021(zha)001:15033: ngo bo nyid sku'i bdag nyid can gyis khrid de
NK021(zha)001:15035: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa dang /
NK021(zha)001:15036: ye shes bla ma'i sa rnams la drangs pas /
NK021(zha)001:15037: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sku gsum gyi
NK021(zha)001:15038: bdag nyid can gyi go 'phang non par mos la
NK021(zha)001:15039: / dga' zhing spro ba dang bcas pas ma yengs par nyan 'tshal /
NK021(zha)001:15041: slob dpon gyis tshig dal zhing 'jebs pas 'di skad do //
NK021(zha)001:15042: nga ni thabs kyi mnyan pa mkhan //
NK021(zha)001:15043: 'khor ba'i chu bo mtha' med las //
NK021(zha)001:15044: srid gsum bsgral bar dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15046: nga ni thabs kyi mig mkhan de //
NK021(zha)001:15047: 'jig rten long pa dpag med rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15048: ling tog bsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15050: nga ni thabs kyi sman pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:15051: grong khyer gsum gyi nad pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15052: gcong rnying 'byin par dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15054: nga ni thabs kyi sa mkhan te //
NK021(zha)001:15055: 'gro ba lam log lam stor rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15056: ma nor 'khrid par dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15058: nga ni thugs rje'i spyan ras mkhan //
NK021(zha)001:15060: thams cad skyob par dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15062: nga ni rdo rje'i rdzong chen te //
NK021(zha)001:15063: 'khor ba'i g.yul chen dmag dpung las //
NK021(zha)001:15066: nga ni thabs kyi tshong dpon te //
NK021(zha)001:15067: 'dod pa rgya mtshos mi ngoms rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15068: gter chen sbyin par dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15070: nga ni thabs kyi sgron me ste //
NK021(zha)001:15071: mun nag smag tu 'khyams pa rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15072: mun nag bsal bar dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15074: nga ni yid bzhin nor bu ste //
NK021(zha)001:15075: yang dag yid bzhin 'dod pa de //
NK021(zha)001:15076: yid bzhin skong bar dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15078: nga ni bka' yi lde mig ste //
NK021(zha)001:15079: bka' sgrom tha ram gsang ba rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15080: rnam par 'byed par dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15082: nga ni bka' yi 'grel pa ste //
NK021(zha)001:15083: gsung gi glegs lam zab mo rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15084: nges par grol bar dam bcas kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15086: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol 'dir //
NK021(zha)001:15087: skal ldan gang zhig su zhugs pa //
NK021(zha)001:15089: nges par 'char gyis brtson par gyis //
NK021(zha)001:15090: de nyid sems kyi me long ste //
NK021(zha)001:15091: mngon sum gsal bar rtogs ma thag /
NK021(zha)001:15092: 'gro ba'i lus la sangs rgyas yin //
NK021(zha)001:15093: rdo rje gsang chen gsang ba yi //
NK021(zha)001:15094: nges don dam pa'i mdzod mchog rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15095: 'dir bgros gsal bar bshad sbyar bas //
NK021(zha)001:15096: lha dang mi yi rig 'dzin las //
NK021(zha)001:15097: rim par brgyud de grags par 'gyur //
NK021(zha)001:15098: lha mi'i 'jig rten thams cad kyi //
NK021(zha)001:15099: mun pa'i gdung ba kun bsal nas //
NK021(zha)001:15101: da ni bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la 'bral mi phod pa'i dad pa bskyed /
NK021(zha)001:15102: yid bzhin gyi nor bu stor ba rnyed pa lta bu'i dga' ba sgoms /
NK021(zha)001:15103: rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi bdag por gyur to snyam du yid spro bar mdzod cig /
NK021(zha)001:15104: de nas slob dpon la man+dala 'bul du bcug nas /
NK021(zha)001:15106: dpal ldan bla ma khyed kyi bka' drin gyis /
NK021(zha)001:15107: da ni bdag gis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK021(zha)001:15108: kyi thugs kyi gsang chen bla na med pa'i rgyud
NK021(zha)001:15109: dang dkyil 'khor gyi bdag por gyur pas rnyed pa'i
NK021(zha)001:15110: mchog rab tu rnyed pas spro lags so //
NK021(zha)001:15111: rje btsun dam pa khyed ye shes rang snang gi sku la 'pho 'gyur mi mnga' ba bzhin du /
NK021(zha)001:15112: gdul bya gzhan snang gi sku 'di nyid kyang nam
NK021(zha)001:15113: mkha' ji srid pa de srid du brtan par bzhugs
NK021(zha)001:15114: nas chos kyi 'khor lo rgyun mi chad par bskor
NK021(zha)001:15116: bdag cag rnams kyang khyod dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK021(zha)001:15117: tshogs rnams spangs nas skyabs gzhan bsten par mi bagyi'o
NK021(zha)001:15118: // de kho na bzhin du 'grub par byin gyis rlob tu gsol /
NK021(zha)001:15119: phata ces bla ma'i khri la spyi bos btud du bcug /
NK021(zha)001:15120: de nas bla mas 'di skad ces gdams te /
NK021(zha)001:15121: ci'i phyir gdung ba'i mun par zhugs //
NK021(zha)001:15122: thub pa mya ngan 'das gdung ba //
NK021(zha)001:15123: de ni nam mkha'i sku mnga' bas //
NK021(zha)001:15126: de skad sprul pa'i sgra byung bas //
NK021(zha)001:15127: sngon du byung ba'i rigs can rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15128: mchog tu dga' ba cher skyes te //
NK021(zha)001:15129: dga' mgu rangs pa'i bsam pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:15130: lus btud shin tu gus sbyar nas //
NK021(zha)001:15132: zhes gsungs pa ltar khyed rang rnams pus btsugs thal
NK021(zha)001:15133: mo sbyar nas bla ma la gus pas bstod pa
NK021(zha)001:15134: 'di'i rjes mtshan mo mun nag sprin rum nas //
NK021(zha)001:15135: glog 'gyus bar snang ston lta bur //
NK021(zha)001:15136: thog ma mtha' ma med pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:15137: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK021(zha)001:15138: rnam dag lam chen de nyid du //
NK021(zha)001:15139: byung ba'i skyes bu don grub khyod //
NK021(zha)001:15140: dam pa rnams kyi gsang 'dzin cing //
NK021(zha)001:15141: gsang ba pa yi bdag por grags //
NK021(zha)001:15143: de nas mnga' gsol ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:15144: so so'i go 'phang dang 'tshams pa'i stan dang dbang rtags 'du byas la /
NK021(zha)001:15145: thog mar bu rnams phyag 'tshal du bcug /
NK021(zha)001:15146: bgegs gtor ram yam kham gis bsang sbyangs /
NK021(zha)001:15147: stong pa'i ngang las yig zhu ba las byung ba'i
NK021(zha)001:15148: gtor ma 'dod yon gyi sprin 'phro bar mos la
NK021(zha)001:15151: deng 'dir rdo rje'i slob ma 'di rnams la bka'
NK021(zha)001:15152: babs kyi brgyud pa gtad de bkra shis kyis mnga'
NK021(zha)001:15153: gsol ba la bar du gcod pa'i gdon bgegs thams
NK021(zha)001:15155: bi shwa badz+ra gyi sngags kyis bgegs bskrad /
NK021(zha)001:15156: h'u zhes brjod pas khro bcu rol pa'i sprin gyis
NK021(zha)001:15157: phyogs kun gtams te cis kyang mi shigs par bsam
NK021(zha)001:15158: la / rdo rje slob dpon dang rgyal theb 'os pa khri lnga brtsegs la 'dug tu bcug nas /
NK021(zha)001:15161: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la
NK021(zha)001:15162: dbang rtags rdo rje dang dril bu gtad pas rang
NK021(zha)001:15163: gzhan gyi don rlabs po che byed nus par gyur
NK021(zha)001:15164: cig / 'chad mkhan la stan sum brtsegs 'khor lo dang dung gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:15166: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la
NK021(zha)001:15167: dbang rtags 'khor lo dang dung gtad pas theg pa
NK021(zha)001:15168: mtha' dag 'chad nus par gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:15169: las mkhan la gdan pad nyi /
NK021(zha)001:15176: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la
NK021(zha)001:15177: dbang rtags rgya gram la sogs pa gtad pas las
NK021(zha)001:15178: bzhi gang la gang 'tshams par spyod nus par gyur
NK021(zha)001:15179: cig / phal pa rnams la stan pad+ma /
NK021(zha)001:15180: phreng ba dang pusti gtad de /
NK021(zha)001:15182: phyogs bcu skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod la
NK021(zha)001:15183: dbang rtags su pusti dang phreng ba gtad pas bka'
NK021(zha)001:15184: phyi nang gi chos nyan pa dang ting nge 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:15185: sgom pa'i nus pa thogs pa med par gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:15186: / de nas rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma rnams byin
NK021(zha)001:15187: 'thibs se byon nas khyod rang rnams la thim pa'i
NK021(zha)001:15188: / mos pa mdzod // spos 'thul zhing rol mo 'khrol bas /
NK021(zha)001:15189: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h'u /
NK021(zha)001:15190: 'og min chos dbyings zhing khams nas //
NK021(zha)001:15191: dgongs rig rna bar brgyud pa yi //
NK021(zha)001:15192: byin rlabs rtsa ba bla ma'i tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:15193: sangs rgyas byang sems 'khor gyis bskor //
NK021(zha)001:15195: khyed kyi rjes su bdag sgrubs shig /
NK021(zha)001:15196: byin gyis rlob phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK021(zha)001:15197: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa bzhes //
NK021(zha)001:15198: bgegs dang log 'dren bar chad sol //
NK021(zha)001:15199: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK021(zha)001:15202: bu rnams nyams byung rgyal du bskyang du gzhug go //
NK021(zha)001:15203: de nas me tog 'thor zhing dril bu 'khrol bas //
NK021(zha)001:15204: chos sku kun bzang longs sku rigs lnga dang //
NK021(zha)001:15205: sprul sku rigs gsum yang sprul dga' rab sogs //
NK021(zha)001:15206: ye shes sku mchog rgyal ba dgongs pas brgyud //
NK021(zha)001:15207: dgongs brgyud bla ma rnams kyi bkra shis shog /
NK021(zha)001:15208: grags ldan mchog skyong klu rgyal 'jog po dang //
NK021(zha)001:15209: gnod sbyin srin po li tsa dri med sogs //
NK021(zha)001:15210: thugs rje gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin rig pas brgyud //
NK021(zha)001:15211: brda brgyud bla ma rnams kyi bkra shis shog /
NK021(zha)001:15212: rgya bal bru sha'i pan grub brgyud pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:15213: gangs can gdung sel bod kyi brgyud pa sogs //
NK021(zha)001:15214: dpang gyur rdo rje gang zag snyan khung brgyud //
NK021(zha)001:15215: rna brgyud bla ma rnams kyi bkra shis shog /
NK021(zha)001:15218: ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la
NK021(zha)001:15219: 'khor 'dus pa rnams kyi gtso bo rig 'dzin kuny+dza
NK021(zha)001:15220: ras / 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum la //
NK021(zha)001:15221: gang dag rim par bkod lags na //
NK021(zha)001:15222: mnyam pas blang dor med spyod cing //
NK021(zha)001:15223: byang chub gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:15224: thabs mchog dpag gis mi lang ba //
NK021(zha)001:15225: nges pa'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK021(zha)001:15227: ston pas nges pa'i theg pa rnam grol gyi lung
NK021(zha)001:15228: mdo chen po 'di 'jig rten du 'byung ba'i dus
NK021(zha)001:15229: bcu gnyis gsungs pa'i bden pa des bstan pa 'jig
NK021(zha)001:15230: rten gyi sgron mer yongs su 'bar bar gyur cig
NK021(zha)001:15231: ces shis pa brjod pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:15233: de kho na nyid nges pa'i theg pa chen po de /
NK021(zha)001:15234: gnas skabs gnyis dang bcur 'byung ste //
NK021(zha)001:15235: gang rmongs pa gdung ba sel ba na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15236: gang 'jig rten gyi sgron ma yongs su bkod pa na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15237: gang gis nges pa rnyed pa na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15238: snying po byang chub nyid du nges pa na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15239: dgongs pa nges par 'grel ba na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15240: gdul bya'i thabs la bab pa'i ched na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15241: byin gyis brlabs las snang ba na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15242: brgyud pa thabs kyis grags pa na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15243: gang gi ched du mdzad pa na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15244: lung chen nges par bstan pa na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15245: las rgyud yongs su gcod pa na yang 'byung /
NK021(zha)001:15246: dgongs pa rnam par bgro ba na yang 'byung ste /
NK021(zha)001:15247: de dag na thams cad kyi thams cad nas thams
NK021(zha)001:15248: cad du kun tu yongs su rnam par snang ngo
NK021(zha)001:15251: zhes bka' stsal bas dri ba dang po'i rtog pa
NK021(zha)001:15252: yongs su chad pa de bzhin du bkra shis par
NK021(zha)001:15253: gyur cig / ces me tog gi sil ma 'thor zhing rol mo'i sgra bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:15257: de nas phyogs dus thams cad du sangs rgyas kyi
NK021(zha)001:15258: bstan pa dang sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams 'dzin skyong
NK021(zha)001:15259: bsrung ba la 'bad par bya ba'i phyir rgya lngas
NK021(zha)001:15260: gdab pa ni / bla ma'i bka' rdzogs slob ma gdung 'tshob kyi rgya dang gcig /
NK021(zha)001:15261: gdul bya rjes su 'dzin pa bstan pa dgongs 'dus kyi rgya dang gnyis /
NK021(zha)001:15262: sgrub rdzas dang me tog yul gyi bca' thang ltar 'bul ba'i rgya dang gsum /
NK021(zha)001:15263: bka'i gnyer gtad chos kyi bdag por mnga' gsol ba'i rgya dang bzhi /
NK021(zha)001:15264: zhu ba pos zhi ba'i gzhung mchod tshogs 'bul ba'i
NK021(zha)001:15265: rgya dang lnga po ci nus sgrub par dam bca'
NK021(zha)001:15266: ba la 'di nyid byin par bya ba yin gyis
NK021(zha)001:15267: / de las gzhan pa rnams re zhig bzung bar
NK021(zha)001:15268: bya ba'i yul ma yin par btang snyoms su bzhag
NK021(zha)001:15269: / la / phyis nas rjes su bzung ba'i yul du smon lam gdab par gyis shig /
NK021(zha)001:15270: ces gdams pa'i lan du 'di'i gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blangs /
NK021(zha)001:15272: deng nas brtsams te sogs kyis yon dbul /
NK021(zha)001:15273: dge ba bla na med pa'i byang chub tu bsngo zhing /
NK021(zha)001:15274: dar yug tshom bu dang bcas pa mjug nas dri la te slob dpon gyi phyogs su bsdu /
NK021(zha)001:15275: rjes tshogs kyi dga' ston la rol zhing /
NK021(zha)001:15276: gnang ba thob na rdo rje glu gar sogs kyang bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:15277: man ngag yig rnying lus phra ma //
NK021(zha)001:15278: rna dbang snyan 'jebs rgyan gyis klubs //
NK021(zha)001:15279: chos smra gzhon nu'i yid kyi dpal //
NK021(zha)001:15280: rang dbang med par 'phrog min nam //
NK021(zha)001:15281: dbang gi gtad rgya'i le tshan no //
NK021(zha)001:15285: 'chi med mchog stsol lhag pa'i lhar //
NK021(zha)001:15286: ston mdzad rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK021(zha)001:15287: phyag byas tshe yi dbang chog bri //
NK021(zha)001:15288: da ni mtha' brten tshe'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:15289: dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub gtor chog dang bcas pa sgrub thabs ltar sngon du btang nas /
NK021(zha)001:15291: bgegs gtor btang la mtshams bcad nas /
NK021(zha)001:15292: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad kyi
NK021(zha)001:15293: don du rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob
NK021(zha)001:15294: par bya / de sgrub pa'i rten phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:15295: shin tu rnyed par dka' zhing rnyed na don chen
NK021(zha)001:15296: po dang ldan pa'i mi lus rin po che 'di
NK021(zha)001:15297: nyid yin la / de thob pa tsam gyis mi chog ste /
NK021(zha)001:15298: spyir dzam+bu gling pa'i tshe la nges pa med cing khyad par tshe'i snyigs ma'i mthar thug pa'i phyir /
NK021(zha)001:15299: dus min du 'chi ba'i rkyen dang bar chad mang bas /
NK021(zha)001:15300: de las skyob pa'i thabs la zab rgyas kyi gdams pa rnam grangs ji snyed cig mchis pa las /
NK021(zha)001:15301: 'dir rtsa ba'i rgyud rdo rje bkod pa kun 'dus
NK021(zha)001:15302: rig pa'i mdo las gsungs pa'i tshe'i dbang bskur gyi
NK021(zha)001:15303: cho ga de nyid sgrub par byed pa la /
NK021(zha)001:15304: slob dpon gyi bya ba rnams sngon du song /
NK021(zha)001:15305: da khyed rang rnams kyi ngo skal du gyur pa
NK021(zha)001:15306: la tshe dbang zab mo zhu ba'i yon du man+dala
NK021(zha)001:15307: phul mdzod / de ltar man+dala phul nas gsol ba
NK021(zha)001:15308: gdab pa 'di'i dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun bdag nyid
NK021(zha)001:15309: phul mdzod / // brtse bas dgongs te bdag la yang //
NK021(zha)001:15310: dbang bskur bdud rtsi chen po nyid //
NK021(zha)001:15311: de ring rab tu stsal du gsol //
NK021(zha)001:15313: de nas rgyun bshags bya ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:15314: slob dpon tshe dpag med du gsal ba'i steng gi
NK021(zha)001:15315: cha la brgyud pa'i bla ma yi dam dkyil 'khor
NK021(zha)001:15316: gyi lha tshogs sangs rgyas byang sems thams cad sprin
NK021(zha)001:15317: gtibs pa bzhin bzhugs par mos la 'di'i rdo rje
NK021(zha)001:15320: de nas slob ma lhar bsgom zhing tshe rten bskyed pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:15321: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis slob bu'i
NK021(zha)001:15322: sems kyi rtog pa dang de las byung ba'i lus
NK021(zha)001:15323: ngag kyang sbyangs te mi dmigs pa las /
NK021(zha)001:15324: rma byas btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri pad nyi
NK021(zha)001:15325: zla ba'i gdan la khyed rang a las bcom ldan
NK021(zha)001:15326: 'das snang mtha' tshe dang ye shes dpag tu med
NK021(zha)001:15327: pa sku mdog dkar po gsal 'tsher 'bar ba /
NK021(zha)001:15328: phyag g.yas pad+ma dmar po dang /
NK021(zha)001:15329: g.yon 'chi med bdud rtsis gang ba'i bum pa 'dzin
NK021(zha)001:15330: pa rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa la
NK021(zha)001:15331: rang 'dra'i yum gos dkar mo pad+ma'i skyil krung gis
NK021(zha)001:15332: 'khril ba / gnyis ka zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu
NK021(zha)001:15333: gsum gyis mdzes shing nyams dgus sgeg pa'i yab kyi
NK021(zha)001:15334: thugs kar nyi zla'i ga'u kha sbyor gyi dbus su
NK021(zha)001:15335: tshe rten byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin thig le
NK021(zha)001:15336: dmar po gsal 'tsher 'bar ba'i rnam par sgom /
NK021(zha)001:15337: de nas tshe dgug pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:15338: snying ga'i thig le las 'od zer 'phros pas 'khor
NK021(zha)001:15339: 'das snod bcud kyi mdangs dang tshe bcud bkrag dang
NK021(zha)001:15340: gzi byin bsod nams dang ye shes thams cad bsdus
NK021(zha)001:15341: nas tshe rten la thim pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:15343: h+r+aih nub phyogs pad+ma dbang gi zhing khams nas //
NK021(zha)001:15344: bcom ldan rigs lnga yab yum tshe dpag med //
NK021(zha)001:15345: sems dpa' sems ma sgo mar bcas rnams kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15346: tshe dang ye shes dgug pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK021(zha)001:15347: n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aahyu she dzahdzahh+aum a /
NK021(zha)001:15348: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la mnga' mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:15349: dkar mo mgyogs ma zhi byed 'od 'phro'i tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:15350: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK021(zha)001:15351: rdo rje tshe mchog 'gugs pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK021(zha)001:15352: n+ri b+h+r+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la sngon mo mgyogs ma rgyas mdzad 'od 'phro'i tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:15353: tshe dang gzi brjid rdo rje tshe mchog n+ri b+h+r+aum
NK021(zha)001:15354: 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la dmar mo mgyogs ma
NK021(zha)001:15356: tshe dang gzi brjid 'gugs pa'i rdo rje tshe mchog
NK021(zha)001:15357: 'gugs pa'i n+ri b+h+r+aum 'gro ba yongs kyi tshe la
NK021(zha)001:15358: ljang mdog mgyogs ma drag byed 'od 'phro'i tshogs //
NK021(zha)001:15359: tshe dang gzi brjid rdo rje tshe mchog n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aahyu she dzahdzahh+aum a /
NK021(zha)001:15361: de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:15362: nam mkha' gang ba'i sangs rgyas tshad med pa rnams kyis tshe'i bum pas dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:15363: bum nang gi lha'i thugs dpal gyi be'u nyi zla'i
NK021(zha)001:15364: ga'u nas 'chi ba med pa'i bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma
NK021(zha)001:15365: dmar gsal 'bar ba'i rnam par byung ba khyod rang
NK021(zha)001:15366: gi spyi bo nas snying ga'i tshe rten la sib
NK021(zha)001:15367: kyis thim pas bkrag mdangs gzi byin 'bar ba'i 'od
NK021(zha)001:15368: kyis lus nang thams cad mer khrig gis gang bas
NK021(zha)001:15369: / rgud pa med pa'i lang tsho /
NK021(zha)001:15372: rtag brtan gzhom gzhig dang bral ba thob pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK021(zha)001:15374: h+r+aih nub phyogs tshe yi dbyings mchog gi //
NK021(zha)001:15375: pad+ma dbang gi zhing khams su //
NK021(zha)001:15376: byams ldan ye shes tshe dpag med //
NK021(zha)001:15377: thugs kyi dpal be'u rin po che //
NK021(zha)001:15380: dmar gsal 'bar ba'i tshe mchog de //
NK021(zha)001:15381: skal ldan rigs kyi bu la 'phro //
NK021(zha)001:15382: spros pas dgu lung dam pa yis //
NK021(zha)001:15383: tsit+ta'i sbubs la bkrag tu bslan //
NK021(zha)001:15384: bum chu spyi bo'i gnas lngar gtig cing /
NK021(zha)001:15385: +aa badz+ra +aahyu she a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK021(zha)001:15386: badz+ra +aahyu she a b+hi s+w+aa badz+ra +aahyu she a
NK021(zha)001:15387: b+hi h+aum badz+ra +aahyu she a b+hi h+aam badz+ra +aahyu
NK021(zha)001:15388: she a b+hi slar yang bum pa spyi bor bzhag
NK021(zha)001:15389: pas / bum nang gi lha'i sku las yig char
NK021(zha)001:15390: ltar babs pa khyed rang gi spyi bo'i lam nas
NK021(zha)001:15391: tshe rten la thim pas sku rdo rje mi shigs
NK021(zha)001:15392: pa'i tshe dbang thob par bsam la //
NK021(zha)001:15393: bcom ldan mgon po tshe dpag med //
NK021(zha)001:15394: sgrib pa'i dri ma ma lus sel //
NK021(zha)001:15395: mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sku mnga' ba //
NK021(zha)001:15396: rdo rje'i sku yi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:15397: k+aa ya sid+d+hi +aahyu h+aum dzah zhes bum pa spyi bor bzhag cing bum chu blud /
NK021(zha)001:15398: tshe 'brang lhar gsal ba'i sku las +aahyiga char ltar
NK021(zha)001:15399: babs pa khyed rang gi mgrin pa'i lam nas tshe
NK021(zha)001:15400: rten la thim pas gsung rdo rje mi shigs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:15401: tshe dbang thob par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:15402: +aah mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i gsung //
NK021(zha)001:15403: gsung rab dam pa yi ge med //
NK021(zha)001:15404: brjod du med cing spros bral ba //
NK021(zha)001:15405: rdo rje'i gsung gi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:15406: +aahw+aa ka sid+d+hi +aahyu h+aum dzah zhes tshe 'brang mgrin par bzhag cing /
NK021(zha)001:15407: tshe ril dang tshe chang yang myang du gzhug go //
NK021(zha)001:15408: mar me lhar gsal ba las h+aum yig char ltar
NK021(zha)001:15409: babs pa khyed rang gi snying ga'i lam nas tshe
NK021(zha)001:15410: rten la thim pas thugs rdo rje mi shigs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:15411: tshe dbang thob par bsam la /
NK021(zha)001:15413: shin tu rnam par dag pa'i thugs //
NK021(zha)001:15414: chags med ye shes gnyis mkhyen pa //
NK021(zha)001:15415: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes che //
NK021(zha)001:15416: rdo rje thugs kyi dbang thob shog /
NK021(zha)001:15417: h+aum tsit+ta sid+d+hi +aahyu h+aum dzah zhes mar me snying gar gtug cing zhun mar byug /
NK021(zha)001:15418: de nas tshe sba ba ni /
NK021(zha)001:15419: de ltar dbang bskur ba'i sgo nas /
NK021(zha)001:15420: tshe gang la bstim pa'i gzhi skal ldan rigs kyi bu nyid dang /
NK021(zha)001:15421: de la bstim bya tshe dang bsod nams dang ye shes kyi rgyud gsum ste /
NK021(zha)001:15422: de thams cad kyang byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin
NK021(zha)001:15423: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa spros bral
NK021(zha)001:15424: 'chi med gnyug pa'i dbyings su rnam par dag par
NK021(zha)001:15425: sus kyang gzhig cing gzhom du med par gyur snyam
NK021(zha)001:15427: h+r+aih tshe yi ngo bo rgyud gsum po //
NK021(zha)001:15428: srog gi ngo bor gzhal yas khang //
NK021(zha)001:15431: 'chi ba med pa'i srog btsugs te //
NK021(zha)001:15432: 'gyur ba med pa'i g.yung drung yin //
NK021(zha)001:15433: chos nyid dbyings su tshe sbas pas //
NK021(zha)001:15434: dus gsum rgyal ba dgrar langs kyang //
NK021(zha)001:15435: de la bzung zhing brtag tu med //
NK021(zha)001:15437: de nas tshe rgyas gdab pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:15438: 'chi med gnyug ma'i rang bzhin las skad cig gis
NK021(zha)001:15439: de'i phyag rgya khyed rang snang mtha' tshe dpag med
NK021(zha)001:15440: du gsal ba'i snying gar zla gam dbang gi dkyil
NK021(zha)001:15441: 'khor / de'i sgor rta mgrin yab yum rgya gram dang bum pa 'dzin pas bsrung ba /
NK021(zha)001:15442: zla gam gyi nang du rin po che dpal be'u zur brgyad pa 'bar ba /
NK021(zha)001:15443: de'i steng du nyi zla ga'u kha sbyor gyi yas
NK021(zha)001:15444: mas nas rdo rje rgya gram gyis gtams pa'i steng
NK021(zha)001:15445: 'og gi rwa rtse 'od zer gyi thag pas bcings
NK021(zha)001:15446: pa / ga'u'i nang du gu h+ya gser gyi rdo
NK021(zha)001:15447: rje mtshon gang ba'i lte bar +aahh+aum gsum dmar po
NK021(zha)001:15448: 'od 'bar ba rnams kyi rgyas btab pa'i mos pa
NK021(zha)001:15449: pa / mdzod / byang chub sems kyi +aahyu de //
NK021(zha)001:15450: skye med dbyings su sbas nas kyang //
NK021(zha)001:15451: tha mar phyag rgya bdun gyis gdab //
NK021(zha)001:15452: dang po sku gsung thugs kyi rgya //
NK021(zha)001:15453: gnyis pa gnon pa'i rgya gram rgya //
NK021(zha)001:15454: gsum pa rta mchog dpal gyi rgya //
NK021(zha)001:15455: bzhi pa rin chen dpal be'u ste //
NK021(zha)001:15456: lnga pa gser gyi gu ya'o //
NK021(zha)001:15457: drug pa zla gam dmar po la //
NK021(zha)001:15459: rgya bdun rim pas btab pa las //
NK021(zha)001:15460: sus kyang 'da' bar mi nus so //
NK021(zha)001:15461: zhes brjid cing re re nas snying gar rdo rje rgya gram du bzhag /
NK021(zha)001:15463: lo brgya thub cing sogs kyis bkra shis brjod do //
NK021(zha)001:15464: de ltar skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyed rnams la 'chi med tshe yi dbang bskur bas /
NK021(zha)001:15465: tshe mi shigs pa'i rdo rje /
NK021(zha)001:15467: mi nub pa'i rgyal mtshan du gyur te /
NK021(zha)001:15468: 'chi ba med pa tshe'i dngos grub la dbang 'byor bar gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:15470: rjes kyi bya ba gdams ngag ngang sgom tshe khrid gdab pa ni /
NK021(zha)001:15471: zhog pa skya rengs dang po 'char ba'i tshe /
NK021(zha)001:15472: rang nyid stan bde ba la bsam gtan gyi 'dug
NK021(zha)001:15473: stangs kyis kha shar phyogs su bltas te 'dug la
NK021(zha)001:15475: rang nyid snang mtha' tshe dpag med du lam gyis bsgoms la /
NK021(zha)001:15476: rlung ro bsal bas nad gdon sogs tshe'i 'gal rkyen thams cad sang gis song bar bsam /
NK021(zha)001:15477: de nas shar phyogs kyi nam mkha'i mtha' gtugs pa'i
NK021(zha)001:15478: lha klu gnod sbyin la sogs pa'i tshe dang bsod
NK021(zha)001:15479: nams thams cad rlung dang lhan cig rngubs nas thub
NK021(zha)001:15481: dbu ma'i nang du sib kyis song nas tsit+ta mi shigs pa'i thig le la thim par bsam /
NK021(zha)001:15482: mi thub pa na sna nas dal bus sang gis btang ngo //
NK021(zha)001:15483: de bzhin du phyogs mtshams gzhan la'ang sbyar te /
NK021(zha)001:15487: zhag bdun 'bad pas tshe bsring bar 'gyur te /
NK021(zha)001:15491: lo gcig gam ni zla gcig gam //
NK021(zha)001:15492: de bzhin zhag gi rnam grangs kyang //
NK021(zha)001:15493: bco lnga'am yang na bdun bar du //
NK021(zha)001:15494: tho rengs thun tha dang po'i tshe //
NK021(zha)001:15496: de ltar mang po sgrubs pa dang //
NK021(zha)001:15497: dpal tshe gzi byin thams cad thob //
NK021(zha)001:15499: bshad rgyud rngam glog las kyang /
NK021(zha)001:15500: phyogs bcur de ltar goms byas na //
NK021(zha)001:15501: dpal chen gzi byin thams cad thob //
NK021(zha)001:15503: des mtha' brten du tshe'i dbang bskur ba man ngag dang bcas pa grub pas /
NK021(zha)001:15504: gnas skabs de dag tu thob pa'i dam tshig rnams
NK021(zha)001:15505: tshul bzhin du bsgrub par bya'o snyam pas 'di'i rjes
NK021(zha)001:15506: zlos mdzod / gtso bos ji ltar sogs kyis khas blangs /
NK021(zha)001:15508: deng nas brtsams te sogs kyis yon dbul /
NK021(zha)001:15510: rjes chog rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK021(zha)001:15511: rtsa bshad rgyud lung man ngag ltar //
NK021(zha)001:15512: tshe yi dbang chog zab don gnad //
NK021(zha)001:15514: rnying bstan snang byed dpal du 'bar //
NK021(zha)001:15515: mtha' rten tshe'i dbang chog gi le tshan no //
NK021(zha)001:15516: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang chog rdo rje'i them skas las /
NK021(zha)001:15517: rjes gtad rgya bya zhing tshe dbang bskur ba'i cho ga bshad pa'i skabs te drug pa'o //
NK021(zha)001:15520: rmad byung rdo rje theg pa'i them skas la //
NK021(zha)001:15521: skal bzang thabs shes gom stabs lhod po yis //
NK021(zha)001:15522: 'dzegs nas bde ba chen po'i khang bzang du //
NK021(zha)001:15523: 'jug pa'i thabs mchog 'dus pa mdo yi dbang /
NK021(zha)001:15525: 1 / rgyud lung man ngag dgongs pa zab don gnad //
NK021(zha)001:15526: grub pa'i dbang sgyur bde ba gsal mdzad kyis //
NK021(zha)001:15527: bkral ba'i chos tshul rjes 'gro legs bshad dpal //
NK021(zha)001:15528: dag cing gsal la ma 'khrugs go bder spel /
NK021(zha)001:15530: 2 / gsang chen rgyud lung mkha' ltar dpag yas pas //
NK021(zha)001:15531: blo rmongs 'dab chags bgrod pas ji ltar mtshon //
NK021(zha)001:15532: 'on kyang mkha' lding 'phur pa'i shul lam la //
NK021(zha)001:15533: nyam chung bung ba rnams kyang 'gro min nam /
NK021(zha)001:15535: 3 / de phyir bdag blo'i rtsal stobs mchog min kyang //
NK021(zha)001:15536: rje btsun bla ma'i bzhed dgongs gang+g+aa'i rgyun //
NK021(zha)001:15537: dad brtson snying gi 'bab stegs la gzhol bas //
NK021(zha)001:15538: gdung sel bdud rtsi'i zegs ma ci yang 'thor /
NK021(zha)001:15540: 4 / rgyud dang man ngag so so'i lugs phyed pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:15541: rtog dpyod dkyus sar phyin pa'i rta mchog bzhin //
NK021(zha)001:15542: snga btsan zhen pa'i srab skyogs la bcug kyang //
NK021(zha)001:15543: lung rig bde ba'i thang la thal bar gyur /
NK021(zha)001:15545: 5 / legs bshad gang mchis gter chen bla ma'i drin //
NK021(zha)001:15546: bka' drin rjes su dran pas gus phyag 'bul //
NK021(zha)001:15547: nyes gyur bdag blo rmongs pa'i skyon lags pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:15548: bla ma lhar bcas tshogs la bzod par gsol /
NK021(zha)001:15550: 6 / 'dis thob dge bas mtha' yas 'gro ba rnams //
NK021(zha)001:15551: skye zhing skye ba kun tu 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK021(zha)001:15552: smin grol lam bzang 'di dang mi 'bral zhing //
NK021(zha)001:15553: dpal ldan sku bzhi'i go 'phang myur thob shog 7 /
NK021(zha)001:15554: 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dbang gi chu bo bzhi
NK021(zha)001:15555: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gcig tu dril nas
NK021(zha)001:15556: bskur ba'i dbang chog rdo rje'i them skas zhes bya
NK021(zha)001:15557: ba 'di ni / sku na gzhon nur gyur kyang
NK021(zha)001:15558: blo gros kyi lus stobs rgyas pas shes bya rig
NK021(zha)001:15559: pa'i gnas kun la thogs pa med pa'i mkhyen rab
NK021(zha)001:15560: phul du byung zhing zab mo'i lam la bsnyen sgrub
NK021(zha)001:15561: mthar phyin pa'i rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po rgyal
NK021(zha)001:15562: ba'i sras mchog shes rab rnam rgyal rdo rje'am mtshan
NK021(zha)001:15563: gzhan pad+ma 'gyur med rgya mtsho'i sde'i bka' stsal spyi
NK021(zha)001:15564: bos nod de rtsom 'dun yid la bcags pa nyid
NK021(zha)001:15565: ba 'di ni / / 'phral du sgrub pa'i rkyen
NK021(zha)001:15566: sad byed sngon goms kyi yon tan du mas rnam
NK021(zha)001:15567: par brgyan pa'i skyes mchog pad gling lnga pa gsung
NK021(zha)001:15568: sprul ngag dbang kun bzang rdo rje dang /
NK021(zha)001:15569: 'od mchog sprul pa'i sku lce ston ngag dbang kun bzang rang grol /
NK021(zha)001:15570: thang 'brog sprul pa'i sku kun bzang legs par grub
NK021(zha)001:15571: pa la sogs te bstan pa gsal bar mdzad pa'i
NK021(zha)001:15572: skyes chen du ma'i gsung nan dang /
NK021(zha)001:15573: gzhan yang mdo khams go 'jo bla ma rnam grol bzang po dang /
NK021(zha)001:15574: bsal bla ma ye shes dang rdo rje mgon sogs
NK021(zha)001:15575: dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang bstan pa la mchog tu
NK021(zha)001:15576: gus pa mang pos kyang nye bar bskul zhing /
NK021(zha)001:15577: khyad par rgyal kun 'dus pa'i spyi gzugs rigs dang
NK021(zha)001:15578: dkyil 'khor kun gyi khyab bdag khams gsum 'gro ba'i
NK021(zha)001:15579: bla ma rje btsun thams cad mkhyen pa gter chen
NK021(zha)001:15580: chos kyi rgyal po 'jigs bral phyogs thams cad las
NK021(zha)001:15581: rnam par rgyal ba'i sde'i bka' lung gis dbugs 'byin
NK021(zha)001:15582: pa'i gnang ba legs par thob pa la brten nas
NK021(zha)001:15583: / gang gi bka' drin kho nas 'tsho ba'i gnyos
NK021(zha)001:15584: kyi dge slong rmongs pa d+har+m+aa sh+r+ais rang lo lnga
NK021(zha)001:15585: bcu nga gcig pa nyi sgrol byed ces shing pho
NK021(zha)001:15586: spre'u'i lo ston zla 'bring po'i tshes bcu drug gi
NK021(zha)001:15587: snga dro rab tu brtan pa sdig pa'i dus sbyor
NK021(zha)001:15588: gyi dbyu gu bzhi pa chu khams pa wa sangs
NK021(zha)001:15589: kyis spyod pa'i dus res gza' bkra shis tha skar
NK021(zha)001:15590: dang rtse ba'i 'grub sbyor bzang po la //
NK021(zha)001:15591: bshad sgrub kyi chu bo ma lus pa 'du ba'i rgya mtsho /
NK021(zha)001:15592: lung rigs man ngag rin po che'i 'byung gnas 'og
NK021(zha)001:15593: min o rgyan smin grol gling gi chos grwar sug
NK021(zha)001:15595: 'dis kyang bstan pa dang sems can la phan pa rgya chen po 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur cig //
NK021(zha)001:15598: tshogs gnyis mthar phyin sku bzhi'i rgyal thabs mchog /
NK021(zha)001:15599: rdo rje can gyi sa chen yongs bzung nas //
NK021(zha)001:15600: thugs rje'i rnam rol rigs can blor 'tshams pa'i //
NK021(zha)001:15601: bstan pa rgya mtshos sa gsum shis par mdzad /
NK021(zha)001:15603: 1 / khyad par gsang chen theg pa mchog gi lam //
NK021(zha)001:15604: brgyud gsum bla ma'i zhal lung bdud rtsi'i chab //
NK021(zha)001:15605: smin grol ro brgya ldan pa mdo yi dbang //
NK021(zha)001:15606: skal bzang sku bzhir smin byed 'di rmad byung /
NK021(zha)001:15608: 2 / gang yang theg pa'i go rim rnam dbye dang //
NK021(zha)001:15609: cho ga'i bya ba ji bzhin ma 'dres par //
NK021(zha)001:15610: rang gzhung nges pa'i khungs kyis yid ches can //
NK021(zha)001:15611: klags pa tsam gyis dgos don 'grub byed gang /
NK021(zha)001:15613: 3 / skal bzang mchog 'dod rnams la yid bzhin gyi //
NK021(zha)001:15614: nor bu nyid phyir blo ngan rnyog pa'i dri //
NK021(zha)001:15615: sbyangs nas bshad sgrub rgyal mtshan rtser mchod pas //
NK021(zha)001:15616: dngos grub 'dod dgur 'jo ba'i mchog sbyin mkhan /
NK021(zha)001:15618: 4 / mkhas btsun bzang po'i dpal gyis mngon mtho ba //
NK021(zha)001:15619: ngag gi dbang phyug chos dpal rgya mtsho zhes //
NK021(zha)001:15620: skad gnyis smra ba'i zla ba bstan 'dzin gyi //
NK021(zha)001:15621: rgyu skar phreng ba'i dbus na gsal de'o /
NK021(zha)001:15623: 5 / legs bshad rin chen don gnyer skye bo la //
NK021(zha)001:15624: 'bad med chos gter rgyu rkyen phun tshogs sgo //
NK021(zha)001:15625: 'byed po kun dga' tshul khrims rgya mtsho yi //
NK021(zha)001:15626: ma smad 'byor ba'i bang mdzod nyid las spel /
NK021(zha)001:15628: 6 / yi ge'i byed po o rgyan dpal 'byor gyis //
NK021(zha)001:15629: bris pa ji bzhin o rgyan tshogs gnyis dang //
NK021(zha)001:15630: phun tshogs bstan 'dzin rdo rje tshe brtan gyi //
NK021(zha)001:15631: rnam dpyod sor mo'i 'phrul chen par du grub /
NK021(zha)001:15633: 7 / zhus dag byed po sdom brtson 'bum phrag gzhung //
NK021(zha)001:15634: smra mkhas o rgyan skal bzang zhes bya ste //
NK021(zha)001:15635: do dam las 'dzin dge slong rab 'phel gyis //
NK021(zha)001:15636: nye bar sgrubs sogs legs byas dpyid du grub /
NK021(zha)001:15638: 8 / tshul 'di o rgyan mkhan po'i smin grol gyi //
NK021(zha)001:15639: ring lugs bshad sgrub mngon par mtho ba'i gling //
NK021(zha)001:15640: nges don dga' ba'i tshal gyi chos grwa cher //
NK021(zha)001:15641: sa skyong zhes bya'i lo la bsgrubs pa'o /
NK021(zha)001:15643: 9 / 'dis thob dge bas rgyal bstan 'phel zhing rgyas //
NK021(zha)001:15644: 'gro kun srid zhi'i dpal gyis nyer 'tsho zhing //
NK021(zha)001:15645: rlabs chen rgyal ba'i mdzad pa rmad byung gis //
NK021(zha)001:15646: phan bde'i snang ba phyogs bcur rgyas byed shog 10 /
NK021(zha)001:15647: ces 'dus pa mdo'i sgrub dkyil dbang chog cha lag
NK021(zha)001:15648: dang bcas pa'i par byang du 'gyur med rdo rjes
NK021(zha)001:15650: mdo sngags chos tshul tshang la ma nor ba //
NK021(zha)001:15651: mkhas shing grub brnyes rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i srol //
NK021(zha)001:15652: thub bstan snying po gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba'i //
NK021(zha)001:15653: bstan pa 'phel rgyas 'dzam gling khyab gyur cig /
NK021(zha)001:15654: mkhan slob chos gsum ring lugs che //
NK021(zha)001:15656: 'gro rgyud mchog gsum snang ba dang //
NK021(zha)001:15657: mi 'bral dus gsum dge legs shog /
